240017865,SOLD,"JC, Heights",164 HUTTON ST,Condominium,594,6078,"$283,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1L,"JC, Heights",07307,3601,48,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,5,,"$283,000","$309,000",$476.43,$476.43,9/7/2024,7/8/2025,7/31/2025,304,301,,10/3/2025,,,,"$5,212",2023,$375,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & Kennedy Blvd,"Investors opportunity only for a private and perfectly property located oasis in the Heights.   Welcome to your private and perfectly located oasis in the Heights.  This 2 bedroom, 1bath condo has everything you need! Private outdoor space, hardwood floors and a Ductless mini-split AC system that was recently inspected and professionally maintained. The kitchen has Stainless steel appliances, brand new dishwasher, granite counters and a stylish tile backsplash.  A private, in unit and washer/dryer installed early this year, contemporary ceiling light fixtures in every room  as well as your own private entrance round out the space. New replacement fence panels were installed on the sides of the outdoor space.    This also has a floor plan with bedrooms on opposite sides of the unit, which was just freshly painted. This convenient location has easy access to Central Ave shopping district, Pershing Field, and NYC transit options."
230020010,SOLD,"JC, Heights",415-417 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,659,1702,"$285,000",CONDO-COOP,,1st,1F,"JC, Heights",07307,02805,00032,Heights,,,,,1,0,1,4,,"$285,000","$299,900",$432.47,$432.47,12/1/2023,12/6/2023,1/16/2024,5,5,,1/17/2024,,,,"$4,400",2022,$257,,Conventional,,,,,,Thorne St and South St on Central Ave,"Spacious 1B/1B in Jersey City Heights. With an open kitchen and a large living room - including space for a home office or dining room - this home features hardwood floors throughout, a large bedroom and ample closet space. Located on the 1st floor with common laundry in the building. This home is steps to shopping and dining along Central Avenue, NYC transportation, beautiful parks and an easy walk to the elevator down to Hoboken. Rental Parking Available On Site For Additional Fee."
220004781,SOLD,"JC, Heights",120 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,627,1653,"$285,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2A,"JC, Heights",07307,2904,29,Heights,,,,,1,0,1,3,,"$285,000","$295,000",$454.55,$454.55,3/17/2022,3/21/2022,4/25/2022,4,2,,4/25/2022,,,,"$5,022",2021,$222,2021,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Griffith St & Bowers St,"Condo unit in desirable building, few blocks east and west to bus routes to NYC Port Authority or JSQ Path Train Station.  JC Heights offers many warm and cozy restaurants, easy access to local stores, and bus routes."
250023604,SOLD,"JC, Heights",77 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,749,1623,"$285,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,2,0,1,4,,"$285,000","$280,000",$380.51,$380.51,11/18/2025,1/5/2026,2/28/2026,48,48,,3/2/2026,,,,"$5,940",2024,$446,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & Kennedy,"Welcome to your charming retreat on picturesque, tree-lined Sherman Place. This inviting condo offers a thoughtfully designed layout with great storage throughout, including a walk-in pantry and an oversized living room perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Both bedrooms are generously sized, and the beautiful new flooring adds a fresh, elevated touch to the entire home. Enjoy truly low-maintenance living with an HOA that covers general upkeep, trash removal, water, heat, and gas—giving you peace of mind and more time to enjoy your surroundings. Step outside and immerse yourself in the vibrant energy of Pershing Field Park or explore the shops, cafés, and restaurants along Central Ave, all just moments from your door. With effortless access to NYC transportation, this home offers the perfect blend of neighborhood charm, convenience, and city connectivity. Don’t miss your chance to own this warm and welcoming haven in one of the area’s most desirable locations."
230017942,SOLD,"JC, Heights",44 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,568,1597,"$285,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1c,"JC, Heights",07307,04502,00002,Heights,Riverview Terrace,,,,1,0,1,3,,"$285,000","$280,000",$501.76,$501.76,10/24/2023,11/3/2023,12/18/2023,10,10,,1/7/2024,,,,"$4,094",,$426,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin and Hutton Streets,"City chic one bedroom condo for sale at Riverview Terrace Condominiums. Riverview Terrace is located in the heart of Jersey City Heights at 44 Sherman Ave. Upon entering this condo you are greeted with soaring ceilings as you enter your warm and inviting living room. A fully updated kitchen with tall cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, quartz counter tops with breakfast bar and stunning subway tile backsplash. Generously sized bedroom with customized closet space. Beautifully renovated tiled bathroom. Hardwood floors, great closet space and natural light complete this home. Riverview Terrace is an elevator building and offers a washer/dryer room on each level. Parking is available for an extra monthly fee*. Convenient to NYC transportation, light rail elevator, restaurants, coffee shops & more! *currently a wait list for parking"
210024975,SOLD,"JC, Heights",77 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,678,6199,"$285,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,5A,"JC, Heights",07307,03603, 00017,,,,,,1,0,1,3,,"$285,000","$305,000",$420.35,$420.35,11/3/2021,1/12/2022,3/26/2022,70,70,,3/27/2022,,,,"$3,951",2021,$304,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit and Sanford,"Welcome home! Spacious one bedroom with updated private terrace at Sherman Pl. Corner condo unit, boasting an open floor plan and quietly tucked away bedroom. A comfortably sized living area and kitchen, complemented by a generously sized private terrace making it a great home for indoor and outdoor grilling and entertaining. Take advantage of this excellent investment opportunity located in the highly sought-out area of Jersey City,  “The Heights”. With it's magnificent location, this 1br home provides smooth accessibility to major NJ/NY transportation options like bus transit & the light rail and near cities like Hoboken, Union City and Bayonne. BONUS - this home includes a deeded parking spot! Location, location, Sherman Pl! Walking distance to Pershing Field Park, JFK Blvd, Central Avenue, schools, restaurants, retail stores and houses of worship! Less than 25 minutes from New York, Lower Manhattan, Downtown Jersey City, Hoboken, Newark Liberty Airport and all major hubs! Multiple authentic restaurants, cafes and markets. This property is a financial gem with included utilities (heat, hot water, water and gas), low monthly HOA fees and competitive taxes!  This property is a must see! Start building your equity now!"
