230000326,SOLD,"JC, Heights",76 HUTTON ST,Condominium,631,1597,"$299,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,5,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,5,,"$299,000","$299,000",$473.85,$473.85,1/6/2023,1/25/2023,3/3/2023,19,19,,3/3/2023,,,,,,$310,,Conventional,,,,,,Cambridge & Hancock,"Located less than one block from Central Avenue in Jersey City Heights, and walking distance to Riverview Fisk Park with jaw-dropping NYC skyline views and 9th street Lightrail access, this newly renovated two bedroom home offers ultimate location and lifestyle.  Beautiful brick exterior gives way to the fully updated two bedroom, one bath floorplan with classic style and all the upgrades. Timeless design shines through the split layout home with elements like classic wood casing around windows and neutral color palette. Wide plank hardwood floors, plus neutral slab tile in kitchen allow for both coziness, convenience and cottage feel.   Kitchen features contrasting black quartz counters with white cabinets including accent glass displays, white tile backsplash and stainless appliances. Bathroom hosts neutral tile with mosaic accents, spacious vanity with black porcelain counter plus medicine cabinet mirror for additional storage.  It’s no wonder Jersey City Heights is in such high demand with its vibrant community, eclectic restaurants and shops, excellent schools, spacious parks and easy NYC access."
230010028,SOLD,"JC, Heights",231 GRIFFITH ST,Condominium,630,1597,"$299,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,E,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,5,,"$299,000","$299,000",$474.60,$474.60,6/16/2023,7/7/2023,8/16/2023,21,21,,8/16/2023,,,,,,$245,,Conventional,,,,,,Milton Ave & Summit Ave,"Freshly refinished two bedroom home offers unbeaten location and excellent opportunity. Step in from the tree-lined street, through the secure entrance, and into the flowing layout finished with wide plank floors and classic finishes.   Fully updated eat-in kitchen showcases traditional white cabinets, contrasting black quartz counters, white tile backsplash and stainless appliances, plus full-size closet for pantry. Bedrooms offer extras like beautiful windows, ceiling fan and massive walk-in closet, while bathroom is finished with spacious vanity, tile finished to ceiling, and bathtub plus shower.   Located directly across from Leonard Gordon Park in the heart of Jersey City Heights, this home offers walkability to excellent parks and major thoroughfares of Central and Summit Ave. The Heights is known for its vibrant artist’s culture, close-knit community and easy access to NYC, Hoboken and surrounding neighborhoods."
