220012803,SOLD,"JC, Heights",80 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,595,1713,"$300,000",CONDO-COOP,,2nd,2L,"JC, Heights",07307,04505,00011,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,5,,"$300,000","$305,000",$504.20,$504.20,7/14/2022,9/20/2022,11/7/2022,68,68,,11/8/2022,,,,"$3,708",2021,$359,,FHA,,,,,,Ferry & Franklin St,"Welcome home to your 2 bedroom condo in a beautifully renovated building just blocks from Pershing Field Park & Riverview Fisk Park in Jersey City Heights. An abundance of natural light pours in from your oversized windows and high ceilings, dark stained hardwood flooring, and high end finishes complete this well laid out unit with bedrooms on each end of the home. Enjoy your open modern kitchen with its gleaming white quartz counters & white cabinetry, mosaic tile backsplash and Frigidaire stainless appliances. Bathroom includes a large glass shower with polished chrome fixtures, beautifully tiled walls, plus medicine cabinet vanity for additional storage needs. The building offers storage units for each unit in the basement along with bike storage and common washer and dryer.The Heights offers walkable community that is lively and has an array of boutiques, galleries, bars and restaurants, and easy access to NYC. (all other units are in great condition, however, if interested, you have the option for the 3R upgrade package available for all other units.  Please ask your agent to look under the associated documents in the mls for details or you can buy the unit with the finish that is offered currently.)"
