250003341,SOLD,"JC, Heights",13 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,665,6078,"$320,000",CONDO-COOP,,"1,2",Rear,"JC, Heights",07307,4402,24,Heights,,,,,1,0,1,3,,"$320,000","$284,900",$481.20,$481.20,2/20/2025,2/28/2025,4/18/2025,8,8,,4/22/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave,"Welcome to 13 Manhattan Ave #4, a brand-new construction unit in the heart of Jersey City Heights, offering modern elegance and high-end finishes. This unique home is a separate carriage house—a one-bedroom, one-bath duplex with its own entrance, providing plenty of privacy. Perfect for mother-daughter living or generating additional monthly income, this thoughtfully designed space offers both flexibility and value. The main living area features an open-concept layout that seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living space. The kitchen is equipped with custom shaker cabinetry and stainless steel appliances, including a gas range. Natural light floods the home, highlighting the hardwood floors throughout. Upstairs, you’ll find a spacious bedroom with a walk-in closet and a large en-suite bath. An in-unit washer and dryer adds everyday convenience, while mini-split wall units ensure year-round comfort. A 10-year builder’s warranty offers peace of mind, making this an excellent opportunity for modern urban living. Located within walking distance to Pershing Field Park, this home is perfectly situated between Central and Palisade Avenue, offering easy access to shops, restaurants, and everyday conveniences. Commuters will appreciate the proximity to NJ Transit bus lines into Manhattan and the 2nd Street Light Rail station. Reach out to schedule your private tour today!"
