240001776,SOLD,"JC, Heights",787 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,818,6078,"$340,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,7,"JC, Heights",07307,4801,15,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,5,,"$340,000","$340,000",$415.65,$415.65,1/30/2024,2/20/2024,3/8/2024,21,21,,3/8/2024,,,,"$5,970",2023,$540,,Cash,No,No,No,,,Summit Ave & Troy St,"The best layout and largest 2 bedroom Renovated Condo Unit has just become available at 787 Summit Ave! It is rare when an opportunity like this one, comes up! 787 Summit Ave is a solid, well kept, 17 unit Pre-war brick building. Located in the center of the Heights close enough to the Path Station and distanced enough from the hustle and bustle of Journal Square - granting you that real neighborhood feel. When you walk in to this gem, you will find richly dark hardwood floors and generous sized bedrooms situated on opposite ends of the apartment offering the privacy everyone desires in a living space! Enjoy Pershing Field Park and the Historic Reservoir which is right across the street. So close to shopping, grocery stores, popular restuarants, schools, places of worship and quick access to NYC via bus right on Central Ave or a brisk walk to the path station! Book your appointment to tour today! Sorry this is a No Pet building."
