220001179,SOLD,"JC, Heights",140 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,545,1691,"$344,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1R,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,1,0,1,4,,"$344,000","$349,000",$631.19,$631.19,1/20/2022,2/8/2022,4/7/2022,19,19,,4/9/2022,,,,,,$200,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith St & Hutton St,"The ultimate urban lifestyle combination of luxury and location is found with this newly renovated, one bedroom unit in the heart of JC Heights. The space opens up with oversized windows, exposed brick, and wide plank white oak floors throughout. Open concept kitchens are finished with white custom shaker cabinets with exposed corner shelves, white quartz countertops, contrasting black and white marble-inspired backsplash, matte-black fixtures and stainless steel appliances. Moving through the well-planned flow of the units, modern bathrooms boast a combination of black and grey large slab tile, stylish vanities and brass fittings. The bedroom brings beautiful morning light to start your day off right! Outdoor space is at your fingertips with both Riverview Fisk Park and Pershing Field a short walk away. Enjoy the best of Jersey City Heights and Hoboken, with the eclectic urban scene surrounding, incredible walkability and easy access to NYC."
