220021528,SOLD,"JC, Heights",101 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,722,1597,"$345,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1L,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,1,1,5,,"$345,000","$350,000",$477.84,$477.84,12/15/2022,12/23/2022,4/24/2023,8,8,,4/24/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,JFK and Summit Ave,"Perfectly positioned in the heart of Jersey City Heights, this completely updated home offers classic design and thoughtful layout to tick all of the urban luxury boxes. Light radiates onto the neutral palette and beautifully stained original hardwood floors of this 2 bedroom and 1.5 bath home, while the split bedroom layout give optimal privacy and flexibility. Unit 1L also hosts private balcony that flows into the backyard.   Walk into the open floorplan living and kitchen area complete with charcoal-gray cabinets, white quartz counters, classic subway tile backsplash, matching stainless sink and appliances plus nickel fixtures. The front bedroom boasts oversized bay windows and huge side-by-side closets, plus full bath adjacent. Through to the back, owners enjoy convenient in-unit washer and dryer, plus additional half bath and bedroom. Building exterior received recent upgrades as well with updating siding and fresh trim.   Less than 1 block from Leonard Gordon Conservancy Park, this home is also quick walking distance to urban thoroughfares Summit and Central Ave plus beautiful Pershing Field Park and next door Reservoir. Jersey City Heights offers vibrant community, great restaurants and essential shops, excellent schools, and easy NYC access."
