240009579,SOLD,"JC, Heights",179 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,761,6078,"$362,500",CONDO-COOP,,4,1D,"JC, Heights",07307,4301,11,,,,,,2,0,1,4,,"$362,500","$378,000",$476.35,$476.35,5/20/2024,6/21/2024,8/23/2024,32,32,,8/23/2024,,,,"$4,816",,$282,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy and Montrose,"Welcome to your charming new home in the heart of Jersey City Heights! This delightful 2 bed, 1 bath condo offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Inside,  find hardwood floors that add warmth and character to the space. The cozy eat-in kitchen is perfect for casual dining and comes equipped with modern appliances, making meal preparation a breeze. Ceiling fans in the living area and bedrooms ensure a cool and comfortable atmosphere throughout the year. For your convenience, there is a dedicated washer/dryer room in the basement, so you'll never have to worry about laundry again. Additionally, the low HOA fees make this home an affordable choice. Located in a fantastic neighborhood, this condo is just minutes away from a variety of local eateries and cafes. Enjoy delicious meals at popular spots like The Cliff, Fox & Crow, and Modcup Coffee. Commuting to NYC is a breeze with easy access to public transportation, including buses and the nearby PATH station, ensuring you're just minutes away from the hustle and bustle of Manhattan. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this adorable condo in one of Jersey City's most desirable areas. Schedule a viewing today and make this lovely home yours!"
