260005960,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",50 RESERVOIR AVE,Condominium,986,1702,"$374,900",CONDO-COOP,,G Fl,B1,"JC, Heights",07307,05007,00019,,,,,,2,0,1,5,,,"$374,900",$380.22,,4/3/2026,,,6,,,4/3/2026,,,,"$7,269",2025,$954,2026,,,,,,,Corner of Reservoir & Webster,"Bright, spacious 2 bed / 1 bath in one of Jersey City Heights’ most elegant pre-war condominium buildings. This stylishly renovated apartment features LED lighting, porcelain tile, luxury plank flooring, gorgeous steel columns, and your own private entrance off Webster Avenue. The kitchen includes a sizable pantry, granite countertops, subway tile backsplash & under cabinet lighting. Equipped with a GE dishwasher, refrigerator, stainless-steel gas range and washer/dryer hook-up. Windows in every room fill this unit with natural light. The ceilings are high, and the bedrooms are large - big enough for king sized beds. One of the best locations and a short stroll from Reservoir #3’s walking trails, the Pershing Field Athletic Center, Riverview Farmers Market, and the hip shops and restaurants along Central & Palisade Avenues. Abundant transit & CitiBike options. The professionally managed Reservoir Condominium building is a pre-war gem, featuring a spacious lobby, elevator, and app-enabled video entry system & laundry machines. Condo dues include heat and hot water. Pets welcome. Come see for yourself! This meticulously renovated condominium residence is an opportunity not to be missed.  Book a viewing today! "
