230005501,SOLD,"JC, Heights",104 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,745,1603,"$375,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,B4,"JC, Heights",07306,06901,00014,,,,,,1,0,1,6,,"$375,000","$349,000",$503.36,$503.36,4/5/2023,4/18/2023,8/11/2023,13,13,,8/11/2023,,,,"$7,104",2022,$388,,Conventional,,,,,,SE corner of Fleet St. and Palisade Ave,"Here it is - the perfectly laid out over-sized one bedroom that you've been waiting for ... right on Palisade Ave!  104 Palisade B4 is just one flight up with high ceilings and large windows inviting tons of sunlight in all day long. The condo itself is very quiet thanks to the building's pre-war construction.  And B4 is one of very few units in the building with an in-unit washer/dryer grandfathered in.  There hasn't been one like this on the market in years.  The kitchen ticks all of the boxes too.... with white stone countertops, a beautiful Fisher-Paykel refrigerator and built-in pantry on one wall, and additional storage, seating, and counter space built in on another.  The extra counter space is simply perfect for a dedicated coffee or juice bar.  The bedroom currently has a king sized bed and still has plenty of room for office and work-out space.  And if you have a sofa that seats 10, no problem :).  The living room can accommodate it.  Building amenities include a gym, community room, and sunny shared outdoor space. Check it out.  This one has been worth the wait."
