220016604,SOLD,"JC, Heights",120 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,749,1603,"$375,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3H,"JC, Heights",07307,00029,02904,Heights,Sherman Heights,,,,1,0,1,4,,"$375,000","$375,000",$500.67,$500.67,9/15/2022,9/21/2022,11/7/2022,6,6,,11/7/2022,,,,"$7,389",2022,$298,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith & Bowers,"Soaring ceilings welcome you into this unique, loft-style 1 bed, 1 bath in the heart of the Riverview Arts District. The entry hall leads to an open concept living/dining space with gorgeous mocha hardwood floors and a lovely kitchen ready for all your culinary adventures and equipped with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and two-tone cabinetry. Down the hallway, where you can peek at the Freedom Tower from the window, you’ll find a full bath with updated fixtures, ceramic tile, and mocha cabinetry. The spacious bedroom, tucked away for privacy, boasts two large closets and nearly a full wall of windows. The building features a full-sized gym, elevator, common storage area, laundry on each floor, parking garage with bike storage, new Butterfly entry system, and more! Close to Riverview Park, bus routes on Palisade Ave, the Congress Street Light Rail, Washington Park, Corto Restaurant, Riverview Wines, Fox & Crow, Lucky Honeybee, ModCup, Bread & Salt, and so much more!"
