240007163,SOLD,"JC, Heights",12 POPLAR ST,Condominium,800,298,"$376,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,#6,"JC, Heights",07307,802,29,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,5,,"$376,000","$359,000",$470.00,$470.00,4/17/2024,5/3/2024,10/16/2024,16,16,,10/21/2024,,,,"$6,889",2023,$261,2023,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Central Avenue and Summit Avenue,"Welcome home to this loft-like 2-bedroom, 1 bath condo. Your 800+ sq. ft. feels much more spacious with the soaring 12-14 ft ceilings, over-sized windows and four skylights that flood your living space with natural light. There are hardwood floors throughout. Reasonable HOA fee and taxes. Located in the desirable Jersey City Heights – home to artists, restaurants, cafes, nightlife and a vibrant community. Central Ave furnishes most of your shopping needs. Craving outdoor space? This condo is conveniently situated just a few doors to Washington Park with picnic area, basketball courts, playground & dog run and convenient to Riverview Park with spectacular NYC view, seasonal weekly Farmers Market and more! Best location for commuting to NYC and surrounding areas. Multiple choices include: the light rail elevator to Hoboken PATH, NYC 125 bus service & jitneys on Kennedy Blvd, 85 bus at corner or 123 or 119 buses on Palisade Ave. Call today!"
