260003435,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",787 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,818,5926,"$379,900",CONDO-COOP,,3rd,11,"JC, Heights",07307,4801,15,Heights,Summit Park,,,,2,0,1,4,,,"$379,900",$464.43,,2/27/2026,,,41,,,2/28/2026,,"$218,900",2024,"$5,111",2025,$571,,,No,No,No,,,Summit and Troy St,"Welcome to 787 Summit Ave, Unit 11 – Your Gateway to Jersey City Living  Step into this well-maintained 2-bedroom, 1-bath condo offering 818 sq ft of comfortable living space, perfectly positioned for both convenience and value.  This home is ideal for first-time buyers or savvy investors looking to break into the Jersey City market without breaking the bank. The layout is efficient, with bright living spaces and bedrooms that offer flexibility for work-from-home, guests, or rental potential. All buyers are welcome!  Location is the real star here. You’re just minutes from PATH trains, putting you in Manhattan in under 30 minutes, with easy access to the Port Authority—   Whether you're looking to stop renting, start investing, or just plant roots in a growing area—this is one of those opportunities that checks the right boxes. Just steps from Central Avenue’s vibrant shops, cafés, and dining, and moments from Pershing Field Park, Reservoir #3, and Leonard Gordon Park, this location places the best of the Heights right at your doorstep. Commuters will appreciate nearby NY and JSQ bus stops, Also, walkable distance to Journal Square and Path Trains."
