230019197,SOLD,"JC, Heights",351 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,748,1603,"$425,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3F,"JC, Heights",07307,4504,24,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,5,,"$425,000","$425,000",$568.18,$568.18,11/14/2023,12/1/2023,1/19/2024,17,17,,1/20/2024,,,,"$6,543",2023,$281,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Franklin & Ferry St,"Immerse yourself in urban living at this immaculate two-bedroom, one-bathroom modern condo on coveted Palisade Avenue in the Heights of Jersey City. Sunlight bathes the gleaming hardwood floors that grace this contemporary space, offering an exceptional open layout for comfortable living and dining. Generously sized bedrooms provide ample closet space, while loft-like ceilings, LED recessed lighting, Central HVAC, and custom window treatments, including brand-new triple pane windows by Pella, add modern comforts. Step out onto designated and common roof decks to bask in breathtaking views of the New York City skyline, including the iconic Empire State Building and Freedom Tower. 351 Palisade Ave ensures convenience with on-premises laundry and additional storage options, while parking is available nearby for an additional cost. This vibrant neighborhood places the area's finest shopping, dining, galleries, parks, and more just minutes away. With buses at your doorstep, reaching NYC, Hoboken, Downtown Jersey City, LightRail, PATH Stations, and Journal Square is effortless. Make this modern gem your next urban sanctuary—schedule a tour today to explore the possibilities."
210009812,SOLD,"JC, Heights",1209 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,1198,1526,"$425,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,416,"JC, Heights",07307,00501,00002,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$425,000","$425,000",$354.76,$354.76,4/25/2021,5/17/2021,7/19/2021,22,21,,7/20/2021,,,,"$6,292",2020,$344,,Conventional,,,,,,5th and Hague,"Built in 2010 - Contemporary condo that feels like a house! Bright & airy top floor duplex with open concept floorplan that feels much larger than its 1198sf. Modern kitchen with granite counters & stainless steel appliances; comes with 2 full baths, central A/C, on-demand hot water heater, hardwood floors, lots of windows AND garage parking. The Heights  - a vibrant community where new restaurants, coffee shops & juice bars are popping up everywhere - is a booming area less than 30 minutes to New York City.  NYC bus stop directly in front of the building that comes every few minutes. Get Manhattan chic at a fraction of the price while the  Heights is still affordable!  OPEN HOUSE 5/1 AND 5/2 1-3p"
240013561,SOLD,"JC, Heights",145 BOWERS ST,Condominium,870,1623,"$425,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02802,00021,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,7,,"$425,000","$425,000",$488.51,$488.51,7/12/2024,9/18/2024,11/6/2024,68,68,,11/6/2024,,,,"$6,456",2022,$195,2023,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave and Summit Ave,"Charming parlor level 2 Bedroom condo with private yard and basement storage. This delightful condo offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Featuring split system air conditioning, gleaming hardwood floors throughout, airy high ceilings, and two decorative fireplaces that adds a touch of elegance, this is a place you'll love to call home. Unwind in your private yard, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a cup of coffee al fresco. In-unit washer and dryer provides ultimate convenience. The basement offers a large private secured storage space for all your belongings. Ideally situated near shopping, so you'll have everything you need just a short stroll away. Enjoy the tranquility of nearby parks, easy access to NYC via public transportation. Don't miss this opportunity to live in a truly special place!  Contact us today to schedule a showing!"
240023723,SOLD,"JC, Heights",120 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,770,6494,"$425,900",CONDO-COOP,,3,3D,"JC, Heights",07307,2904,29,,,,,,1,0,1,5,,"$425,900","$415,000",$553.12,$553.12,12/12/2024,12/21/2024,2/7/2025,9,9,,2/7/2025,,,,"$7,341",2023,$308,,Conventional,,,,,,Sherman & Webster Ave,"Stunner in Historic Jersey City Heights Building  Discover the perfect blend of historic charm and modern living in this 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condominium nestled in a beautifully preserved building in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Located just 2 blocks from Riverview-Fisk Park, this home offers breathtaking views of the New York City skyline and a vibrant weekly farmers market right around the corner.  Highlights: * 11 Foot ceilings * Elevator building * Spacious and bright with classic architectural details like arched windows * Modern kitchen with sleek finishes, new appliances, and ample storage * Massive bedroom with generous closet space for all your essentials * Bathroom features jacuzzi tub * Additional nook perfect for home office  Prime Location: * Situated in the buzzing Jersey City Heights neighborhood, known for its trendy cafes, local boutiques, and a strong sense of community. * Enjoy the convenience of being just minutes from the Hoboken PATH station, offering easy access to Manhattan. * Bus direct to Port Authority NYC bus stop easy access on both Palisade & Central Avenues, making NYC commutes seamless.  * Close proximity to Riverview Park, a local favorite for its green spaces, events, and stunning city views.  This apartment is ideal for those seeking a lifestyle that combines the charm of a historic building with the energy and convenience of urban living. Don’t miss out—schedule your showing today and step into your new Jersey City Heights home! "
250005931,SOLD,"JC, Heights",391 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,644,1713,"$426,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,4,"JC, Heights",07307,2804,30,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,6,,"$426,000","$425,000",$661.49,$661.49,3/27/2025,4/28/2025,5/23/2025,32,32,,5/27/2025,,$0,0,"$5,525",,$300,,Cash,,,,,,Charles and Thorne streets,"Nestled in the vibrant heart of Jersey City Heights, 391 Central Ave #4, only a two flight walk up, presents a charming and modern living space. This newly gut renovated space  features two generously sized bedrooms, accompanied by a versatile den that can easily adapt to your lifestyle, whether you need a dedicated home office, a cozy guest room, or a creative studio. Bathed in natural light, the apartment boasts gleaming hardwood floors that create a warm and welcoming ambiance throughout. The kitchen is a true highlight, designed with both style and functionality in mind. It showcases sleek stainless steel Whirlpool appliances, complemented by elegant shaker cabinets and a classic subway tile backsplash, offering a sophisticated culinary experience. The bathroom provides a touch of contemporary elegance with its glass-enclosed tub, creating a serene space for relaxation. Adding to the convenience of modern living, an in-unit washer and dryer eliminate the hassle of laundry day. Massive amounts of additional storage space is included, in basement. Situated in a prime Jersey City Heights location, this apartment offers easy access to a diverse array of local shops, restaurants, and convenient transportation options. This desirable address provides the perfect blend of comfort, style, and urban convenience, making it an ideal place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to invest in Jersey Cities hottest and soon to be, most established neighborhood! Schedule your private tour today. Parking available nearby for an additional fee"
