210009346,SOLD,"JC, Heights",104 HOPKINS AVE,Condominium,750,1419,"$430,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2B,"JC, Heights",07306,05704,00024,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$430,000","$469,000",$573.33,$573.33,4/21/2021,7/16/2021,8/24/2021,86,87,,8/24/2021,,,,,,$205,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Oakland Ave & Central Ave,"An unbeatable location, between the border of Five Corners and Palisade Ave. This beautiful 2 bedroom / 2 bathroom unit with high ceilings is located on a quiet tree lined street in the Heights. The unit was newly renovated and is completely outfitted with all modern finishes. Custom made chef's kitchen with designer Cashmere Carrara quartz countertops and high end Bosch appliances. There is also additional space above the kitchen cabinets for long term storage. Sleek bathrooms with Porcelanosa fixtures, tile; and Hansgrohe plumbing. Oak hardwood flooring, custom made closets, and LED lighting throughout. The bedrooms are located on the opposite sides of the house to offer increased privacy. The unit is equipped with central air, managed by Nest thermostats, Sonos system, video doorbell,  and an in unit washer/dryer. Close proximity to schools and an abundance of transportation options including: the PATH, the Light Rail and Buses, it has all the makings of your perfect home. The seller can install an island upon buyer's request!"
