220004521,SOLD,"JC, Heights",11 CUNEO PL,Condominium,850,1605,"$435,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,4D,"JC, Heights",07307,5202,30,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,4,,"$435,000","$425,000",$511.76,$511.76,3/15/2022,3/21/2022,5/9/2022,6,6,,5/19/2022,,,,"$5,399",2021,$310,2021,Conventional,No,No,,,,ODGDEN AND PALISADE,"STUNNING 2 BED 1 BATH condo in the most sought after section of JC heights!  Complete with door to oversized fire escape offering PLENTY OF fresh air and peaceful view. Wood floors, lots of windows and closet space. Building has w/d room, rooftop deck with stunning views of the manhattan skyline, and a tranquil landscaped backyard with grills for all the residents to enjoy! This location can't be beat! Next to a newly updated park, Ogden's End Community Garden, and a dog park. So many neighborhood amenities within 3 blocks. Fully stocked grocery store w/ amazing produce, butcher, deli, and seafood dept. Belly up to the bar for a cold beer or craft cocktail & mouth-watering pizza at Low Fidelity (LoFi to the locals). Stop for a scratch-made ice cream sandwich at Milk, Sugar, Love. Grab a coffee and croissant at Choc-O-Pain bakery. Pick up a few essentials at the Farmers Market in Riverview Park. Nearby you'll find neighborhood favorites like Bread & Salt, Corto, and take in some live music at Fox & Crow!! Close to Hoboken, Lightrail, NJ transit buses and more! Our own JC mayor calls The Heights home. Stop renting and own a piece of the neighborhood or make an investment with this highly desirable rental opportunity. Building requires 20-25% down.  Sorry no pets allowed!"
