220021732,SOLD,"JC, Heights",122 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,605,1419,"$440,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,202,"JC, Heights",07307,04504,00001,Heights,The York,,,,1,0,1,4,,"$440,000","$499,000",$727.27,$727.27,12/20/2022,1/19/2023,2/3/2023,30,30,,2/6/2023,,,,,,$209,2022,Cash,,,,,,Ferry St. & Franklin St.,"LIVE IN LUXURY MORTGAGE FREE FOR YOUR FIRST YEAR!* Love where you live at The York in the Jersey City Heights! Don't miss this rare opportunity to see and live in The Jersey City Heights newest development - The York! With large serene private terraces and direct elevator access to a the huge communal deck; this elevator building optimizes every square foot of the floor plan and includes two communal rooftop decks, a large garage, and a bike rack on the 1st floor. A tranquil oasis is awaiting you in the Jersey City Height with unobstructed Manhattan views! Radiant and inviting, this airy condominium entails 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom. Equipped with chef's kitchen, Bosch stainless steel appliances, modernized cabinetry, in-unit washer/dryer, and in-ceiling speakers managed by Sonos amplifier. 5 wide french oak plank hardwood floors throughout, Porcelanosa tile and plumbing fixtures, LED lighting and heated bathroom floors create a true luxurious experience. The builder spared no cost in making this home sound proofed by using sound channels and sound clips, Quietrock, green/noise proofing compound, and even foam insulation, dampening the noise. This rare Heights location is easily commutable and accessible to public transportation being only 1 block from Palisade Ave; with direct bus lines to NYC Port Authority, Hoboken, and Downtown JC. The Hudson Light Rail Stations are only minutes away as well as Pershing Field's indoor pool and ice skating rink being only 3 blocks away. Riverview Park with its amazing views offers Farmers Market, movie nights, and neighborhood events. Builder has filed for a 5 year tax abatement. 10 year new construction warranty. Please contact listing agent for private showing!"
