220003425,SOLD,"JC, Heights",43 THORNE ST,Condominium,680,1691,"$440,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1L,"JC, Heights",07307,2804,10,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$440,000","$435,000",$647.06,$647.06,2/28/2022,4/21/2022,7/13/2022,52,52,,7/13/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave & Central Ave,"Modern and stylish 2-bedroom condos in the center of Jersey City make an ideal option for everyone from first-time home buyers to investors, and everyone in between. Contemporary design and high-end sophistication combine with shared outdoor space and chic lounge for coveted living amenities. Striking exterior showcases bright white siding, bay windows and contrasting black trim, leading to the black marbled lobby and secure entrance.  Designer kitchens host impeccably styled matte black custom cabinets with open shelving accents, wine rack and brass fixtures, topped with waterfall marbled quartz counters and backsplash. Bedrooms offer spaciousness and smart storage options, while bathrooms boast floor-to-ceiling oversized porcelain tile with matte black fixtures and glass shower or bath.  Situated in the center of The Heights, residents are walking distance to excellent cafes, essential shops, great schools and easy NYC access. Expansive Washington Park and Riverview Fisk Park with NYC views are just around the corner, each offering running trails, sports facilities, playgrounds and community events.  Square footage is approximate. "
