240004689,SOLD,"JC, Heights",1 CONGRESS ST,Condominium,945,1597,"$440,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,C10,"JC, Heights",07307,02404,00041,,,,,,1,0,1,5,,"$440,000","$409,000",$465.61,$465.61,3/12/2024,4/10/2024,5/22/2024,29,29,,5/23/2024,,,,"$6,894",2023,$295,,Conventional,,,,,,Corner of Ogden Ave,"Nestled atop the cliff overlooking Hoboken, this spacious one-bedroom apartment with a den and fully renovated bathroom offers both comfort and convenience. Step into the open layout living and dining area, seamlessly connected to the large, updated kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and modern countertops. With solid hardwood floors throughout and ample closet space, including a substantial walk-in closet in the primary bedroom, this apartment is designed for modern living. Building amenities include an on-site laundry room, with assigned parking available for an additional $40 monthly fee. Located in the sought-after Heights neighborhood, just steps away from the 9th Street light rail, this apartment provides easy access to transportation options for commuters. Additionally, enjoy the vibrant dining scene, from the rustic charm of Corto's homemade Italian to the many restaurants & bars in the area. Begin your mornings with a freshly brewed cup of coffee at The Cliff or Modcup Coffee, both known for their artisanal blends and cozy atmospheres.  For outdoor enthusiasts, nearby parks like Riverview-Fisk Park offer breathtaking views of the Hudson River and the Manhattan skyline, perfect for picnics or leisurely strolls and farmers market during the summer. Experience the best of urban living in Jersey City Heights, where diverse dining, cozy cafes, and picturesque parks await at your doorstep.  There will be future assessment of approximately $20,000 that the seller will pay in full before closing  "
