230002315,SOLD,"JC, Heights",238 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,734,6494,"$465,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03904,00018,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,4,,"$465,000","$465,000",$633.51,$633.51,2/9/2023,2/17/2023,4/21/2023,8,8,,4/24/2023,,,,"$6,858",,$350,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Griffith St & Franklin St.,"Beautifully renovated in 2021, this 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom condo is located on desirable Ogden Ave, only 1 block from Riverview Park, in Jersey City Heights! The kitchen is equipped with solid oak cabinets, quartz countertops, porcelain backsplash and stainless steel appliances. With a total or 8 windows on 3 sides (North/East/South), there is an abundance of natural sunlight flooding onto the 6 wide American White Oak flooring. The elegant renovated bathroom has honeycomb porcelain tile, a double sink vanity, French glass shower doors and the convenience of in unit washer/dryer combo. Other renovation highlights include: new 6 base molding throughout the entire condo, new interior doors, custom radiator covers, customized bedroom closet and new blinds on all windows. There is a common outdoor backyard area for entertaining and rooftop with NYC views. The well maintained basement has a private storage room and shared washer/dryer, free of charge. Short walk, .4 miles, to the 2nd St Light Rail station."
