220005493,SOLD,"JC, Heights",71 BEACON AVE,Condominium,994,1597,"$490,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07306,05905,00006,,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$490,000","$499,000",$492.96,$492.96,3/31/2022,4/14/2022,5/20/2022,14,14,,5/21/2022,,,,"$6,105",2021,$301,,Conventional,,,,,,Oakland and Baldwin,"Superbly located in the sought-after Jersey City Heights just moments to the neighborhood’s renowned restaurants and shopping, Journal Square PATH Station, Mana Contemporary, Downtown Jersey City, Hoboken and several parks, this recently renovated Two Bedroom and Two Bathroom Condominium residence with an expansive private backyard is a rare find. Having undergone a complete overhaul in 2020, the residence is in an immaculate, move-in ready condition. The open kitchen is outfitted with Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and custom cabinetry. Both bathrooms are beautifully designed with gorgeous tiles. In the rear, the covered patio invites an intimate, private sitting area. Up a few steps, the large garden exclusively designated to the unit is perfect for entertaining and gardening. Remaining Tax Abatement in place."
220018800,SOLD,"JC, Heights",82 RESERVOIR AVE,Condominium,1701,5845,"$490,000",CONDO-COOP,,G&1,1,"JC, Heights",07307-2478,00507,00033,,,,,,3,0,3,8,,"$490,000","$519,000",$288.07,$288.07,10/21/2022,12/8/2022,1/16/2023,48,48,,1/18/2023,,,,,,,,Cash,,,,,,Webster Ave & Lienau Pl,"MOTIVATED SELLER! PERFECT FOR INVESTORS OR FIRST TIME HOME BUYERS! Welcome home to 82 Reservoir. This 3-unit building was meticulously renovated with an eye to providing everything today's discerning buyer needs. Unit 1 is a duplex home offering 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms on the main floor, and an additional 2 rooms and full bathroom on the lower level. The lower level also has access to your private patio.  The chef's kitchen is complete with maple cabinetry, quartz countertops and stainless-steel appliances. The open concept living area has ample space for a separate dining area. The primary bedroom features an en suite bathroom. Beautiful oak floors throughout, brand new Anderson windows, central a/c and in home laundry & a common roof deck with sweeping NYC views. Perfectly situated in one of the most sought-after areas in Jersey City Heights, only minutes to shopping, restaurants, Pershing field park and recreation and offering an easy commute to NYC."
210006258,SOLD,"JC, Heights",281 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,,1691,"$495,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2A,"JC, Heights",07307,3702,129,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$495,000","$495,000",,,3/16/2021,3/16/2021,1/5/2022,0,0,,1/10/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton St & Sherman Pl,"Level up in every way at The Beckford. Style, smart-tech and sophistication come together in these sleek urban luxury condos settled on Central Avenue in Jersey City Heights. Take the elevator directly to your two-bedroom, two-bath, high-end oasis with modern upgrades and access to the shared rooftop deck with NYC views, thoughtful seating areas and grass space, or downstairs garden with grill.  Bright and airy, each home is finished with wide-plank, white oak hardwood flooring throughout  with floor to ceiling windows for excellent natural light. Kitchens feature luscious black ice quartz waterfall countertops with sleek black or white custom cabinetry, mosaic penny tile backsplash and Dacor appliances. Luxurious bathrooms invite with pattern floortile, glass showers with niche, floating vanities and matte black finishes. Thoughtful floor plans offer elevated sound privacy and flow, plus simple access to all building amenities.   Central Avenue offers the ultimate access to all that Jersey City Heights has to offer. The main thoroughfare is home to the vibrant artist community, essential shops and award-winning restaurants, while also 2 blocks to massive Pershing Field Park and Reservoir and easy NYC access. Building amenities include the massive shared roof deck and garden, secured elevator and bike storage room. Estimated completion late spring 2021."
