240020920,SOLD,"JC, Heights",74 BOWERS ST,Condominium,700,1713,"$499,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,101,"JC, Heights",07307,2301,1,,,,,,1,0,1,5,,"$499,000","$499,000",$712.86,$712.86,10/24/2024,10/31/2024,12/13/2024,7,7,,12/14/2024,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Sherman & Webster,"Discover modern luxury at its finest with this impeccably designed 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo located in the heart of Jersey City Heights. With garage parking, a private storage room, and an EV charger, every detail has been thoughtfully crafted for today’s urban lifestyle. Step into the open-concept living area where a gourmet kitchen awaits, featuring premium Café appliances, sleek countertops, and a stunning waterfall island—ideal for both casual dining and culinary creativity. The space flows seamlessly into the living and dining areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation and entertainment. The generously sized bedroom is bathed in natural light, providing a peaceful retreat, while the elegant bathroom boasts contemporary finishes and high-end fixtures, offering a spa-like experience at home. Located in the thriving Jersey City Heights, this home places you near trendy shops, local cafes, and easy transportation options for a quick commute to New York City. Embrace sophisticated urban living in this exceptional condo—your perfect modern retreat awaits!"
