210009834,SOLD,"JC, Heights",155 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1209,1691,"$499,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2903,13,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,7,,"$499,000","$499,000",$412.74,$412.74,4/26/2021,5/14/2021,7/16/2021,18,18,,7/20/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith & Bowers,"Open the door to endless opportunity with this beautifully maintained and well-located 2 bedroom, 1 bath condo with additional, detached bonus suite (both with access to private paved backyard)! Classic elements like hardwood floors, crown molding and french doors highlight bright upgrades like recess lighting and pendant accents. Add the two full floors of well-finished living space with three total bedrooms & two bathrooms to get endless combinations from mother-in-law suite to office space and beyond.  The upstairs two-bedroom main home opens to a tasteful kitchen and living area with oversized windows, granite counters, mosaic tile backsplash and stainless appliances. Step out back to the large private back garden complete with paved seating area, plus landscape rock terrace, or through the double doors to an extra large bedroom with plenty of closet space and built-in bookshelves. Bathroom beautifully boasts porcelain tile floors, refreshed lighting, polished chrome fixtures and convenient bath shower combo. Bedrooms are separated on either end of the layout, ideal for a variety of set-ups. The additional detached downstairs suite is complete with bonus room, wet bar plus spacious den and full bath.  Ideally located in The Heights, residents enjoy walkability to nearby Palisade and Central Avenues with vibrant community and essential shopping and Riverview Fisk park with play areas, dog run, seasonal farmers market and NYC views."
260004242,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",41 BEACON AVE,Condominium,668,1623,"$499,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07306,05904,00005,,,,,,2,0,2,4,,,"$499,000",$747.01,,3/11/2026,,,29,,,3/11/2026,,,,"$7,343",2024,$225,2026,,,,,,,Palisade/Baldwin Aves.,"Modern, recently constructed (2021) 2-bedroom, 2-full bathroom condo has it all! Located in the vibrant Heights section of Jersey City, this home features 2 bedrooms that flank opposite sides of the unit. The primary bdrm has an en suite bathroom, and each full bathroom is fitted with spa like showers and marble tile finishes. A chef's dream kitchen features a large breakfast bar/prep area, an oversized under-mount sink, and warranted stainless steel appliances. White oversized shaker cabinetry and quartz countertops complete the space. Wide plank maple hardwood flooring, a built-in Washer/Dryer and central A/C round out this beautiful unit. Blocks away is Pershing Field with pickle ball and tennis courts, ice skating rink, track and the nearby recently refurbished bucolic trail around Reservoir#3 offering a natural escape just a stone's throw from your urban oasis. St. Anthony's Park on Palisade Ave. hosts year-round community events, a Cherry Blossom festival, summer yoga series, basketball courts, and a community garden. Located conveniently to Palisade Ave. where you will find coffee shops, dining, and shopping and NJ Transit bus to NY Port Authority, plus JSQ PATH is only minutes away. This home is the perfect landing spot at the end of the day, and move-in ready! Come by and see this true gem for yourself."
