230018881,SOLD,"JC, Heights",34 GRACE ST,Condominium,950,6078,"$520,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,4,"JC, Heights",07307,00504,00035,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$520,000","$520,000",$547.37,$547.37,11/8/2023,2/5/2024,4/16/2024,89,89,,4/17/2024,,,,,,$200,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave. and Central Ave.,"Free downpayment assistance credit for first time homebuyers of up to 22k through preferred mortgage lender. Introducing a brand-new, boutique-style 2-bed, 2-bath condo with a private rooftop oasis and stunning views of the NYC Skyline & Washington Park. Located in the prime Jersey City Heights neighborhood, Grace Residence features high-end appliances, in-unit washer/dryer, 14-ft ceilings, and Bay-Style Pella Architect Series Windows. Custom closets, quartz countertops, European-style stairs, and innovative showers with linear drains & three-way plumbing fixtures elevating the design & shower experience. Cove lighting, upgraded tiles, and soundproofing ensure a peaceful living environment. Conveniently situated near Washington Park and major transit options, this condo provides sophisticated living with easy access to NYC."
240002927,SOLD,"JC, Heights",34 GRACE ST,Condominium,1500,6078,"$520,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,00504,00035,Heights,,,,,2,1,2,7,,"$520,000","$625,000",$346.67,$346.67,2/16/2024,3/5/2024,4/16/2024,18,18,,5/29/2024,,,,,,,350,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave. & Central Ave.,"**Up to 22k in free grant for 1st time home buyers and/or fixed 4.5% rate through preferred lenders** Welcome to this brand-new boutique-style duplex condo featuring 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a bonus den complete with a second kitchenette. Enjoy the luxury of your private backyard oasis in the heart of prime Jersey City Heights. This exceptional Grace Residence is adorned with high-end appliances and finishes, an in-unit washer and dryer and distinctive bay-style Pella Architect Series windows that flood the home with an abundance of natural light.  The design is further accentuated by custom-built closets, sleek quartz countertops in the kitchens, real oak European-style stairs, and innovative three-way plumbing fixtures in the bathrooms, allowing for both a waterfall and regular shower simultaneously. Cove lighting throughout the bathrooms, upgraded tile finishes, floor-to-ceiling tiling, and real shower glass doors add to the property's allure. To ensure a peaceful living environment, extreme soundproofing has been expertly implemented to prevent noise transmission between floors.  Ideally located next to Washington Park and nestled between Central and Summit Avenue, this condo is within walking distance of major bus lines and the light rail train, offering direct transportation into NYC."
250011134,SOLD,"JC, Heights",44 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1058,1603,"$520,000",CONDO-COOP,,5&6,5E,"JC, Heights",07307,4502,2,Heights,,,,,2,1,1,5,,"$520,000","$525,000",$491.49,$491.49,6/3/2025,6/25/2025,8/22/2025,22,22,,8/23/2025,,,,"$8,671",,$721,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"Wake up to breathtaking, northeast-facing views of the Midtown Manhattan skyline from nearly every room in this high-floor duplex, located in one of the few elevator buildings in booming Jersey City Heights. With soaring ceilings and a bright, open layout, this residence offers the space and flow of a true home, complete with duplex-style living that separates your entertaining and private areas across two levels. Enjoy skyline views from the living and dining areas, both bedrooms, the kitchen, and your own private terrace. Brand new PTAC units ensure year-round comfort, while thoughtful touches like real (non-spiral) stairs, USB outlets, and abundant closet space add to the home's appeal. Building amenities include a welcoming entry foyer, resident laundry room, and on-site fitness center. Ideally located near Palisade Avenue’s best shops, dining, parks, and public transit—this is skyline living with the comfort of home."
220018574,SOLD,"JC, Heights",65 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1352,1294,"$520,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$520,000","$499,000",$384.62,$384.62,10/19/2022,10/28/2022,12/12/2022,9,9,,12/14/2022,,,,"$6,928",2021,$471,,Conventional,,,,,,Ferry & Franklin St,"Bright and Spacious 3 Bed, 2 Bath on the highly sought-after block of Webster Ave in the Riverview Arts District of Jersey City Heights! A full modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, dishwasher, granite countertops and a breakfast bar. A window overlooks the nook off the kitchen, large enough for a dining room table. Ample storage space at your disposal: 2 walk-in closets, 2 additional closets, extra space in the separate HVAC and Laundry Room and a wide open shared basement for even more storage! Another nook off the living room is the perfect space for an office, play area or can be converted into an additional closet for storage. The master bedroom has a walk-in-closet and en-suite bath with a jacuzzi tub/shower. Exposed bricks and crown molding throughout, wide-plank hardwood floors, full-size in-unit washer/dryer and central Heat/AC. Within blocks of 2 parks: Riverview Park & Pershing Field Park. Conveniently located near the “100 Steps” for easy access to Hoboken and the Light Rail. Between Central Ave & Palisades Ave gives you access to even more public transportation, shops, restaurants and nightlife."
220019257,SOLD,"JC, Heights",71 NORTH ST,Condominium,1139,1186,"$520,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,403,"JC, Heights",07307,01602,0000101,Heights,Parkview Manor,,,,2,0,2,4,,"$520,000","$525,000",$456.54,$456.54,11/1/2022,11/21/2022,2/10/2023,20,20,,2/11/2023,,,,"$6,900",2022,$355,,Cash,,,,,,Cambridge Ave & Hancock Ave,"Welcome to this beautiful and well maintained 2-bedroom, 2 full bathroom condo in Jersey City Heights. Perfectly situated across from Washington Park, this home features 10-foot ceilings, granite countertops, SS appliances, central air, a private terrace and hardwood floors throughout.  This open concept layout leaves ample room for a formal dining area and allows for a large, comfortable living space. City views, an elevator, and on-site laundry room round this home out.  Numerous restaurants and nightlife within walking distance, minutes from Hoboken and both the Lincoln & Holland Tunnels make this the ideal location and a fit for any lifestyle."
210015949,SOLD,"JC, Heights",549 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1,1691,"$520,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$520,000","$499,000","$520,000.00","$520,000.00",7/2/2021,7/23/2021,11/14/2021,21,21,,11/14/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,South St & Congress St,"Modern design and mindful finishes heat things up in coveted Jersey City Heights. The white-hot facade of this beautifully refinished Tudor-style stonework building leads to a secure entrance for each of the four 2-bed, 2 full bath homes. Each slightly different floorplan offers a variety of must-haves, each boasting modern design, fresh finishes plus common storage.  Clean lines and simple design echo throughout each unit with gleaming hardwood floors and flowing floorplans. Kitchens shine brightly with sparkling quartz counters, shaker cabinets and stainless Frigidaire appliances, while bathrooms showcase porcelain tile finished to the ceiling plus optimal soaker tubs and showers. Sizable bedrooms with ceiling fans, plus Samsung washer and dryer are standard in each home.  This perfect Palisade location is walking distance to Riverview Fisk and Washington Parks, plus just steps from essential shops, vibrant community, excellent schools and easy NYC, PATH and Light Rail access."
250014916,SOLD,"JC, Heights",351 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1098,1606,"$520,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2B.R.. 202,"JC, Heights",07307,4504,24,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$520,000","$529,000",$473.59,$473.59,7/22/2025,9/19/2025,10/30/2025,59,59,,11/19/2025,,,,"$10,673",23,$411,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Ferry,"Welcome to this beautiful  three-bedroom, two-bath condo in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Boasting high ceilings and an open-concept layout, this home is bathed in natural light, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere.  The primary bedroom offers a serene retreat with an en-suite bath, while two additional bedrooms provide flexibility of living space.  Located in the vibrant Heights neighborhood ,steps away from restaurants including LoFi, Choc o Pain &  The Alps. Relax and  enjoy the  panoramic New York City views from the common partial ROOF DECK, with storage and laundry on site.... don't miss out...make this gem your home today!       "
250015251,SOLD,"JC, Heights",247 CAMBRIDGE AVE,Condominium,809,1603,"$521,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3 (301),"JC, Heights",07307,01601,00036,,,,,,2,0,2,9,,"$521,000","$529,000",$644.00,$644.00,7/25/2025,8/4/2025,9/4/2025,10,10,,9/5/2025,,,,"$8,869",2022,$295,,Cash,,,,,,Congress and North,"This meticulously rebuilt (2017) 3-unit condo building presents a sun-drenched and spacious 3rd-floor, 809sqft unit with 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, in Jersey City's vibrant The Heights neighborhood. It features a modern kitchen equipped with LG stainless steel appliances, including an externally vented range, dishwasher, and microwave. Both bathrooms boast floor-to-ceiling porcelain tiles, high-end designer cabinets, and European fixtures, with curved shower rods and frameless glass doors. Enjoy partial NYC views, 10-foot ceilings with crown moldings, and a generous 112 square feet private terrace for entertaining. Additional conveniences include private deeded storage, a washer and gas heat dryer, and central air conditioning. The prime location offers immediate access to parks, restaurants, shopping, cafes, grocery stores, and Citi Bike stations, along with easy access to NYC via nearby buses and the Hoboken 9th Street Light Rail (PATH connection). This unit also comes with deeded roof rights, providing potential for a roof deck and stairs (subject to zoning approvals after sale)."
210002140,SOLD,"JC, Heights",207 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,890,1603,"$523,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3R,"JC, Heights",07307,03903,00071,,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$523,000","$535,000",$587.64,$587.64,1/25/2021,3/12/2021,4/28/2021,46,46,,4/30/2021,,,,"$7,190",2019,$264,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Griffith St,"Welcome to 207 Ogden, a boutique 6-unit building on the most desirable, beautifully tree-lined block of Jersey City Heights. Just two flights up, this 900 square foot two bedroom home is perfectly disbursed with bedrooms on opposite ends & an open concept living space with plenty of room to allow for work from home space. The recently renovated and upgraded kitchen features stainless steel appliances, perfectly crafted quartz countertops, and white shaker-style cabinetry that extends into the dining area; easily accommodating a full-sized dining set. Bonus oversized pantry behind the trendy barn door. Two tastefully redesigned bathrooms inclusive of an en-suite. This home is bright, flooded with natural light via the large windows in every room. Other highlights include 10 foot ceilings, central air/heat, decorative crown molding, hardwood floors, custom blinds, tailor-made closet shelving, in-home laundry & ample storage throughout. 207 Ogden features a shared courtyard, a private 6x9 storage room and plans for a rooftop with NYC views!  Ideal for the everyday commuter with very close proximity to NJ Transit bus routes,  the 2nd Street Light Rail Station and all major highways. Steps to Hoboken! Best of all, a short distance from all that the Heights has to offer; parks & recreational activities, coffee shops, supermarkets, shopping & local restaurants like Corto, Lo-Fi, ModCup Coffee, and more! Welcome Home!"
240001262,SOLD,"JC, Heights",44 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,957,5873,"$525,000",CONDO-COOP,,5,B5,"JC, Heights",07307,4502,2,Heights,Riverview Terrace,,,,2,0,1,7,,"$525,000","$525,000",$548.59,$548.59,1/22/2024,2/3/2024,3/22/2024,12,12,,4/15/2024,,,,"$7,118",2023,$425,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Between Franklin St and Hutton St,"Prepare to be WOWED by this one of a kind 2 bedroom loft condo with breathtaking views of Midtown and Downtown NYC, all the bells and whistles, AND in the heart of JC Heights! Step into this beautifully laid out unit with an abundance of light and space. The open concept kitchen was recently renovated and comes with SS appliances, mobile center island for easy accessibility and additional prepping space, Moen smart kitchen faucet, and a loft space overviewing the living room which could be used as a small dining area or additional storage space. The large living room with 12ft high ceilings is welcoming and overviews the NYC skyline, perfect for entertaining. The two bedrooms are nicely sized, with an added bonus loft perfect for a play room, office, or walk-in closet area - time to be creative!!. The renovated bathroom comes with the luxury and convenience of double sinks, Bluetooth speakers and two mirrors that turns into a screen so you never miss your favorite show or an important email (Verizon acct required). As if it wasn't enough, this unit also comes with its own washer/dyer for added comfort. A few other upgrades worth mentioning: water heater is brand new, appliances are one year old, windows, recessed lighting and AC units replaced last year, and mood lighting throughout is wi-fi controlled.  As for the building and its location, Riverview Terrace is an elevator building with a newly updated gym (steps from your apartment door) and laundry rooms, a AND it is pet friendly!! There is parking available for an additional fee - seller is on the waitlist, which can be transferred to the buyer at closing, if desired. This unit is within close distance to two supermarkets, three local parks, schools, coffee shops, restaurants and bars, and the Central Avenue shopping district. Are you a commuter? No worries! This building is conveniently located near many transportation options within 3 blocks - NYC bus (Port Authority), Hoboken Terminal bus (PATH, NY Waterway Ferry, NJ Transit), and close to the 2nd Street Light Rail station.  What are you waiting for?? This is the condo you've been searching for!"
240020535,SOLD,"JC, Heights",549 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,930,6502,"$525,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,4,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$525,000","$525,000",$564.52,$564.52,10/17/2024,10/28/2024,12/9/2024,11,11,,12/10/2024,,,,"$8,159",2023,$500,,Conventional,,,,,,South St & Bowers St,"Welcome home to this charming 2-Bed, 2-Bath Condo in the heart of The Heights in Jersey City. This beautiful and impeccably maintained 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. An open floor plan makes this a great place for entertaining with abundant natural light and custom built-ins. The well-appointed modern kitchen features stainless steel appliances and ample cabinetry. Enjoy living on Palisade Ave close to everything The Heights has to offer- amazing restaurants, cafes and shops as well as Riverview-Fisk Park. To top it all off, you are right by the Ninth Street/Congress Street station for easy access to NYC and Hoboken!"
260004468,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",91 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,0,5069,"$525,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,1,0,1,4,,,"$525,000",,,3/13/2026,,,27,,,3/13/2026,,,,,,,,,No,No,Yes,,,Webster and Palisade,"Off-site Parking options available.  Unit 2 went under contract in just one week-- don't miss your chance to make this one yours! Welcome to 91 Hancock Avenue, Rear ADU a brand new 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom residence by Jack & Lumber, Jersey City's premier ultra-luxury home builder and the only one in The Heights crafting true boutique residences. Designed for those who expect more, this home offers a rare blend of visionary design, refined materials, and exceptional craftsmanship.The bespoke Italian kitchen is a standout, featuring integrated LED-lit glass cabinetry, a paneled Sub-Zero Designer Series refrigerator, black glass Wolf appliances, and a Neolith porcelain island with integrated sink and induction cooktop. Buster & Punch solid brass hardware and lighting add sculptural tactility, while the signature Jack & Lumber floating staircase framed in glass and lit with LEDs anchors the home like a modern art installation.Triple-pane Drutex windows reduce exterior noise and increase energy efficiency, while radiant-heated Neolith-clad bathrooms with smart toilets offer spa-like comfort. Italian closets, 8-foot American walnut interior doors, and concealed magnetic hardware elevate every detail. This is more than a home. It's a lifestyle statement crafted for those who appreciate the extraordinary. Schedule a private appointment and fall in love with Jack & Lumber.Property comes with 10-Year Builder Warranty."
