220014203,SOLD,"JC, Heights",3568 KENNEDY BLVD,Condominium,900,6199,"$530,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,4,,"$530,000","$549,000",$588.89,$588.89,8/4/2022,2/6/2023,3/2/2023,186,186,,3/3/2023,,,,,,$136,,Cash,No,No,Yes,,,Graham & Congress,"SPECIAL LOW INTEREST RATE FROM MID 5%’s PROGRAM AVAILABLE, NO PMI, LOW DOWNPAYMENT, SAVING THOUSANDS OF DOLLARS: Part of census tract mortgage program which features below market interest rate with 30 year fix option. Featuring Another Signature Luxury brand new Construction by Blue Chip Living from the pages of Architectural Digest to the heart of booming Jersey City Heights, a business district, residential area, and transportation hub. Open your private entry door to this captivating condo featuring 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, open concept living space with LED electric fireplace and oversized wrap around windows that flood the space with natural light. The chef’s kitchen boasts impeccable white high-gloss European Style cabinetry, stainless steel premium smart appliances, modern porcelain backsplash, central island with a waterfall quartz, pot filler, pendant lighting, and drawer microwave. The 2 bedrooms share a spa–like bathroom with matte black hardware, luxurious vanity. This unit has access to a large picturesque private yard. Other perks include West Elm lighting, laundry room hook ups, central/heat/air, 8’ solid-core doors & designated storage area. Full smart home technology creates ease of living with ButterflyMX Video Intercom System, Nest thermostat, Smart Lighting Dimmer Switches accessible via smart phone. Private Storage Are included. All major transportation at your fingertips. Make this your Dream Home Oasis today! Maintenance includes cold water, sewer, snow removal, trash removal, common area utilities.  *Eligible for 5 year tax abatement & 1 year free parking."
