250007114,SOLD,"JC, Heights",579 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1000,6638,"$541,600",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2304,22,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,4,,"$541,600","$525,000",$541.60,$541.60,4/11/2025,5/28/2025,6/11/2025,47,47,,6/19/2025,,,,"$9,399",2023,$405,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress & South St.,"Welcome to this beautifully renovated duplex condo, ideally situated right on Palisade Avenue! Just steps from the Congress Street light rail station, this one-of-a-kind property offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and convenience. Enjoy sweeping panoramic views of the NYC skyline from the expansive shared rooftop deck – an entertainer’s dream! This spacious condo features a multi-floor layout with an open-concept living area, built-in surround sound speakers, and elegant finishes throughout. The gourmet kitchen is fully equipped with top-of-the-line appliances, including a wine fridge, perfect for hosting friends and family. Retreat to the luxurious bathroom, complete with multiple jet shower heads and heated floors for added comfort. Living here means being surrounded by local shops, parks, trendy restaurants, and easy access to transportation into Manhattan. Don’t miss out on the opportunity to own this unique property in one of the most sought-after locations in Jersey City Heights! Inquire today to learn more about potential credits on closing costs (ranging from $8,000 to $22,000) through our preferred lender."
210009606,SOLD,"JC, Heights",103 FERRY ST,Condominium,900,1419,"$543,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2R,"JC, Heights",07307,04401,00016,Heights,Le Navire,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$543,000","$559,000",$603.33,$603.33,4/22/2021,7/14/2021,8/25/2021,83,83,,9/14/2021,,,,,,$197,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave & Abbett St,"Le Navire on Ferry St is a luxurious listing that you don’t want to miss! No details were spared within these units considering the 12 ft ceilings, a large private roof deck with direct NYC views, the wide plank oak hardwood floors, dynamic LED lighting, and Pella windows run throughout the entire home. This building was completely and meticulously gut renovated and upgraded with new plumbing and electric systems, a central sprinkler system, and fire protection. This beautiful home offers custom-made chef's kitchens with designer quartz countertops, Bosch stoves, high-end Bosch appliances, and extra storage above your kitchen cabinets! Your home will be equipped with central air, managed by Nest thermostats, a pair of pre-wired speakers in each room, high-end RING intercoms, operated from your phone, and in-unit washer/dryers. The seller spared no cost on noise reduction and used sounds channels and sound clips, foam insulation, Rockwool, and SounFX sheetrock. The seller can install and L-shaped island upon buyer's request for free or $1000 credit. Details aside, the location is another bonus that adds to the unlimited amenities here at Le Navire. Being located in this Jersey City Heights neighborhood leaves you less than 100 feet from the Central Ave Shopping district and nearest bus stops to the PATH and NYC. If you decide to leave your home, Stop and Shop is only a few blocks away and there are an abundance of surrounding eateries including, The Hutton Bar & Grill, Rumba’s Cafe, and two of the highest-rated locations, Dulce de Leche Bakery and Pampita Butcher Shop, all conveniently located. The selections are endless when you reside at Le Navire on Ferry St!  - One parking space is still available!"
