220021275,SOLD,"JC, Heights",142 CHARLES ST,Condominium,973,1653,"$545,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,402,"JC, Heights",07307,2603,51,Heights,The Packard,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$545,000","$549,000",$560.12,$560.12,12/9/2022,12/29/2022,2/15/2023,20,20,,2/17/2023,,,,,,$419,,Conventional,,,,,,John F Kennedy & Summit Blvd,"SELLER PAYS $15,000 BUYER CLOSING COSTS FOR CLOSINGS BEFORE FEB 28, 2023!! SPECIAL PROGRAM AVAILABLE - 10% DOWN, NO PMI. This is a rare and sought-after opportunity to secure your very own slice of history in booming Jersey City Heights. The Packard JC boasts 14 new luxury condominiums that combine the very best in contemporary comfort with original details from this building’s industrial past. The Penthouse units all feature 2 beds, 2 baths and most units offer sweeping views of Manhattan, Journal Square & beyond Jersey City. Cooking will be a pleasure in the stylish kitchens with stainless steel appliances, under-mount sinks, breakfast bars and leathered granite countertops with a waterfall edge. Central AC, Navian on-demand tankless water heaters and an in-unit washer-dryer ensure absolute comfort plus there’s a host of dramatic features including 12 ft ceilings, concrete beams, exposed ductwork and engineered hardwood herringbone flooring.   Once the Packard Motor Car Company showroom, this steel and concrete construction, loft-style building is located close to the bustling Central Avenue with restaurants, shopping, cafes and parks nearby. Nearby buses connect you to NYC with easy links to the Journal Square transportation hub.  Photos are of a similar staged unit in the building."
