210013774,SOLD,"JC, Heights",72 COLUMBIA AVE,Condominium,1354,1419,"$599,650",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02602,00047,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$599,650","$598,000",$442.87,$442.87,6/7/2021,6/17/2021,10/29/2021,10,10,,11/5/2021,,,,,,$266,,Conventional,,,,,,Lincoln & Thorne,"Breathtaking unit that includes soaring ceiling heights, oversized Pella windows, and a lavish entertainment space! This huge single level condominium has been outfitted to perfection with over 1,350 square feet consisting of 3 bedrooms with an abundance of custom closet space and 2 full porcelanosa bathrooms. This smart home is equipped with New speakers managed with Sonos amplifier, Ring doorbell, and Nest Thermostats operable with your smartphone, connecting you with your home even when you're on the go. Custom Italian kitchens with double convection oven, Bosch stainless steel appliances and refrigerator. There is oak hardwood flooring throughout, quartz countertops, and an avcenter island with a built-in wine refrigerator. Over 1000 square feet of outdoor space, nearly doubling your total square footage and when you’re relaxing, you’ll have Manhattan & Hudson Meadow Views around you. The space also has a built-in outdoor sound/entertainment system and water and gas connections. Less than 2 blocks to JFK bus stops, under 10 minutes to Journal Square, and there is easy access to Tonnelle Ave and 1&9. You’ll also be located less than 3 blocks to the Leonard Gordon Park Conservancy and The Hutton, one of the Height's premier eateries. 1 car parking included!"
