220017391,SOLD,"JC, Heights",40 FLEET ST,Condominium,1177,1597,"$615,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$615,000","$650,000",$522.51,$522.51,9/21/2022,10/27/2022,1/18/2023,36,29,,1/18/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Baldwin & Concord,"Bright, airy and spacious, this new two-bedroom, two-bathroom home offers expansive layouts, loads of natural light and private outdoor plus storage in Jersey City Heights. Step inside to extra high 12ft ceilings and beautiful big black trimmed bay windows illuminating the light oak floors and open floorplan. The living area features an indoor sunroom balcony plus a striking exposed banister and glass stairwell leading to the full-size private rooftop with panoramic cityscape views.   Eat-in kitchen offers exquisite accents like polished marble honeycomb tile with gold trim backsplash, waterfall quartz counter, clean modern white upper custom cabinetry with natural wood lowers, matte black and brass fittings and stainless appliances. Primary bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet, while bathrooms are complete with elements like smart mirrors, double vanity and multi-function shower system.  Settled on a tree-lined street in a quiet corner of The Heights, this home is walking distance to Journal Square PATH, Central Ave, and Pershing Field Park. Jersey City Heights is known for its vibrant community, eclectic vibe, excellent schools and easy NYC access."
