230006657,SOLD,"JC, Heights",266 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1365,1725,"$632,500",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,43,2,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$632,500","$659,000",$463.37,$463.37,4/26/2023,5/15/2023,6/30/2023,19,19,,6/30/2023,,,,"$9,849",2022,$175,,Cash,No,No,,,,North and Congress,"Light-filled, spacious 3-bedroom 2-bathroom condominium with almost 1400 sq ft of living space, situated perfectly in the north end of Jersey City Heights. Step into the large, freshly painted open living area with vaulted ceilings, formal dining space and well-appointed upgraded kitchen with brand new countertops and brand new Whirlpool appliances. Enjoy evening sunsets on the West-facing balcony. Down the hallway, you’ll find the laundry room with a full washer and dryer, two identically-sized bedrooms and a full bathroom. The entire rear of the home features the main suite, with dual closets and a full en-suite bathroom. The unit has dedicated storage space and there is also a shared backyard, great for grilling and entertaining. Located just a few doors down from Washington Park and within walking distance to restaurants, cafes and shops, plus easy access to NYC"
