240011958,SOLD,"JC, Heights",185 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1015,1713,"$635,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2C,"JC, Heights",07307,2904,22,Heights,,,,,2,1,1,6,,"$635,000","$625,000",$625.62,$625.62,6/20/2024,6/26/2024,9/25/2024,6,6,,9/25/2024,,,,"$9,300",,$605,,Conventional,,,,,,GRIFFITH AND BOWERS,"Welcome to 185 Webster Ave, Unit 2C, a delightful 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom condo nestled in the vibrant community of Jersey City. This thoughtfully designed loft style home features an inviting layout, with gorgeous hardwood floors, soaring 14' ceilings, and abundant natural light that creates a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The heart of the home is the beautifully redone kitchen, boasting sleek cabinets and ample counter space, perfect for both everyday cooking and entertaining. The open and airy design ensures that meal preparation is a joy, while the natural light enhances the kitchen’s appeal. Both bedrooms are generously sized and offer ample closet space, providing plenty of room for storage and relaxation. The full bathroom is a luxurious retreat, featuring a rainfall showerhead and new glass shower guard where you can unwind after a long day. An additional half bathroom adds convenience for guests and busy mornings and convenient attic storage for your extra belongings. This unit’s thoughtful design and modern upgrades make it an ideal place to call home. Building offers a shared rooftop deck w/ breathtaking views of NYC and garage parking. Situated in a desirable location, you’ll enjoy easy access to local amenities, parks, and transportation options. Embrace the perfect blend of comfort and style at 185 Webster Ave, Unit 2C, and discover the best of Jersey City living."
