250005722,SOLD,"JC, Heights",256 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1213,1597,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$650,000","$699,000",$535.86,$535.86,3/25/2025,4/28/2025,5/15/2025,34,34,,8/13/2025,,,,,,$298,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers and South St,"This newly refinished grey brick building blends modern design with classic details. Offering three thoughtfully designed residences, each unit features light oak hardwood floors, crown molding, and oversized windows allowing for an abundance of natural light. The open-concept living areas are spacious enough for a full-size dining table, creating a comfortable and functional layout.  The kitchens are finished with waterfall quartz countertops, a herringbone tile backsplash, and a striking combination of white upper and dark indigo lower custom cabinetry. Brass fixtures add warmth, while LG stainless steel appliances complete the space with a sleek, modern touch. The primary suite in each unit is designed as a peaceful retreat, accented by a tranquil feature wall. Bathrooms showcase floor-to-ceiling tile, double vanities, matte black fixtures, and either a glass-enclosed shower or a deep soaking tub with a built-in niche. Each unit includes a full-size laundry room with a Samsung champagne washer and dryer for added convenience. Unit 1 offers three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a private balcony.  Set in the heart of Jersey City Heights, this location is just blocks from Riverview Fisk Park, where residents can take in sweeping views of the Manhattan skyline and enjoy local farmers' markets and community events. The 9th Street elevator provides easy access to Hoboken, while the nearby Light Rail connects directly to the PATH train and ferry, making commuting into New York City seamless."
230009433,SOLD,"JC, Heights",56 RESERVOIR AVE,Condominium,944,1597,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$650,000","$649,000",$688.56,$688.56,6/7/2023,6/12/2023,8/21/2023,5,5,,8/21/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Lienau & Webster,"Modern design and urban escape combine to bring this newly renovated home to Jersey City Heights. Presented with carefully curated finishes, private outdoor space and quality craftsmanship, this property is located just off Pershing Field Park and Reservoir, and nestled on a tree-lined street between Palisade and Central Avenue.  Gorgeous green siding, beautiful black trim plus soffits, and classic front porch lead the way to the impeccably designed interior. Featuring high ceilings and white oak floors, the two bedrooms, two bath floorplan offers style and spaciousness. Kitchen showcases custom gray cabinetry with under lighting, matching quartz counters, matte black fixtures, and stainless appliances. Sliding glass doors lead you to your own private deck and backyard, and also feature access to the quintessential front porch, perfect for watching the world go by. Black half-wall wainscotting offers timeless appeal in the primary ensuite, while bathrooms boast floor to ceiling tile, natural wood vanities and extras like a shower nook and bronze or black fixtures.  Nestled in a sweet spot of Jersey City Heights, owners enjoy nearby Pershing Field Park with swimming pool, tennis courts, sports facilities and more. Also within walking distance is bustling Central Avenue with shops, cafes and restaurants, and the 2nd Street stairs with direct access to Hoboken and Lightrail Station. The Heights is known for its tight-knit community, excellent parks, great schools and easy NYC access."
220007030,SOLD,"JC, Heights",974 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,1052,1744,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,4th,407,"JC, Heights",07307,2801,5.01,,,,,,2,0,2,4,,"$650,000","$650,000",$617.87,$617.87,4/21/2022,5/26/2022,6/21/2022,35,35,,6/22/2022,,,,"$5,888",2021,$412,2021,Cash,,,,,,Summit Ave & Lincoln St,"Welcome home to this beautiful duplex unit located in the sought after neighborhood of Jersey City Heights. This stunning 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom is only two years young and it features a spacious living area flooded with natural light on the penthouse level, stainless steel appliances, abundant of floor to ceiling kitchen cabinets, and additional closets outside the bedrooms, Nest thermostat and Nest Yale locking system, central a/c as well as a washer/dryer in the unit. Enjoy the views of New York City and invite friends for an incredible rooftop gatherings watching the sunset on the most beautiful views of Manhattan while out of the oversized shared rooftop deck. No need to order a new Peloton as you find it at this perfect size gym on the second floor. Parking #21 is included with the purchase. This building is equipped with elevator, gym and parking. Indulge in the brand new restaurants and pubs opening up within walking distance to you along with more shopping, parks and the local pool. Come fall in love with your future home today!"
220020561,SOLD,"JC, Heights",3316 KENNEDY BLVD,Condominium,1050,1702,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,201,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,Sherman Place,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$650,000","$729,900",$619.05,$619.05,11/24/2022,11/22/2022,12/29/2022,0,0,,1/4/2023,,,,$0,,$431,,Conventional,,,,,,Manhattan Ave/ Sherman Place,"SELLER Pays 3 YEARS HOA or $15,000 in Buyers Closing Costs *Inquire for details*close this year. Must visit-SHERMAN PLACE this weekend. New, ground up construction, 14-unit luxury condos. One-of-a-kind, corner location, New York City skyline, Park & River views. Panoramic rooftop deck, indoor bike storage, tech-savvy homes, elevator, professional property management, package room. DEEDED indoor parking available for purchase. Vented-out kitchen and laundry, quartz counters, top of the line materials, built for modern living. Convenient to all, Central Ave-Restaurant Row, CitiBike rental station, Journal Square PATH/NYC bus at your door.  Multiple floor plans range from 1,000-2,200 Sq ft. Tax abatement, 2-10 Builders Home Warranty. Reach out for Private showings all week."
220019263,SOLD,"JC, Heights",3316 KENNEDY BLVD,Condominium,1050,1702,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,3rd,301,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,Sherman Place,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$650,000","$699,900",$619.05,$619.05,11/1/2022,11/23/2022,12/28/2022,22,22,,2/23/2023,,,,$0,,$431,,Conventional,,,,,,Manhattan Ave/ Sherman Place,"NEW CONSTRUCTION, SELLER PAYS 3 YEARS HOA OR $15,000 in BUYERS CLOSING COSTS*Inquire for more details. SHERMAN PLACE Open House this weekend. Saturday & Sunday, Jersey City new condos for sale with DEEDED parking. 14-unit, ground up NEW construction, layouts range from 1,000-2,200 square ft. homes. Professionally managed, elevator, garage parking available for purchase. Panoramic NYC views, rooftop deck with lounge seating, secure package room, virtual doorman & indoor bike storage. Low monthly HOA, 5 yr. Tax abatement, 2-10 yr. builder warranty. Across from acres of open-green space,  near Central Ave/JSQ. All transportation options, CitiBike station at your door.  Unit 301, amazing views for days, 2 private Juliet balconies, 2 bedroom, 2 full baths, quartz counters, storage & walk-in closet, tankless water-heater, vented-out kitchen appliances/ vented-out laundry.  Tech savvy home, built for modern-quiet-living with soundproofing. The property is Not In a Flood Zone  where Flood Insurance is Not Required."
250020904,SOLD,"JC, Heights",21 CONCORD ST,Condominium,1147,5164,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,2nd,2,"JC, Heights",07306,6805,13,,,,,,3,0,2,5,,"$650,000","$639,000",$566.70,$566.70,10/9/2025,11/1/2025,12/19/2025,23,23,,12/20/2025,,"$518,900",2024,"$11,660",2023,$176,,Conventional,,,,,,Rt 139 & Fleet St,"Discover this beautifully renovated three-bedroom, two-bathroom condominium in the desirable Heights neighborhood of Jersey City. Spanning over 1,100 square feet, this second-floor residence in an intimate two-unit building offers the ideal alternative for those seeking to escape Manhattan and Brooklyn's premium pricing without sacrificing accessibility or quality of life. Step inside to find a completely refreshed interior with contemporary finishes throughout. Climate control is effortless year-round thanks to the central HVAC system with smart thermostat technology, maximizing energy efficiency while keeping utility costs predictable. The kitchen features smart appliances, while the in-unit full-size washer and dryer eliminates laundromats and shared facilities. With two full bathrooms and three generous bedrooms, there's ample space for remote work, guests, or simply spreading out in comfort. Location is where this home truly shines for the NYC commuter. Journal Square PATH station is just moments away, providing direct access to Manhattan's World Trade Center. Palisade Avenue and Central Avenue bus routes offer additional convenient options to reach Midtown and Downtown Manhattan, giving you back precious hours in your week. Yet despite this exceptional connectivity, 21 Concord Street offers a peaceful retreat on a quiet, tree-lined street. You'll experience a genuine neighborhood feel that's increasingly rare in the metro area while building equity and enjoying more space at lower monthly costs. This is Jersey City living at its finest—where smart location meets thoughtful renovation, and where your housing dollar simply goes further."
240024003,SOLD,"JC, Heights",98 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,992,1597,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$650,000","$660,000",$655.24,$655.24,12/18/2024,1/17/2025,3/7/2025,30,30,,3/7/2025,,,,,,$239,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"Step into this brand-new, thoughtfully designed two bedroom, two bath home in vibrant Jersey City Heights. Set on a corner lot with a beautiful red brick exterior, light streams into the spacious open-concept floor plan showcasing modern finishes and wide plank hardwood floors. Oversized windows showcase the eat-in kitchen, finished with modern black and natural light oak custom cabinetry, white quartz waterfall countertops plus matching backsplash. Premium Bertazzoni appliances add additional quality and sophistication, making the ideal space for budding chefs or entertaining.  The primary ensuite bathroom brings sophistication with luxury finishes like floor-to-ceiling picket pattern tile, accented by elegant gold trim and a glass-enclosed shower featuring a multi-spray system and rain head. Finally, ample closet space and a separate utility room with brand new washer and dryer provide added convenience and storage.  Located just one block from popular cafés and restaurants like Froth on Franklin and The Franklin, the heart of The Heights is at your doorstep. Owners can easily access the 2nd Street stairs to Hoboken for Lightrail, PATH and ferry for a quick trip to NYC. Jersey City Heights is known for its vibrant community, excellent parks and schools, stunning NYC skyline views and easy access to surrounding neighborhoods."
230011440,SOLD,"JC, Heights",269 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1122,1597,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,4,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$650,000","$650,000",$579.32,$579.32,7/10/2023,7/10/2023,7/10/2023,0,0,,7/10/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith & Franklin St,"Modern and move-in ready, this newly renovated ground floor two-bedroom with private backyard is perfectly positioned on desirable Ogden Avenue in the Heights. Modern design brings artistry and spaciousness with wide plank oak floors, clean lines and open floorplan.   Kitchen commands presence with sleek custom cabinetry, gleaming quartz counters and backsplash, and stainless appliances. Split floorplan offers bedrooms on either end of the living space, while elegant bathroom brings creamy porcelain tile & soaker tub. Bedrooms offer wide doorways while extra large windows allow lots of natural light. Large backyard is finished with pavers, landscaping and lawn for ideal outdoor living.   Beautiful brick building offers secure entrance on a tree-lined street less than one block to nearby Riverview Fisk Park with breathtaking NYC views or 9th Street Lightrail Station for Hoboken and NYC access. Jersey City Heights is known for its artisan shops and restaurants, close-knit community, excellent parks and schools."
220002568,SOLD,"JC, Heights",42 PROSPECT ST,Condominium,1457,1598,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,1+2,1D,"JC, Heights",07307,05801,00030,Heights,The Juliette,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$650,000","$650,000",$446.12,$446.12,2/14/2022,3/23/2022,10/17/2022,37,37,,5/17/2022,,,,"$7,566",2021,$470,2022,Conventional,,,,,,Baldwin Ave & Palisade Ave,"Exquisite 3 bedroom duplex with 2 full baths, a bonus room and a private deeded backyard. This charming residence offers two levels of spacious living with high ceilings and hardwood floors throughout. The living area is bright and open with an exposed brick wall. The kitchen is updated with new custom cabinets, new fridge, new dishwasher, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Home boasts Central Air, NEST thermostat and lock, new in-unit washer/dryer, new custom closets, recessed lighting, plenty of storage and an updated private outdoor oasis. All of this is conveniently located in the heart of Jersey City Heights & is close to restaurants, shopping, playgrounds, parks & transportation. Light rail & PATH are minutes away & buses with direct routes to NYC & Hoboken are easily accessible along Palisade Avenue. Parking is available for rent nearby. Truly a wonderful place to call home!"
240003167,SOLD,"JC, Heights",65 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1356,1713,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,04501,00034,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$650,000","$635,000",$479.35,$479.35,2/20/2024,3/6/2024,4/30/2024,15,15,,5/2/2024,,,,"$9,164",,$471,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin and Ferry,"Introducing this bright and spacious 1356 sq ft, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom unit located in the highly sought-after Riverview Arts District of Jersey City Heights. This beautiful unit boasts natural light floods through large windows, highlighting the exposed brick walls and crown molding, creating an ambiance of timeless elegance. The wide-plank hardwood Brazilian floors exude warmth and character, perfectly complementing the tasteful design choices throughout. A full-size in-unit washer and dryer, as well as central heating and air conditioning add to modern comfort with classic charm. The heart of this home is the full modern kitchen, thoughtfully appointed with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher. The granite countertops and breakfast bar provide ample space for culinary creations and entertaining guests. Storage is never a concern in this remarkable residence. With two walk-in closets and two additional closets you'll have room for all your belongings. Furthermore, a wide-open shared basement presents additional storage possibilities, ensuring an organized and clutter-free living environment. Retreat to the primary bedroom, a serene sanctuary boasting a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom complete with a luxurious jacuzzi tub/shower combination. This private oasis offers the perfect respite from the demands of daily life. Convenience and accessibility are key features of this exceptional home. Just moments away, you'll find two beautiful parks, Riverview Park and Pershing Field Park, offering lush green spaces and recreational opportunities. The proximity to the renowned 100 Steps ensures effortless access to Hoboken and the Light Rail, simplifying your daily commute. Located between Central Ave and Palisades Ave, you'll enjoy an abundance of public transportation options, trendy shops, delectable dining establishments, and a vibrant nightlife scene. Don't miss this rare opportunity. Schedule your private showing today! Taxes are $6941/year."
250012820,SOLD,"JC, Heights",35 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1495,6078,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,G&1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,4402,13,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,8,,"$650,000","$650,000",$434.78,$434.78,6/24/2025,7/1/2025,8/28/2025,7,7,,8/30/2025,,,,"$11,839",24,$336,,Conventional,,,,,,Central & Sherman Ave,"TWO LEVELS OF COMPLETE BLISS w/PRIVATE BACKYARD. Indulge in elevated living with this impeccably renovated three-bedroom plus den, three-bathroom condominium, completed in 2022 with a full scale, modern transformation. Situated in the coveted Jersey City Heights, this residence seamlessly blends contemporary design with thoughtful functionality. Upon entry, the parlor level unveils a grand, open concept living space with soaring 10foot ceilings. The chef’s kitchen is outfitted with premium Bosch appliances, quartz countertops, and a built-in breakfast nook - ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. This level also features a spacious guest bedroom, a full guest bathroom, and a serene primary suite with direct access to a beautifully landscaped private backyard. The lower level offers exceptional flexibility with a generously sized recreation/family room, a spa-inspired full bathroom, an additional bedroom, a private office/den, and laundry room. Ideally located just moments from parks, top-rated restaurants, schools, and boutique shops, and with seamless access to New York City via NJ Transit, this home offers a rare blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience."
210025917,SOLD,"JC, Heights",108 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1163,6078,"$650,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,301,"JC, Heights",07307-1311,5202,22,,,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$650,000","$700,000",$558.90,$558.90,11/18/2021,3/19/2022,5/16/2022,121,121,,5/24/2022,,,,"$4,950",2021,$332,,Private,,,,,,Ogden Ave & Cuneo Pl,"Newly upgraded 2 BD/ 2 BATHS duplex with two private outdoor spaces for incredible downtown Jersey City, Hudson River and NYC skyline views. Brownstone style building on the best side of Ogden St, the Southeast facing unit with abundance of light, luxury and location. Hardwood floors throughout, pendant lighting, and a distinctive spiral staircase, plus fundamental upgrades like all new electric replaced within the last year. Open floorplan living area. Newly upgraded eat-in kitchen features gorgeous Carrara marble backsplash & waterfall counters, shaker cabinets with crown molding, and high-end modern appliances like a smart faucet, wine fridge and brand new garbage disposal. Primary bedroom features sliding glass doors and oversized windows leading to extra large balcony perfect for lounge area or urban gardening. The spacious secondary bedroom features double closets and light streaming from the bay window. Bathroom brings both function and luxury with soaker tub and glass shower, plus heated towel rack and double-wide mirrors. Located directly across from Janet Moore Park with playground and gorgeous grounds with a view, Jersey City Heights offers walkability to essential shops, excellent schools and easy Hoboken and NYC access. There's nearby parking available for $150/ month."
210012430,SOLD,"JC, Heights",258 HUTTON ST,Condominium,2321,1419,"$652,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,3406,28,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$652,000","$699,000",$280.91,$280.91,5/21/2021,6/21/2021,9/16/2021,31,30,,9/16/2021,,,,$0,2021,$0,2021,Conventional,,,,,,Liberty Ave & JFK Blvd,"Spacious 3 bedroom and 3 bathroom duplex unit is located right in the desirable Jersey City Heights! With hardwood floors throughout, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a great amount of space on the lower level, this home leaves with you endless opportunity. The peaceful private backyard is the perfect place to relax or gather with friends! Conveniently located if you need to commute with bus stops around the corner and the Journal Square PATH nearby.  One car parking space included."
240003219,SOLD,"JC, Heights",172 SOUTH ST,Condominium,1008,1597,"$655,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,2103,20,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$655,000","$649,000",$649.80,$649.80,2/21/2024,2/28/2024,4/30/2024,7,7,,4/30/2024,,,,"$9,960",2023,$386,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & Pierce,"Conveniently located one block from the burgeoning Central Avenue lined with shops, cafes and restaurants, this South facing 3 bedroom, 2 bath is flooded with natural light featuring high ceilings, in-unit washer/dryer, central A/C, plentiful storage and a large private balcony. Perfect for entertaining, the open concept living area includes a kitchen with stainless-steel appliances, custom cabinetry, breakfast bar and quartz countertops that overlooks the incredibly spacious living room and dining area with beautiful bay windows. The first bedroom (currently used as office) can fit a queen or king bed and the second bedroom (currently used as dressing room) can fit a full bed or used as an office. Both bedrooms have amazing closet space. The guest bathroom with bathtub is located across the hall. The sizable primary bedroom features an en-suite bathroom with walk-in shower, walk-in closet with built-ins and leads to your large private balcony. Enjoy easy access to bus service to NYC from both Summit and Central Avenues and walking distance to the beloved Washington Park with playgrounds, sports fields and dog runs, and Riverview Park with its panoramic views of NYC and farmer’s markets."
230012836,SOLD,"JC, Heights",70 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,1350,283,"$655,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,4,"JC, Heights",07307,03602,00042,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$655,000","$569,000",$485.19,$485.19,8/2/2023,8/9/2023,10/16/2023,7,7,,10/18/2023,,,,"$13,906",2022,$360,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave & Sanford Pl,"Welcome to 70 Sherman Place, where history meets modernity in Jersey City Heights. With over 1300 sqft of living space, Unit #4 boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, with an open living/dining area. You'll find top-notch stainless steel appliances, including a gas-range oven, a refrigerator equipped with an Android Tablet, a microwave, and a dishwasher.  Embrace the comfort of a tankless water heater and enjoy the convenience of a dedicated laundry room featuring heated flooring. This unit is partially attached at the rear, with a separate entrance and direct access to a private outdoor space. The condo comes with the convenience of deeded basement storage and 1 car parking. Close to major commutes, shopping, schools, and parks. Don't miss the chance to call this historic treasure your new home! (For showings, advance 24hr notice Please) "
240011527,SOLD,"JC, Heights",108 BOORAEM AVE,Condominium,995,1598,"$655,000",CONDO-COOP,,3RD,3R,"JC, Heights",07307,4401,32,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$655,000","$660,000",$658.29,$658.29,6/15/2024,7/22/2024,10/7/2024,37,38,,10/8/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,LIENAU AND ABBETT,"Stunning, High-End Renovation, on a Desirable, Picturesque Block with a Private 227 sq.ft. Roof Deck!  This 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home is an amazing value and offers a highly functional layout, vaulted ceilings, hardwood floors throughout, multi-zoned HVAC, in unit W/D, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops and custom double height cabinets for amble storage.  Located on the extremely sought after Booraem Avenue, where you're literally blocks away from shopping, restaurants, NYC transportation, parks, schools and so much more.  These homes will not last on the market long, so schedule your private viewing!  Fyi photos may be of similar unit in the building."
240013804,SOLD,"JC, Heights",441 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1254,6078,"$655,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03902,00023,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$655,000","$645,000",$522.33,$522.33,7/16/2024,7/22/2024,8/15/2024,6,6,,8/15/2024,,,,"$8,446",2022,$350,,Cash,No,No,No,,,GRIFFITH AND HUTTON,"Welcome home to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath unit in the heart of Jersey City's hottest area, the Heights. 441 Palisade ave unit 2 spans the entire floor of open concept living. Newly refinished hardwood floors and freshly painted so all you have to do it move in. With one bedroom in the front and 2 bedrooms in the back, you'll love this huge 1254 sq ft layout. The kitchen is spacious and updated with oak cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and stylish subway tile. The Primary bedroom has an ensuite bathroom & walk in closet. Outdoor spaces are abundant, a terrace in the front, a deck off the primary bedroom and a huge shared backyard with only 2 other units. Other highlights; updated bathrooms, laundry room, ceiling fans in all rooms, nice closet space, and only 1 floor up. Don't miss your chance to owner occupy or use this as a great investment property."
220001696,SOLD,"JC, Heights",580 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1038,1692,"$657,500",CONDO-COOP,,3,301,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,The Riveview,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$657,500","$657,500",$633.43,$633.43,1/29/2022,2/11/2022,6/7/2022,13,12,,6/20/2022,,,,,,$343,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress and South,"Step inside and immediately feel at ease in this unit. BRAND NEW GROUND UP CONSTRUCTION at The Riverview offers impeccable comfort and convenience, situated on Palisade Avenue, at the heart of the neighborhood’s exciting retail/dining corridor. Choose from two- and three-bedroom residences in this intimate 13-unit building, crafted to meet your every need. The well-proportioned units are carefully constructed with today’s most in-demand elements. Flow-through rooms and thoughtful appointments combine for luxurious comfort. Expansive energy-efficient insulated windows frame the interiors with abundant natural light. Elegant top-line finishes include wide plank flooring, granite countertops and premium Fischer-Paykel appliances. Thoughtfully curated amenities bring ease to today’s busy lifestyles. A package room, 12-car parking garage with electric chargers and ground-level bike storage are among the building’s many essential comforts designed to enhance your lifestyle. Make this inspired collection of pet-friendly condominiums home. 10-year New Home Warranty, Manufacturer’s Warranty on all appliances and systems, and tax abatement. Photos are of model unit."
220009737,SOLD,"JC, Heights",113 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1259,298,"$660,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$660,000","$699,000",$524.23,$524.23,5/31/2022,8/24/2022,10/20/2022,85,85,,10/24/2022,,,,"$7,570",21,,,Conventional,,,,,,SUMMIT AND JFK,"Beautifully crafted unit located in the heart of JC Heights. This lux unit offers 3 bedrooms/2 full baths single floor unit. You will find modern finishes, high-end appliances, and hardwood floors through out. The chef’s kitchen is spacious and really compliments the open concept feel of the unit. Custom trim work, custom closets, Laundry room, ample storage space and a shared driveway compliment all the features this property has to offer. Being centrally located you're a near all that the booming Jersey City Heights has to offer.  Come see today! Please visit http://sites.visionnj.com/113zabriskiestreetunit2 for video walk through, 3D tour and floor plan"
210026477,SOLD,"JC, Heights",33 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,1158,1653,"$660,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3701,17,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,5,,"$660,000","$679,000",$569.95,$569.95,12/2/2021,2/28/2022,4/4/2022,88,88,,4/5/2022,,,,"$5,464",,$175,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central & Summit Ave,"Welcome to the Condos at 33 Sherman Place! Originally built in the 1860’s on one of the most coveted and historic blocks in Jersey City. Come home to Unit 2 which offers 1,158 sf 3 bedroom 2 bath offers open concept living, soaring 10 feet high ceilings and a “FLEX” room. This kitchen also features 42 inch white shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, herringbone marble backsplash, and ss appliance package, a wine cooler, and an oversized pantry room. Bathrooms are designed w/floor to ceiling tiles, Kohler fixtures, white shaker vanities with quartz countertops. Private 600 sft rooftop w/ dual seating areas and stunning NYC views. The unit also comes with a tankless on-demand water heater. Unit features 5 inch espresso hardwood floors throughout, LED lighting, Anderson windows, NEST controlled central A/C & central heat, and laundry rooms. A custom designed under the stairs “pet suite” was created in each unit. Jersey City Heights exemplifies convenient, commuter friendly living in a timeless charming neighborhood! *virtually staged photos"
220014027,SOLD,"JC, Heights",199 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,1350,6078,"$660,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$660,000","$649,000",$488.89,$488.89,8/2/2022,8/15/2022,10/24/2022,13,13,,10/25/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,off lincoln,"Brand NEW CONSTRUCTION with 5 Year Tax Abatement.  Residence 2 features a stunning open concept living with wide plank oak flooring throughout & large private rooftop deck for entertaining. Enjoy 13+ ft soaring high ceilings in your living room with built-in surround sound ceiling speakers & plenty of day time light from the premier quality Anderson 400 series oversized windows & skylights. Enjoy cooking in your chef’s kitchen equipped with European style custom cabinetry , Calacatta Belo Quartz Counter tops with waterfall edge & matching backsplash. The Samsung appliance package includes a 5 burner range, French door refrigerator, & 29 bottle built-in wine cooler. Spacious bedrooms offer plenty of closet space, with the primary en-suite featuring double glass doors to the private balcony. Beautifully designed bathrooms feature Porcelanosa tiles, fixtures & vanities This home is also integrated with the latest smart technology including touch screen security system, outdoor cameras, video intercom & outdoor speakers. Last, but not least desirable 1 tandem parking spot included! 199 Lincoln St. is conveniently situated minutes from transportation to and from NYC, local parks & nearby restaurants. Included is a 5 year tax abatement! Come take a tour of this beautiful property today!"
210000132,SOLD,"JC, Heights",289 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,,1691,"$665,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,1,2,6,,"$665,000","$665,000",,,1/4/2021,1/21/2021,3/19/2021,17,17,,4/1/2021,,,,,,$217,,Conventional,,,,,,South St and Congress St,"Leave it to Webster to define a new design norm. The fully renovated 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom duplex with generous bonus room and private backyard sparkles with modern style and high-end finishes in this sought-after Heights location.  Interior elements like the 5.25” maple flooring throughout, 9.5’ ceilings, 8’ doors and Pella windows open the space and bring unique texture and warmth. Kitchen impresses with Italian cabinets and quartz countertops, plus Bosch 800 appliances and a must-have wine fridge. Bathrooms feature excellent Hans Grohe fixtures and design choices like concrete patterned accent walls and floating vanities. Smart home tech includes Nest thermostat, Ai phone video intercom, and Schlage keyless entry and hardware.   Positioned in a sweet spot within Jersey City Heights, these homes are 2 blocks from Congress Street Light Rail, 22-acre Washington Park, and a few local favorites like Fox & Crow and The Cliff."
250021684,SOLD,"JC, Heights",145 BLEECKER ST,Condominium,1350,6078,"$665,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2005,3,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$665,000","$699,000",$492.59,$492.59,10/20/2025,2/15/2026,4/6/2026,118,118,,4/6/2026,,"$375,300",2024,"$8,433",2023,$150,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy & Columbia,"A rare Heights offering on a quiet street featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, soaring 20+ ft ceilings with dramatic skylights, exceptional natural light, and abundant storage. Immaculately maintained with only one owner since built, this home includes a private balcony, parking for two cars (garage + driveway), a dedicated, spacious laundry closet with washer and dryer, attic storage, and two large private storage closets in the garage. Skylights in both the living room and second bathroom enhance the bright, airy feel throughout. Conveniently located with a bus stop less than one minute away offering direct access to Journal Square PATH and Manhattan-bound buses. A true standout, this top-floor condo combines space, light, storage, and seamless NYC access in the heart of the Heights."
210024100,SOLD,"JC, Heights",201 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1113,1685,"$667,500",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03805,00019,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$667,500","$699,000",$599.73,$599.73,10/21/2021,12/6/2021,2/10/2022,46,46,,2/11/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton St. & Griffith St.,"New Construction luxury at its finest. This elegant open floor plan features 9 ft ceiling, semi- custom kitchen with floating shelves, along with beautiful gold brass finishes and a beautiful waterfall quartz countertop, along with the appliances that feature GE Profile 30” smart slide in range, Sharp Stainless Steel Microwave Draw oven, GE Profile Counter Depth fingerprint resistant French Door Refrigerator, GE Profile Dishwasher. Walk into your efficient bedrooms featuring Custom made closets designed by “Closets by Design”, Master bathroom with sleek matte black bathroom hardware, Hexagon polished Marble with Mosaic backsplash tiles, frameless glass shower door. The apartment is ready to go “smart home”, wired with interior speakers in the master bath & living room areas, network and cable installation, Honeywell security system that communicates & notifies authorities if alarm is set off and Video intercom accessible through your phone & system. Builder took extra step for noise reduction & sound attenuation between apartments by adding Resilient J channels, purple sound break sheetrock & Serenity mat under hardwood floors, easy commute to NYC and Hoboken via 9th/Congress, 2nd Street light rail, quick bus ride, or a quick 10-minute walk. You'll love being seconds from all the best restaurants and shops that the Riverview Arts District has to offer. Riverview-Fisk Park undergoing a $2M renovation. Come see what this thriving neighborhood has to offer. **5-year tax abatement as per Jersey City Tax assessor, subject to sales price**Images are renderings. This spacious 3 bedrooms/2 full bath features wide planked select oak floors with natural finish throughout, an exclusive private outdoor deck approx. 68 sq ft that opens from the suite master bedroom."
210025267,SOLD,"JC, Heights",179 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,1725,298,"$670,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02504,00019,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$670,000","$699,000",$388.41,$388.41,11/8/2021,12/7/2021,1/20/2022,29,29,,1/21/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy Blvd & Milton Ave,"Craftsmanship and attention to detail is what you will find with this freshly refinished 2-unit building primely located in Jersey City Heights. Unit 1 is a spacious 3 bedroom 3 bathroom with a rec room and private backyard.  This unit also offers a private driveway and garage. Interior boasts 10' ceilings with clean and modern finishes. Kitchens will impress with clean white custom cabinets with matte black hardware, white quartz counters and backsplash. High end appliances and a wine fridge finish off this perfect kitchen.  The Bathrooms, wow with large showers, modern finishes and a spa-like feel. Windows give impeccable natural light, and the basement which also serves as a rec room with a full bathroom is the perfect place to entertain.  while the private backyard provides excellent outdoor escape. Nestled on a quiet dead end street in the Western Slope of the Heights, you have easy access to the highway and transportation to the city.  Come see for yourself."
260000945,SOLD,"JC, Heights",391 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1144,1623,"$670,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,202,"JC, Heights",07307,3901,24.01,Heights,Gallery Lofts,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$670,000","$675,000",$585.66,$585.66,9/19/2025,1/21/2026,3/17/2026,124,1,,3/20/2026,,,,"$9,439",,$530,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin St. & Hutton St.,"Welcome home to Gallery Lofts, a boutique 16 unit concrete and steel construction condo building built in 2020 and located in Jersey City Heights. Unit #202 is a 2 bed, 2 bath home with its own private terrace. This home is outfitted with timeless selections that have a touch of European flair: Bertazzoni appliances, porcelain slab countertops, Imported porcelain tile, Mittel Cucine cabinets imported from Italy, and Kohler fixtures. The spacious living area opens to a quiet private terrace which looks out to a green roof. Both bedrooms are extremely spacious and the primary has a massive walk-in closet with tons of organizational potential. Located on prime Palisade Avenue in the Heights, Gallery Lofts is perfectly situated footsteps away from local shops, restaurants, cafes, parks and all the conveniences of a vibrant neighborhood. All this while still having easy access to the city via public transit. *Photos are virtually staged."
