220000030,SOLD,"JC, Heights",287 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1630,1691,"$690,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1A,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,1,2,7,,"$690,000","$699,000",$423.31,$423.31,1/2/2022,1/12/2022,3/1/2022,10,10,,3/1/2022,,,,,,$286,,Conventional,,,,,,South St and Congress,"Stately and palatial on the outside, luminous and modern on the inside, this freshly refinished 3-unit building is perfectly positioned in Jersey City Heights just blocks to Central Avenue, Washington Park and Riverview Fisk Park. This spacious 2 bedroom 2.5 bathroom duplex offers additional bonus flex room, private storage and private backyard.   Interior elements like soaring 10' ceilings with exposed industrial elements combine with wide plank white maple flooring and large bay windows to create a design-lovers dream. Kitchens impress clean white custom cabinets with matte black hardware, sparkling white quartz counters and island, grey tile backsplash and eye-popping pendant lighting. Bathrooms wow with carrera marble tile from top to bottom, white floating vanities, shower niche and super sleek design. Oversized windows give impeccable natural light, while the large private backyard provides excellent outdoor escape.  Positioned in a sweet spot within Jersey City Heights, these homes are nestled into a tree lined street steps away from Congress Street Light Rail, 22-acre Washington Park, cityscape views of Riverview Fisk and a few local favorites like Fox & Crow and The Cliff.  "
230005929,SOLD,"JC, Heights",3568 KENNEDY BLVD,Condominium,1360,6199,"$690,000",CONDO-COOP,,G,Ground,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$690,000","$699,000",$507.35,$507.35,4/13/2023,5/25/2023,7/10/2023,42,42,,7/10/2023,,,,,,$207,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Graham St & Congress St.,"SPECIAL LOW INTEREST RATE FROM MID 5%’s PROGRAM AVAILABLE, NO PMI, LOW DOWNPAYMENT, & ELIGIBLE FOR GRANT! Rare opportunity, perfect for an entrepreneur to own a luxury urban chic, one of a kind live/work space with its own separate commercial entrance! This unique workspace equipped with its own ½ bathroom and storage closet can be reimagined as a storefront, business office, boutique, or even could be used as a 3rd bedroom. This Unit is Another Signature Luxury brand new Construction by Blue Chip Living from the pages of Architectural Digest to the heart of booming Jersey City Heights, a business district, residential area, and transportation hub. Open your private entry door to this captivating condo featuring 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, open concept living space with LED electric fireplace and oversized Andersen windows that flood the space with natural light. The chef’s kitchen boasts impeccable white high-gloss European Style cabinetry, stainless steel premium smart appliances, modern porcelain backsplash, central island with a waterfall quartz, pot filler, pendant lighting, and drawer microwave. The bedrooms share a spa–like bathroom with matte black hardware, luxurious vanity and 8‘ x 8’ full glass sliding doors leading to your picturesque private yard. Other perks include West Elm lighting, laundry room hook ups, central/heat/air, 8’ solid-core doors, private yard space & designated storage area. Full smart home technology creates ease of living with ButterflyMX Video Intercom System, Nest thermostat, Smart Lighting Dimmer Switches accessible via smart phone.Private Storage Are included. The Property has all major transportation at your fingertips. Maintenance includes cold water, sewer, snow removal, trash removal, common area utilities.  Eligible for 5 yr tax abatement!"
220014047,SOLD,"JC, Heights",199 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,1637,6078,"$694,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,9,,"$694,000","$679,000",$423.95,$423.95,8/2/2022,8/17/2022,10/21/2022,15,15,,10/25/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,OFF LINCOLN,"Brand New Construction with 5 year tax abatement! Residence 1 features a stunning open concept duplex with wide plank oak flooring throughout. Enjoy cooking in your chef’s kitchen equipped with European style custom cabinetry , Calacatta Belo Quartz Countertops with waterfall edge & matching backsplash. The Samsung appliance package includes a 5 burner range, French door refrigerator, & 29 bottle built-in wine cooler. Enjoy movie nights in your living room with recessed lighting, built-in surround sound ceiling speakers & plenty of day time light shining through your oversized Anderson 400 series windows. Spacious bedrooms offer plenty of closet space, with the primary en-suite featuring double glass doors to the private balcony. Beautifully designed bathrooms feature Porcelanosa tiles, fixtures & vanities. Head downstairs to a bonus rec room, ½ bath, & spacious walk out landscaped fenced-in private backyard. This home is also integrated with the latest smart technology including touch screen security system, outdoor cameras, video intercom & outdoor speakers. The home includes 1 tandem garage parking spot! 199 Lincoln St. is conveniently situated minutes from transportation to and from NYC, local parks & nearby restaurants. Come take a tour of this beautiful property today!"
