260005236,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",221 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1200,6267,"$695,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2205,26,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$695,000",$579.17,,3/25/2026,,,15,,,3/25/2026,,,,"$10,063",2025,$195,,,,,,,,South St & Bowers St,"Welcome to the Heights section of Jersey City! Conveniently located near NYC transportation, Hudson-Bergen Light Rail, NJT Bus, Jitney, Waterway Ferry, and Hoboken PATH station and has seasonal views of the Freedom Tower! Boasting about 1,200 square feet, this spacious condo features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The living room offers vaulted ceilings and 2 skylights, providing the open concept layout with great natural light. The living room flows seamlessly into the dining area and then into the kitchen. With custom cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of storage - all of your kitchen needs will be met! The primary bedroom offers a walk-in closet, balcony, and an ensuite with tub shower and storage vanity. There are 2 additional spacious bedrooms and an additional full bathroom with a tub shower. One of the best features is laundry in unit!"
220013309,SOLD,"JC, Heights",347 LIBERTY AVE,Condominium,1300,1702,"$695,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02504,00032,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,5,,"$695,000","$699,000",$534.62,$534.62,7/21/2022,10/20/2022,12/2/2022,91,91,,12/3/2022,,,,,,$214,,Conventional,,,,,,Lincoln St and Zabriskie St,"Brand new premier construction in the Jersey City Heights located just two blocks to Leonard Gordon Park and two blocks from JFK Blvd bus lines to NYC. This spacious PH boasts 1300 interior sq ft of luxury plus private roof top terrace. Spacious great room with vaulted ceilings and several skylights. Across the home enjoy real hardwood floors, dark oil rubbed bronze hardware, recessed lighting, central air conditioning, and custom design lighting fixtures. Superior sound attenuation via Anderson 400 Series windows and double 5/8” sheetrock. Kitchen features contrast gray center island, white quartz countertops and shaker cabinets, gas range, and marbled backsplash. In unit laundry room with LG side by side front loading washer and dryer. Master suite offers walk in closet complete with organization unit, private terrace with sliding glass doors, master bath double sink, full body shower system, and LED backlit mirror. Home includes parking and 5 yr tax abatement."
220011281,SOLD,"JC, Heights",580 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1030,1692,"$695,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,203,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,The Riveview,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$695,000","$695,000",$674.76,$674.76,2/1/2022,2/11/2022,6/25/2022,10,0,,7/11/2022,,,,,,$343,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress and South,"Step inside and immediately feel at ease in this unit. BRAND NEW GROUND UP CONSTRUCTION at The Riverview offers impeccable comfort and convenience, situated on Palisade Avenue, at the heart of the neighborhood’s exciting retail/dining corridor. Choose from two- and three-bedroom residences in this intimate 13-unit building, crafted to meet your every need. The well-proportioned units are carefully constructed with today’s most in-demand elements. Flow-through rooms and thoughtful appointments combine for luxurious comfort. Expansive energy-efficient insulated windows frame the interiors with abundant natural light. Elegant top-line finishes include wide plank flooring, granite countertops and premium Fischer-Paykel appliances. Thoughtfully curated amenities bring ease to today’s busy lifestyles. A package room, 12-car parking garage with electric chargers and ground-level bike storage are among the building’s many essential comforts designed to enhance your lifestyle. Make this inspired collection of pet-friendly condominiums home. 10-year New Home Warranty, Manufacturer’s Warranty on all appliances and systems, and tax abatement. Photos are of model unit."
210018676,SOLD,"JC, Heights",4 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1748,6142,"$695,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07030,4501,1,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$695,000","$700,000",$397.60,$397.60,8/5/2021,8/26/2021,11/4/2021,21,21,,11/5/2021,,,,"$8,694",,$175,,Conventional,,,,,,Corner of Ferry,"Welcome to Jersey City Heights. New Jersey's most exciting revitalized neighborhood, named Expedia's top ten most walkable city in the country. Skip the crowds of Manhattan, and step out to enjoy the exciting cultural scene, without compromising on convenience of course! Sherman Avenue is set atop the Hudson Cliffs, just above Hoboken. Enter 4 Sherman Avenue, a full floor residence in an intimate two family house. Sunlight bathes this home from morning till sunset with exposures on all four sides. Dramatic cathedral ceilings welcome you home as you get ready to entertain in the expansive living, and dining room. A beautiful bright white kitchen with gorgeous sparkling Quartz counters and stainless steel appliances is ready for you to try out a new recipe. Upstairs is a bonus loft currently being used as a play room. Continue down the hallway and you'll find two generous bedrooms, a full bath and the primary suite at the end of the hall with East exposure and a view of downtown Manhattan!  Enjoy all this vibrant neighborhood has to offer, the coffee shops, the parks and the art, and you'll see quickly why Jersey City Heights is beloved by so many. All this plus one car garage is included as well as a private laundry and storage room. Visit this link, by copying and pasting into your browser to experience 4 Sherman Avenue in 3D virtual tour. https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=chrqYtkidY5&mls=1  And then show your friends and family the full movie tour at https://vimeo.com/583665688 **"
240017192,SOLD,"JC, Heights",573 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,931,1603,"$695,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2A,"JC, Heights",07307,02304,00024,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$695,000","$695,000",$746.51,$746.51,9/3/2024,9/12/2024,10/30/2024,9,9,,10/31/2024,,,,$0,,$346,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Congress St & South St,"Welcome to 573 Palisade Avenue, where unparalleled sophistication meets breathtaking views in an exclusive collection of seven condominium homes in a boutique-style elevator building.  Each two-bedroom, two-bathroom condominium home features spacious open floor plans of meticulously designed living space and private outdoor spaces. 10 - 14 ft ceilings soar above engineered hardwood floors, creating an airy sanctuary illuminated by recessed and custom light fixtures. The expansive triple pane Pella windows frame stunning vistas of the Manhattan skyline, inviting you to unwind against a backdrop of urban splendor. Kitchens feature custom 2-toned cabinetry, Samsung stainless steel appliances, Calacatta Laza Quartz countertops, wine cooler and direct vent exhaust hood. Bathrooms include Porcelanosa tiles with Kohler fixtures, deep soaking tubs and dual flush toilets.  You'll love the convenience of having in-home laundry, integrated intercom and security system and a home that is prewired for home automation.  Unwind and socialize on our exclusive residents rooftop lounge offering sweeping NYC views, providing an extraordinary backdrop for relaxation or entertaining guests. This property boasts unparalleled ease of access to New York City, making your commute as breezy as a walk in the adjacent Fisk Park. Whether you prefer the NJ Transit buses or the convenience of the 9th Street-Congress Street Light Rail Station right at your doorstep, your connection to the city has never been smoother. And with breathtaking views of the Manhattan skyline from your window, every day feels like a picturesque escape. This prime Jersey City Heights location offers you not just a home, but a lifestyle."
240000777,SOLD,"JC, Heights",589 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,1500,6706,"$695,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,503,23,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$695,000","$699,999",$463.33,$463.33,1/12/2024,1/29/2024,4/5/2024,17,17,,4/6/2024,,,,$0,,$275,,Conventional,,,,,,Paterson Plank Rd and Leonard St,"Welcome to the 589 Quantum Residences, a newly constructed boutique community of three exquisite homes. Nestled just across the street from the picturesque Washington Park, this is urban living at its finest. Offering breathtaking views of the iconic New York City skyline, and every unit includes private parking. Featuring 3bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms approx. 1500 sq ft, hardwood flooring, Pella windows and doors, solid wood white shaker cabinets, quartz counter tops, stainless steel appliances, Samsung washer and dryer, tankless hot water heater, central air and heat, floor to ceiling porcelain tiles in all bathrooms, crown and base molding throughout, home theater wall and ceiling speakers in living room, custom closet shelving and solid doors. This property draws its inspiration from the legendary Quantum Sound music studio, located only a couple of doors down, where some of the biggest stars of the 80s and 90s, including Madonna, recorded major hits. Moreover, situated on Jersey City Heights' renowned Restaurant Row, Central Ave, very close to award-winning restaurants and shops. Add to that the convenience of extremely quick transportation into NYC, and you have a residence that truly encapsulates the best of city living. Experience luxury, history, Parkside tranquility, and an epicurean paradise all in one exceptional address."
240023637,SOLD,"JC, Heights",404 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1229,1713,"$696,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3903,18,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$696,000","$710,000",$566.31,$566.31,12/11/2024,12/23/2024,2/11/2025,12,12,,2/13/2025,,,,"$10,933",,$235,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton and Griffith,"  Welcome to this beautiful, newly renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Jersey City Heights, one block away from Riverview Park . This condo features a modern kitchen with high-quality finishes - quartz countertops, Samsung stainless steel appliances, and stylish shaker cabinets. The open layout includes a spacious living area with hardwood floors throughout, recessed lighting, and sound insulation between floors for added peace and quiet. The expansive primary bedroom boasts a private balcony, a luxurious updated ensuite bathroom with standing shower, and a walk-in closet with a washer and dryer. Both additional bedrooms have special details like plantation shutters and a cozy reading nook. The second bathroom has upgraded finishes, and a soaking tub. Sellers are able to transfer a rental parking spot nearby."
220008904,SOLD,"JC, Heights",15 NELSON AVE,Condominium,1250,5678,"$696,969",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,01301,00070,Heights,15 Nelson,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$696,969","$699,999",$557.58,$557.58,5/18/2022,6/8/2022,7/18/2022,21,21,,7/19/2022,,,,"$8,037",,$196,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Bleecker and North,"Contemporary 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom condo with 2 CAR PARKING, and an oversized PRIVATE rooftop deck with 360-degree views of NYC, Port Elizabeth, and the Meadowlands! Built by one of Jersey City's premier builders in 2015. Unique & desirable split floorplan with bedrooms on the opposite side for added privacy, an oversized primary bedroom with double closets and an en-suite bathroom, and a bonus finished attic. The condo overflows with plenty of natural light with east/west exposures. Enjoy an open concept living room and kitchen with marble countertops, breakfast bar, SS appliances, and plenty of cabinet space. This condo also features hardwood floors, custom closets, crown molding, a smart-home NEST thermostat/ RING doorbell, central AC/Heat, and an in-unit washer/dryer. This condo has 2 off-street parking spaces (1 tandem garage spot and 1 outdoor spot). Close proximity to direct NYC bus to Port Authority or buses to Journal Square PATH for an easy commute to World Trade Center. Steps away at the end of Congress is the Light Rail. High Walk Score and major amenities nearby; close to 3 schools, near Washington Park, near Central & Palisade shopping, dining, and business district, and more!"
220021457,SOLD,"JC, Heights",84 FERRY ST,Condominium,1327,1597,"$699,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,unit 2,"JC, Heights",07307,04402,00040,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$699,000","$699,000",$526.75,$526.75,12/14/2022,2/2/2023,6/7/2023,50,50,,6/8/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave and Sherman Ave,"Situated in the heart of Jersey City Heights between Central and Sherman Avenue and a stone’s throw to Pershing Field Park, this impeccably designed new boutique condominium residence feature approximately 1300sf of generous indoor living space, 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms and windows on three sides. This sprawling residence is equipped with two serene bathrooms with Porcelanosa tiles and fixtures and a stunning chef’s kitchen featuring custom white cabinets, Samsung appliances, Quartz Calcutta countertop and backsplash, and sizable waterfall peninsula. The sumptuous primary bedroom suite includes a walk-in closet, en-suite bathroom and sliding glass doors. Further, this artfully constructed condominium is furnished with washer and dryer, Central AC & Heat and recessed lighting. Unit #2 has a balcony off the primary suite, picturesque bay windows and hardwood floors throughout. This beautifully proportioned residence is 22ft wide and centrally located convenient to restaurants, shops, markets, public transportations to NYC and parks.   Parking can be secured at St Nicholas Church for a fee."
240006446,SOLD,"JC, Heights",146 NELSON AVE,Condominium,1390,1597,"$699,000",CONDO-COOP,,2&3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,6,,"$699,000","$699,000",$502.88,$502.88,4/8/2024,4/22/2024,8/14/2024,14,14,,8/15/2024,,,,,,$224,,Conventional,,,,,,Grace & Leonard,"Redefine modern comfort and convenience with this newly renovated, two-story home in the Western Slope neighborhood of Jersey City Heights. First impressions are everything with fresh siding, elegant brick accents, and Dutch colonial architecture. Industrial chic design echos throughout the interior with bright white oak flooring, white crown molding and black window trim, and all the modern conveniences.   Beautiful bay windows offer extra natural light, plus super spacious open concept living. In this upstairs unit, owners enjoy high ceilings, plus a two bedroom, den and three full bath layout. Featuring not one, but two private outdoor spaces, indulge in the private terrace off the living room and the secluded roofdeck for skyline city views.  The contemporary kitchen hosts a spacious eat-in island with white waterfall quartz countertops. Finishes include modern gray cabinets including custom touches like wine storage over the refrigerator, brass fixtures and stainless appliances. Bathrooms offer style with beautiful porcelain tile, spacious vanities, bathtub and shower combos and continued brass fixtures.  This home is nestled in the peaceful neighborhood of Western Slope in The Heights, walking distance to Washington Park, 9th Street Lightrail and Hoboken, Central Avenue and more. The Heights is known for its vibrant community, great shops, restaurants and cafes, excellent schools and easy NYC access.  "
260003124,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",134 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1132,1597,"$699,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,,"$699,000",$617.49,,2/23/2026,,,45,,,2/23/2026,,,,,,$309,,,,,,,,Franklin & Ferry,"Designed for both serenity and sophistication, this elevated home offers modern finishes, tree-top views and an unbeatable Heights location just 1 block to 2nd Street stairs and Lightrail station. A hidden haven in the Heights, this beautifully crafted 2 bed, 2 bath residence blends bespoke finishes with semi-private garden access for a rare retreat.   Wide plank floors ground the space, while natural light floods through the floor-to-ceiling windows illuminating the modern finishes and open floorplan. The kitchen offers clean lines and contemporary flair with modern white cabinetry, gleaming quartz countertops, herringbone tile backsplash, sleek brass-accented fixtures and stainless steel appliances.   Both bathrooms are beautifully finished with floor-to-ceiling porcelain tile, herringbone floors, and luxurious rainhead multi-spray shower systems and soaking tub. One bedroom is shielded with privacy glass giving both sunshine and seclusion, while the primary ensuite opens directly to the garden through a full wall of glass, and an effortless flow to the backyard. Top it off with a brand new stacking LG washer and dryer for everyday ease and convenience.   Situated just one block from the 2nd Street Light Rail station, this home not only provides direct access to Hoboken and NYC connections, but also Riverview Fisk and Pershing Field Park and Reservoir. Jersey City Heights is known for its vibrant community, excellent parks and schools, boutique shops and restaurants and close proximity to NYC and surrounding areas."
220019100,SOLD,"JC, Heights",258 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1500,1597,"$699,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,1,2,7,,"$699,000","$699,000",$466.00,$466.00,10/28/2022,1/31/2023,4/12/2023,95,95,,4/12/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,South St & Congress,"Light, bright and modern, this newly finished two bedroom duplex with private backyard is one block to either Washington or Riverview Fisk Park in Jersey City Heights. Elegant design shines with loads of light illuminating hardwood floors and stylish contrasting matte back doors throughout.   Step inside to the kitchen and dining or den upstairs, and continue to the full-floor oversized living area downtstairs. Step out back to your own private backyard finished with patio pavers and lush lawn.   Eat-in kitchen gleams with white quartz counters, exposed shelves, custom cabinets, tile backsplash and stainless appliances. Bedrooms boast ample closet space, while bathrooms host finishes like traditional penny tile shower floors, large vanities and polished chrome fixtures. Home features dedicated laundry area for added convenience.  Ideally located in the heart of The Heights, this home is perfectly positioned walking distance to major thoroughfares, great parks, and easy NYC access. Jersey City Heights is known for its excellent community and parks, great schools, eclectic shops and restaurants, and proximity to surrounding urban areas."
250025668,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",152 BEACH ST,Condominium,1699,1702,"$699,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,04201,00036,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,,"$699,000",$411.42,,9/19/2025,,,202,,,1/1/2026,,,,"$14,673",2024,$218,,,,,,,,Tonnelle Ave & Liberty Ave,"Welcome to 152 Beach Street, Unit 1, in the heart of Jersey City Heights, where contemporary flair harmonizes with cozy comfort, adding a dash of charisma to create your personal retreat. This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom duplex condo is more than just a home; it's a lifestyle.  Step into the expansive chef's kitchen featuring sleek quartz countertops and custom wood cabinetry that could inspire your next masterpiece. Equipped with stainless-steel appliances, cooking becomes a breeze, and you can savor your creations al fresco in your private two-tier backyard.  Venture upstairs to find three inviting bedrooms. The primary suite is a haven of modern luxury, boasting a chic en-suite bathroom with a floating vanity, double sink, and step-in shower, alongside his and her walk-in closets. The two additional bedrooms offer ample space for rest and relaxation, each thoughtfully designed with custom-built closets featuring organizational systems.  The open living area, adorned with Red Oak floors and a charming Juliet balcony, invites abundant sunlight, creating the perfect ambiance for both relaxation and entertaining.  Not to be overlooked, this home is equipped with central air conditioning and heating, an in-unit washer and dryer, and a tandem garage parking spot with extra storage closets. Conveniently situated near parks, local shops, and culinary delights, and with easy access to highways and the Holland Tunnel, your commute will be as smooth as your morning coffee. Welcome home!  "
230019043,SOLD,"JC, Heights",489 LIBERTY AVE,Condominium,1356,1724,"$699,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,01202,00062,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$699,000","$699,000",$515.49,$515.49,11/10/2023,11/25/2023,12/28/2023,15,15,,12/28/2023,,,,,,$250,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Thorne & Bleeker St.,"Welcome to your dream home in one of Jersey City's most sought-after locations, JC Heights/Western Slope! This expansive and gorgeously modern new construction is a 3-bedroom, 2-bath masterpiece that combines luxury and sophistication. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the stunning red oak hardwood flooring that spans the entire home, creating an elegant and timeless atmosphere. Natural light floods the living spaces through large windows, giving the interior a bright and airy feel. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring quartz countertops that blend seamlessly with beautiful blue counters, creating a chic and modern aesthetic. Whether you're entertaining guests or preparing a gourmet meal, this kitchen is sure to impress. All three bedrooms are generously sized, providing ample space for comfort and relaxation. The master bedroom is a true retreat, complete with a master bath for added luxury and a private balcony where you can unwind and enjoy the outdoors in your own oasis. Venture upstairs to discover an expansive roof deck that offers breathtaking views. Imagine entertaining friends or simply soaking in the scenery as you enjoy the fresh air and panoramic vistas. This property is not only a stunning living space but also a wise investment. With a 10-year new homeowner warranty and a 5-year tax abatement, you can enjoy peace of mind and financial benefits. Please note that property taxes are to be independently verified by the Jersey City Tax Office. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this extraordinary home yours. At this fantastic price, this property won't stay on the market for long. Act now and step into the epitome of modern luxury living in the heart of Jersey City!        "
210023675,SOLD,"JC, Heights",281 COLUMBIA AVE,Condominium,2000,6005,"$699,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2-3,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,3,8,,"$699,000","$699,000",$349.50,$349.50,10/14/2021,10/18/2021,1/7/2022,4,4,,2/2/2022,,,,,TBD,,,Conventional,,,,,,NORTH & LEONARD,"Welcome to the western slope section of Jersey City Heights! This new construction triplex condo has 3 levels of luxurious living space, with its very own private rear yard. This unit features 3 bedrooms with 2 Full Baths and 2 Half Baths, Kitchen, living room, dining room, Family Room & a Recreation room. Enjoy the expansive floor plan with over 2000 Sq Ft of living space! Beautiful construction with many high-end extras. Located on a beautiful tree lined street and close to all mass transit. Comes with a 10 yr new homeowner warranty."
220014196,SOLD,"JC, Heights",3568 KENNEDY BLVD,Condominium,1330,6199,"$699,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & 3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,5,,"$699,000","$699,000",$525.56,$525.56,8/4/2022,11/28/2022,2/10/2023,116,116,,2/13/2023,,,,,,$200,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Graham & Congress,"SPECIAL LOW INTEREST RATE FROM MID 5%’s PROGRAM AVAILABLE, NO PMI, LOW DOWNPAYMENT, SAVING THOUSANDS OF DOLLARS: Part of census tract mortgage program which features below market interest rate with 30 year fix option from mid 4%’s.  Featuring Another Signature Luxury brand new Construction by Blue Chip Living from the pages of Architectural Digest to the heart of booming Jersey City Heights , a business district, residential area, and transportation hub. Open your private entry door to this captivating duplex featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms with open concept living space with LED electric fireplace and oversized Andersen windows and 2 balconies. The chef’s kitchen boasts impeccable white high-gloss European Style cabinetry , stainless steel premium smart appliances, pot filler, modern porcelain backsplash, central island with a waterfall quartz, pendant lighting and drawer microwave. The Master bedroom includes an en suite spa–like bathroom with matte black hardware, vanity, an expansive walk–in closet and 8‘ x 8’ full glass sliding doors leading to your picturesque balcony with NYC views. Other perks include West Elm lighting, private storage space, laundry room hook ups, central/heat/air, 8’ solid-core doors, large private roof deck with NYC views. Full smart home technology creates ease of living with ButterflyMX Video Intercom System, Nest thermostat, Smart Lighting Dimmer Switches accessible via smart phone. Private Storage Are included. All major transportation at your fingertips. Make this your Dream Home Oasis today! Maintenance includes cold water, sewer, snow removal, trash removal, common area utilities.  *Eligible for 5 year tax abatement."
220021584,SOLD,"JC, Heights",159 LIBERTY AVE,Condominium,1140,1603,"$699,000",CONDO-COOP,,2&3,2,"JC, Heights",07306,05304,00020,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$699,000","$699,000",$613.16,$613.16,12/16/2022,12/28/2022,2/23/2023,12,12,,2/23/2023,,,,$0,,$0,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Spruce St and Stagg St,"Absolutely stunning ground-up new construction home, developed by Jersey City's highly reputable developers, GN Management. 159 Liberty Avenue is located on a dead end, private street on the Western Slope of Jersey City Heights. This 1140 sf open floor plan, two-story home includes 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and a large private rooftop with sunset views. Home features include white oak hardwood flooring through out, soaring 10' ceilings, 9' solid wood doors with black channels, oversized windows allowing for an abundant of natural lighting, central a/c, laundry on same level of bedrooms, recessed and custom lighting and sleek horizontal black railings. Amazing kitchen with breakfast island, slow closing shaker cabinetry, Quartz countertops, backsplash, stainless steel appliances and pot filler. Stunning baths with designer fittings and finishes including LED mirror lighting and glass enclosed showers. Master bedroom includes ensuite with large closet and second bedroom includes a private terrace. 1 car parking included! This smart home includes built-in audio speakers, smart mirrors and ring doorbell. Located close to Rt 1&9, NJ Turnpike, Holland Tunnel, PATH train and the 125 bus to Port Authority; commuting has never been easier! Only a few short blocks from Pershing Field Park and the Central Ave shopping district as well as JSQ path and shopping district. A neighborhood that needs no introduction, Jersey City Heights has become one of Hudson County's most desirable places to live. 159 Liberty Ave includes a 10-year new home warranty and is eligible for 5-year tax abatement!"
210014108,SOLD,"JC, Heights",366 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1228,6349,"$699,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02404,00014 0001,,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$699,000","$699,000",$569.22,$569.22,6/10/2021,6/18/2021,7/29/2021,8,8,,7/29/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers and South,"LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!!!! Beautifully renovated 2 bedroom 2 bathroom  condo located on the desirable Ogden Ave, Jersey City. This unit has immaculate views of the Manhattan skyline that can be  enjoyed from the first level balcony or lower level private patio. This 2 level condo boasts an open concept floor plan on the first level with updated modern kitchen, stainless steel appliances, living room with double door access to balcony and below patio and washer/dryer!! On the second level you will find the master bedroom with bathroom, two spacious closets and a breathtaking view of NYC to wake up to every morning!! The second level also has another spacious bedroom and second bathroom!! Central air/heat throughout both levels, hardwood floors, plenty of storage space and in a much desirable neighborhood, close to amazing restaurants and transportation! This condo will not last long, book an appointment to see this stunning condo ASAP!!"
230010365,SOLD,"JC, Heights",84 FERRY ST,Condominium,1400,1597,"$700,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1 - GARDEN,"JC, Heights",07307,04402,00040,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$700,000","$699,000",$500.00,$500.00,6/22/2023,6/27/2023,7/31/2023,5,5,,8/1/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave and Sherman Ave,"Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Jersey City Heights! This stunning new boutique condominium residence boasts 1400sf of luxurious indoor living space, featuring 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms and windows on three sides for an abundance of natural light. Impeccably designed with two serene bathrooms adorned with Porcelanosa tiles and fixtures, and a breathtaking chef’s kitchen complete with custom white cabinets, Samsung appliances, Quartz Calcutta countertop and backsplash, and a sizable waterfall peninsula - this is truly a home chef's dream come true.   The sumptuous primary bedroom suite is the perfect retreat, complete with a walk-in closet, en-suite bathroom and french doors. Enjoy the convenience of a washer and dryer, Central AC & Heat and recessed lighting in this artfully constructed condominium. Unit #1 offers the added bonus of a private 27ft backyard, Porcelanosa replica wood tiles throughout and private entry.   This beautifully proportioned residence is 22ft wide and centrally located, offering easy access to the best restaurants, shops, markets, public transportation to NYC and parks. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your forever home!  "
240021523,SOLD,"JC, Heights",380 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1190,1597,"$700,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1A,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$700,000","$699,000",$588.24,$588.24,11/4/2024,12/5/2024,1/31/2025,31,31,,1/31/2025,,,,,,$400,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"Find the ultimate contemporary urban living in the vibrant Heights neighborhood! This newly constructed 3-unit building boasts a secure entrance on a tree-lined street with access to surrounding Hoboken and NYC access. Each unit offers a spacious 3 (or 4!) bedroom layout with private outdoor space, checking all the buyer must-haves.  Unit 1 hosts a private back patio and garden, coupled with a thoughtfully designed split floorplan for ultimate flexibility.   Modern design and upgrades emanate throughout each home, with wide plank light oak floors and carefully curated lighting. White kitchens feature sleek quartz counters, tile backsplash, an eat-in island, sleek custom cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. Bathrooms bring luxury with floor-to-ceiling tile, shower and soaker tub options, sleek vanities and polished chrome fixtures. The dedicated utility/laundry room gives maximum flexibility and convenience in your daily routine, hosting stacking Samsung washer and dryer. Storage is maximized with excellent closet space, including large walk-ins in each primary ensuite.   Situated just one block from Riverview Fisk Park with breathtaking Manhattan views, and the Hoboken stairs leading to the 2nd Street Lightrail, this location is offers the ultimate urban luxury lifestyle. The Heights is known for its vibrant community, excellent parks and schools and easy access to NYC and surrounding neighborhoods."
230020123,SOLD,"JC, Heights",65 FLEET ST,Condominium,1125,1468,"$700,000",CONDO-COOP,,2nd,4,"JC, Heights",07306,06806,00008,,,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$700,000","$719,000",$622.22,$622.22,12/3/2023,12/19/2023,2/1/2024,16,16,,2/2/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Baldwin Ave and Oakland Ave,"This is a gorgeous 2 BR/2full bath condo in pristine condition located in the heart of JSQ with easy access to JSQ PATH train. The unit features crown-moldings, recessed lightings , and an  eat-in breakfast bar counter . The kitchen has custom-made cabinetry, Carrera Marble countertops , S/S appliances and modern subway backsplash. The spacious primary bedroom has enough space for an additional home office/working space and has a walk-in closet as well. The bathrooms features a tub and a glass standing shower. This building is equipped with a fitness room. One garage-parking spot is assigned to the unit."
210001165,SOLD,"JC, Heights",22 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,1500,1691,"$700,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$700,000","$725,000",$466.67,$466.67,1/13/2021,2/1/2021,4/9/2021,19,19,,4/9/2021,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit and Central,"Say hello to thoughtful modern luxury in the Heights. This beautifully renovated 3 bedroom 2.5 bath duplex condominium with full-sized washer dryer room and finished basement (home office/rec room) brings elegance and sophistication to a quiet tree-lined street just off Central Avenue.  Simple, clean design delights upon entry with bright, open floor plan.  Contemporary kitchens impress with custom charcoal grey lower cabinets, clean white uppers and marbled quartz counters. Bathrooms bring interest and enviable design with elements such as floating custom vanities, pocket doors, oversized slab tile and complementary brass and black fixtures.  Master en-suite boasts sliding French doors leading to private balcony (perfect for al fresco coffee or cocktails). Side door leads to a spacious *private* backyard.   Part of a completely renovated 3-unit building, all three homes offer additional storage and ideal walkability to surrounding Central & Palisade Avenue for all essential shopping needs, plus Pershing Field, Washington or Riverview Fisk Parks. The Heights is a thriving community with excellent schools, award-winning restaurants & businesses plus easy NYC access!  Rental parking available nearby!!"
220020859,SOLD,"JC, Heights",218 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1322,1597,"$700,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$700,000","$729,000",$529.50,$529.50,12/1/2022,12/15/2022,2/8/2023,14,14,,2/8/2023,,,,,,$201,,Conventional,,,,,,South St & Congress,"Make your next move to this beautifully renovated home with private rooftop, storage and EV charger parking from Nkay Construction. Set one block from Washington Park in Jersey City Heights, the three bedroom layout is classically finished with crown molding, hardwood floors and large Pella windows.   White kitchen shines with sparkling waterfall quartz counters, stainless farm sink, shaker cabinets, blue accent shiplap, and black Samsung appliances. Smarthome features include ring doorbell, camera and security system, and nest thermostat.   Soak in the scenery with a private rooftop showcasing incredible cityscape views. Bathrooms boast beautiful marble double vanity, glass shower or bathtub combo and polished chrome fixtures. Owners enjoy a dedicated utility area with Samsung washer and dryer, plus private basement storage area and side-by-side, EV charger, compact car parking.  Modern gray brick building is settled on a tree-lined street just around the corner from expansive Washington Park with sports facilities, playground and walking paths. Jersey City Heights is known for its great community, excellent schools and easy NYC access, with vibrant shops, restaurants and parks!   "
210005621,SOLD,"JC, Heights",88 THORNE ST,Condominium,1323,6467,"$700,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,88 Thorne,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$700,000","$715,000",$529.10,$529.10,3/9/2021,3/24/2021,6/2/2021,15,15,,7/21/2021,,,,,,$132,2021,Conventional,,,,,,summit,"Sun-lit and elegantly designed, 88 Thorne Street is a modern new building located in the heart of JC Heights. With 1,323 SF, this home features three-bedrooms, two bathrooms, a private rooftop terrace, and one deeded parking spot in the building’s garage.   This expansive home features an open and flexible layout, a generously proportioned living space, oversized windows, a modern kitchen, ample closet space, recessed lighting, central A/C, in-unit laundry, and hardwood flooring. The windows face east and west, maximizing the sense of space by bringing the outdoors in and providing natural light throughout the day. Beautiful custom designed and fitted shades have been installed in every window of this home.   The kitchen includes custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, subway tile backsplash, a smart fridge, and state-of-the-art stainless-steel appliances. The sleek kitchen is designed for entertaining and flows seamlessly into the spacious living and dining area. The primary bedroom offers a large custom walk-in closet, spacious balcony, and a beautifully designed spa-like en-suite bathroom.   This pet-friendly smart-home completed construction in January 2020.   The stunning private rooftop captures coveted unobstructed New York City views from the Empire State building to One World Trade.    Proximity to restaurants, shopping, and both Leonard Gordon and Washington Park make this an ideal home. "
210010512,SOLD,"JC, Heights",22 THORNE ST,Condominium,1500,1691,"$700,000",CONDO-COOP,,"2, 3",2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$700,000","$699,000",$466.67,$466.67,5/3/2021,5/18/2021,7/21/2021,15,15,,7/2/2021,,,,"$7,269",,,,Conventional,,,,,,Central and Summit,"Breathe in bright light and spaciousness with this 3-bedroom duplex plus private rooftop located just off Central Avenue in the Heights.   Built with beautiful brick, the majestic windows and parking garage beckon from the street view. On the interior, clean and modern design opens with two-story high soaring windows in the eat-in kitchen plus dining area and powder room. Sleek slab tile flooring and crisp crown molding highlight the natural wood cabinetry, waterfall quartz counters, tile backsplash and GE appliances. Upstairs leads to the airy and open loft-space living area, plus three bedrooms and two full baths. Master ensuite offers porcelain counters, great storage and glass shower with penny tile mosaic floor.   Step up to the stunning split-level fully-finished roof deck with spectacular NYC views and endless fresh air. Steps from the main thoroughfare of Central Avenue, this beautiful tree-lined residential street offers walkability to expansive Washington park, excellent schools and easy metro transportation."
230020216,SOLD,"JC, Heights",203 HOPKINS AVE,Condominium,1773,1713,"$700,000",CONDO-COOP,,Dup,1,"JC, Heights",07306,05503,00001,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,8,,"$700,000","$749,000",$394.81,$394.81,12/5/2023,12/28/2023,3/8/2024,23,23,,3/8/2024,,,,$0,,$510,,Conventional,,,,,,corner of Bevan Sy & Hopkins Ave,"Welcome to this newly renovated 1700 SQ FT + 3 bedroom / 3 bath duplex condo, in the booming sector of The Heights, minutes from Holland Tunnel, Downtown JC and major routes like Rt. 280, NJ Turnpike, and much more! This duplex features modern style finishes, a large open concept living space, great sized bedrooms, and baths, as well as a groomed patio and  1-car parking, with garage.  Step inside and soak in the beautiful light hardwood floors, and luminous array of recessed lighting. A modern and chic style kitchen awaits with a full set of state-of-the-art appliances, and an abundance of gleaming white cabinetry with featured gold hardware. An oversized island makes it the perfect space for hosting family and friends! Two great sized bedrooms and two baths featuring a tub and shower with floating dual vanities complete this floor! Head down the beautifully finished windy stairs onto an open space perfect for a rec area or family room, the third bedroom and bath are also located on this floor, perfect for a guest room or home office. The tucked away laundry area features full-size front loaders and utility sink. This fabulous condo is a must see."
