240012233,SOLD,"JC, Heights",573 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,941,1603,"$719,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3B,"JC, Heights",07307,02304,00024,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$719,000","$719,000",$764.08,$764.08,6/25/2024,7/1/2024,10/18/2024,6,6,,10/18/2024,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Congress St & South St,"New construction home in elevator building with two private terraces! Welcome to 573 Palisade Avenue, where unparalleled sophistication meets breathtaking views in an exclusive collection of seven condominium homes in a boutique-style elevator building.  Each two-bedroom, two-bathroom condominium home features spacious open floor plans of meticulously designed living space and private outdoor spaces. 10 - 14 ft ceilings soar above engineered hardwood floors, creating an airy sanctuary illuminated by recessed and custom light fixtures. The expansive triple pane Pella windows frame stunning vistas of the Manhattan skyline, inviting you to unwind against a backdrop of urban splendor. Kitchens feature custom 2-toned cabinetry, Samsung stainless steel appliances, Calacatta Laza Quartz countertops, wine cooler and direct vent exhaust hood. Bathrooms include Porcelanosa tiles with Kohler fixtures, deep soaking tubs and dual flush toilets.  You'll love the convenience of having in-home laundry, integrated intercom and security system and a home that is prewired for home automation.  Unwind and socialize on our exclusive residents rooftop lounge offering sweeping NYC views, providing an extraordinary backdrop for relaxation or entertaining guests. This property boasts unparalleled ease of access to New York City, making your commute as breezy as a walk in the adjacent Fisk Park. Whether you prefer the NJ Transit buses or the convenience of the 9th Street-Congress Street Light Rail Station right at your doorstep, your connection to the city has never been smoother. And with breathtaking views of the Manhattan skyline from your window, every day feels like a picturesque escape. This prime Jersey City Heights location offers you not just a home, but a lifestyle. Photos of staged unit."
240018189,SOLD,"JC, Heights",126 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1379,64,"$720,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3B,"JC, Heights",07307,4503,17,Heights,Hugo Pronti Lofts,,,,1,0,1,4,,"$720,000","$749,900",$522.12,$522.12,9/13/2024,12/18/2024,1/27/2025,96,96,,1/27/2025,,,,"$13,425",2023,$551,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton St. & Franklin St.,"RARE True Loft Living in an elevator building! Enter the Hugo Pronti Lofts, located in the Riverview Artist District of Jersey City heights. This 3rd floor corner 1 bed/1bath loft offers nearly 1400 Sq Ft of wide-open space and features NYC views, a private terrace, hardwood floors, Central A/C, a large modern kitchen w/a dishwasher & microwave, an APEC water filtration system, 13 ft ceilings, lot's of light, a working gas fireplace and large windows. This large unique loft condo can easily be converted to a 1 or 2 bedroom. One can customize this large space in many different ways. The building features a shared W/D room in the basement. Additionally this great apt comes w/a private storage space and private secure parking spot. It's close to the bus & light rail to Hoboken & NYC. It's also close to shopping, restaurants, cafes, Riverview-Fisk Park and all the other great things that the heights offers. Some of the furniture in the pics has been virtually added."
240007617,SOLD,"JC, Heights",366 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1180,1719,"$720,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02304,00009,,,,,,2,1,1,5,,"$720,000","$725,000",$610.17,$610.17,4/24/2024,5/2/2024,6/3/2024,8,8,,6/3/2024,,,,"$10,160",,$180,,Conventional,,,,,,South St. & Congress St.," Experience the pinnacle of modern luxury living at this newer construction exceptional 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home, adorned with 10 high ceilings and pristine 5 hardwood floors throughout. Indulge your culinary desires in the sleek and contemporary chef's kitchen, equipped with top-of-the-line Samsung stainless steel appliances, 42 cabinets, quartz countertops, and a charming country-style farmer sink. Features two spacious bedrooms, a generously-sized office space, and the privilege of your very own private backyard, creating a serene outdoor sanctuary. This home is thoughtfully designed with modern amenities, including home entertainment wiring with speakers, ring door bell system, a Nest thermostat, honeywell alarm system, custom closets, and an electric 50 stainless steel fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings. Immerse yourself in the tranquility of this abode, boasting extra-thick soundproofing, subfloor, and insulation, ensuring a peaceful retreat from the bustling city life. Nestled in the coveted Jersey City Heights neighborhood, known for its excellent schools and easy access to NYC, indulge in the vibrant local scene with nearby attractions such as Hoboken’s Trader Joe’s and an array of diverse restaurants, bakeries, cafes, and bars. Enjoy seamless public transportation options to NYC just around the corner, expansive Washington Park a block away, and convenient access to the Lightrail and Citibikes nearby. Welcome to your urban oasis - where luxury meets convenience and tranquility awaits. 2-year tax abatement. Schedule a private tour today!"
220007265,SOLD,"JC, Heights",58 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1211,1603,"$720,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,00746,00318,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$720,000","$685,000",$594.55,$594.55,4/26/2022,5/4/2022,6/4/2022,8,8,,6/17/2022,,,,"$9,700",,,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton & Franklin,"Start your summer off right - enjoying your *private* backyard in the heart of the Riverview Arts section of Jersey City Heights. A charming gated front yard and brick steps lead up to the private entrance of this spacious 3 bed, 2 full bath unit. Upon entry, the wide and airy living room flows into the thoughtfully-designed kitchen with gleaming quartz countertops, soft-close shaker cabinets, and Bertazzoni appliances. The primary bedroom boasts an en-suite and walk-in closet. The second and third bedrooms are perfect for offices, guest rooms, or nurseries. With large closets, a full laundry room, and a huge basement storage area, this home offers room to grow. Additional features include wide plank hardwood floors, modern full bathrooms, and high ceilings throughout. Situated between Riverview and Manhattan Parks, you’ll have easy access to Palisade and Central Avenue bus routes and the 2nd Street Light Rail Station in Hoboken. One block from great coffee and restaurants on Franklin Street, come enjoy all the Heights has to offer. Welcome home!"
220011411,SOLD,"JC, Heights",127 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1365,1702,"$721,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03601,00005,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$721,000","$745,000",$528.21,$528.21,6/22/2022,7/13/2022,9/6/2022,21,21,,9/9/2022,,,,$0,,$221,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy & Summit,"Brand new premier construction in the center of JC Heights. Located just half mile to Pershing Fields, farmers market at Riverview Fisk Park, and one mile to Jr Sq PATH train. This spacious PH boasts 1365 interior sq ft of luxury plus private 230 sq ft roof top terrace with panoramic NYC views. Across the home enjoy real hardwood floors, dark oil rubbed bronze hardware, recessed lighting, central air conditioning, and custom design lighting fixtures. Superior sound attenuation via Anderson 400 Series windows and double 5/8” sheetrock. Kitchen features farmhouse sink, white quartz countertops and shaker cabinets, gas range, wine fridge, marbled matching floor tiles and backsplash. In unit laundry room with Samsung side by side front loading washer and dryer. Master suite offers walk in closet complete with organization unit, master bath double sink, full body shower system, and LED backlit mirror. Home includes parking and 5 yr tax abatement."
220015936,SOLD,"JC, Heights",502 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1323,1605,"$722,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,204,"JC, Heights",07307,2401,101,,Palisade Square,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$722,000","$725,000",$545.73,$545.73,9/6/2022,9/21/2022,11/14/2022,15,15,,11/15/2022,,,,"$9,061",2022,$366,2022,Conventional,,,,,,Congress and South,"This is the home you've been waiting for!  This stunning and spacious two bed, two bath condo offers over 1,300 square feet of open living space and spacious rooms throughout.  Why settle when you can have all the space you need to live and work from home?  The modern kitchen features ample space to cook your gourmet meal.   Offering stunning Italian cabinetry, quartz countertop, subway tile backsplash and Kitchenaid appliance package, this is a chefs dream.  The kitchen opens up to an entertainers dream; comfortably accommodating a dining table and sectional sofa, this is the space to have friends over for dinner.  The pendant lighting above the island and under-cabinet lighting is a nice touch.  The primary bedroom comfortably accommodates a king sized bed and has a massive walk in closet.  The primary bathroom features a large shower stall, radiant heated stone flooring and his/hers sinks.  The second bedroom, conveniently located next to the primary, is perfect for a home office or child's room.  Central cooling/heating, recessed LED lighting, wide plank hardwood floors, and a large capacity vented Whirlpool washer/dryer, this unit checks all the boxes.  Built from the ground up in 2019 and only owner occupied for two years, this stunner at Palisade Square is an ideal choice.  Sleek and contemporary, this elevator building offers luxury living at a manageable price point.  Featuring low HOA fees and amazing location, Palisade Square is located ideally next to Riverview Fisk Park (amazing NYC views and a farmers market) and a couple of blocks from the Congress Street elevator.  Bus to NYC is located right outside on Palisade Ave and with local hotspots like Corto, Bread and Salt and Mod Cup coffee, location is everything with this property.  A true commuters dream!"
220021094,SOLD,"JC, Heights",126 IRVING ST,Condominium,1500,1598,"$722,000",CONDO-COOP,,2+RF,2,"JC, Heights",07307,00703,00058,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$722,000","$749,000",$481.33,$481.33,12/6/2022,12/17/2022,1/25/2023,11,11,,1/25/2023,,,,$0,,$0,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy Blvd & Nelson,"Reintroducing 126 Irving st,  the last unit remaining of the 4 luxury new construction units and now offering the Community Advantage Program, super low rates in 4% range, with only 5% down CONV NO PMI and a large lender credit of 1% towards closing costs also possible Down payment assistance.  These units were designed & constructed by one of Jersey City's most renowned builders, Medna Developers. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms home features an expansive open-concept living space with immaculate attention to detail, craftsmanship and design. The open concept chef's kitchen boasts premium stainless steel appliances, wine fridge and quartz countertops. Throughout the home you'll notice smart features such as intercom, security, speakers and thermostat. Master bedroom has a private terrace, walk-in closet and plenty of natural light! Bathroom includes floor to ceiling custom tile, smart mirror and modern fixtures. Your private rooftop offers beautiful views and privacy. Most importantly, unlike 90% of the other properties on the market, NO SHARED TANDEM PARKING, Private only, so you don't have to coordinate/bother with your neighbor about parking and moving cars, Priceless!"
240009922,SOLD,"JC, Heights",139 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,1048,5906,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,5,503,"JC, Heights",07307,03503,00001,Heights,Sherman Place,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$725,000","$740,000",$691.79,$691.79,5/23/2024,7/25/2024,12/6/2024,63,63,,12/6/2024,,,,"$11,828",2023,$477,,VA,,,,,,Kennedy and Sanford,"Presenting an exquisite condo in JC Heights, this splendid residence offers over 1,000 square feet of living space w/ 2 spacious BRs & 2 elegant BTHs. The interior features an open-concept layout seamlessly transitioning from the inviting living room to a well-appointed kitchen, boasting top-of-the-line SS appliances, sleek cabinetry & ample countertop space. Natural light floods through large windows, creating an airy atmosphere. The primary bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom, while the 2nd bedroom offers versatility as a guest room, home office, or personal sanctuary. Both bathrooms have contemporary finishes, evoking a spa-like ambiance. The unit also features in-unit WD, an energy-efficient tankless water heater, a smart NEST thermostat & a huge walk-in closet. Enjoy NYC views from your window or the building's rooftop deck. With a deeded parking space, indoor bicycle storage, and a secure package room, commuting is easy with Citi bikes and express buses right outside. A must-see for modern urban living!"
240015354,SOLD,"JC, Heights",380 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1128,1597,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$725,000","$725,000",$642.73,$642.73,8/6/2024,9/4/2024,10/4/2024,29,29,,10/8/2024,,,,,,$380,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"Find the ultimate contemporary urban living in the vibrant Heights neighborhood! This newly constructed 3-unit building boasts a secure entrance on a tree-lined street with access to surrounding Hoboken and NYC access. Each unit offers a spacious 3 (or 4!) bedroom layout with private outdoor space, basement storage, checking all the buyer must-haves.  Unit 1 hosts a private back patio and garden, coupled with a thoughtfully designed split floorplan for ultimate flexibility.   Modern design and upgrades emanate throughout each home, with wide plank light oak floors and carefully curated lighting. White kitchens feature sleek quartz counters, tile backsplash, an eat-in island, sleek custom cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. Bathrooms bring luxury with floor-to-ceiling tile, shower and soaker tub options, sleek vanities and polished chrome fixtures. The dedicated utility/laundry room gives maximum flexibility and convenience in your daily routine, hosting stacking Samsung washer and dryer. Storage is maximized with excellent closet space, including large walk-ins in each primary ensuite.   Situated just one block from Riverview Fisk Park with breathtaking Manhattan views, and the Hoboken stairs leading to the 2nd Street Lightrail, this location is offers the ultimate urban luxury lifestyle. The Heights is known for its vibrant community, excellent parks and schools and easy access to NYC and surrounding neighborhoods."
250016269,SOLD,"JC, Heights",184 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,1129,1597,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$725,000","$735,000",$642.16,$642.16,8/8/2025,8/25/2025,10/17/2025,17,17,,10/17/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Reservoir and Booraem,"Perched above peaceful Pershing Field Park, this completely reimagined residence provides the perfect blend of indoor outdoor living with attainable luxury flair. With quality construction from revered local builder, Nkay, this 2 bedroom, 2 bath home offers a front-row seat to parkside living, plus modern design and unbeatable location in Jersey City Heights.  Light floods in through the floor-to-ceiling windows and double glass doors welcoming the Western facing sunsets and highlighting the light oak hardwood floors. The kitchen is sharp and thoughtfully composed with deep blue lower cabinets, white uppers, clean quartz counters, herringbone tile, and stainless appliances. The eat-in peninsula opens easily to dining and living, with access to a private balcony that sits just above the treetops.  Each bedroom offers Juliet balconies and tree-top views, bringing outdoor living easily indoors. Bathrooms bring elegant extras—one with a soaking tub, the other with an oversized shower and a multi-spray system—plus tile finished to the ceiling, smart mirrors and sizable vanities keep things clean and contemporary.  Settled on a tree-lined street in the heart of Jersey City Heights, owners are in close proximity to Central Avenue shops, Reservoir #3 and Pershing Field Park and 2nd Street Lightrail with connections to PATH and Hoboken ferry terminal. The Heights are proudly known for their excellent parks, vibrant community and easy access to NYC. "
230013418,SOLD,"JC, Heights",139 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,1080,1713,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,5,504,"JC, Heights",07307,03503,00001,,Sherman Place,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$725,000","$749,900",$671.30,$671.30,8/10/2023,10/11/2023,11/13/2023,62,62,,11/14/2023,,,,,,$471,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy and Sanford,"Presenting an exquisite condominium nestled in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This splendid residence boasts two generously proportioned bedrooms and two elegant bathrooms, providing a perfect blend of comfort and luxury. Just over 1000 square feet, the condo offers a well-thought-out layout that maximizes both space and functionality. Upon entering, you are greeted by a sophisticated and modern interior design that sets the tone for the entire unit. The open-concept living area seamlessly transitions from the inviting living room to the well-appointed kitchen, creating a harmonious space for relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen features top-of-the-line appliances, sleek cabinetry, and ample countertop space, catering to the needs of culinary enthusiasts and hosts alike. The two spacious bedrooms are designed to offer tranquility and privacy. The primary bedroom comes complete with an en-suite bathroom, providing a serene retreat after a long day. The second bedroom, equally spacious, offers versatility for use as a guest room, home office, or personal sanctuary. Both bathrooms are adorned with contemporary finishes and fixtures, evoking a spa-like ambiance. Natural light floods the living spaces through large windows, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere. The condo also features thoughtfully integrated storage solutions, ensuring a clutter-free living environment. Commuting to Manhattan and other parts of Jersey City is a breeze, thanks to the well-connected transportation options in the vicinity. This building truly caters to a sophisticated urban lifestyle. A unique opportunity to own a slice of modern elegance and urban convenience. A must-see!  "
260004421,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",10 SOUTH ST,Condominium,930,1597,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,301,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,1,0,1,4,,,"$725,000",$779.57,,3/12/2026,,,28,,,3/12/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Palisade Ave and Ogden Avenue,"Discover an exceptional new collection of homes where historic character meets modern design. Rising up to four stories, these thoughtfully crafted residences capture the energy and sophistication of city living while offering a serene retreat at home.  Enjoy the convenience of a full-service elevator building with a secure lobby, intercom access, available on-site heated garage and handicap-accessible parking, and EV charging stations. Just three blocks from the Hoboken Light Rail, residents enjoy effortless access to Manhattan and beyond.  Inside, every detail has been considered—from European floor-to-ceiling windows and wide-plank white oak flooring to Gyp-Crete soundproofing that ensures quiet and comfort. Select homes include private balconies, dens, or roof decks designed for seamless indoor-outdoor living.  The interiors reflect a mid-century modern aesthetic with timeless craftsmanship, highlighted by granite waterfall islands, European cabinetry, Kohler fixtures, GE Café and Fisher & Paykel panel-door appliances, smart mirrors, and imported glass lighting. Open-concept kitchens flow into airy living spaces, creating the perfect backdrop for sophisticated urban life. Full kitchens provide a refined setting for entertaining,  For those seeking style, convenience, and connection, these residences reimagine Jersey City Heights living with an inspired blend of design, comfort, and modern amenities.   This home represents one of three, 1 bedroom plus den 10SouthSt.com.  Available On -Site Garage Parking (heated) w/ HC & EV options."
260000150,SOLD,"JC, Heights",63 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,905,6494,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,4501,35,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,4,,"$725,000","$725,000",$801.10,$801.10,1/8/2026,1/23/2026,3/19/2026,15,15,,3/23/2026,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin St & Ferry St,"Elevated Living Starts Here!! Nestled in the heart of The Heights, the fully renovated 63 Webster Ave offers three luxurious condos. Unit 1 features 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, sleek modern finishes, smart layouts, and exclusive access to a private backyard retreat! The Heights neighborhood of Jersey City boasts vibrant energy and is commuter-friendly. Just a few blocks from Pershing Field Park and Riverview-Fisk Park. Enjoy top-rated restaurants, cozy cafés, and local markets all within reach. *virtually staged backyard photos *preliminary floor plans on architectural drawings. Final floor plans to come"
240020700,SOLD,"JC, Heights",108 IRVING ST,Condominium,1480,5832,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,703,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$725,000","$725,000",$489.86,$489.86,10/21/2024,11/11/2024,1/15/2025,21,21,,1/15/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,JFK Blvd and Nelson,"Nestled in the heart of vibrant Jersey City Heights, this spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath duplex condo offers modern elegance with an abundance of natural light and a host of impressive features. The unit boasts large windows throughout, filling the home with natural sunlight and creating a bright, airy ambiance. The highlight of this exceptional property is the oversized private rooftop deck, perfect for al fresco dining, entertaining, and enjoying breathtaking views of Midtown and Lower Manhattan. Watch the Macy's Fourth of July fireworks from the comfort of your own home!  Inside, the chef's kitchen features custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and a large breakfast island, making it the ideal space for casual meals or more formal gatherings. An additional dining area provides flexibility for every occasion.  Upstairs, the extra living space is complemented by three generously sized bedrooms, including a serene primary suite with a luxurious en-suite bathroom, featuring a spa-like stand-up rain shower for relaxation.  The prime location adds to the home's appeal with easy access to trendy restaurants, shops, parks like Washington Park, and convenient transportation. Bus service to Penn Station is just steps away at the corner of JFK Blvd & Poplar St., ensuring a quick and easy commute. This exceptional unit is attractively priced for sale—don’t miss out on this opportunity! Whether you're looking for your next home or a smart investment, now is the time to act. Submit your strongest offer and secure this beautiful property before it’s gone!"
240017813,SOLD,"JC, Heights",314 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1300,6199,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,1,7,,"$725,000","$699,000",$557.69,$557.69,9/10/2024,9/30/2024,11/8/2024,20,20,,11/13/2024,,,,,,$252,,Conventional,,,,,,Palisade and Franklin,"This rare and exceptional home stands out with its perfect blend of unique character and modern luxury. Enjoy the expansive, private backyard, beautifully finished with stone, lush green grass, and privacy trees. Inside, every room is bathed in natural light, thanks to two walls of brand-new windows adorned with elegant plantation shutters. With hardwood floors throughout and dramatically high ceilings with crown molding, the home exudes both grandeur and warmth. The smart air-conditioning system allows you to control the temperature with ease from your phone. Additional touches include a recently renovated bathroom, a charming laundry room door, and a pantry full of personality. Every closet is fully customized for your convenience. No more carrying groceries upstairs, and commuting is a breeze with the bus to Manhattan stopping right next door. #1 anchors an attractive, 3-unit condominium building located in an ideal Jersey City Heights neighborhood that overlooks the Greatest City in the World."
210013558,SOLD,"JC, Heights",26 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,,6451,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,4,,"$725,000","$680,000",,,6/4/2021,6/8/2021,7/27/2021,4,4,,7/28/2021,,,,"$7,192",,$218,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Ferry & Franklin,"This sparkling new 2-year young two-floor condo is filled with natural sunlight, high ceilings, glistening hardwood floors, recessed lighting, designer fixtures and a new custom kitchen / bathrooms. Enjoy entertaining outside on not one but TWO! private decks, one off of the kitchen and one on the rooftop with NYC views. You'll be stunned by the home's massive closets, a bright white kitchen, spacious bedrooms and the most prime location- centrally located in all the vibrant and bustling energy JC Heights has to offer. You'll thrive being a few steps from Pershing Field and Riverview Park, and a quick commute to NYC via bus, PATH and Hoboken Lightrail within blocks. 1 year of free parking next door with your purchase with the opportunity to renew. Pack your bags and move right in."
240004328,SOLD,"JC, Heights",543 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1234,1724,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02305,00030,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$725,000","$749,000",$587.52,$587.52,3/7/2024,3/21/2024,4/24/2024,14,14,,9/24/2024,,,,,,$429,,Conventional,,,,,,South and Bowers,"Two car deeded parking spaces included in the price.  An amazing combination of space and luxury is rarely found at this price point, 543 Palisade is a highly sought-after location due to its proximity to the Light rail station, Riverview Park, and the many shops and restaurants. This large and bright 3 bedroom 2 full bath home, solid hardwood flooring runs throughout this sun-drenched home space, coupled with the high ceilings and beautiful high-end finishes, such as custom cabinetry, washer and dryer in unit and top-of-the-line appliances. This rare Heights location is easily commutable and accessible to public transportation on Palisade Ave; with direct bus lines to NYC Port Authority, Hoboken, and Downtown JC. The Hudson Light Rail Stations are only minutes away as well as Pershing Field's indoor pool and ice skating rink being only 3 blocks away. Riverview Park with its amazing views offers Farmers Market, movie nights, and neighborhood events.   Pictures 1 and 2 are virtually staged."
260005889,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",192 CAMBRIDGE AVE,Condominium,1117,1597,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,B,"JC, Heights",07307,2203,2.01,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,,"$725,000",$649.06,,4/2/2026,,,7,,,4/2/2026,,,,$0,,$311,,,No,No,No,,,Congress Street & South Street,"Five new-construction condominium homes redefine modern living in Jersey City Heights. Each home showcases a refined aesthetic and carefully curated details. Chef-inspired kitchens feature expansive Taj Mahal quartz islands, premium LG stainless appliances with gas range, a Frigidaire wine cooler, and Sharp built-in microwave. Primary baths offer a spa-like escape with porcelain and ceramic tiles, frameless glass showers, brushed gold hardware, Kohler fixtures, and natural teak vanities, while secondary baths boast sleek subway tiles, matte black channels, Moen fixtures, and LED mirrors. Wide-plank French oak flooring, soaring ceilings, custom lighting, and built-in electric fireplaces bring warmth and style throughout, creating homes that balance modern sophistication with everyday comfort.  192 Cambridge sits in prime location only one block to Washington Park and a few short blocks to The Arts District surrounding Riverview Park.  Enjoy neighborhood cafés, Central Avenue shops, and vibrant restaurants, with the Congress Street Light Rail a short walk away, you’ll enjoy effortless access to Hoboken and Manhattan while keeping the Heights’ neighborhood charm at your doorstep."
230003016,SOLD,"JC, Heights",116 BOORAEM AVE,Condominium,1853,1597,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,0 & 1,1A,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$725,000","$749,000",$391.26,$391.26,2/22/2023,3/7/2023,4/21/2023,13,12,,4/24/2023,,,,,,$240,,Conventional,,,,,,Abbett St & Central Ave,"Explore the perfect mix of urban sophistication and modern spaciousness with this newly refinished luxury duplex located in a sweet spot of Jersey City Heights. Bright and airy, light floods in through the windows lined with matte black trim and white molding, and onto the wide plank white oak floors throughout.   Step into the open floorplan highlighted by the waterfall marbled quartz eat-in peninsula island with built-in exposed black shelving. Kitchen continues with white tile backsplash, gold trim, sleek white custom cabinets with black casing and impeccably chosen pendant lighting. Finishing touches include the separate bar area including wine fridge and built-in bottle display, ideal for entertaining or your everyday beverage station.   The upstairs hosts two bedrooms and two baths, while the downstairs offers loads of extra living with a beautifully tiled basement and two additional rooms. The primary bedroom features striking deep blue wall paneling, plus walk-in closet and bright light streaming from the big bay window. Design-lovers bathrooms each showcase carefully curated wall-to-wall and top to bottom tile plus shower / soaker tub combo with matte black fixtures and toiletries niche.   All units include a centrally located dedicated washer / dryer closet for convenience. This newly refinished building offers excellent curb appeal, beautifully finished communal stairwell with exposed banister and stylish accents, plus can’t-be-beat location.   Steps to either Pershing Field Park and Reservoir, or bustling Central Avenue, this home offers walkability to essential shops, excellent outdoor space and easy NYC access."
250004160,SOLD,"JC, Heights",302 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1156,1702,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,203,"JC, Heights",07307,05201,00013,,Palisade Heights,,,,2,0,2,4,,"$725,000","$705,000",$627.16,$627.16,3/5/2025,3/17/2025,5/1/2025,12,12,,5/1/2025,,,,"$12,765",2023,$550,2025,Conventional,,,,,,Ravine & Booraem,"Culminate a new beginning at Palisade Heights, a mid-rise 12 residence condominium in the trendy Heights neighborhood of Jersey City. Built in 2016, this building offers the finest in contemporary living. Residence 203 is superior; the largest floor plan in the complex with approximately 1,150 square feet of living space. Complete with hardwood floors, this two bedroom & two full bath home has it all; in-home laundry, recessed lighting, & video intercom. The open-concept layout allows for both a comfortable living & dining space! Enjoy sun-lit mornings with East-facing windows & sliding glass doors that open to a Juliette balcony. The oversized en-suite bedroom accommodates a king-sized bed + additional furnishings & the second bedroom offers versatility, ideal for a guest room or home office. Best of all, residents can also enjoy a large shared back patio & the comfort of pulling right into their parking space via the enclosed parking garage. Experience effortless connectivity to transportation, shops, and dining, with easy access to major highways and the Holland Tunnel. Discover the epitome of modern living at Palisade Heights. "
210017035,SOLD,"JC, Heights",88 POPLAR ST,Condominium,2556,1702,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$725,000","$725,000",$283.65,$283.65,7/16/2021,8/20/2021,9/30/2021,35,36,,10/7/2021,,,,"$7,500",2021,$150,,Conventional,,,,,,Grace St. and Irving St.,"Welcome to 88 Poplar St., a luxury 2-unit new construction brownstone in Jersey City Heights. Residence #1 has been thoughtfully designed offering 3 Bedrooms/2.5 Bathrooms and 2556 SF of open-concept floor plan. The primary bedroom has a beautiful balcony, a five-star en-suite bath, and large walk-in closet. In addition to two other properly sized bedrooms and another full bath, the home has a full walkout basement with powder room, a private backyard, and 1 car tandem parking with tons of storage. This turn-key property has been appointed with high-end finishes and is smart home enabled. 88 Poplar is situated closely to Bus transportation to NYC, schools, and the amazing Washington Park. Do not miss the opportunity to tour this incredible opportunity!"
220004277,SOLD,"JC, Heights",250 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1010,1691,"$725,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$725,000","$725,000",$717.82,$717.82,3/11/2022,3/11/2022,6/2/2022,0,0,,6/2/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers & South St,"Bright white interiors and brand new, ground-up construction, this two unit building in The Heights offers a private roofdeck, garage parking and individual storage for each luxury home. The two bedroom and two baths are designed with thoughtful split plan layout, each with modern style and up-to-date tech.   Dark hardwood floors meet with clean palette white walls, extra large windows with black trim and carefully curated designer pendant lighting throughout. Kitchens showcase beautiful white quartz counters with herringbone backsplash, stainless appliances and ample cabinet space with wall pantry and built-in coffee bar.   Primary ensuite showcases private balcony and walk-in closet. Oversized bathrooms boast natural light plus double panel glass shower including niche and multi system showerhead.   Owners enjoy several must-have amenities including their own private roofdeck with impressive NYC views and invaluable outdoor living. In addition, each home has access to tandem garage parking and their own ground-level storage area.  Set on a quiet street in the heart of Jersey City Heights, this location offers walkability to beautiful Riverview Fisk Parks with panoramic NYC and Hudson River views, plus 9th street elevator Light Rail for easy NYC and Hoboken access."
220014956,SOLD,"JC, Heights",113 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1785,298,"$726,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,1,8,,"$726,000","$699,000",$406.72,$406.72,8/16/2022,9/7/2022,10/27/2022,22,22,,10/28/2022,,,,"$7,784",2021,$250,2022,Conventional,,,,,,SUMMIT AND JFK,"DUPLEX UNIT, PRIVATE BACKYARD. Beautifully crafted unit located in the heart of JC Heights. This lux unit offers 3 bedrooms/2.5 bath duplex unit. You will find modern finishes, high-end appliances, and hardwood floors throughout. The chef’s kitchen is spacious and really compliments the open concept feel of the unit. Custom trim work, custom closets, Laundry room, ample storage space and a shared driveway compliment all the features this property has to offer. Being centrally located you're near all that the booming Jersey City Heights has to offer. Come see today! This property is eligible for the following COMMUNITY ADVANTAGE Program - 5% down CONV NO PMI and a large lender credit and discounted interest rate.   "
230005746,SOLD,"JC, Heights",302 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1004,5845,"$726,200",CONDO-COOP,,4,404,"JC, Heights",07307,05201,00013,,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$726,200","$690,000",$723.31,$723.31,4/11/2023,5/5/2023,6/19/2023,24,24,,6/20/2023,,,,"$11,032",2022,$404,,Conventional,,,,,,Cuneo & Ravine,"Welcome to Palisades Heights Condominiums and this stunning, top floor, 2 bedroom/2 bath home with Empire State Building and World Trade Center views.  Large eastern facing windows saturate the home in natural light accentuating the hardwood floors and open floor plan. The flawless kitchen features stainless steel JennAir appliances,  quartz countertop, Arabesque backsplash, ample cabinet space and breakfast bar. Spacious  en-suite master bedroom provides large closets and bathroom with walk in, glass enclosed shower. Juliet balcony, custom wine bar, central air controlled by smart thermostat, video intercom, and washer/dryer round out this amazing apartment. Elevator building with shared backyard  situated in the heart of The Heights close to Lo-fi, Choc-o-Pain, shopping and everything you need. Garage parking, NYC Bus on the corner and just a couple of blocks away from stairs to Hoboken and light rail make commuting a breeze. "
230015868,SOLD,"JC, Heights",13 CHARLES ST,Condominium,1273,1739,"$730,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02803,00022,,,,,,2,1,2,6,,"$730,000","$739,000",$573.45,$573.45,9/21/2023,9/27/2023,11/10/2023,6,6,,11/10/2023,,,,"$9,692",23,$155,,Conventional,,,,,,Central and Summit Ave,"A stunning duplex home with a private yard and single car parking, welcome to the epitome of JC Heights living. Welcome to 13 Charles Street! Unit 1 redefines upscale urban living, as the location is nestled between Central Ave’s booming shopping and dining, NYC transportation, as well as local parks. Built by AB Cruz, known for their top-tier craftsman ship, this home’s features include red oak hardwood flooring with a popular gray stain, oversized porcelain tiles to give a modern feel, GE Profile appliances, Lusso Cuccina cabinets, and Calcutta quartz countertops. The first-floor flows seamlessly from kitchen and dining to your walkout backyard, while the second floor is laid out perfectly for living, with an immense living room and both bedrooms with two baths. Do not miss this opportunity to own in The Heights, do not miss the opportunity that is 13 Charles Street."
220008317,SOLD,"JC, Heights",102 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1110,1623,"$730,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,403,"JC, Heights",07307,05202,00023,,Ogden Park View,,,,2,1,1,5,,"$730,000","$735,000",$657.66,$657.66,5/10/2022,5/27/2022,8/8/2022,17,17,,8/10/2022,,,,"$8,042",2021,$358,2022,Conventional,,,,,,end of Ogden Ave,"Wow NYC Views! Ogden Avenue Duplex Penthouse w/Two terraces with new synthetic decking and railings overlooking Manhattan skyline. Two Bedrooms, 1.5 Baths, Open floor plan, exposed brick walls, wood burning fireplace, renovated kitchen, featuring 3cm Aurea stone countertops, SS gas appliances which includes a brand new Bosch dishwasher. The condo has new hand scraped solid acacia hardwood floors, high ceilings, new Samsung W/D in unit, new Anderson windows and doors, Nest thermostats for dual zone, custom closets, walk-in closet, newly renovated bathrooms, featuring Kohler fixtures pedestal sink, Bianco Carrara honed marble floors and shower walls, double vanity with Carrera marble countertop.  The unit also features a spiral staircase with custom railing, two zone A/C and heat. A/C unit, furnace and hot water heater (2016). Playground and community garden and dog park, quiet street (dead end), easy street parking, panoramic NYC views."
230017674,SOLD,"JC, Heights",139 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,1050,1713,"$730,000",CONDO-COOP,,5,501,"JC, Heights",07307,03503,00001,,Sherman Place,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$730,000","$724,900",$695.24,$695.24,10/19/2023,11/21/2023,12/22/2023,33,32,,12/22/2023,,,,$0,,$431,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy and Sanford,"Presenting an exquisite condominium nestled in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This splendid residence boasts two generously proportioned bedrooms and two elegant bathrooms, providing a perfect blend of comfort and luxury. Just over 1000 square feet, the condo offers a well-thought-out layout that maximizes both space and functionality. Upon entering, you are greeted by a sophisticated and modern interior design that sets the tone for the entire unit. The open-concept living area seamlessly transitions from the inviting living room to the well-appointed kitchen, creating a harmonious space for relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen features top-of-the-line appliances, sleek cabinetry, and ample countertop space, catering to the needs of culinary enthusiasts and hosts alike. The two spacious bedrooms are designed to offer tranquility and privacy. The primary bedroom comes complete with an en-suite bathroom, providing a serene retreat after a long day. The second bedroom, equally spacious, offers versatility for use as a guest room, home office, or personal sanctuary. Both bathrooms are adorned with contemporary finishes and fixtures, evoking a spa-like ambiance. Natural light floods the living spaces through large windows, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere. The condo also features thoughtfully integrated storage solutions, ensuring a clutter-free living environment and in-unit Washer and Dryer. Commuting to Manhattan and other parts of Jersey City is a breeze, thanks to the well-connected transportation options in the vicinity. Parking is also available for purchase! This building truly caters to a sophisticated urban lifestyle. A unique opportunity to own a slice of modern elegance and urban convenience. A must-see!"
250005645,SOLD,"JC, Heights",256 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1380,1597,"$730,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$730,000","$775,000",$528.99,$528.99,3/24/2025,6/6/2025,8/8/2025,74,74,,8/14/2025,,,,,,$389,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers and South St,"This newly refinished grey brick building blends modern design with classic details. Offering three thoughtfully designed residences, each feature light oak hardwood floors, crown molding, and - In Unit 3 - sliding glass doors, allowing for an abundance of natural light. The open-concept living areas are spacious enough for a full-size dining table, creating a comfortable and functional layout.  The kitchens are finished with waterfall quartz countertops, a herringbone tile backsplash, and a striking combination of white upper and dark indigo lower custom cabinetry. Brass fixtures add warmth, while LG stainless steel appliances complete the space with a sleek, modern touch. The primary suite in each unit is designed as a peaceful retreat, accented by a tranquil feature wall. Bathrooms showcase floor-to-ceiling tile, double vanities, matte black fixtures, and either a glass-enclosed shower or a deep soaking tub with a built-in niche. Each unit includes a full-size laundry room with a Samsung champagne washer and dryer for added convenience.  Unit 3 features three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a vaulted ceiling with sliding glass doors leading to a private balcony.  Set in the heart of Jersey City Heights, this location is just blocks from Riverview Fisk Park, where residents can take in sweeping views of the Manhattan skyline and enjoy local farmers' markets and community events. The 9th Street elevator provides easy access to Hoboken, while the nearby Light Rail connects directly to the PATH train and ferry, making commuting into New York City seamless."
210009184,SOLD,"JC, Heights",341 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1749,1673,"$730,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2306,35,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$730,000","$725,000",$417.38,$417.38,4/18/2021,5/5/2021,6/25/2021,17,17,,6/28/2021,,,,$0,,$300,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers & South St.,"Just what you've been looking for! 3 bed, 3 bath newly renovated duplex condo with an office. Spacious, elegant modern finishes- kitchen includes marble countertops. In the buzzing section of Jersey City heights. Close to shopping, transportation and NYC. Look no further now that you can finally park not just one vehicle- but two, in your deeded driveway in the back of the home. Contact us today for a private showing!"
210000609,SOLD,"JC, Heights",131 CONGRESS ST,Condominium,1410,66,"$730,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,TWO,"JC, Heights",07307,01506,00015,Heights,131 Congress Residences,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$730,000","$735,000",$517.73,$517.73,1/7/2021,1/21/2021,5/21/2021,14,14,,5/26/2021,,,,$0,,$275,2021,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Central Ave & Passaic Ave,"Say Goodbye to Tandem Parking! Side by side garage & the added space of an oversized 26.5' lot!  New construction penthouse condo boasting a spacious sunlit floor plan, great room w/ cathedral ceilings, impeccable finishes, private roof deck, garage parking, storage and a full home warranty! Distinguished by a combination of contemporary design, luxury finishes, craftsmanship and value. Details include hardwood floors throughout, custom trim work, solid core doors, custom Hardi facade and upgraded Andersen 400 series windows & doors. Three bedrooms culminate in the master suite w/ balcony, en-suite bath w/ dual-vanity and large walk-in closet. The bathrooms are adorned with custom tile, floating vanities, seamless glass showers, full-width mirrors & abundant lighting. The open kitchen has Quartz waterfall counters, SS appliances, tiled backsplash eat-in island w/ built-in microwave, & tons of storage in the Shaker cabinets. From the great room, full-size stairs lead to the private roof deck w/ NYC views!  Central A/C, in-unit washer/dryer & expansive closets round out the myriad of features meticulously incorporated into this home. Steps to the Central Ave business district & express NYC transportation. New home warranty & 5-year tax abatement application included. Estimated Completion: Late Feb. Model Home Available Daily for Tours."
210026332,SOLD,"JC, Heights",580 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1182,1692,"$730,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,204,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,The Riverview,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$730,000","$699,000",$617.60,$617.60,11/30/2021,12/6/2021,4/13/2022,6,6,,6/13/2022,,,,,,$390,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress and South,"Step inside and immediately feel at ease. BRAND NEW GROUND UP CONSTRUCTION at The Riverview offers impeccable comfort and convenience, situated on Palisade Avenue, at the heart of the neighborhood’s exciting retail/dining corridor. Choose from two- and three-bedroom residences in this intimate 13-unit building, crafted to meet your every need. The well-proportioned units are carefully constructed with today’s most in-demand elements. Flow-through rooms and thoughtful appointments combine for luxurious comfort. Expansive energy-efficient insulated windows frame the interiors with abundant natural light. Elegant top-line finishes include wide plank flooring, and premium Fischer-Paykel appliances. Thoughtfully curated amenities bring ease to today’s busy lifestyles. A package room, 12-car parking garage with electric chargers and ground-level bike storage are among the building’s many essential comforts designed to enhance your lifestyle. Make this inspired collection of pet-friendly condominiums your home. 10-year New Home Warranty, Manufacturer’s Warranty on all appliances and systems, and tax abatement. Photos are of model unit."
210003580,SOLD,"JC, Heights",95 THORNE ST,Condominium,1815,1691,"$732,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & 3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2603,27,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$732,000","$732,000",$403.31,$403.31,2/12/2021,2/22/2021,4/7/2021,10,10,,4/7/2021,,,,"$8,969",2019,$175,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy and Summit,"Expand into this less than two-year-young towering condo complete with parking and private rooftop deck.  Purchased as new construction, this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom offers 1,815 sq ft of high-end finishes and intelligent layout, making it feel like a single family dream home.   Pull into deeded parking and head upstairs to the two-story tall Andersen picture windows, showcasing the thoughtfully laid out open floor plan. Modern kitchen features imported custom cabinetry, Italian Calcutta waterfall countertop with mosaic backsplash and stainless steel appliances. The overhang balcony concept living room gives grandeur and interest, while the oak flooring, cathedral banister and crown molding anchor the design. Smart home features impress with video intercoms, WiFi thermostats, central vacuum and more.   Large bedrooms and clean, simple bathroom designs make the ideal interior design canvas, while the real showstopper is the rooftop with NYC views and unbeatable outdoor space. Set in the heart of Jersey City Heights, enjoy walkability to vibrant Central Avenue, Washington and Leonard Gordon parks, excellent schools and easy NYC access.   Built by one of Jersey City’s finest developers, this home includes the majority of a 10-year builders warranty & tax abatement remaining."
220001573,SOLD,"JC, Heights",948 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,1147,1597,"$735,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03704,00003,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$735,000","$725,000",$640.80,$640.80,1/27/2022,2/4/2022,3/18/2022,8,8,,3/21/2022,,,,"$8,036",2021,$263,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton & Griffith,"Featuring an expansive private roof terrace with panoramic views that includes Manhattan’s skyline and an indoor tandem parking in the garage below, this condominium residence with 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms is a true urban oasis in the sought-after Jersey City Heights. The generously proportioned home is flooded with natural light throughout the day, and the view from every room is open and serene. The meticulously crafted condominium constructed in 2019 boasts oversized Pella windows, a Dome security system with cameras, a video intercom, home theatre speakers, and Central Heating and AC. The sumptuous primary bedroom suite is furnished with a walk-in closet and an exquisite en-suite bathroom. Both beautifully designed bathrooms are outfitted with floor-to-ceiling tiles by Porcelanosa. The crisp and modernistic kitchen is equipped with Quartz countertops, Oxford latte white cabinets, a waterfall island and LG black stainless appliances. The spacious and elegant home further boasts hardwood floors, wainscoting, recessed lights and ample closets including an additional walk-in closet in the second bedroom. Set in a central spot of Jersey City Heights, the residence is conveniently situated near acclaimed restaurants, bakeries, markets, several parks including Riverview Fisk and Pershing Field, and PATH train and buses to NYC."
220017929,SOLD,"JC, Heights",176 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1293,1702,"$735,000",CONDO-COOP,,1.5,103,"JC, Heights",07307,2301,2,,The Bakery Lofts,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$735,000","$749,000",$568.45,$568.45,10/7/2022,10/31/2022,1/6/2023,24,24,,1/17/2023,,,,"$11,254",2021,$613,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers & South St.,"Ultra private, ultra quiet Jersey City loft for sale at The Bakery Lofts.   This expansive 1293sf home features solid industrial warehouse construction, an open concept  living/dining/kitchen space, private sleeping quarters, 2 full bathrooms, a spectacular 35’x14’ outdoor patio with jacuzzi for 8 and 2 deeded, heated garage parking spaces.   Additional features include new hardwood floors, new dishwasher, new hot water heater, mature patio landscaping with irrigation system, power awning, in unit washer/dryer room, central heating/AC, shared roof top deck accessed by elevator.  Completely gut renovated in 2006, The Bakery Lofts is a 17-unit elevator building conveniently located on a quiet tree-lined street only 5 minutes from the Congress Street Light Rail stop and 3 short blocks from Palisade Avenue and bus service to NYC."
240004921,SOLD,"JC, Heights",974 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,1276,6048,"$735,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,404,"JC, Heights",07307,2801,5.01,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$735,000","$724,900",$576.02,$576.02,3/14/2024,3/18/2024,5/15/2024,4,4,,6/19/2024,,,,"$9,889",2023,,,Conventional,,,,,,Between summit and central ave,"This New Construction Jersey City Heights 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom Duplex condo with North-East exposure offers the epitome of urban living. Located within a sleek building, with partial amenities, residents enjoy a luxurious lifestyle paired with breathtaking views of the city skyline on the rooftop terrace. Upon entering, you're greeted by an open-concept living space inviting an abundance of natural sunlight. The interior features modern finishes, including hardwood floors throughout. The gourmet kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, high end GE cafe appliances, Nest thermostat,Yale smart digital locks, central AC, full size washer/dryer and ample cabinetry, providing both functionality and elegance. The bedrooms, with large windows that ensure natural light, offer a tranquil retreat and with spacious closets to store your belongings. Plenty of storage in addition to an enormous walk-in closet right off your bathroom featuring luxurious fixtures, and a walk-in shower. Once you step outside of this modern brick building you will find yourself in proximity to Central Ave's restaurant row, transportation connecting you to NYC, Hoboken, Downtown JC, and all the beautiful parks that JC Heights has to offer! Take a look at our dedicated property"
210005045,SOLD,"JC, Heights",15 LEONARD ST,Condominium,1444,1681,"$735,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,00504,00018,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$735,000","$725,000",$509.00,$509.00,3/3/2021,3/8/2021,5/10/2021,5,5,,5/10/2021,,,,"$7,090",,$289,,Conventional,No,No,,,,"use GPS, off JFK Blvd","Don't miss this 3BR/2.5BTH duplex condo w/ private, newly renovated yard sure to WOW the most discerning buyer! Steps from Washington Park this condo was built 2 years ago and features all the bells and whistles one could hope for. Gourmet kitchen/ Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and large pantry over looking vast formal dining room or living room. A Master Suite w/ newly built custom, walk-in closet and terrace with a master bath boasting radiant heated floors. Venture downstairs to find a large living room with walk out to the yard of your dreams recently completed by Small Green Space. Yard contains gorgeous, new pavers w/ irrigation system, lighting and astro turf area. Condo comes w/ tandem parking and tons of extra storage space in the garage along with washer/dryer room. 8 years left on the New Home Warranty and tax abatement in effect."
230004240,SOLD,"JC, Heights",124 THORNE ST,Condominium,1293,6706,"$735,000",CONDO-COOP,,2nd,#2,"JC, Heights",07307,2104,76,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$735,000","$749,000",$568.45,$568.45,3/16/2023,4/14/2023,5/25/2023,29,29,,5/25/2023,,,,"$9,133",,$155,,Conventional,,No,,,,Summit Ave & JFK,"The Heights is one of Jersey City's most desirable neighborhoods. This turnkey newer construction 3-bedroom, 2 bath condo boasts approx 1300 Sq Ft of open concept living. High ceilings, white oak floors, a nest thermostat and oversized windows flood the space with natural light. The kitchen offers beautiful white shaker cabinets, SS appliances and the island with white quartz countertops creates the perfect place to gather. The Primary bedroom offers an en-suite bath, porcelain tile, step over tub shower combo, custom closets, and a sliding glass door leading to the balcony. The 2nd and 3rd bedrooms both offer plenty of space, custom closets, and can also be used as flex rooms ie. a social media studio, an office, gamer room, art studio etc. In-unit washer and dryer, 2 dedicated storage closets in the garage, and tandem covered parking -all included. On the 2nd floor be prepared to host and entertain on the oversized private rooftop deck with stunning views of NYC. Located between Summit & JFK Blvd. The property is a quick bus ride to Journal Square PATH. Another option is taking a bus directly into the Port Authority at Times Square. Convenient to Union City and NYC."
210025532,SOLD,"JC, Heights",96 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1900,1713,"$739,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03804,00029,,,,,,2,1,2,7,,"$739,000","$739,000",$388.95,$388.95,11/12/2021,11/23/2021,1/14/2022,11,11,,1/19/2022,,,,"$8,133",,$250,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith & Hutton,"Do not miss this incredibly spacious approximately 1900 sq ft 2BD/2.5BA townhome with covered garage parking, on coveted Sherman Avenue in the Heights section of Jersey City. This move-in ready home features an open concept large living dining area on the main level, along with an eat-in kitchen and a half bath. Walk into your beautiful private backyard that has two sitting areas and is customized with built-in benches to accommodate a firepit. With easy access through the kitchen, this is an entertainer's paradise. Relax in an additional living space with a gas fireplace on the upper level. This space could either be converted to a third bedroom or be used as an office or family room. The massive master bedroom boasts an ensuite and a large walk-in closet. This home also boasts 2.5 baths, hardwood floors, in-unit washer-dryer, central air as well as a covered garage with an additional storage closet. You can easily park two cars in the garage and driveway.  Conveniently located a couple blocks off Palisade Avenue and a stone's throw from River View Park, restaurants, farmer's market and the light rail to the Hoboken Path, you could not ask for a better location."
210025004,SOLD,"JC, Heights",222 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1850,6078,"$739,000",CONDO-COOP,,1$2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,5,0,3,10,,"$739,000","$749,995",$399.46,$399.46,11/4/2021,11/13/2021,1/18/2022,9,9,,3/14/2022,,,,"$7,753",2021,$356,2021,Conventional,,,,,,Webster & Palisade,"Oversized 5 bedroom / 3 bathroom just minutes a block to RiverView Park in Jersey City Heights!  This home features upgrades throughout, including Kitchen Remodel (2018), Bathroom Remodels (2018), back patio remodel (2019). First floor is a 3 Bedroom / 2 Bathroom. Lower level is a separate 2 bedroom layout, perfect as an in-law suite or extended stay for family members.  Home includes PRIVATE Patio and Private Garage + Driveway!"
220021233,SOLD,"JC, Heights",179 HOPKINS AVE,Condominium,1585,1724,"$740,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07306,06601,00002,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$740,000","$749,000",$466.88,$466.88,12/9/2022,12/19/2022,2/8/2023,10,10,,2/9/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Central & Perry Street,"New construction luxury at it's finest. Welcome home to 179 Hopkins Ave, the epitome of luxury and convenience designed. Travel though your bright and airy living room boasting high ceilings and engineered hard wood floors into your own chef's kitchen with a bevy of amenities. This sleek and modern kitchen is equipped with plentiful custom cabinets, vented hood and a full suite of high end stainless steel appliances. The master en-suite boasts high ceilings, an oversized bathroom with double sinks, large walk in  space, and your own private balcony. This home features two other bedrooms, full sized washer/ dryer, and one other bath providing ample space for all your needs. All baths are fitted with top-of-the-line fittings and have backlit heated mirrors. Travel upstairs to your own private roof deck with stunning views of the famous NYC skyline, perfect for hosting and gatherings. Large windows all over the condo, high ceilings with recessed lighting, surround sound speakers in the living area, and 1 car garage tandem parking are included with this unit. There are dedicated closets in the shared garage for extra storage and the condo comes with the Ring security system for your peace of mind. Just the pure luxury of this home will make it an enjoyable place to call home. Located minutes away from Journal Square, light rail and all the transportation options making this the perfect location for any commuter. Take advantage of the 5 yeartax abatement, Must see!!"
