250021850,SOLD,"JC, Heights",113 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1259,5836,"$740,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2-A,"JC, Heights",07307,3601,12,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$740,000","$749,000",$587.77,$587.77,10/22/2025,10/30/2025,12/8/2025,8,8,,12/8/2025,,,,"$11,566",,$275,,Conventional,,,,,,SUMMIT AND JFK,"Constructed in 2019, this lovely top floor residence welcomes you with soaring ceilings, custom trim work, and gleaming hardwood floors. The spacious layout offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, in-unit laundry with extra shelving, a beautiful terrace off the primary bedroom, and non-tandem garage parking. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances and granite countertops with counter seating, as well as space for a full dining room table. All three bedrooms boast ample closet space and get great sunlight. The primary is home to an en-suite and walk-in closet, and the lovely terrace is perfect for enjoying a morning coffee or glass of wine. Other features include: central a/c, attic storage, garage storage, and custom closet systems. Enjoy coffee and pastries at Dulce de Leche and become regulars at The Hutton and Don. The Heights. Located between vibrant Pershing Field & newly renovated Leonard Gordon Park. Come experience all The Heights has to offer. Welcome home!"
