220020860,SOLD,"JC, Heights",218 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1366,1597,"$740,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$740,000","$749,000",$541.73,$541.73,12/1/2022,12/14/2022,1/30/2023,13,13,,1/30/2023,,,,,,$207,,Conventional,,,,,,South St & Congress,"Make your next move to this beautifully renovated home with private rooftop, storage and EV charger parking from Nkay Construction. Set one block from Washington Park in Jersey City Heights, the three bedroom layout is classically finished with crown molding, hardwood floors and large Pella windows.   White kitchen shines with sparkling waterfall quartz counters, stainless farm sink, shaker cabinets, blue accent shiplap, and black Samsung appliances. Smarthome features include ring doorbell, camera and security system, and nest thermostat.   Soak in the scenery with a private rooftop showcasing incredible cityscape views. Bathrooms boast beautiful marble double vanity, glass shower or bathtub combo and polished chrome fixtures. Owners enjoy a dedicated utility area with Samsung washer and dryer, plus private basement storage area and side-by-side, EV charger, compact car parking.  Modern gray brick building is settled on a tree-lined street just around the corner from expansive Washington Park with sports facilities, playground and walking paths. Jersey City Heights is known for its great community, excellent schools and easy NYC access, with vibrant shops, restaurants and parks!   "
210008993,SOLD,"JC, Heights",61 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1250,1623,"$740,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,4501,36,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$740,000","$725,000",$592.00,$592.00,4/15/2021,4/30/2021,6/11/2021,15,15,,6/11/2021,,,,"$10,548",2020,$169,2021,Conventional,No,No,,,,Ferry & Franklin St,"Newly built in 2019. Bright, open spaces, luxurious finishes, private roof deck, garage parking, & storage! The versatile living and dining room is flooded with natural light and flows naturally to a full stairway to your private roof deck with NYC views! The chef's kitchen has Quartz counters, SS Appliances, Carrara marble backsplash & 42 Cabinets. White oak hardwood floors, custom trim & solid core doors projects craftsmanship.  custom tiled bathrooms, floating vanities & abundant lighting. The owner's suite has a balcony, en-suite bath with large walk-in closet. Central A/C, in-unit washer/dryer and tons of closet storage make this the perfect home for any buyer seeking space in the fantastic Heights neighborhood with easy access to 2nd St Lightrail, Hoboken and JSQ PATH trains to NYC."
