t is Approx. 587 sq. ft. of outdoor rooftop space, equipped with outdoor speakers & and gas line exclusively for your BBQ set or any outdoor cooking. Great for entertainment or relaxing and enjoying the views of the freedom tower & Manhattan skyline."
