210000832,SOLD,"JC, Heights",433 LIBERTY AVE,Condominium,,298,"$749,000",CONDO-COOP,,3+RT,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02503,00030,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,9,,"$749,000","$749,000",,,1/10/2021,4/1/2021,6/3/2021,81,81,,6/5/2021,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,,,,btw Thorne & Lincoln,"Welcome to 433 Liberty Avenue! This newly constructed 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with stunning details is ideally located in the Western Slope neighborhood of Jersey City Heights. Fall in love with the elegant floor-through plan, featuring a boutique-style kitchen complete with quartz waterfall countertops and top-of-the-line Samsung appliances. The open concept living space boasts oversized windows, custom trim and crown molding throughout. A beautiful staircase leads up to your private roof deck with unobstructed views, fully equipped with gas, water, electric and entertainment hook ups. Design features include custom built-out closets, large format imported porcelain tile, Red Oak hardwood flooring, distinctive lighting, and modern finishings throughout. Unit 2 offers 1300 sq ft of living space, in addition to a full length roof deck, an oversized garage, and a balcony off the master bedroom. More features include high efficiency HVAC system, security/entertainment system, central vacuum system and much more! Additionally, buyers can look forward to winning with Jersey City’s 5-year “new construction” tax abatement; manufacture warranties, as well as a 10 year limited home warranty provided by the developer. Call or text the listing agent to schedule a tour.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           "
