240018006,SOLD,"JC, Heights",135 PROSPECT ST,Condominium,1134,1741,"$750,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,04902,00013,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$750,000","$775,000",$661.38,$661.38,9/12/2024,10/2/2024,11/22/2024,20,20,,11/22/2024,,,,"$12,887",,$247,,Conventional,,,,,,Central & Lienau,"Welcome to your fully updated Jersey City Heights condo w/ huge 1,300+ sq ft PRIVATE backyard! As you enter this three bedroom unit, you'll notice its high ceilings, oak flooring, designer kitchen and two tastefully renovated bathrooms. The kitchen features quartz counters, a center island w/ wine fridge, SS Appliances and 42 cabinets. Other features include full size laundry in unit, recessed LED lighting, 9' ceilings, Central HVAC, and a huge deeded storage room (13' x 12'). This home is ideally located just a block from the nearest bus stop to NYC, half a block from the Reservoir which is going through a multi-million dollar renovation including a hiking trail, less than 2 blocks from Pershing Park which includes a track, playground, indoor pool & ice skating rink, and a few blocks to Central Ave & Palisade Ave shopping districts which include shopping, cafes, restaurants and supermarkets."
220000792,SOLD,"JC, Heights",21 CONCORD ST,Condominium,1,1644,"$750,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07306,,,,,,,,2,0,4,5,,"$750,000","$729,000","$750,000.00","$750,000.00",1/13/2022,1/24/2022,3/24/2022,11,11,,3/29/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Observer Highway and Fleet St.,"Welcome Home. Modern styled luxury living in this Gut renovated condo.. Nestled on a quiet tree lined street within a short walk to Journal Square. Brick façade with black trim accents highlight the beauty of this home. This condo unit offers Duplex living (about 1900sqft) : complete with 3 full baths. First floor features a Spacious Living/Dining area off the kitchen. Kitchen is fully equipped with stainless steel appliances & Quartz counters. A Primary suite complete with a WIC and Primary Bath provide access to the tranquil yard space. Secondary bedroom complete this floor. The lower level features a fully finished Rec Room/Lounge Area, W/D, and a Full Bath, easily convertible to an In-law suite/Guest Room.  Access into the paver, fenced in backyard. Centrally located between Journal Square and the Heights, this property is a short walk to retail, restaurants, Path and Downtown JC"
210000037,SOLD,"JC, Heights",31 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,3050,6078,"$750,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03703,00012,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$750,000","$769,000",$245.90,$245.90,1/1/2021,2/2/2021,4/16/2021,25,25,,4/16/2021,,,,"$10,500",2020,,,Cash,No,No,,,,Central Ave and Summit Ave,"Welcome to 31 Zabriskie Street, Jersey City, an exquisite property where modern meets traditional. This captivating Victorian style home, with beautifully restored antique exterior is a rare find, in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Custom quality, thoughtful design, state-of-the-art modern finishes, built by one of Jersey City's finest developers, is elevating the standards of sophisticated and modern living. This brand new 3 bedroom 2.1 bathroom smart home spans over a 25’x107’ lot, offering 3050 square feet of open-concept living, with a state of the art Chef's Kitchen. This immaculate condominium features 10' ceilings, 7' solid-core doors, white oak hardwood flooring and oversized bay windows to allow abundant natural light.   The impeccable white high gloss European Style kitchen cabinetry with soft close, luxury stainless steel appliances, a wifi & bluetooth enabled refrigerator, central island featuring waterfall quartz countertop, a wine cooler and drawer microwave, spares no expense in the intricate design kitchen. The master bedroom includes an ensuite spa-like bathroom with dual rain showers, and an expansive walk-in closet. This magnificent condo with carefully considered floor plan that rivals Manhattan standard luxury, also provides large second bedroom, a dedicated Home Office space and a second bathroom featuring clean design, waterfall mosaic tiles, floating vanity and a soaking tub. The encompassed 1560 sqft. of recreation room, half-bath, mechanical, laundry and private enclosed fenced backyard featuring approx. 566 sqft. of outdoor space is unbeatable. This Smart Home creates ease of living and efficiency through a central HVAC sys regulated by the Nest thermostat, Wi-Fi enabled lights, Smart doorbell, all integrated via a Smart home hub. This unit also comes fully equipped with washer and dryer.   Set in the heart of Jersey City Heights, enjoy walkability to vibrant Central Avenue, where you will find the neighboring grocery stores, supermarket, major banks, public library, pharmacy, famous café and restaurants, that make routine shopping trips a breeze. Located at 2 mins walk from Hutton ST bus stop, 119 bus to NYC takes you to Port Authority within 25 mins. Close to Washington and Leonard Gordon parks, excellent schools and easy NYC access makes this property quintessential. "
220020324,SOLD,"JC, Heights",154 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1934,1727,"$750,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1B,"JC, Heights",07030,05103,00009,Heights,Pohlmann's Hall,,,,2,0,1,6,,"$750,000","$775,000",$387.80,$387.80,11/17/2022,11/30/2022,1/6/2023,13,13,,1/13/2023,,,,"$11,197",2022,$320,,Conventional,,,,,,Ferry and Franklin,"Bright, loft style condo in Pohlmann's Hall, a historic factory conversion listed in the National Register of Historic Places. Located on one of the most desirable streets in Jersey City Heights, #1B offers a private entrance from your personal parking spot & is the largest home in the building with 1900 square ft. of interior space over 3 floors, an exclusive deck, side yard, NYC views & sunlit southeastern exposure. With 2 bedrooms, a modern kitchen, super high ceilings, oversized windows & walk-in cedar closet this apartment has it all. Elevator building with a common yard, storage room, and bike room. Laundry on every floor. Close proximity to Hoboken, light rail, bus to NYC, local parks, community garden, shopping and restaurants."
210009481,SOLD,"JC, Heights",278.5 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,,1691,"$750,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,1604,35,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$750,000","$750,000",,,4/21/2021,3/5/2021,4/30/2021,0,0,,4/30/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress St & North St,"Do a double-take with this dazzling two bedroom duplex, with over 1,500 square feet and priceless private rooftop with gorgeous NYC views. Feel the spaciousness in this newly constructed home, and truly trade up with the high-end finishes and quality upgrades prevalent by this coveted Jersey City developer.   Glide through the white oak floors into the ample living, dining and kitchen areas and onto your beautiful rooftop. Kitchen features waterfall white quartz counters, stone tile accents, farmhouse sink with pull-down faucet and black Samsung appliances. Home brings both a classic and modern appeal with classic crown molding, recess lighting and excellent smart-home extras.   Steps from enormous Washington Park with tennis, baseball, soccer, splash pad, soft play, dog run and more, this home is settled on a quiet residential street in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Enjoy access to essential shops on Central Avenue, excellent schools, vibrant community and easy NYC access. "
220000026,SOLD,"JC, Heights",320 TERRACE AVE,Condominium,1528,1691,"$750,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$750,000","$775,000",$490.84,$490.84,1/2/2022,1/27/2022,3/18/2022,25,25,,3/24/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,North St & Leonard St,"Please note, some finishes may differ from these photos/copy.  One of Jersey City's finest builders is at it again! These two new construction condominiums will quarrel over nothing except which wide open layout offers the best flow, and whose oversized outdoor space should host the next summer barbecue. This top floor 3 bed 2 bath home will be beautifully finished with absolute thoughtfulness and top-notch quality. Main floor living and dining area layout flows into chef-inspired kitchens finished with white marble waterfall island, inlay farm sink, Fabuwood cabinets, Samsung stainless steel appliances, must-have wine fridge, kohler fixtures and modern pendant lighting. Master suite and additional bedrooms boast ceiling fans, Pella windows, and custom walk-in closets, while bathrooms host high-end porcelain tiles, modern vanities and multiple shower heads. You'll be able hear a pin drop in this ultra-peaceful atmosphere, thanks to the extra-thick soundproofing, subfloor and insulation. A tech-lovers dream with every mod con, finishes include home entertainment wiring with 5.1 speakers, Ring doorbell, camera and security system, central vacuum and Nest thermostat. This top unit’s brag-worthy expansive roof deck with speakers, gas & water for ultimate entertaining (or your own private dance party) shows incredible NYC views! Steps from Riverview Fisk and Washington parks - as well as both 2nd St & 9th St Light Rail stations - this neighborhood is known for great schools and easy NYC access, all amid the eclectic and vibrant scene of Jersey City Heights. *Photos are of similar listing, different location*"
220002216,SOLD,"JC, Heights",109 POPLAR ST,Condominium,1225,6199,"$750,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,00803,00020,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$750,000","$739,000",$612.24,$612.24,2/8/2022,3/4/2022,4/28/2022,24,24,,4/29/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy & Nelson,"Brand new construction!!  No expense was spared in the heart of booming Jersey City Heights this captivating condo features 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, modern open concept living, fully equipped kitchen with state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances, 5 burner stove, convection oven, custom cabinets, quartz counter tops with breakfast bar. Main bedroom with private en-suite bath and sliding glass doors that lead to your balcony, 2 generous sized bedrooms. Private roof top deck. Features include hardwood floors throughout, central air/heat, washer and dryer and LED lighting. 1 car shared tandem spot included. Minutes to Journal Square PATH and bus station, restaurants, shops and all major highways and tunnels. Come and see for yourself why Jersey City was named the Sixth Borough of New York City. This property is eligible for a 5 year tax abatement."
220010865,SOLD,"JC, Heights",63 SOUTH ST,Condominium,1020,1691,"$750,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,1,2,5,,"$750,000","$750,000",$735.29,$735.29,6/14/2022,6/14/2022,6/14/2022,0,0,,6/14/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Sherman Ave & Webster Ave,"Make this modern marvel home in The Heights! Local builders, Nkay Construction, have done it again with this super smart floor through 2 bed, 2.5 bath complete with parking (equipped with eCharging stations for each unit!).  Situated on the corner of a tree-lined street, this impressive home offers oversized windows with sunlight streaming in on three sides of the 2 bed and 2.5 bath layout. Beautiful bay windows open to the spacious upstairs with flowing kitchen, living and dining area complete with pewter oak hardwood floors and crown molding.   Gorgeous navy blue accents in island highlight the bright eat-in kitchen with waterfall quartz counters, tile backsplash and custom shaker cabinets. Additional features include apron sink, black stainless Samsung appliances and matte black fixtures including wall mounted pot filler faucet. Stylish bathrooms offer highlights such as herringbone grey porcelain tile, smart mirrors and glass shower with penny tile floor pattern plus multi head rain shower system. Primary ensuite offers a must-have double vanity and built-out walk-in closet.   Additional tech upgrades include smart doorbell, smart thermostat, camera and security system and central vacuum. Situated walking distance to bustling Central Avenue, expansive Washington Park or Riverview Fisk Park with NYC views and light rail access, this home is the ideal combination of location and modern luxury."
230000902,SOLD,"JC, Heights",87 LEONARD ST,Condominium,1352,1707,"$755,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,#2,"JC, Heights",07307,00403,00028,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$755,000","$755,000",$558.43,$558.43,1/16/2023,4/26/2023,7/5/2023,100,100,,7/6/2023,,,,,,$225,,Conventional,,,,,,*off JFK Blvd,"New NKAY Construction in a spectacular tree lined and prime location; JC Heights (steps away to NY transportation)!  *BUYERS CONCESSION:  $5,000 CREDIT AT CLOSING FOR ALLOWABLE CLOSING COSTS*  This superior quality 3 bed, 2 bath condo features 1352 square foot of living space with deeded parking (Electric Charging Station) and private 1200 square foot (approx.) roof deck (like no others + gas-water-electric connections) with NY views, modern kitchen containing quartz counter tops with waterfall island & Samsung black stainless steel appliances, wine fridge, Kohler plumbing fixtures, custom closets, high end finishes, aluminum railings, low voltage system (burglar alarm, video door bell, 5.1 channel home theater), elevated framing materials used for improved insulation and sound proof penetration, garage parking and much more! *10 years builders warranty & 5 year tax abatement included. Close to NY transportation, shopping, restaurants, parks and schools.  Schedule now!"
240014766,SOLD,"JC, Heights",185 COLUMBIA AVE,Condominium,1576,1598,"$755,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,51,1203,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$755,000","$735,000",$479.06,$479.06,7/30/2024,8/6/2024,10/1/2024,7,7,,10/4/2024,,,,"$10,316",2023,$200,,Conventional,,,,,,North & Bleecker,"Welcome to 185 Columbia Ave, a stunning, 2 years young property by one of Jersey City's premier builders. This home features a unique façade with charcoal board, batten paneling and red brick siding, blending modern and traditional styles on a 25'x100 lot. This luxurious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom condominium offers 1,576 square feet of open-concept living space with a state-of-the-art Chef's Kitchen. Enjoy 9' ceilings, 7 Amaro European White Oak hardwood flooring, and oversized Anderson windows that flood the space with natural light. The chef's kitchen boasts a breakfast bar, white shaker cabinetry, luxury Samsung appliances, quartz countertops and white subway tiles. The open living and dining area extends to a private terrace and offer stunning sunset views. The extra large master bedroom includes an ensuite spa-like bathroom and two spacious walk-in closets. The condo also features a second bedroom, a home office, and a second bathroom with porcelain tiles and a soaking tub. Entertain your guests on the 413 sq ft private rooftop deck with panoramic sunset views and hookups for a gas barbecue grill! The home is equipped with a central HVAC system and Samsung full size washer and dryer."
