230004924,SOLD,"JC, Heights",201 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1150,1728,"$755,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03805,00019,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$755,000","$750,000",$656.52,$656.52,3/28/2023,5/3/2023,6/26/2023,36,36,,6/28/2023,,,,"$9,747",2022,$250,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton and Griffith,"Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, this immaculate property features wide-planked select oak flooring with natural finish throughout, and an exclusive private outdoor deck that can be accessed from the suite's master bedroom. It features a sophisticated open floor plan with 9 ft. ceilings, semi-custom kitchen with floating shelves, and beautiful gold brass finishes, complemented by a luxurious waterfall quartz countertop. Appliances are also provided and include a GE Profile 30” Smart Slide-in Range, Sharp Stainless Steel Microwave Draw Oven, GE Profile Counter Depth Fingerprint Resistant French Door Refrigerator, and a GE Profile Dishwasher. Each of the bedrooms comes with custom-made closets designed by “Closets by Design”, and the master bathroom is equipped with sleek matte black hardware, Hexagon polished marble, mosaic backsplash tiles, and a frameless glass shower door. The property is a “smart home” and comes wired with interior speakers in the master bedroom and living room, as well as a Honeywell security system, and a Video intercom accessible via phone and system. Conveniently located near 9th/Congress and 2nd Street light rail, and within a short 10-minute walk to the Riverview Arts District and all its popular restaurants and shops, it is the perfect place for commuting to NYC and Hoboken. The neighborhood is currently undergoing a $2M renovation, making it even more appealing."
