220015426,SOLD,"JC, Heights",210 CONGRESS ST,Condominium,1625,1603,"$755,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,1402,43,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$755,000","$759,900",$464.62,$464.62,8/25/2022,9/19/2022,10/28/2022,25,25,,10/28/2022,,,,"$7,555",2021,$200,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit and JFK,"Gorgeous new construction (2020), with 1,625 sq feet of living space inside and 1,000 sq ft of private living space outside. Get everything on your wish list: 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms; a kitchen outfitted with white shaker cabinets, sleek white quartz countertop, breakfast bar, and wine fridge, and an open concept living room with over-sized south-facing windows and sliding doors. That means bright, beautiful, sunlight all day long.  Primary bedroom easily fits a king sized bed - with plenty of extra space to work or lounge.  Both (2) additional bedrooms are large enough for a queen sized bed, a second workspace, a nursery, a play room, or an exercise room - great flex space for whatever your need!   And that roof deck... it's an outdoor bonus room for your home, and it's private - solely for you use.  BBQ and entertain with all of your family and friends. NYC views to the east, sunsets to the west, and cool breezes everywhere on those hot summer days.   *Note: Three years remain on city's tax abatement and 8 years remain on builder's warranty.  Home centrally located - bus to NYC (23 min. commute) on the corner, 1.5 blocks to shops on Central Ave., and just a 12 minute walk to the Hudson Light Rail.  Also walking distance to the #1 K-8 charter school in Jersey City - rating 10 out of 10 by greatschools.org's national ratings. Stop by this weekend 1-4pm both days."
250015000,SOLD,"JC, Heights",176 GRIFFITH ST,Condominium,1675,1653,"$755,800",CONDO-COOP,,G & 1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2801,38,,,,,,2,1,2,7,,"$755,800","$685,000",$451.22,$451.22,7/23/2025,7/30/2025,10/1/2025,7,7,,10/2/2025,,,,"$10,370",2025,$395,2025,Conventional,No,No,,,,Central & Summit Ave,"1600+ SqFt Duplex Condo with a private and exclusive Backyard. Step into your new home in the heart of Jersey City Heights.  This home is a winner with modern finishes and a fantastic layout that feels spacious and airy.  On the main living level are 2 sizable bedrooms, along with a great big open concept kitchen, living, dining with access to the yard, lots of closet space & Washer/dryer on this level.  Main features are the soaring high ceilings, and big windows letting light pour in, warm recessed lighting, natural hardwood floors, and decorative fireplace.  In the kitchen you have a Quartz waterfall Countertop, an outside vented stove fan to keep smells away, newer appliances and two-tone cabinetry.  Downstairs you have access via the interior stairs or directly from the front/outside of the house adding to the appeal and conveniences.  This space is extra living space, home office or whatever you can imagine and also offers a ½ bath on this level.  The home has central A/C and an energy-efficient tankless water heater. Best part? You get your very own huge backyard—a perfect place to relax, dine alfresco, or just chill after work and on weekends.  The size and scope of this home and additional yard are incredible and must be seen to be felt and appreciated.  Step outside the property and your right in the buzzing Heights District, close to neighborhood parks like Pershing Field & Riverview Park.  Surrounded by shopping and restaurants and in a transportation Meca with bus, Light Rail and PATH all within reach.  Call now for more information or to schedule a private tour! "
210005588,SOLD,"JC, Heights",33 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1200,6078,"$756,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,B,"JC, Heights",07307-2341,4403,24,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$756,000","$759,000",$630.00,$630.00,3/9/2021,4/14/2021,7/3/2021,36,36,,4/5/2022,,,,,,$195,,Conventional,,,,,,Manhattan & Franklin,"BRAND NEW HIGH-END NEW-CONSTRUCTION in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This amazing 3 Bedroom 2 Bath has 1200 square feet of open floor plan living space with soaring 10-foot ceilings, and oversized custom windows drenching the space in natural light. The renovated Chef’s kitchen features shaker style white cabinetry, dark grey center island with Waterfall Quartz countertops, and the Stainless Steel Premium GE Cafe Package, complete with Smart Refrigerator and dishwasher. The large master bedroom has an en-suite bath, designer fixtures, and spacious walk-in closet. Two more generous bedrooms have double closets, and share a second full bathroom with quartz countertops and soaking tub. Your large private roof deck with close to 300 square feet has views of the Empire State building and Freedom Tower. This home has everything you need, including central air/heating system, hardwood floors throughout, 7-foot solid doors, in-unit laundry, plenty of storage and closets, AND 1 car Garage parking spot included. Close to 2nd St Light-Rail and minutes to PATH Train, this space is a commuters dream. Smart Home Technology with Nest thermostat and Smart Lock. Eligible for 5-year tax abatement! Come see the home today! Owner is a licensed realtor."
210005587,SOLD,"JC, Heights",33 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1400,6078,"$756,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2,A,"JC, Heights",07307-2341,4403,24,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$756,000","$779,000",$540.00,$540.00,3/9/2021,4/14/2021,7/28/2021,0,0,,4/1/2022,,,,,,$225,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Manhattam,"BRAND NEW HIGH-END NEW-CONSTRUCTION in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This amazing 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath has 1400 square feet of open floor plan living space with soaring 10-foot ceilings, and oversized custom windows drenching the space in natural light. The renovated Chef’s kitchen features shaker style white cabinetry, dark grey center island with Waterfall Quartz countertops, and the Stainless Steel Premium GE Cafe Package, complete with Smart Refrigerator and dishwasher. The large master bedroom has an en-suite bath, designer fixtures, and spacious walk-in closet. Also on the main floor are two more generous bedrooms with double closets, and a second full bathroom with quartz countertops and soaking tub. On the lower level, enjoy the family room with half bath, and sliding glass doors that lead to a private landscaped backyard and patio. This home has everything you need, including central air/heating system, hardwood floors throughout, 7-foot solid doors, in-unit laundry, plenty of storage and closets, AND 1 car Garage parking spot included. Close to 2nd St Light-Rail and minutes to PATH Train, this space is a commuters dream. Smart Home Technology with Nest thermostat and Smart Lock. Eligible for 5-year tax abatement! Come see the home today! Owner is a licensed realtor."
230017859,SOLD,"JC, Heights",180 BLEECKER ST,Condominium,1736,1724,"$758,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,01202,00073,,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$758,000","$849,000",$436.64,$436.64,10/23/2023,11/13/2023,1/23/2024,21,21,,1/24/2024,,,,$0,2022,,,Conventional,,,,,,South St. & Paterson St.,"Welcome to this spacious and sunlit new construction in the Jersey City Heights! This modern duplex is pre-designed for the latest in home technology and entertainment. Boasting wide plank solid hardwood floors throughout, 10ft ceiling, modern crown molding, 8ft custom doors in unit washer dryer, LED lighting, and private landscaped backyard! Pure white quartz counters with waterfall feature, custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and luxurious finishes provides an elevated ambiance in your home. Unit number 1 is a large 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, and also has an additional living room giving you ample space for entertainment and flexible living with a beautiful private backyard. While unit number two offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and a private roof deck. This property is situated in an unbeatable area of the JC Heights, providing easy commutability and excellent access to public transportation. Direct bus lines to NYC Port Authority, Hoboken, and Downtown JC make commuting a breeze. The convenience continues with nearby Hudson Light Rail Stations, as well as Pershing Field's indoor pool and ice skating rink just a few blocks away. Moreover, residents can enjoy the scenic beauty of Riverview Park, which not only offers breathtaking views but also hosts a variety of exciting activities such as Farmers Market, movie nights, and engaging neighborhood events!"
250009265,SOLD,"JC, Heights",63 JEFFERSON AVE,Condominium,1200,6638,"$760,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Journal Square,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$760,000","$739,000",$633.33,$633.33,5/9/2025,6/18/2025,9/22/2025,40,40,,10/23/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Baldwin Ave. & Oakland Ave.,"Discover the perfect blend of sophisticated design and urban convenience in this strikingly modern duplex condo, nestled on a quiet side street between Palisade and Central Avenues. Featuring dramatic architectural elements and sleek, clean lines, this home offers an expansive two-story layout designed for effortless living and entertaining.   The open-concept main level is anchored by an oversized double waterfall island, seamlessly integrating defined living and dining spaces. Glass railings and a floating staircase add to the contemporary aesthetic, with a stylish powder room on main floor. The chef’s kitchen boasts bold black quartz countertops, a tiled backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and custom cabinetry, with an oversized island offering seating for four.   Upstairs, a glass-walled staircase leads to three spacious bedrooms and two luxurious full baths. The king-sized primary suite features a spa-inspired ensuite with black and white marble tile, a glass-enclosed rain shower, and an oversized floating vanity. The second bath exudes tranquility with wood-toned tiles, an extra-deep soaking tub, and dual showerheads.   Perfectly positioned for commuters, this home is just steps from Hoboken Stairs, 2nd Street Light Rail, Congress Street Elevator, and Journal Square PATH. Enjoy the vibrant neighborhood with coffee shops, restaurants, farmer’s markets, Pershing Field, and Riverview-Fisk Park offering breathtaking  NYC skyline views.   Deeded parking space available for purchase. **Reach out to our preferred lender e for special financing programs, offering $8,000 to 22,000 grants for down payment assistance or closing costs.**"
210011548,SOLD,"JC, Heights",15 NELSON AVE,Condominium,1950,1707,"$760,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2+,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,10,,"$760,000","$739,000",$389.74,$389.74,5/13/2021,5/18/2021,8/6/2021,5,5,,8/9/2021,,,,"$7,674",,$307,,Conventional,,,,,,*off Kennedy,"2015 (NKAY) Construction - Attention to Detail: Immaculate 3 bed, 2.5 bath condo conveniently located featuring a modern kitchen containing granite countertops with stainless steel appliances, approximately 1950 square feet of living space which includes a family room on the ground floor and private/custom finished basement, central air/heat, spacious closets, high end finishes including crown moldings, NEST thermostat, RING door bell, washer/dryer, central vacuum system, 1 car tandem garage parking (including side by side in front), private deeded back yard for your entertaining and much more!  Very close to NY transportation (bus & rail), shopping, restaurants, parks, and schools.  (monthly fee includes: water, insurance, reserves, common space)"
240008054,SOLD,"JC, Heights",177 LAIDLAW AVE,Condominium,1852,1526,"$760,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307-0000,,,,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$760,000","$725,000",$410.37,$410.37,5/1/2024,5/10/2024,6/28/2024,9,9,,7/17/2024,,,,"$9,201",2023,$250,2023,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & Central,"Location, Location this 2018 building is nestled on the border of Journal Square and Jersey City Heights making this 3 bedroom, 3 bath condo a perfect property for investors, home occupants as well as Air BNB potential. Walking distance to PATH and low maintenance fee. Second floor is a beautiful 2 bedroom 2 bath with tons of natural light, hardwood floors and a primary suite currently renting month to month for $2500. First floor is vacant 1 bedroom with parking and all separate utilities can be rented for $2,000    "
220010820,SOLD,"JC, Heights",580 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1192,1692,"$760,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,404,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,The Riveview,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$760,000","$760,000",$637.58,$637.58,12/16/2022,12/6/2022,6/7/2023,0,176,,6/13/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress and South,"Step inside and immediately feel at ease in this unit. BRAND NEW GROUND UP CONSTRUCTION at The Riverview offers impeccable comfort and convenience, situated on Palisade Avenue, at the heart of the neighborhood’s exciting retail/dining corridor. Choose from two- and three-bedroom residences in this intimate 13-unit building, crafted to meet your every need. The well-proportioned units are carefully constructed with today’s most in-demand elements. Flow-through rooms and thoughtful appointments combine for luxurious comfort. Expansive energy-efficient insulated windows frame the interiors with abundant natural light. Elegant top-line finishes include wide plank flooring, granite countertops and premium Fischer-Paykel appliances. Thoughtfully curated amenities bring ease to today’s busy lifestyles. A package room, 12-car parking garage with electric chargers and ground-level bike storage are among the building’s many essential comforts designed to enhance your lifestyle. Make this inspired collection of pet-friendly condominiums home. 10-year New Home Warranty, Manufacturer’s Warranty on all appliances and systems, and tax abatement. Photos are of model unit."
220002592,SOLD,"JC, Heights",469 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,2200,64,"$760,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03001,00018,Heights,,,,,2,1,1,7,,"$760,000","$749,999",$345.45,$345.45,2/14/2022,3/2/2022,4/18/2022,16,16,,4/18/2022,,,,"$9,101",2021,$474,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Griffiths & Bowers,"Exquisitely remodeled 2BD|1.5BA home located in the heart of JC Heights conveniently located on the highly desirable Palisade Avenue.  With just over 2,000SF of expansive living space, this retro/chic gem boasts contemporary style and sleek modern design, while featuring a wealth of original architectural details, including original leaded glass archways, vintage built-in mirrors, boxed ceilings, meticulous corbels, medallions and crown molding throughout.   No detail has been overlooked at this impeccably designed home; from hardwood floors and state-of-the-art appliances to oversized windows allowing for a flood of natural light and stunning NYC views.   Awaken your culinary spirit in an airy chef-inspired kitchen featuring a stained glass skylight and stainless steel appliances, a 5 Burner GE Monogram Stovetop/Oven, Bosch Dishwasher, GE Café Fridge, double sink, built-in wine refrigerator, plenty of cabinets, and an extended breakfast bar with granite countertops.   The elegantly designed Master Suite has a high ceiling windowed en-suite bath with dual vanity, marble sink with cabinetry, enormous soaking tub and fabulous separate shower. A massive walk-in closet and den/office nook also awaits in this gorgeous Master suite allowing for ample storage and work from home ease.  Central A/C. Nest Thermostat. Washer/Dryer in unit.    Palisade Avenue is bustling with sought-after restaurants, boutique shopping, and endless public transportation into NYC via bus and train. Your quest for timeless modern living awaits!"
240021318,SOLD,"JC, Heights",988 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,1445,6706,"$760,000",CONDO-COOP,,2/3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2802,4,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$760,000","$789,000",$525.95,$525.95,10/30/2024,12/19/2024,1/23/2025,50,50,,1/27/2025,,,2023,,2023,$185,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Bower St and Lincoln St,"Welcome to 988 Summit Avenue! This new luxury ground up construction offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Experience an open floor layout drenched in natural lighting and breath-taking cathedral ceiling in the living room. Enjoy the ample cabinet space in your state-of-the-art kitchen, with Samsung stainless steel appliances and smart fridge. Kitchen cabinets are two tone shaker cabinets, designed with a beautiful accent gold hardware. The kitchen peninsula can easily sit 4 people. Features include Hardwood floors, custom trim, recess lighting, chic designer tiles throughout, in unit laundry, and modern fixtures. Master bedroom offers a sliding door to walk out to your private balcony, a large walk-in closet, and a master bathroom which includes a double sink vanity. Entertain in your private roof top deck and enjoy the luxury of having a wet bar just a few feet away as you entertain. Close to Pershing Field Park, amazing restaurants on Central Ave, close to NYC transportation, new upcoming reservoir where you can enjoy water activities. Schedule a tour today! OPEN HOUSE THIS SUNDAY (DEC 14) 2PM-4PM"
240020209,SOLD,"JC, Heights",320 TERRACE AVE,Condominium,1528,1657,"$760,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307-3964,,16,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$760,000","$799,000",$497.38,$497.38,10/14/2024,4/22/2025,5/22/2025,190,190,,5/22/2025,,,,"$9,630",2023,,,Conventional,,,,,,North Street & Leonard Street,"Modern Loft with Stunning Views & Sunsets Discover your urban oasis in this sun-drenched three-bedroom condo at 320 Terrace Avenue, #2. This beautifully designed loft boasts modern finishes, expansive outdoor space, and breathtaking views and magnificent sunsets.  Key features include: •	Open Floor Plan: Enjoy a spacious living area with oversized windows that flood the space with natural light. •	Chef's Kitchen: The gourmet kitchen features high-end appliances including a wine chiller, large quartz island, and plenty of counter space to entertain. •	Primary Suite: The master bedroom includes a walk-in closet, a private bathroom with a luxurious shower, and stunning city views. •	Guest Bedrooms: Two additional bedrooms offer comfortable retreats for family or guests. •	Outdoor Oasis: Relax on your private roof deck, complete with surround sound outdoor speakers, a Weber gas grill and water hookups, and breathtaking sunsets. •	Smart Home Features: Enjoy the modern conveniences of a smart home system with features like a security camera, Nest thermostat, automated luxury window treatments and central vacuum. •	Prime Location: Situated in the vibrant Jersey City Heights neighborhood, this condo offers easy access to NYC via public transportation and is close to parks, schools, and shops. •	Parking: no worries….Enjoy a tandem garage parking with extra storage and a large wide driveway! Don't miss this opportunity to own a truly exceptional urban residence. Schedule a viewing today to experience the beauty and convenience of this modern loft. •	BONUS included in sale: Roof deck outdoor furniture, Sonos amp and Weber Genesis Gas Grill with accessories"
250002587,SOLD,"JC, Heights",376 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,2269,6078,"$760,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,3903,4,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$760,000","$749,900",$334.95,$334.95,2/7/2025,3/3/2025,6/10/2025,24,24,,6/12/2025,,"$509,300",2023,"$11,444",2023,,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton St and Franklin St,"Come check out this Massive 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath Loft style apartment in Prime Location of Jersey City Heights! 16 Ft ceilings, amazing custom graffiti-art from local Jersey City's finest, Mr. Mustart. Beautiful loft w/ industrial upgrades overseeing the apartment. Newly re-pointed exposed brick in Master bedroom with a large custom open closet layout that connects to the master bathroom which acts as a Jack & Jill setup. Enough room for your own gym, an office/bar area, living & dining! A 7-minute walk to 2nd Street Light Rail Station to get you to the Hoboken PATH in 1 stop (less than 4 minute train ride). Also a bus stop on the corner direct to Port Authority, close to shops, parks & great restaurants!"
240017264,SOLD,"JC, Heights",573 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,943,1603,"$760,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,4A,"JC, Heights",07307,02304,00024,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$760,000","$765,000",$805.94,$805.94,9/3/2024,9/27/2024,10/31/2024,24,24,,10/31/2024,,,,$0,,$351,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Congress St & South St,"Direct stunning NYC views! 1 private storage space included in sale. Welcome to 573 Palisade Avenue, where unparalleled sophistication meets breathtaking views in an exclusive collection of seven condominium homes in a boutique-style elevator building.  Each two-bedroom, two-bathroom condominium home features spacious open floor plans of meticulously designed living space and private outdoor spaces. 10 - 14 ft ceilings soar above engineered hardwood floors, creating an airy sanctuary illuminated by recessed and custom light fixtures. The expansive triple pane Pella windows frame stunning vistas of the Manhattan skyline, inviting you to unwind against a backdrop of urban splendor. Kitchens feature custom 2-toned cabinetry, Samsung stainless steel appliances, Calacatta Laza Quartz countertops, wine cooler and direct vent exhaust hood. Bathrooms include Porcelanosa tiles with Kohler fixtures, deep soaking tubs and dual flush toilets.  You'll love the convenience of having in-home laundry, integrated intercom and security system and a home that is prewired for home automation.  Unwind and socialize on our exclusive residents rooftop lounge offering sweeping NYC views, providing an extraordinary backdrop for relaxation or entertaining guests. This property boasts unparalleled ease of access to New York City, making your commute as breezy as a walk in the adjacent Fisk Park. Whether you prefer the NJ Transit buses or the convenience of the 9th Street-Congress Street Light Rail Station right at your doorstep, your connection to the city has never been smoother. And with breathtaking views of the Manhattan skyline from your window, every day feels like a picturesque escape. This prime Jersey City Heights location offers you not just a home, but a lifestyle."
210007690,SOLD,"JC, Heights",130 SOUTH ST,Condominium,,1653,"$760,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$760,000","$760,000",,,4/1/2021,5/27/2021,7/16/2021,56,56,,7/19/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & Central,"Location location location! Steps away from Central Ave Shopping District, 130 South St redefines luxury condos. This ground up new construction offers 2 units with impeccable finishes, parking space, and private outdoor space. Unit 2 offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a large living room with beautiful coffered ceilings and a private rooftop terrace with full NYC views. Features include Hardwood floors, custom trim, large spacious kitchen with Samsung stainless steel appliances and smart fridge, a wine fridge, quartz countertop, chic designer tiles throughout. Lots of closet space throughout with custom shelving, in unit laundry, and modern fixtures. Master bedroom offers a sliding door to walkout to your private balcony, a large walk in closet, and a master bathroom with a spa shower panel. Steps away from Washington Park, amazing restaurants on Central Ave, close to NYC transportation. Schedule a tour today! For virtual tour and floor plans visit 130southst.com "
