220021912,SOLD,"JC, Heights",94 IRVING ST,Condominium,1616,270,"$770,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,703,42,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$770,000","$799,000",$476.49,$476.49,12/27/2022,2/13/2023,5/30/2023,48,48,,5/30/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,KENNEDY AND NELSON AVE,"Welcome to a luxury and Modern Condominium in the Heights!! This spectacular modern duplex offers on the lower floor an extra room space with wet bar and half bath, plus direct access to the backyard ideal for a daily entertainment. On the top Enjoy your primary bedroom with its own en-suite, walk-in closet, and a full bath with a double vanity, led light mirrors and marble titled. The second and third bedrooms, with a large closet and 1 full bath are perfect for the whole family and friends. Beautiful open concept with a stunning kitchen equipped with custom two-tone cabinetries, beautiful waterfall island with gleaming quartz countertops and stainless-steel appliances. Include hardwood floors throughout, central air/heat, washer and dryer plus 1 car tandem shared spot. Close to Washington Park, major public transportation to NYC, Schools, restaurants, coffee shops and more!! call for a private tour now."
