240017534,SOLD,"JC, Heights",65 CHARLES ST,Condominium,2161,1597,"$770,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$770,000","$779,000",$356.32,$356.32,9/6/2024,10/17/2024,2/21/2025,41,41,,2/21/2025,,,,,,,,FHA,,,,,,JFK and Summit Ave,"Be at home in this beautiful newly renovated duplex in the heart of The Heights, where classic design meets modern convenience in an unbeatable location. With over 2,000 sq ft, this spacious home features two-stories, three bedrooms, two and a half baths, and a private yard plus parking. The interior invites with 9-inch ceilings and natural light illuminating the wide plank oak hardwood floors. The eat-in kitchen hosts clean white quartz countertop, matching backsplash, white shaker cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Head downstairs to enjoy the added bonus room complete with custom wet bar, or to your private yard for outdoor living and daily relaxation. Each bedroom is designed with ample closet space for all your storage needs. Bathrooms bring style and sensibility with extras like floor-to-ceiling tile, a double vanity, and a choice of a soaker tub or a glass shower.  Just one block from Summit and Central Avenue, you’ll have endless shops and restaurants at your doorstep. Explore the nearby parks—Leonard Gordon, Pershing Field Park, and Washington Parks—offering playgrounds, nature trails, sports facilities, farmers markets, and a swimming pool. Jersey City Heights is known for its excellent community, artistic vibe, incredible parks and schools and easy access to NYC and surrounding neighborhoods."
220003567,SOLD,"JC, Heights",112 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1937,1605,"$770,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03404,00034,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$770,000","$749,000",$397.52,$397.52,3/2/2022,3/9/2022,4/25/2022,7,7,,4/25/2022,,,,"$7,499",2021,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & JFK,"Now is your opportunity to have all the modern day conveniences and enjoy city living. Make this expansive, sunny and bright, beautiful newly constructed 3 bedroom/2.5 bathroom plus bonus office/living/playroom, parking and private walk-out backyard your new home. Additional thoughtful features of this home include: central HVAC, Quartz countertops, hardwood floors throughout, open floor plan living space, walk-in closet and balcony in master bedroom, recessed lighting, in-unit washer/dryer, Bosch and Samsung appliances, and Anderson windows. With over 1900 sq ft of living space and the private backyard, this is a dream home, perfect for living, working, and entertaining. Close to restaurants, shops, parks and NYC transportation. Truly a wonderful place to call home!"
230006015,SOLD,"JC, Heights",129 CONGRESS ST,Condominium,1650,1568,"$775,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,01506,00015,Heights,129 Congress Residences,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$775,000","$795,000",$469.70,$469.70,4/15/2023,5/22/2023,7/14/2023,32,32,,7/14/2023,,,,"$10,723",2022,$312,2022,Conventional,No,No,,,,Central Ave & Passaic Ave,"This recently built luxury condo is conveniently located in the center of booming neighborhood of Jersey City Heights. This home offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, two living rooms, an open chef’s kitchen, a spacious pantry, a backyard, a balcony, parking space and a storage room. Features include hardwood floors, modern GE appliances, in-unit washer and dryer, Ring security system, WiFi enabled Schlage lock, smart switches and Nest thermostat. Custom blinds and drapery plus West Elm light fixtures give this unit a truly deluxe feel. The bonus family room is ideal for hosting friends and family. The room opens into an expansive backyard for indoor-outdoor entertaining. With excellent commute options including the 85 bus to Hoboken and 119 bus to NYC-Port Authority right around the corner, you can reach NYC in just 20 mins. Located on an idyllic street, you will be steps away from beautiful parks and the best restaurants and cafés in the neighborhood."
260004739,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",135 NELSON AVE,Condominium,1300,1623,"$775,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,00701,00016,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$775,000",$596.15,,3/18/2026,,,22,,,3/18/2026,,,,,,$288,2026,,,,,,,Grace and Leonard St.,"Welcome to 135 Nelson Avenue — a stunning newly constructed luxury condo in the heart of Jersey City Heights.  Built in 2024, this exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence showcases soaring 10-foot ceilings, oversized 8-foot doors, and a dramatic floor-to-ceiling glass façade that floods the home with natural light.  Designed for modern living, the open-concept layout features a sleek chef’s kitchen equipped with premium Samsung Bespoke appliances, stylish two-tone cabinetry, quartz countertops, and a peninsula with seating—perfect for both everyday living and entertaining.  The oversized primary suite offers a private retreat, complete with a spacious walk-in closet, additional storage, and an elegant en-suite bath. French doors lead directly to a beautifully appointed terrace, creating a seamless indoor-outdoor experience. Two additional bedrooms provide versatility for guests, a home office, or a growing household.  Additional highlights include hardwood floors throughout, central air and forced hot air, in-unit washer/dryer, and abundant closet space.  Enjoy the expansive rooftop deck—ideal for relaxing or entertaining with skyline views. The home also includes one garage parking space, pre-wired for an electric vehicle charger.  Situated on a charming tree-lined street, just moments from Central and Palisade Avenues, you’ll have easy access to top dining, shopping, and everyday conveniences. Experience the best of Jersey City Heights living, with excellent schools, vibrant local businesses, and a quick commute to NYC."
250015047,SOLD,"JC, Heights",15 NELSON AVE,Condominium,2672,1742,"$775,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,01301,00070,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$775,000","$799,000",$290.04,$290.04,7/23/2025,8/26/2025,11/3/2025,34,34,,11/3/2025,,,,"$13,940",2024,$307,,Conventional,,,,,,1st St and 2nd St,"Explore this exquisite contemporary condo featuring 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, crafted with a chic modern style. The kitchen is equipped with elegant granite countertops and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Offering over 2,000 square feet of living space, this home includes a ground floor family room, a private finished basement, and central air/heat. Appreciate the spacious closets and premium finishes such as crown moldings, a NEST thermostat, and a RING doorbell. Additional features include a washer/dryer, central vacuum system, pantry closet, and one car parking. Entertain effortlessly in your private deeded backyard. Constructed in 2015 by one of Jersey City's leading builders, the condo showcases a distinctive split floor plan for enhanced privacy. The oversized primary bedroom includes double closets, Norman blackout shades, and an en-suite bathroom with a spa-like rain shower. The other bedrooms share a newly updated bathroom with a jacuzzi bathtub. Flooded with natural light from its east/west exposures, the condo also provides two off-street parking spaces (one tandem garage spot and one outdoor side-by-side spot) and an EV charger. Ideally situated close to NYC transportation (bus & rail), shopping, dining, parks, and schools."
230000323,SOLD,"JC, Heights",76 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1527,1597,"$775,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$775,000","$795,000",$507.53,$507.53,1/6/2023,2/16/2023,4/13/2023,41,41,,4/13/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & JFK,"High ceilings, oversized windows and modern upgrades promise to impress in this ground-up new construction home in Jersey City Heights. Complete with classic gray hardwood floors, crown molding and an inlay marble fireplace, the two-story, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home includes a private backyard and side-by-side parking for ultimate homeowner appeal.  The modern brick exterior is accented with driveway pavers and tasteful landscaping. Step inside into a flowing open floorplan with spacious kitchen, living and dining, punctuated with stylish pendant lighting and exposed wrought-iron and wood banister. Kitchen offers gleaming white quartz countertops, striking tile backsplash, custom cabinetry with accent glass-front doors and stainless appliances including wine fridge.   Well-designed bathrooms are finished with porcelain tile, smart mirrors, glass showers and matte black hardware. A full-floor primary ensuite offers private sanctuary with an expansive walk-in closet, sliding glass doors with private balcony and double vanity in the bathroom. Downstairs leads to the beautiful backyard complete with both pavers and lawn.   Walking distance to both Washington Park with sports facilities, dog run, playgrounds and walking trails, and Central Avenue for essential shops and vibrant community, this home offers ultimate urban living. Settled on a coveted street in The Heights, this neighborhood is known for its walkability to nearby parks, boutiques, schools and NYC access."
230007144,SOLD,"JC, Heights",283 TERRACE AVE,Condominium,2200,1419,"$775,000",CONDO-COOP,,2&3,2,"JC, Heights",07307-3953,601,22,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,11,,"$775,000","$809,900",$352.27,$352.27,5/3/2023,8/1/2023,1/4/2024,90,90,,1/9/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,North & Leonard,"Introducing the massive new construction beauty at 283 Terrace Ave.  Unit 2 contains 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths and 1 half bath that stretches over 2,200 sq ft.  There is a private garage space with EV charging station and a multitude of outdoor spaces.  Step into the living space and notice the 5 wide oak floors that stretch throughout the entire residence.  The elegant kitchen with two tone cabinets, waterfall quartz counters and top of the line LG black SS appliance package, enabled with bluetooth via 'Smart Things' is sure to excite!  Additionally, the kitchen contains a Sharp drawer style automatic microwave.  The primary bedroom has a large walk in closet and private terrace as well as en suite baths with double vanity and stand in shower.  Each of the 3 additional bedrooms has large closets, all with built in fixtures.  The unit also has a tankless HWH as well as full W/D.  The bathrooms contain smart mirrors with built in lighting and defogging functionality in addition to floating vanities.  The home also comes equipped with a Ring Doorbell system.  All the terraces of the building have trex decking and the home is 3' wider than your typical new construction home.  To top it off there is large private roof deck with trex decking and hookup for a sink and gas grill"
