240001507,SOLD,"JC, Heights",52 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1750,1603,"$775,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3,4502,,,,,,3,0,2,5,,"$775,000","$775,000",$442.86,$442.86,1/25/2024,2/5/2024,3/20/2024,11,11,,3/20/2024,,,,"$10,257",,$213,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"High ceilings and white oak hardwood floors welcome you to this stylish 3 bed, 2 full bath in the heart of the vibrant Riverview Arts District in Jersey City Heights. The large living dining space is perfect for entertaining and the kitchen leaves nothing to be desired, featuring Viking stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, a built-in microwave, a custom dining table extension, and a wall mount pot filler. The primary bedroom boasts an en-suite, walk-in closet, and an adorable terrace for enjoying your morning coffee or a glass of wine. Two additional bedrooms are perfect for offices, guest rooms, or nurseries. Other features include: laundry room off the kitchen, additional basement storage, central air, and a Nest thermostat. Situated between Riverview and Manhattan Parks, you’ll have easy access to Palisade and Central Avenue bus routes and the 2nd Street Light Rail Station in Hoboken. Less than a block from Alessio’s Cafe, Green Pear Heights, and Froth on Franklin, come enjoy all the Heights has to offer. Welcome home!"
220018780,SOLD,"JC, Heights",97 LAIDLAW AVE,Condominium,1390,1603,"$775,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,4,"JC, Heights",07306,05705,00014,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$775,000","$799,000",$557.55,$557.55,10/21/2022,2/7/2023,3/17/2023,109,109,,3/20/2023,,,,$0,,$518,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave & Oakland Ave,"97 Laidlaw Ave is a collection of five timeless new construction condominium homes consisting of three and four bedrooms, two and three bath homes. Unit 4 is a three bedroom, two bath home and includes a private backyard and partial NYC view from your living room.  Full-service kitchen designed to flow smoothly into and out of the living area features Frigidaire appliances in slate, two-toned matte cabinetry with custom integrated cabinet lighting, Himalayan White Granite waterfall countertops and floating wall shelves. This elegant space with dining area is perfectly suited for casual dining as well as entertaining. Luxurious bathrooms offering you a spa-like retreat with an assortment of carefully selected materials and textures that are exceptional including Roca Piasentina silver polished large format tiles throughout, 60'' double vessel sink on a floating vanity, 30'' natural oak vanities, showers with horizontal niche and integrated led lighting, fixed glass enclosed shower with rain shower head and more. Every home offers unparalleled detail from expansive open floor plan living spaces and high-end finishes to massive private balconies, exclusive backyards, elevator, garage parking and deeded rooftop spaces with NYC views.  97 Laidlaw Ave sits in prime location only a few short blocks from Pershing Field Park and only one block to the Central Ave shopping district. Commute with ease to NYC via NJ Transit buses right on Central Ave or a quick 15 minute walk to the JSQ PATH train. City-bikes located one block from the property. Offering you larger living spaces at desirable price points while maintaining close proximity to NYC, these one-of-a-kind new construction homes are so luxurious you’ll never want to leave!  Property qualifies for 5 year tax abatement. Open House 1/14 - 12pm-2pm!Open House 1/15 - 1pm-3pm!"
