220020308,SOLD,"JC, Heights",147 TERRACE AVE,Condominium,1954,1685,"$775,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02502,00039,Heights,,,,,4,2,3,7,,"$775,000","$775,000",$396.62,$396.62,11/17/2022,11/17/2022,1/18/2023,0,0,,1/19/2023,,,,,,$350,,Conventional,,,,,,Lincoln Street & Thorne Street,"Brand new ONE OF A KIND LUXURY UNIT ! GN Management does it again , providing top of the line finishes and technology throughout this home! This duplex unit boasts 4 bedrooms (2 of which are master suites with walk-in closets) 5 perfectly designed bathrooms, open concept living room/dining room, eat-in kitchen with large quartz waterfall island, faucet over stove, built in cabinet microwave, farmhouse sink, an electrical fireplace, washer/dryer closet, a balcony in one of the master suites, garage parking, and private roof deck perfect for entertainment. Not to mention the super high ceilings in the front of the unit with floor to ceiling windows bringing in lots of natural light into the front of the unit and the mezzanine from the kitchen overlooking the 1st level makes this unit stand out from the rest ! Each bathroom was designed meticulously with high end finishes, modern vanities & lights. This is a tech-lovers dream, built in audio speakers , cable ready, security system, and nest thermostat. When it comes to noise and energy efficiency, thanks to the extra-thick soundproofing and great quality insulation. The developer truly went above & beyond with modern design, quality of material, number of bedrooms and bathrooms, and custom carpentry/trim. Transportation is very accessible making it an easy commute to NYC PORT AUTHORITY, JSQ PATH, Downtown JC and Hoboken. Also conveniently located near parks and schools. Developer is offering a 10 Year new home warranty! Eligible for a 5 year TAX ABATEMENT. Take advantage of the opportunity to purchase this unique one of a kind unit."
210024505,SOLD,"JC, Heights",69 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1,1691,"$775,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3A,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$775,000","$775,000","$775,000.00","$775,000.00",10/27/2021,11/16/2021,1/14/2022,20,20,,1/14/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith & Hutton,"Now offering up to $10K in closing costs for buyers! Preferred Lender: Cross Country Mortgages -   Magnificent and modern, this brand new, bright and airy, custom home shines with space and sophistication in the heart of Jersey City Heights. High ceilings, high-end finishes and a high rooftop view elevates these luxury lifestyle upgrades to the next level. This penthouse unit expand to a 3-bedroom floorplan, plus soaring ceilings and an upstairs private roof deck.   Finished with light oak floors plus matte black pendant lighting and trim throughout, each home features wide open windows along the back wall with western-exposure for excellent sunsets and seclusion. Kitchens excite with sleek light wood or matte black custom cabinetry, finished with waterfall quartz counters, tile backsplash, brass fixtures and Bertazzoni appliances. Freshly designed bathrooms feature ribbon gray porcelain tile, glass shower with niche and rain head faucet, floating vanity and contrasting matte black fixtures.  Settled into a tree-lined street just off Central Avenue with essential shops and award-winning restaurants, this home is located blocks from both Riverview Fisk and Pershing Field Park, plus walkable access to NJ and NY transit or Citi bike stations. Jersey City Heights is home to the perfect blend of urban and escape, including vibrant community, excellent schools and impressive lifestyle to value ratio."
