240003171,SOLD,"JC, Heights",295 TERRACE AVE,Condominium,1395,1597,"$780,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07306,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$780,000","$775,000",$559.14,$559.14,2/20/2024,4/11/2024,6/3/2024,51,51,,6/4/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,North St & Leonard St,"Buying a home has never been smarter with this high tech, high-end, new construction home in The Heights. Power is at your fingertips with full control home automation systems in the 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath layout, plus major must-haves like private backyard and full garage parking.   Control your home with Alexa voice activation, mobile phone, or the 8-inch touch screen giving access to lighting, window shades, security, temperature, or professional audio system with zones in each room! Super smart appliances include dishwasher, washer and dryer, microwave and 36in refrigerator that gives recipes, shopping lists, content review and more.   Modern design matches the interior theme with clean lines, bright tones and thoughtful floorplan. Living room shines with floor to ceiling windows including private front terrace access, plus marble fireplace with built-in floating fireplace. Incredible craftsmanship is showcased through stylish accents such as light oak herringbone floors, ceiling molding, and carefully curated pendant lighting.   Marbled quartz waterfall counters with eat-in peninsula island and modern white and wood custom cabinetry finish the open floorplan kitchen. Bathrooms boast elements like floor to ceiling tile or matte black wall with matching wide pedestal wash basin. Midnight blue wainscotting bathes the primary ensuite with oversized windows and closet space.  Duplex offers an additional living room with private backyard off the downstairs bedroom. Owners also enjoy access to the secure full private garage parking.  Settled on a tree-lined street in a quiet corner of Jersey City Heights, these homes offer walkability to Central Avenue, Washington Park and easy NYC access.  TECH FEATURES Full control home automation system with Alexa voice activation Control your home at your finger tips with smart phone or built-in 8 inch screen the security cameras, video, doorbell, locks, temperature, lighting and all other switches  Full professional audio system with separate zones for each room Fully automated window shades Smart appliances  Microwave Dishwasher Washer & dryer"
