230000526,SOLD,"JC, Heights",21 WAVERLY ST,Condominium,1293,1581,"$780,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07306,05803,00012,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$780,000","$799,000",$603.25,$603.25,1/10/2023,2/10/2023,3/28/2023,31,31,,3/31/2023,,,,$0,,$120,,Conventional,,,,,,Palisade Ave & Baldwin Ave,"BRAND NEW CONDOMINIUM WITH A PRIVATE ROOFTOP in Jersey City Heights located in a commuters dream location just minutes away from Manhattan! This 2nd floor unit occupies 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths featuring modern fixtures with contemporary high-end finishes! As you enter this unit, you will be welcomed with a spacious entryway, go up the stairs and you are greeted with a spacious living dining room combo and modern beautifully designed kitchen. The entire unit has plenty of large windows and 10 ft ceilings throughout with abundant natural light flowing in every room. This unit is equipped with high end stainless steel appliances, modern quartz slab counters and fully walled marble backsplash as well as open shelving. This charming gem also provides you with a Master Bedroom En-Suite, 2 additional bedrooms with a built-in closet for ample storage, and 1 full bathroom. Both bathrooms feature a marble-tiled shower highlighting modern black matte fixtures! The cherry on top is the Modern Rooftop with unobstructed Manhattan view with a closet for your entertaining and grilling storage. This unit has wireless speakers in the unit as well as the rooftop. This impeccable condominium also includes amazing features like an in-unit laundry including stackable washer & dryer, central heating / cooling, gleaming hardwood floors, and has an incomparable location! Residing here will have you just blocks away from parks, cafes, shops, and restaurants along with public transportation like NJ transit, the light rail, and the NY/NJ PATH, getting you into Manhattan in just minutes. This condominium is the epitome of urban luxury living! Schedule a private tour today to see your dream condominium!"
250007070,SOLD,"JC, Heights",37 BOWERS ST,Condominium,1012,5845,"$780,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & G,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03001,00002,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$780,000","$750,000",$770.75,$770.75,4/10/2025,4/18/2025,6/20/2025,8,8,,6/25/2025,,,,"$12,021",,$413,,Conventional,,,,,,Palisade and New York Ave,"Stunning 3-Bedroom Condo with a Private Backyard & Bonus Flex Space in Jersey City Heights. Welcome to this beautifully renovated three-bedroom, two-bathroom condo, just one block from Riverview Park in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This home features a light filled, open-concept living and dining area with gleaming quartz countertops, sleek white cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances, creating a modern and inviting space. All three bedrooms are generously sized, and both updated bathrooms offer stylish finishes. But the added bonus? A garden-level 752 sq. ft. flex space—ideal for a home office, gym, media room, or whatever suits your lifestyle. Step outside to your private backyard, perfect for relaxing, gardening, or entertaining. Located just steps from Riverview Park, beloved restaurants like The Alps and Corto, local shops, and convenient transit options including the Light Rail and bus stop, this home offers the best of city living with a neighborhood feel."
220000025,SOLD,"JC, Heights",320 TERRACE AVE,Condominium,1786,1691,"$780,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$780,000","$780,000",$436.73,$436.73,1/2/2022,2/10/2022,3/29/2022,39,39,,4/9/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,North St & Leonard St,"One of Jersey City's finest builders is at it again! These two new construction condominiums will quarrel over nothing except which wide open layout offers the best flow, and whose oversized outdoor space should host the next summer barbecue. This duplex 3 bed 2.5 bath home will be beautifully finished with absolute thoughtfulness and top-notch quality. Main floor living and dining area layout flows into chef-inspired kitchens finished with white marble waterfall island, inlay farm sink, Fabuwood cabinets, Samsung stainless steel appliances, must-have wine fridge, kohler fixtures and modern pendant lighting. Master suite and additional bedrooms boast ceiling fans, Pella windows, and custom walk-in closets, while bathrooms host high-end porcelain tiles, modern vanities and multiple shower heads. You'll be able hear a pin drop in this ultra-peaceful atmosphere, thanks to the extra-thick soundproofing, subfloor and insulation. A tech-lovers dream with every mod con, finishes include home entertainment wiring with 5.1 speakers, Ring doorbell, camera and security system, central vacuum and Nest thermostat. Rec room to be completed with wet bar; backyard with outdoor speakers *and* fire pit! Steps from Riverview Fisk and Washington parks - as well as both 2nd St & 9th St Light Rail stations - this neighborhood is known for great schools and easy NYC access, all amid the eclectic and vibrant scene of Jersey City Heights."
230002676,SOLD,"JC, Heights",124 IRVING ST,Condominium,1547,1598,"$781,000",CONDO-COOP,,2+RF,2,"JC, Heights",07307,00703,00057,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$781,000","$779,000",$504.85,$504.85,2/16/2023,2/28/2023,4/17/2023,12,12,,4/17/2023,,,,"$8,743",2022,$0,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy Blvd & Nelson,"Introducing 124 Irving st,  the last unit remaining of the 4 luxury new construction units and now offering the Community Advantage Program, super low rates in 4% range, with only 5% down CONV NO PMI and a large lender credit of 1% towards closing costs also possible Down payment assistance.  These units were designed & constructed by one of Jersey City's most renowned builders, Medna Developers. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms home features an expansive open-concept living space with immaculate attention to detail, craftsmanship and design. The open concept chef's kitchen boasts premium stainless steel appliances, wine fridge and quartz countertops. Throughout the home you'll notice smart features such as intercom, security, speakers and thermostat. Master bedroom has a private terrace, walk-in closet and plenty of natural light! Bathroom includes floor to ceiling custom tile, smart mirror and modern fixtures. Your private rooftop offers beautiful views and privacy. Most importantly, unlike 90% of the other properties on the market, NO SHARED TANDEM PARKING, Private only, so you don't have to coordinate/bother with your neighbor about parking and moving cars, Priceless! *Photos of similar unit."
220011432,SOLD,"JC, Heights",209 HUTTON ST,Condominium,1330,1603,"$785,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307-1111,03602,00008,Heights,Hutton Place,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$785,000","$799,000",$590.23,$590.23,6/22/2022,8/8/2022,11/4/2022,47,47,,11/7/2022,,,,"$8,171",2021,$180,2021,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Sanford and Summit,"Welcome home to Hutton Place by Black Diamond Homes, this one-of-a-kind bright, spacious, open layout and modern 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom in the booming Jersey City Heights is only one flight up, featuring professionally designed upgrades that include soaring 20' ceilings, Andersen Windows, 5 oak HW floors throughout, tons of LED recessed lighting, solid core doors, custom tile bathrooms w/ upgraded fixtures, central AC, glass-front washer/dryer and keyless entry. The open chef's kitchen comes fully equipped with stainless steel appliances, Quartz countertops and walnut shaker cabinets. 2 large guest rooms are anchored by a beautiful guest bath with soaking tub. Master Suite features large walk-in closet, bright picture windows and en-suite bath with custom glass shower. Begin and end your day enjoying your very own PRIVATE ROOF DECK overlooking all of Jersey City and slight views of NYC. All the bells and whistles, this home has it all, including 1 DEEDED PARKING SPOT and just steps away to the Heights' best shopping, dining, art galleries, parks and easy transportation into Hoboken, Downtown Jersey City and/ or NYC. Photos and matterport from previous listing."
250000064,SOLD,"JC, Heights",93 LAIDLAW AVE,Condominium,1301,1597,"$785,000",CONDO-COOP,,3 & R,2,"JC, Heights",07306,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$785,000","$790,000",$603.38,$603.38,1/2/2025,1/22/2025,3/7/2025,20,20,,3/7/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Oakland and Central,"Relax into luxury with this stunning home located in a quiet corner of Jersey City Heights. The three bedroom, two bath layout exudes sophistication with high ceilings, an exposed stairwell, and a full-floor private rooftop showcasing captivating NYC skyline views. Newly refinished, the exterior boasts immediate curb appeal with pristine white siding, complemented by matte black trim and pavers on a tree-lined street.  Light streams through the beautiful bay windows and showcases the thoughtful design, carefully curated lighting and timeless wide plank red oak hardwood floors throughout. The kitchen is a culinary dream with waterfall white quartz counters, tile backsplash, and custom cabinets in refreshing white and green. Stainless steel appliances and gold fixtures and fittings complete the aesthetic.  The bedrooms offer ample square footage and closet space, while beautifully designed bathrooms feature elements like striking patterned porcelain wall tiles, spacious double vanities, matte black tile floors, plus multi-system showers and bathtubs. Owners will appreciate the brand new stacking LG washer and dryer for added convenience.  Conveniently located just one block from Pershing Field Reservoir and Park, residents enjoy sports fields, playgrounds, nature trails and even a swimming pool. The proximity to the 2nd Street Light Rail station and Hoboken Stairs provides easy access to NYC and surrounding neighborhoods. Jersey City Heights is known for its vibrant community, artistic vibe, excellent parks and schools, plus boutique shops and restaurants."
240024365,SOLD,"JC, Heights",29 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1097,1724,"$785,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$785,000","$740,000",$715.59,$715.59,1/1/2025,1/5/2025,2/24/2025,4,4,,2/26/2025,,,,"$13,985",,$256,,Conventional,,,,,,Manhattan Ave & Franklin Ave,"Built in 2017, this meticulously maintained home blends timeless design with modern functionality, offering high-end finishes and thoughtful upgrades throughout. The chef's kitchen showcases Carrara marble countertops and backsplash, paired with wide-plank hardwood floors that add warmth and elegance. Bathrooms are designed with Porcelanosa tiles and fixtures, exuding contemporary sophistication.    The private roof deck boasts breathtaking NYC skyline views, while the serene master bedroom terrace offers a quiet retreat. Additional highlights include garage parking, solid-core wood interior doors, upgraded Andersen 400 series windows and doors, central A/C, an in-unit washer/dryer, and abundant storage.    Bright, open spaces are illuminated by recessed and custom lighting, demonstrating the home's superior craftsmanship and exceptional care. This is the ideal choice for those seeking space, style, and convenience in a vibrant neighborhood with excellent transportation options and amenities just steps away.   "
230021014,SOLD,"JC, Heights",32 TERRACE AVE,Condominium,1277,1724,"$785,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03304,00015 01,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$785,000","$799,000",$614.72,$614.72,12/22/2023,1/11/2024,2/14/2024,20,20,,2/15/2024,,,,,,$300,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Manhattan and Zabriski,"Elevate Your Lifestyle in Jersey City Heights. Welcome to a splendid new construction home in the heart of Jersey City Heights, where contemporary living meets urban convenience. This 1277 sq ft residence offers a blend of modern amenities and sleek design, making it the perfect home for those seeking the finest in city living. Upon entering, you're greeted with a spacious and open living and dining layout, designed for modern living and entertaining. Large windows adorn the exterior, inviting abundant natural light into your home, creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere. The well-appointed kitchen boasts an abundance of cabinetry for ample storage, a stylish quartz countertop breakfast bar, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, making it a chef's delight. Three generously sized bedrooms offer space and comfort, each equipped with customized closets for your convenience.The master bedroom features a full bath and spacious closets, providing a private retreat within your home. Ascend the stairs to discover a spacious 444 sq ft roof deck, offering a unique and private outdoor space, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or hosting gatherings with friends. This home includes a one-car garage parking spot, tandem with Unit 1, ensuring the security and convenience of your vehicle. Nestled in the vibrant Jersey City Heights, this property provides an urban lifestyle with all the charm of a quiet neighborhood. Enjoy easy access to major highways, including 1&9 and RT 3, ensuring seamless commutes.This newly constructed home is the epitome of modern luxury, offering contemporary design, top-of-the-line amenities, and a prime urban location. -Eligible for 5 year tax abatement "
230017232,SOLD,"JC, Heights",32 TERRACE AVE,Condominium,1851,1724,"$785,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03304,00015 01,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,6,,"$785,000","$825,000",$424.10,$424.10,10/13/2023,11/3/2023,2/8/2024,21,21,,2/9/2024,,,,,,$300,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Manhattan and Zabriski,"Discover Urban Elegance in Jersey City Heights. Welcome to the epitome of modern living in Jersey City Heights. This brand new construction home, spanning 1851 sq ft, boasts a harmonious fusion of space, style, and convenience, making it the perfect urban oasis for those seeking the best of both worlds. Upon entering, you're greeted with a spacious and open living and dining layout, designed for modern living and entertaining. The well-appointed kitchen boasts an abundance of cabinetry for ample storage,  stylish quartz countertops, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, making it a chef's delight.The three generously sized bedrooms are equipped with custom closets, providing plenty of storage space for your personal belongings. The master bedroom boasts a full bath and offers direct access to your private backyard, creating a tranquil retreat within the city. Venture downstairs, where you'll discover a beautiful 650 sq ft rec room, complete with a partial kitchen featuring a mini fridge and wine cooler – perfect for hosting gatherings and movie nights, a full bath on this level adds convenience and versatility to the space. The full-size Samsung washer/dryer and a Navien tankless water heater make laundry a breeze and ensure a constant supply of hot water. This home includes a one-car garage parking spot, tandem with Unit 2, providing security and convenience for your vehicle. This newly constructed home offers a harmonious blend of modern amenities, contemporary design, and urban living. Located in the highly sought-after Jersey City Heights, this property offers easy access to the heart of the city while providing a quiet and peaceful retreat from the bustling streets. Minutes away from major highways, including 1&9 and RT 3, making commuting a breeze.Eligible for 5 year tax abatement."
230005136,SOLD,"JC, Heights",152.5 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,2000,6078,"$785,000",CONDO-COOP,,1/2/2,B,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,9,,"$785,000","$745,000",$392.50,$392.50,3/31/2023,4/6/2023,6/12/2023,6,6,,6/12/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,off webster,"LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION...Welcome to 152.5 Webster Avenue #2, featuring a massive 3 Bedroom plus den with PRIVATE ROOF DECK in the most desirable area of JC Heights, minutes walk to 9th St Hoboken Light-Rail & only 2 blocks to Riverview Park overlooking Manhattan!  Unit 2 features a massive 3B/2.5B Duplex (over 1900 sq ft) with oak hardwood floors throughout, gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, bonus living space, 26'X16' Master Bedroom, & PRIVATE ROOFDECK with partial city views .  Come live in a vibrant community close to all shops, parks restaurants that JC Heights has to offer!  Schedule your tour today!"
230006142,SOLD,"JC, Heights",98 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1510,1597,"$789,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$789,000","$779,000",$522.52,$522.52,4/18/2023,5/10/2023,6/21/2023,22,22,,6/22/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave & JFK,"Dream a little dreamhome with this modern marvel in The Heights. Brand new construction home offers three bedrooms, loads of square footage, gorgeous private rooftop, plus garage parking for the ultimate urban appeal.  To-the-ceiling Pella windows shine loads of natural light through to the open concept floorplan finished with classic design and modern upgrades like fresh oak hardwood floors, crown molding and smart home tech throughout. Upstairs glass staircase leads to full size private rooftop with excellent 360 cityscape views.   Contemporary eat-in kitchens offer clean white quartz waterfall island, counters and backsplash, plus seamless custom cabinetry and stainless LG appliances including wine fridge. Primary ensuites host glass doors to private balcony plus large built-out walk-in closets. Bathrooms feature elements like double vanity, glass shower with multihead system or soaker tub for added convenience. Designated utility area features stacking Samsung washer and dryer. Shared garage parking is also available.  Glass and brick modern building is one block from Leonard Gordon Park, Citi bike station, and also main thoroughfare Summit Ave. Jersey City Heights is known for its eclectic vibe, great community, excellent schools and accessibility to NYC and surrounding areas."
230001179,SOLD,"JC, Heights",118 BLEECKER ST,Condominium,1247,1419,"$789,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02101,00047,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$789,000","$799,000",$632.72,$632.72,1/20/2023,5/18/2023,7/10/2023,118,118,,7/11/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,South St & Paterson St,"A new construction you can personalize! A Jersey City Heights gem reveals itself on Bleecker St! This modern 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom is pre-designed for the latest in home technology and entertainment. Boasting hardwood floors throughout, 8ft custom doors, high ceiling, modern crown molding, in unit washer dryer, LED lighting, and private roof deck! Pure white quartz counters with waterfall feature, custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and luxurious finishes provides an elevated and modern ambiance in your home. Located in an unbeatable area of the Heights that is easily commutable and accessible to public transportation with direct bus lines to NYC Port Authority, Hoboken, and Downtown JC. The Hudson Light Rail Stations are also nearby as well as Pershing Field's indoor pool and ice skating rink being only a few blocks away. Riverview Park with its amazing views offers Farmers Market, movie nights, and neighborhood events! 1 car parking included! Call us for a private tour today, building is projected to be finished February 2023, 2 units are available. Unit #1 has a private yard."
260006285,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",272 TERRACE AVE,Condominium,1198,1597,"$789,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,B,"JC, Heights",07307,1202,28,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,,"$789,000",$658.60,,4/8/2026,,,1,,,4/8/2026,,,,$0,,,,,No,No,No,,,Bleecker Street and North Street,"Welcome to this stunning new construction residence offering modern luxury and thoughtful design throughout. This sun-filled home features an open-concept layout with wide-plank flooring, oversized windows, and high ceilings. The chef’s kitchen is equipped with premium stainless steel smart appliances, wine fridge, custom cabinetry, quartz countertops with continuous backsplash, and a spacious waterfall island perfect for entertaining. Generously sized bedrooms include ample closet space with custom built-ins, and spa-inspired bathrooms showcasing sleek finishes and contemporary fixtures. Enjoy outdoor living with a private terrace off your master bedroom as well your own private rooftop, ideal for entertaining, relaxing, or taking in neighborhood views. Additional highlights include one garage parking space, in-unit laundry, and central air.  Conveniently located near transportation, shopping, dining, and parks, the Western Slope never looked this good! A perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience—don’t miss this exceptional opportunity. Can be purchased as 2 family.  Seller has applied for 5 year tax abatement but makes no guarantees.  10 year warranty."
260005886,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",192 CAMBRIDGE AVE,Condominium,1178,1597,"$789,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2203,2.01,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$789,000",$669.78,,4/2/2026,,,7,,,4/2/2026,,,,$0,,$328,,,No,No,No,,,Congress Street & South Street,"No stairs plus private patio!  Five new-construction condominium homes redefine modern living in the best location of Jersey City Heights. Each home showcases a refined aesthetic and carefully curated details. Chef-inspired kitchens feature expansive Taj Mahal quartz islands, premium LG stainless appliances with gas range, a Frigidaire wine cooler, and Sharp built-in microwave. Primary baths offer a spa-like escape with porcelain and ceramic tiles, frameless glass showers, brushed gold hardware, Kohler fixtures, and natural teak vanities, while secondary baths boast sleek subway tiles, matte black channels, Moen fixtures, and LED mirrors. Wide-plank French oak flooring, soaring ceilings, custom lighting, and built-in electric fireplaces bring warmth and style throughout, creating homes that balance modern sophistication with everyday comfort.  192 Cambridge sits in prime location only one block to Washington Park and a few short blocks to The Arts District surrounding Riverview Park.  Enjoy neighborhood cafés, Central Avenue shops, and vibrant restaurants, with the Congress Street Elevator/Light Rail a stones throw away, you’ll enjoy effortless access to Hoboken and Manhattan while keeping the Heights’ neighborhood charm at your doorstep.  This unit includes a fenced-in, private paved patio space."
250025709,SOLD,"JC, Heights",141 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1471,6706,"$790,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2903,20,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$790,000","$799,000",$537.05,$537.05,1/2/2026,1/7/2026,2/20/2026,5,5,,2/23/2026,,"$465,000",2024,"$10,096",2025,$153,2025,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Bower and Griffth Street,"Welcome to unit 2 of 141 Sherman Avenue nestled in the east side of Jersey City Heights! This new luxury condo unit offers 3 bedrooms with 2 full bathrooms. Experience an open floor layout with natural lighting and breath-taking coffered ceiling design in the living room. Enjoy the ample cabinet space in your state-of-the-art kitchen, with Samsung stainless steel appliances and a smart fridge. Kitchen cabinets are two tone European style cabinets, complimented with quartz countertop placed also on backsplash. The kitchen easily sits 4 people for entertaining. Master bedroom offers a sliding door to walk out to your private balcony, a walk-in closet, and a master bathroom which includes a double sink vanity. Features include hardwood floors, custom closet and trim work, recess lighting, chic designer tiles throughout, in unit laundry, and modern fixtures. Entertain in your private roof top deck while also enjoying a section of green outdoor space. Close to Parks, amazing restaurants on Central Ave, shopping centers, commuter friendly, close to NJ transit public transportation for quick access to the city. Reserved parking for one car steps away from the property."
230001485,SOLD,"JC, Heights",948 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,1800,1713,"$790,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03704,00003,,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$790,000","$799,000",$438.89,$438.89,1/26/2023,2/3/2023,3/15/2023,8,8,,3/15/2023,,,,"$11,450",,$284,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith & Zabriskie St,"Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath, 1800+sf duplex. This light and bright, high-ceiling home is appointed with Pella windows and doors, crown moldings, has a private backyard with bluestone stepping stones and grill area, and a large deck perfect for entertaining. The first floor features an open kitchen/living area floorplan with quartz countertops, oxford latte white cabinets, LG stainless steel appliances, side-by-side washer and dryer, with utility shelving system in the laundry area, and a 1/2 bath. The second floor has an oversized primary suite with a walk-in closet, luxe bath with a double-wide fully mirrored medicine cabinet over double sinks, and beautiful floor-to-ceiling Porcelanosa tiles. Lutron Maestro dimmer switch system for upstairs hallway lighting. Two additional bedrooms with generous closets, and an extra hallway storage room provide plenty of additional space. Custom Hunter Douglas Blinds for Living Room window wall. Custom Levelor wooden blinds in all bedrooms. Garage with massive storage closets. Located just steps from the NJ Transit bus stop with buses to Journal Square, the PATH station in 10 min or to NY Port Authority in 30 min, less than 1 mile from Congress St Light Rail station and also close to Route 1&9, with easy access to all major highways. Centrally located in JC Heights, this residence is conveniently situated near acclaimed restaurants, bars, bakeries, markets, and neighborhood parks."
230000781,SOLD,"JC, Heights",120 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1352,6078,"$790,000",CONDO-COOP,,2/3,Two,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$790,000","$795,000",$584.32,$584.32,1/13/2023,1/23/2023,3/21/2023,10,10,,3/21/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,off graham,"Brand NEW CONSTRUCTION in highly desirable JC Heights built by NKAY.  *SELLER OFFERING A $5,000 CREDIT AT CLOSING FOR BUYER CLOSING COSTS  Welcome to this SOUTH FACING luxurious 3 bed, 2 bath condo featuring an open concept design with wide plank oak flooring throughout & garage parking.  The kitchen features white shaker cabinets, sleek quartz countertops with waterfall island & high end appliances; Samsung, wine fridge, Kohler plumbing fixtures.  Generous sized bedrooms including a master bedroom w en-suite spa-like bathroom with double vanity sinks.  Head upstairs to your very own private roof deck with NYC Views.  Other features include custom closets, high end finishes with custom molding,  video door bell, surround sound and more.  The garage comes with 1 parking spot (Electric Charging Station) 10 years builders warranty & 5 year tax abatement included. A short commute via BUS to PORT Authority NYC & close walk to all restaurants , shopping, parks nearby."
210023691,SOLD,"JC, Heights",359 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,2200,1653,"$790,000",CONDO-COOP,,"1,2",1,"JC, Heights",07307,01604,00009,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,8,,"$790,000","$749,800",$359.09,$359.09,10/14/2021,10/23/2021,12/20/2021,9,9,,12/21/2021,,,,"$10,383",2020,$285,2021,Cash,,,,,,North and Congress,"Unlike any other in the area, you must see this fantastic two-story home featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, private PATIO/BACKYARD, 2 PARKING SPACES, and over 2200+ SqFt or real living space! Step up into a large and bright living room with Juliet balcony and dining area adjacent to an open kitchen with granite countertops, newer stainless steel appliances, and plenty of cabinets. Three excellently-sized bedrooms and two full renovated baths on the same level; including main bedroom with en-suite bath, large closet, and balcony overlooking your own private patio. Then walk to the lower level (fully above ground) and into an extra large living area perfect for entertaining, media/playroom, gym, and more, doors to the patio or garage, powder room (1/2 bath)….plus ANOTHER BEDROOM! Hardwood floors throughout, central AC/heat, 2 entrances, washer & dryer room, and lots of closet/storage space. All this plus your private indoor parking garage with extra high ceilings and an additional parking space in the driveway. Incredible location in the northeast section of Jersey City Heights, effectively blending a vibrant urban community lifestyle with a house-like feel, just 1/2 block to wonderful Washington Park, easy in/out of town, nearby NJ transit Light Rail on Congress St., buses to NYC and other great areas, walkable access to Citi bike station, nearby restaurants, a 94 on Walkscore.com (Walker’s Paradise)! Location is zoned for highly-rated PS 28 (Christa McAuliffe School). Are you ready to make a move to a wonderful home?"
220005811,SOLD,"JC, Heights",124 THORNE ST,Condominium,1734,1468,"$790,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02104,00076,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$790,000","$740,000",$455.59,$455.59,4/4/2022,4/7/2022,6/21/2022,3,3,,6/21/2022,,,,"$7,566",2021,$99,,Conventional,No,No,,,,charles and south st,"Completed in 2020 with the finest finishes, in the desirable Jersey City Heights. This amazing over 1700 sq. ft. 3-bedroom, 2.5 bath of open living space with high ceilings, white oak floors throughout, oversized windows drenched in natural light. Chef’s kitchen with shaker cabinets, High-end stainless-steel appliance package, mosaic back splash, center island with white quartz counter tops. Large Primary bedroom with en-suite bath, stand up shower, porcelain tile, walk in closet, double windows & sliding door leading to balcony. 2 generous bedrooms with closets, 2nd bathroom with soaking tub, Porcelain Tile in Black/White. 2 zone Central air/heating system, washer/dryer room, custom blinds. Separate Zone added in the bonus space in 2021, Riverstone brick patio added 2020. Plenty of storage & closets, 1 car tandem garage included. The spacious private backyard is the perfect place to relax & have a BBQ in the summer. Located right off Central Ave, catch a short bus ride to Journal Square PATH or take one bus straight into Port Authority Times Square. Convenient commute to Jersey City and NYC. Don't miss out on this home, it is ready for you!"
220012582,SOLD,"JC, Heights",580 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1030,1692,"$790,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,402,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,The Riveview,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$790,000","$790,000",$766.99,$766.99,2/10/2022,2/11/2022,7/5/2022,1,0,,7/11/2022,,,,,,$343,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress and South,"Step inside and immediately feel at ease in this unit. BRAND NEW GROUND UP CONSTRUCTION at The Riverview offers impeccable comfort and convenience, situated on Palisade Avenue, at the heart of the neighborhood’s exciting retail/dining corridor. Choose from two- and three-bedroom residences in this intimate 13-unit building, crafted to meet your every need. The well-proportioned units are carefully constructed with today’s most in-demand elements. Flow-through rooms and thoughtful appointments combine for luxurious comfort. Expansive energy-efficient insulated windows frame the interiors with abundant natural light. Elegant top-line finishes include wide plank flooring, granite countertops and premium Fischer-Paykel appliances. Thoughtfully curated amenities bring ease to today’s busy lifestyles. A package room, 12-car parking garage with electric chargers and ground-level bike storage are among the building’s many essential comforts designed to enhance your lifestyle. Make this inspired collection of pet-friendly condominiums home. 10-year New Home Warranty, Manufacturer’s Warranty on all appliances and systems, and tax abatement. Photos are of model unit."
