220000406,SOLD,"JC, Heights",28 CLIFF ST,Condominium,1400,270,"$795,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07306,04603,00030,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$795,000","$819,000",$567.86,$567.86,1/7/2022,1/27/2022,5/6/2022,20,20,,5/10/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy Blvd & Liberty Ave,"Location Location!! New Construction Luxury and Modern condominium, custom quality modern design, lots of natural sunlight. Features spacious large 3 bdrs, 2 full bthrms, double vanity with led light mirror and marble titled. Laundry room space, hardwood floors. The stunning kitchen is equipped with custom two-tone cabinetries, stainless steel appliances, beautifully waterfall island with marbled quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances.This unit included 1 car garage parking, and a perfect terrace on the top floor with a spectacular view.This house presents the perfect opportunity to live in a quiet section of Jersey City while having all of the nightlife  restaurants, shopping, art galleries, and easy access to public transportation to NYC."
220008576,SOLD,"JC, Heights",9 STAGG ST,Condominium,2106,1597,"$795,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & 3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$795,000","$799,000",$377.49,$377.49,5/12/2022,6/29/2022,8/26/2022,48,48,,8/27/2022,,,,,,$267,,VA,,,,,,Liberty Ave & JFK,"Set your sights on these completely renovated homes with private outdoor and storage from one of Jersey City’s top builders, Nkay Construction, now available in a quiet corner of The Heights. Both duplexes offer three bedrooms plus added living area and expansive roof deck or backyard with patio.  Built-in floating gas fireplace is the show-stopping centerpiece, beautifully encased in a classic custom mantle in the wide-open living area. Modern yet classic finishes include crown molding, hardwood floors, Pella windows and ceiling fans throughout. Open floorplan kitchen includes sparkling quartz waterfall eat-in peninsula including eye-catching blue kick plate, tile backsplash, custom shaker cabinets, stainless farm sink and matte black Samsung appliances including much-needed wine fridge, plus Kohler fixtures and modern pendant lighting. Tech upgrades include ring doorbell, camera and wired for security system, and nest thermostat. Bathroom finishes include marble double vanity, glass shower or bathtub combo with polished chrome fixtures.  Unit two offers a fullsize roof deck with 360 views, plus an extra half bath off the main living area. Both units have a dedicated utility area with Samsung washer and dryer, as well as private basement storage area.  Modern gray brick building on idyllic tree-lined street in a quiet corner of The Heights Western Slope is blocks from Leonard Gordon Park, and easy access to the JSQ PATH station, 2nd St  Light Rail, and all major roads. Jersey City Heights is known for its great community, excellent schools and easy NYC access, with vibrant shops, restaurants and parks!"
210023939,SOLD,"JC, Heights",185 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1450,1597,"$795,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02205,00036,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$795,000","$824,000",$548.28,$548.28,10/19/2021,1/24/2022,3/24/2022,97,97,,3/24/2022,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers st. and South st.,"Impeccably designed and newly constructed with the highest level of craftsmanship, this spacious Three Bedroom Condominium leaves nothing to be desired. The overall atmosphere of the residence furnished with 5” red oak hardwood floors, soaring vaulted ceilings and skylights in the living room, recessed lighting and black metal hardware and fixtures throughout is serene and warm. This voluminous residence boasts 1350sf of generous indoor living space, two uniquely designed bathrooms, an in-garage tandem Parking Space and a 567sf private Roof Terrace with jaw-dropping unobstructed views to all directions. The primary bedroom suite features an en-suite bathroom adorned with elegant tiles, a private balcony overlooking the neighboring gardens and a fully built-out walk-in closet. Each additional bedroom is in excellent proportions with ample closets. The stunning chef’s kitchen is equipped with custom two-tone cabinetries, Samsung stainless steel appliances, beautifully tiled backsplash and a peninsula with waterfall Quartz countertops. This stunning brand-new residence is further outfitted with Central AC, Nest Thermostat and Doorbell, washer and dryer and Pella windows. Ideally located in the highly sought-after Jersey City Heights just a few blocks to cafes, restaurants, shops and services on Palisade Avenue and Central Avenue, Riverview Fisk Park and transportations to Manhattan, Hoboken, Journal Square and Downtown Jersey City, this expertly constructed new condominium residence is not to be missed.  "
210021644,SOLD,"JC, Heights",85 BOORAEM AVE,Condominium,2177,1691,"$795,000",CONDO-COOP,,3 & 4,2A,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,5,0,3,9,,"$795,000","$799,000",$365.18,$365.18,9/16/2021,9/29/2021,11/19/2021,13,13,,11/19/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Webster & Abbett,"Bright, light and altogether fresh, this beautifully constructed home feels like summertime all year round. Sunlight streams in through the matte black bay windows to illuminate the wide-plank oak flooring and classic 2-story layout. Each smartly designed home shines with flowing 2,000 (plus!) sq ft and four to five bedrooms plus bonus space! The top duplex elevates with a lofty, expansive bonus room plus balcony off master.   Designer kitchens beckon even the simplest chef with gleaming white quartz counters & backsplash, custom cabinets finished to the ceiling, brass hardware plus high-end GE appliances including wine fridge. Interior elements throughout impress like the matte black and brass pendant lighting, solid black wood closet double doors, and added drama to the master bedroom with the full-wall dark matte wainscotting. Bathrooms fully refresh with marbled porcelain tiles and mosaic accents, matte black fixtures, soaker tubs and glass showers. Abundant closet space and storage available throughout.  Set on a quiet tree-lined street just off Palisade Avenue, this breath of fresh air is walking distance to Pershing Field Park and Reservoir, vibrant shops on Central Avenue, excellent schools and easy NYC access via light rail or NJ Path."
220003570,SOLD,"JC, Heights",127 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1725,298,"$798,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03601,00005,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$798,000","$798,000",$462.61,$462.61,3/2/2022,3/11/2022,6/8/2022,9,9,,6/13/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy & Summit,"Beautifully crafted new construction duplex unit located in the heart of JC Heights. This lux unit offers 3 bedrooms/2 full baths on the main living area and an open living space with wet bar and half bath with access to the backyard, which makes for the perfect place to entertain. You will find modern finishes, high-end appliances, hardwood floors and tile through out. The chef’s kitchen is spacious and really compliments the open concept feel of the first floor. Custom trim work, custom closets, Laundry room and ample storage closets compliment all the features this property has to offer. Added bonuses are double 5/8ths sheet rocked and 400 series Anderson windows for increased soundproofing and shared driveway/ garage. Conveniently located near all that Jersey City heights has to offer. Come see for yourself before its gone. 5 year tax abatement"
240003361,SOLD,"JC, Heights",197 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1300,6494,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03805,00021,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$799,000","$799,000",$614.62,$614.62,2/22/2024,3/15/2024,5/3/2024,22,22,,5/6/2024,,,,,,$223,,Conventional,,,,,,Corner of Hutton St.,"This beautifully appointed, spacious 3 BR, 2 Bath home has it all; stunning finishes, soaring ceilings, abundant light, parking, large additional storage room and the perfect Heights location within a couple of blocks of all the best 'hot spots' as well as Riverside Fisk Park. Modern, elegant features mix with warm, rich finishes to create a space that is brimming with high-contrast urban chic. The spectacular layout, with both a corner living room and primary bedroom, allows for a flood of natural light from Eastern, Western, and Southern exposures. Wide-plank white oak floors and oversized windows add to the open and airy feel of this loft-style unit. Custom designed kitchen by Kuche-Cucina boasts sleek Samsung black stainless steel appliances and waterfall quartz countertops. Unwind for the night in your spacious primary bedroom with walk-in closet. Luxuriate in your en-suite spa-like bath enveloped in woodsy warm tones with double vanities and a porcelain tiled rainfall shower. Unit also features a private fenced-in patio. 1 assigned parking spot and 221sf private storage room included. Just a short walk to spectacular Riverview-Fisk Park and some of the Heights' hottest spots like Corto, The Franklin, Bread and Salt, Fox and Crow, Choc au Pain and more. Be a part of the most exciting growth in Jersey City!"
220021232,SOLD,"JC, Heights",179 HOPKINS AVE,Condominium,1646,1724,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07306,06601,00002,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$799,000","$799,000",$485.42,$485.42,12/9/2022,1/10/2023,2/24/2023,32,32,,2/27/2023,,,,$0,2022,,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Central & Perry Street,"New construction luxury at it's finest. Welcome home to 179 Hopkins Ave, the epitome of luxury and convenience. Enter through the main door or through attached garage into your expansive rec-room with a half bathroom and access to a gorgeous backyard, perfect for hosting or for your furry friends. Travel upstairs to your bright and airy living room boasting high ceilings and engineered hard wood floors through out. The sleek and modern kitchen is equipped with plentiful custom cabinets,  vented hood and a full suite of high end stainless steel appliances. The master en-suite boasts an beautiful bathroom with double sinks, large walk in closet, and a deck/terrace overlooking the backyard. This home features two other bedrooms, full sized washer/ dryer, and one other full bath providing ample space for all your needs. All baths are fitted with top-of-the-line fittings and have backlit heated mirrors. Large windows all over the condo, high ceilings with recessed lighting, surround sound speakers in the living area, and 1 car garage tandem parking is included with this unit. There are dedicated closets in the shared garage for extra storage and the condo comes with the Ring security system for your peace of mind. Just the pure luxury of this home will make it an enjoyable place to call home. Located minutes away from Journal Square, light rail and all the transportation options making this the perfect address for any commuter. Take advantage of the 5 yeartax abatement, Must see!!"
260005332,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",545 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1080,1724,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02305,00029,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$799,000",$739.81,,3/26/2026,,,14,,,3/26/2026,,,,,,$380,,,,,,,,South St. & Bowers,"Step directly from your private in-unit elevator into a sun-filled open-concept residence with 10-foot ceilings.  The expansive layout is finished with 4-inch wide oak hardwood floors throughout and oversized windows that flood the home with natural light. The kitchen anchors the living space with custom cabinetry, Calacatta quartz countertops, and high-end stainless-steel appliances.  The primary suite is generously proportioned and features a sleek, modern en-suite bathroom with Porcelanosa tile, a custom floating double vanity, and an oversized LED mirror. The suite also provides ample space for a dedicated home office or additional storage. The second bedroom is thoughtfully set apart, making it ideal for guests or family, while the overall layout allows for the potential creation of a third bedroom, should a buyer desire.  Buyers may have the opportunity to customize layouts and select finish packages, offering flexibility to tailor the home to individual needs.  Ideally located on Palisade Avenue, the home is steps from neighborhood dining, shopping, and cafés, with nearby bus routes and light rail access providing convenient connectivity throughout Jersey City and into New York City."
230017860,SOLD,"JC, Heights",180 BLEECKER ST,Condominium,1377,1724,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,01202,00073,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$799,000","$799,000",$580.25,$580.25,10/23/2023,11/7/2023,1/24/2024,15,15,,1/24/2024,,,,$0,2022,,,Conventional,,,,,,South St. & Paterson St.,"Welcome to this spacious and sunlit new construction in the Jersey City Heights! This modern duplex is pre-designed for the latest in home technology and entertainment. Boasting wide plank solid hardwood floors throughout, 10ft ceiling, modern crown molding, 8ft custom doors in unit washer dryer, LED lighting, and private landscaped backyard! Pure white quartz counters with waterfall feature, custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and luxurious finishes provides an elevated ambiance in your home. Unit number 1 is a large 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, and also has an additional living room giving you ample space for entertainment and flexible living with a beautiful private backyard. While unit number two offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and a private roof deck.  This property is situated in an unbeatable area of the JC Heights, providing easy commutability and excellent access to public transportation. Direct bus lines to NYC Port Authority, Hoboken, and Downtown JC make commuting a breeze. The convenience continues with nearby Hudson Light Rail Stations, as well as Pershing Field's indoor pool and ice skating rink just a few blocks away. Moreover, residents can enjoy the scenic beauty of Riverview Park, which not only offers breathtaking views but also hosts a variety of exciting activities such as Farmers Market, movie nights, and engaging neighborhood events!"
260004292,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",291 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1350,5876,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,0,3,6,,,"$799,000",$591.85,,3/11/2026,,,29,,,3/11/2026,,,,"$18,472",,,,,,,,,,Bowers and South,"Be the first to live in this brand-new 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom duplex residence  thoughtfully designed for modern city living in one of Jersey City Heights’ most desirable locations.  Spanning two full floors, this expansive first-floor duplex offers the feel of a private townhouse while delivering the comfort and efficiency of new construction. The sun-filled interior features high-quality finishes throughout, creating a clean and contemporary atmosphere from the moment you walk in.  The open-concept living and dining area flows seamlessly into a sleek modern kitchen equipped with new stainless steel appliances, stylish cabinetry, and thoughtfully selected finishes—perfect for both everyday living and entertaining.  Each bedroom offers generous proportions and natural light, while the three full bathrooms provide added comfort and flexibility for families, guests, or those working from home.  Extra care and attention were taken during construction to maximize comfort and privacy. The entire residence has been fully soundproofed, creating a noticeably quieter living environment rarely found in multi-family homes.  Step outside to your private backyard, offering a rare outdoor retreat ideal for relaxing, entertaining, gardening, or enjoying quiet evenings at home.  The location is exceptional—just moments from Riverview-Fisk Park, one of the Heights’ most beloved neighborhood parks. Known for its stunning Manhattan skyline views, the park also hosts the popular weekly farmers market, bringing fresh produce, local vendors, and a vibrant community atmosphere right to your doorstep.  Commuting is effortless with quick access to Hoboken Terminal and PATH Train, offering direct routes to both Midtown and Downtown Manhattan. Multiple nearby bus lines provide additional convenient transit options.  Surrounded by local cafés, restaurants, and everyday conveniences, this home offers the ideal combination of modern design, private outdoor space, neighborhood charm, and exceptional connectivity, along with the convenience of a dedicated parking space. Tesla / EV Charger Ready  Schedule your private showing today."
210019193,SOLD,"JC, Heights",241 SOUTH ST,Condominium,1633,6199,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,"1,2",1,"JC, Heights",07307,02104,00005,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$799,000","$799,000",$489.28,$489.28,8/12/2021,11/19/2021,2/3/2022,73,73,,2/4/2022,,,,$0,,$270,2021,Cash,,,,,,Off Kennedy Blvd,"Check out this brand-new construction duplex that spares no expense in the heart of booming Jersey City Heights. Open your private side entry door to this captivating condo featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, modern open concept living, fully equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances, custom cabinets, quartz counter tops with breakfast bar. Main bedroom with private en-suite bath and sliding glass doors that lead to your balcony, 2 generous sized bedrooms. First floor features a nice size family room and ½ bath and walk out to your backyard for some entertaining or relaxation. Features include hardwood floors throughout, central air/heat, washer and dryer and LED lighting. 1 car shared tandem spot included. Minutes to Journal Square PATH and bus station, restaurants, shops and all major highways and tunnels. Come and see for yourself why Jersey City was named the Sixth Borough of New York City. This property is eligible for a 5 year tax abatement."
260003118,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",105 LAIDLAW AVE,Condominium,1224,1597,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,"1,2",4,"JC, Heights",07306,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,,"$799,000",$652.78,,2/23/2026,,,45,,,2/23/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Oakland & Central Ave,"  Set amongst a striking new four-unit development in The Heights, this private, cozy stand-alone residence feels like a single family home; redefining modern living, bold style and curated comfort. The classic floorplan spans two levels with an open living/dining downstairs and sleeping quarters upstairs, this 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath home showcases its very own private pathway and green space.  Step into a sun-soaked living, dining and kitchen space with warm hardwood floors and a modern stairwell with chandelier. The kitchen commands attention with white quartz counters, seamless backsplash, matte black and natural wood custom cabinetry, and premium stainless appliances. Matte black pendant lighting, underlighting on cabinets, and exposed shelves fixtures finish the look.  Retreat to the upstairs bedrooms offering excellent light, space, and primary ensuite with walkin closet. Bathroom finishes include elements like matte black vessel sinks, vertical tile to the ceiling, glass-enclosed multi-spray shower with accent lighting and shower seat. Additional upgrades abound with extras like Bose surround sound speakers throughout the home, or the magazine-worthy powder room with floating vanity and artistic wallpaper.  Just two wee blocks to Reservoir #3 or Pershing Field Park, easy access to the Journal Square PATH (& NYC access), schools up the blocks & shops around the corner... this location offers comfort, community and convenience. Set on a tree-lined street in Jersey City Heights, this quiet neighborhood is known for its creative, inclusive community, boutique shops, local restaurants, excellent parks and schools."
260005659,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",15 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1290,1597,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$799,000",$619.38,,3/31/2026,,,9,,,3/31/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Central and Sherman,"Welcome to The Livy! This trio of brand-new residences blends modern craftsmanship together with rich design. Each home captures a signature balance of sophistication and warmth with curated lighting, high ceilings, wide plank hardwood flooring, and thoughtful layouts intended for everyday elegance. (unit 1 comes with private back yard)  Perfectly positioned near Pershing Field Park and the Reservoir (w/bus options half a block in each direction), plus nearby 2nd Street Light Rail, this address connects effortlessly to both PATH and ferry routes for seamless NYC access. The quiet tree-lined street brings the serenity of neighborhood living, with the charm and community of Jersey City, Hoboken and beyond."
260005964,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",72 COLUMBIA AVE,Condominium,1920,1724,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1V,"JC, Heights",07306,,47,Heights,,,,,4,0,3,9,,,"$799,000",$416.15,,4/3/2026,,,6,,,4/3/2026,,,,,2025,$525,,,,,,,,Linconl and Thorne,"Exceptional opportunity to own a spaciuous 4-bedroom, 3-bath residence offering the comfort and scale of a single-family home, complete with private parking and a  backyard retreat. Designed for both refined living and effortless entertaining, the main residence showcases an expansive layout with generously proportioned bedrooms, multiple living spaces, and a seamless indoor-outdoor flow that enhances everyday living. A standout feature of this home is the fully equipped private suite on the first level, complete with its own entrance, 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, full kitchen, and living area—ideal for extended family, guests, a home office, or potential rental income. Thoughtfully designed to accommodate today’s multigenerational lifestyle or savvy investor, this property offers a rare blend of privacy, flexibility, and functionality. Ideally situated near transportation, shopping, dining, and major commuter routes, this residence delivers both convenience and long-term value in a truly versatile setting.  Ai generated pictures to showcase the opportunity to make this home their own."
260006021,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",160 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,1300,5069,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,4903,3,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,,"$799,000",$614.62,,4/6/2026,,,3,,,4/6/2026,,,,$0,,,,,No,No,Yes,,,Prospect and Reservoir,"Seller offering up to 2 years of fenced in parking at 156 Central Ave!  Welcome to 160 Central Ave Unit 1, a premier high-end new construction condo from NKAY Developers in the heart of Jersey City Heights, conveniently located across from Pershing Field Park. This first floor unit has a private entrance and features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, private backyard and secure rental parking just 2 doors down.  Sleek kitchen is designed with top of the line stainless steel Bosch appliances, quartz waterfall counters and backsplash, oversized stainless steel sink, two-tone custom cabinetry, pot filler, stylish gold hardware and fixtures, and high-end pendant lighting. West facing living and dining room boast a fireplace framed with custom millwork, oversized Andersen windows, and a large closet under the stairs for additional storage. Main bedroom suite faces east and offers ample natural light with a sliding glass door, custom millwork accent wall with dual pendant lighting, walk-in closet with high-end custom built-in shelving and cabinets. Ensuite bathroom offers an oversized double vanity, floor-to-ceiling large format tiles, dramatic warm accent lighting, and a top of the line waterfall shower, sprayer, and jets. Each of the additional 2 bedrooms feature high end custom built-in closets. Washer/dryer in unit add to the convenience of the home.  Private professionally landscaped backyard features grass surrounded by a paver patio and boasts a stainless steel kitchen complete with sink and gas/ electric hookups. The home is equipped with a smart doorbell, keyless entry, Legrand smart dimmers, and energy-efficient Nest thermostats. The exterior facade has been designed with modern yet timeless features, exterior lighting, professional landscaping, and a fenced-in front yard. The property comes with a 10-year warranty. Please note that square footage is approximate. Amazing location is just steps from tons of restaurants, shopping, transit options to the city, and the 13-acre park with a trail/path, reservoir, multiple sport fields, pool, ice rink, and much more!    "
210013464,SOLD,"JC, Heights",93 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1600,1691,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$799,000","$799,000",$499.38,$499.38,6/3/2021,6/23/2021,8/12/2021,20,20,,8/12/2021,,,,,,$200,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers & Griffith,"Fabulous brand-new construction in Jersey City Heights by one of Jersey City's premier builders coming soon! This gorgeous 1600 sq ft duplex featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths (and an additional rec room leading to a private backyard) blends modern luxury with timeless charm. Living here will make commuting in any direction a breeze!  State-of-the-art modern finishes & thoughtful design showcased throughout, including surround sound in the living room & backyard, security, & beautifully built-out closets. Immaculate kitchens are designed with timeless white shaker cabinets. Frigidaire Gallery appliances, wine fridge, and gleaming white quartz countertops. Bathrooms are equipped with modern vessel vanities, Italian tile, and rain shower heads. Tandem parking in garage.  *Photos taken from a similar property developed by the same builders."
210013244,SOLD,"JC, Heights",70 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,2108,1603,"$799,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307-1111,03602,00042,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$799,000","$799,000",$379.03,$379.03,6/2/2021,6/1/2021,7/30/2021,0,0,,8/2/2021,,,,,,,,Cash,No,No,Yes,,,SANFORD AND SUMMIT,"Nestled on one of the most historic Jersey City Heights streets is 70 Sherman Place, a show stopping Victorian home built in 1901 that is bursting with old world charm and character. Consisting of four luxurious fully renovated units, all bathed in light and features crisp modern design, each with their own unique elements. All include deeded parking, a designated private outdoor space, and additional massive private locked storage unit in the basement! Unit#1 boasts over 2,100 square feet of open space as a 3-bedroom, 2 full bathrooms featuring heated temperature controlled modern porcelain tile flooring. The unit itself features soaring 10’ tall ceilings, light-filled interiors framed by oversized casement windows, ample closets all hidden behind custom designed Italian 8’ tall doors and wide-plank original hardwood flooring throughout the entire home. The kitchen wows with white shaker cabinetry featuring black iron and hint of copper hardware. Luxury black stainless steel appliances by Samsung include a gas range oven, large French door refrigerator, microwave and dishwasher. Also to note is the stunning master bedroom with a private en-suite, two spacious guest bedrooms and a guest bathroom. Other features include private use of the front porch, garage parking, all new high efficiency central HVAC, Mitsubishi tankless water heater and dedicated laundry room with full-size washer/dryer. Close to tons of shopping, dining, parks and a range of transport options, commute to NYC in under 30 minutes! Each unit in this splendid grand house is a home to be cherished for many years to come. Book your private tour today!  Square footages and virtual renderings are for reference and visualization purposes only and may differ from the actual unit."
