240003429,SOLD,"JC, Heights",81 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1264,1713,"$820,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,4406,12,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$820,000","$849,000",$648.73,$648.73,2/23/2024,4/15/2024,5/30/2024,52,52,,6/4/2024,,,,$0,,$118,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton & Franklin,"Welcome to the epitome of modern urban living in Jersey City Heights! Unveiling a newly renovated 4-unit condo, this exquisite residence offers a seamless blend of sophistication and comfort. Nestled in the sought-after neighborhood, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom duplex boasts a private backyard, defining the perfect oasis in the heart of the vibrant community. Meticulously designed, the spacious living area unfolds seamlessly, merging the living, dining, and kitchen spaces into an inviting expanse, ideal for both entertainment and relaxation. Three generously sized bedrooms bathed in natural light, provide ample space for personalized style. Contemporary fixtures and elegant tile work adorn both bathrooms, with frameless shower doors adding a touch of modernity and creating a spa-like feel. The condo's clever use of space and thoughtfully crafted floor plan optimizes the expansive layout, ensuring every inch is functional and aesthetically pleasing. Step onto 4” Select Red Oak Hardwood Floors that span the unit, setting the stage for an elegant experience. The kitchen, a culinary haven, features Kraus kitchen sink & faucet, Jenn Air Appliances, and is graced with a peninsula and quartz countertops, embodying the perfect fusion of style and functionality. Solid core interior doors, extra-wide moldings & trims with crown molding throughout the house create an air of sophistication. The unit also features a dedicated backyard, low voltage with proficient brand speakers, custom closet designs, wall decor moldings, and claddings in the master bedroom. Located in the thriving Jersey City Heights neighborhood, renowned for its diverse community, shops, cafes, and cultural attractions, this residence offers easy access to transportation, making New York City just a breezy commute away. A shining example of luxury and convenience in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Welcome home!"
