240002721,SOLD,"JC, Heights",131 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1425,6519,"$820,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03601,00003,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$820,000","$799,000",$575.44,$575.44,2/13/2024,2/25/2024,6/27/2024,12,12,,6/29/2024,,,,"$3,831",2023,$150,,Conventional,,,,,, Kennedy Blvd & Central Ave,"Stunning new construction condominium is a luxurious haven, offering 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The space is thoughtfully designed, featuring a private balcony accessible from the Primary en-suite. The living area encompasses a beautifully designed openconcept kitchen, living/dining room combo, and the convenience of 1-car garage tandem parking.  The Dream Chef's kitchen is ahighlight boasting top of the line appliances a mosaic marble backsplash contemporary style soft close cabinets an all-white waterfallcenter island, a Samsung 4-door customized panel refrigerator and a convenient drawer Microwave.  The Primary en-suite and all bathrooms showcase sophisticated updates with marble walls and mosaic floorings. Every room is adorned with Hunter Douglas blinds providing a lifetime warranty.Local bus stops just a few steps away offer effortless transportation to and from NYC. Don't miss the chance to call this sophisticated condominium yours."
250004864,SOLD,"JC, Heights",106 GRACE ST,Condominium,1390,6354,"$820,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,403,43,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$820,000","$835,000",$589.93,$589.93,3/14/2025,4/30/2025,6/25/2025,47,47,,6/26/2025,,"$148,200",2023,"$3,139",2022,$250,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Nelson And JFK Blvd.,"**NEW Construction** Amazing Opportunity to own this uniquely designed contemporary Condo in the Jersey City Heights section. This home offers a 3 Bed 3 Bath layout, plus a private rooftop deck. Upon entrance you will find Hardwood floors, Recessed Lighting, and a neutral palette throughout. Light & bright Living/Dining Combo features vaulted ceilings and modern gas fireplace. The Eat in Kitchen offers Black SS Appliances, Marbled quartz waterfall counters with eat-in peninsula island and modern white cabinetry. Down the hall the main Full Bath + 3 Bedrooms inc the Primary Suite. Primary boasts a WIC, sleek ensuite bath with Stall Shower & Balcony. Convenient in Unit laundry on this level too! Make your way to the 2nd level to find a large Rooftop Deck, perfect for entertaining guests. Tandem Driveway & 1 Car Garage w/utility closets for storage. 10 Year Builder's Warranty and 5 Year Tax Abatement comes with this property. This conveniently situated property is a few short blocks to Grove PATH, buses, and Light Rail. Enjoy the many eateries and shops nearby. Take in the fantastic views of the waterfront. Don't wait, come and see for yourself! This one won't last!!"
220000027,SOLD,"JC, Heights",1163 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,1700,1691,"$820,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$820,000","$799,000",$482.35,$482.35,1/2/2022,2/3/2022,3/29/2022,32,32,,4/9/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Poplar and Grace,"Light floods into these newly constructed three bedroom homes with private outdoor and available 1-car garage tandem parking in The Heights. Impeccably finished with crown molding, gleaming hardwood floors and oversized Pella windows, respected builders, Nkay Construction, deliver signature quality and thoughtful design every time.  Clean white eat-in kitchen offers quartz counters and tile backsplash, plus stainless steel apron sink, and must-have appliances like the smart refrigerator and wine cooler. Bathrooms showcase floor to ceiling tilework, medicine cabinets and soaker tubs with multi system showers as well. Considered layout allows all three bedrooms in nearby proximity, with the primary ensuite offering a spacious walk-in closet with custom built-in organization.  Located directly off the two-car garage, unit 1 offers a downstairs bonus room finished with wood tile for durability, and includes half bath and designated laundry area for convenience. Double glass doors open to a fully finished private backyard complete with patio pavers, landscaping and storybook white fence.  Located directly on main thoroughfare, Summit Avenue, and only one block to expansive Washington Park, this home offers the best of urban luxury with shops and restaurants plus additional outdoor access. Jersey City Heights is well known for its eclectic art scene, vibrant community, excellent schools and easy access to NYC, Hoboken and surrounding areas."
210005582,SOLD,"JC, Heights",121 NORTH ST,Condominium,1576,1186,"$820,000",CONDO-COOP,,2nd,2,"JC, Heights",07307,01505,00013,Heights,,,,,3,1,1,8,,"$820,000","$849,000",$520.30,$520.30,3/9/2021,5/6/2021,8/10/2021,58,58,,8/12/2021,,,,,TBD,$449,2021,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & Central Ave,"Welcome to this new, environmentally sustainable 3 bedroom, 1 ½ bath condo located in Jersey City. The building is designed using LEED and Passive House standards, as well as Biophilic design principles to bring in natural light and provide views of outdoor vegetation and the NYC skyline. The building features two unique units, equipped with Energy Star rated ‘white’ roof and vegetated ‘green’ roof, so plenty of outdoor space for entertaining or simply relaxing. The home features beautiful white solid oak flooring and high efficiency LED lighting. On the second level, you’ll find your master bedroom and bathroom which includes a Kohler stall shower, and open layout on the third level where you’ll find a large kitchen with pantry, Quartz countertops, Kohler sink & plumbing fixtures, and stainless steel appliances with direct vent exhaust hood. You also have two bedrooms and a half bathroom on this level, along with lots of natural light coming from your high efficiency triple pane windows and peace of mind with High Efficiency insulation on the interior side of all exterior walls and roof. Each unit features a washer dryer, parking space with electric vehicle charging station and common storage and so much more. Jersey City Heights is the go-to spot for living, eating and playing offering an abundance of lush green parks, shops, restaurants, and a fantastic arts district all at your fingertips."
220006816,SOLD,"JC, Heights",63 SOUTH ST,Condominium,1500,1691,"$820,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & L,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,1,2,6,,"$820,000","$849,000",$546.67,$546.67,4/19/2022,4/29/2022,5/27/2022,10,10,,5/31/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Sherman Ave & Webster Ave,"Make this modern marvel home in The Heights! Local builders, Nkay Construction, have done it again with this super smart duplex complete with garage parking plus eCharging station.  Situated on the corner of a tree-lined street, the spacious 2-story home offers oversized windows with sunlight streaming in on three sides of the 2 bed and 2 bath layout. Beautiful bay windows open to the spacious upstairs with flowing kitchen, living and dining area complete with pewter oak hardwood floors and crown molding. Downstairs provides an additional family room with half bath, ideal for entertaining or flex space.   Gorgeous painted wood blue accents highlight the white eat-in kitchen with waterfall quartz counters, tile backsplash and custom shaker cabinets. Additional features include apron sink, black stainless Samsung appliances and matte black fixtures including wall mounted pot filler faucet. Stylish bathrooms offer highlights such as herringbone grey porcelain tile, smart mirrors and glass shower with penny tile floor pattern plus multi head rain shower system. Primary ensuite offers a must-have double vanity and built-out walk-in closet.   Additional tech upgrades include smart doorbell, smart thermostat, camera and security system and central vacuum. Situated walking distance to bustling Central Avenue, expansive Washington Park or Riverview Fisk Park with NYC views and light rail access, this home is the ideal combination of location and modern luxury."
210007684,SOLD,"JC, Heights",130 SOUTH ST,Condominium,1740,1653,"$820,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$820,000","$799,000",$471.26,$471.26,4/1/2021,5/12/2021,7/19/2021,37,37,,7/20/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & Central,"Location location location! Steps away from Central Ave Shopping District, 130 South St redefines luxury condos. This ground up new construction offers 2 units with impeccable finishes, parking space, and private outdoor space. This duplex unit offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a bonus living area with powder room leading to an generous size backyard. Features include Hardwood floors, custom trim, large spacious kitchen with Samsung stainless steel appliances and smart fridge, a wine fridge, quartz countertop, beautiful coffered ceilings in your living room plus an electric fireplace.  Lots of closet space throughout with custom shelving, in unit laundry, and modern fixtures. Master bedroom offers a sliding door to walkout to your private balcony, a large walk in closet, and a master bathroom with spa shower panel. Steps away from Washington Park, amazing restaurants on Central Ave, close to NYC transportation. Schedule a tour today! For virtual tour and floor plans visit 130southst.com "
240015363,SOLD,"JC, Heights",90 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1335,1597,"$825,000",CONDO-COOP,,3 & R,3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,5,,"$825,000","$825,000",$617.98,$617.98,8/6/2024,8/15/2024,9/23/2024,9,9,,9/24/2024,,,,,,$343,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Ferry,"Experience elevated living with this newly constructed 3 bed, 2 bath home with private roofdeck in Jersey City Heights. Oversized windows and a Juliet balcony bring the natural light and a treetop breeze into the super spacious open concept living, kitchen and formal dining area. Crown molding and gleaming red oak hardwood floors add elegance to the classic design, while the full private roof deck is the real showstopper with NYC views, hookups for gas, electric, and water, plus a refreshing living garden space.  The kitchen boasts contemporary white cabinets, quartz counters, herringbone subway tile backsplash, and stainless fixtures and appliances. Bathrooms are beautifully designed with floor-to-ceiling tile, spacious vanities, and options for either a bathtub or a shower. The primary ensuite stands out with a stunning onyx accent wall and wainscoting, as well a substantial walk-in closet. Finally, the dedicated laundry room offers a brand-new LG washer and dryer plus central location for added convenience.  Situated in a classic red brick building on a tree-lined street, this home is just blocks to the 2nd Street Light Rail and the Hoboken stairs, providing easy commutes and access to surrounding areas and NYC. Residents enjoy nearby Riverview Fisk Park and Pershing Field Parks, with stunning city views and playgrounds, or nature spaces, farmer’s markets and swimming! Jersey City Heights is known for its vibrant community, excellent schools, peaceful parks and central location."
250009857,SOLD,"JC, Heights",109 POPLAR ST,Condominium,1627,1653,"$825,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,00805,00020,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$825,000","$825,000",$507.07,$507.07,5/16/2025,6/20/2025,8/7/2025,35,35,,8/8/2025,,,,"$12,439",2023,,,Conventional,,,,,,JFK Blvd & Nelson Ave,"Welcome to this beautifully designed duplex that blends luxury and comfort in one of Jersey City Heights’ most sought-after locations. This spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home offers an open-concept layout ideal for both everyday living and stylish entertaining. The chef’s kitchen features high-end stainless steel appliances, a 5-burner stove with convection oven, custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, and a breakfast bar perfect for morning coffee or casual meals. Upstairs, the serene primary suite boasts a private en-suite bath and sliding glass doors leading to your own balcony retreat. Two additional generous bedrooms offer flexibility for guests, a home office, or growing families. The lower level includes a welcoming family room, convenient half bath, and walk-out access to your private backyard oasis—ideal for relaxing or hosting friends. This home is filled with thoughtful touches, including hardwood floors throughout, central air and heat for year-round comfort, in-unit washer and dryer, and sleek LED lighting. A shared tandem parking spot for one car is also included."
220008148,SOLD,"JC, Heights",27 LEONARD ST,Condominium,1325,1713,"$825,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,00504,00012,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$825,000","$849,000",$622.64,$622.64,5/6/2022,6/13/2022,7/26/2022,38,38,,7/26/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Central and Summit,"Welcome to this luxurious 1300+ sq foot condo in the highly sought after Jersey City Heights! This 3 bed 2 bath condo is all new construction and features a beautiful and serene private rooftop patio that is fully equipped with gas, hot and cold water, Trex decking and beautiful NYC views! The custom chef’s kitchen is complete with Bertazzoni appliances, quartz countertops with waterfall Moen faucet, European style frame less cabinets and 4 solid hardwood flooring. The open floor plan in the kitchen and bright spacious living room allow for great entertainment space. The beautifully updated bathrooms boast frameless shower doors and rain shower heads as well as a double sink vanity. This unit features a modern design throughout, energy efficient full spray foam insulation, separate private entrance, additional private storage and parking spot in the attached garage! Plus, a central Vacuum system, Andersen windows, Rheem HVAC, sound dampening rubber member between floors for sound insulation. Don’t miss the opportunity to own this fabulous unit!"
220015302,SOLD,"JC, Heights",201 COLUMBIA AVE,Condominium,1995,1597,"$825,000",CONDO-COOP,,L/1/2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,9,,"$825,000","$825,000",$413.53,$413.53,8/23/2022,9/27/2022,11/2/2022,35,35,,11/22/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Bleecker St & North St,"Light streams in through the oversized Pella windows illuminating the open floorplan with classic crown molding and gleaming hardwood flooring throughout. White eat-in kitchen shows style with waterfall quartz counters & backsplash, custom shaker cabinets, pot-filler, apron sink, black Samsung appliances and wine fridge. A tech-lover’s dream wired for plenty of mod cons, including smart doorbell, smart thermostat, camera, security system and central vacuum.   First unit *triplex* offers nearly 2000 sq ft and not one, but two lower level bonus rooms; one with wet bar, half bath and gorgeous sliding glass doors to the fully finished private backyard.   Bathrooms bring coveted upgrades like double-vanities, herringbone tile in soaker tub with multi-system shower and niche, and glass shower with pennytile accents. Primary ensuite hosts spacious built-out walk-in-closet for optimal storage and organization.   On a quiet tree-lined street of The Heights, and walking distance to JFK Blvd, Washington Park and 9th St Light Rail station, this neighborhood is known for great community, excellent schools and easy NYC access, all amid the eclectic and vibrant scene of Jersey City Heights.  "
230001879,SOLD,"JC, Heights",204 BOWERS ST,Condominium,1482,1597,"$825,000",CONDO-COOP,,2&R,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,5,,"$825,000","$825,000",$556.68,$556.68,2/2/2023,3/9/2023,4/10/2023,35,35,,4/11/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Milton Ave & Summit Ave,"Reputed builders, NKay Construction, do it again with these freshly renovated, modern, move-in ready homes in The Heights. Set on a beautiful tree-lined street, each spacious three bedroom layout comes with coveted private outdoor and EV charger non-tandem parking.    Stylish finishes and top-level craftsmanship shine with classic crown molding, rich hardwood floors and large Pella windows. Eat-in kitchens showcase sparkling waterfall quartz counters, farm sink, shaker cabinets, blue accent shiplap, and black Samsung appliances including pot filler and added wine fridge. Smarthome features include ring doorbell, camera and security system, and nest thermostat.   Upstairs units includes full-size private rooftop with incredible cityscape views.   Bathrooms boast extras like beautiful blue double vanity, herringbone tile, glass shower with multi-spray system, matte black fixtures and smart mirrors.  All units have a dedicated utility area with Samsung washer and dryer, plus tandem EV charging garage tandem parking.  Newly refinished tan brick and grey paneled building is situated less than one block from Summit Ave, and equidistant to both Washington and Pershing Field Parks. Jersey City Heights is known for its great community, excellent schools and easy NYC access, with vibrant shops, restaurants and parks!"
230002633,SOLD,"JC, Heights",152 CONGRESS ST,Condominium,1455,1653,"$825,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$825,000","$825,000",$567.01,$567.01,2/15/2023,4/3/2023,5/5/2023,47,47,,5/17/2023,,,,,,$161,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central Ave,"Welcome to 152 Congress St - a two unit condo building with all high end lux modern finishes. Unit 2 is very spacious with 1,455 sqft . This condo unit has 3 generous size bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and dining area. 1 Car Parking in driveway deeded to the unit (not tandem). Some features include hardwood floor, beautiful chic tile designs, two tone shaker cabinets with quartz countertop, crown molding, custom closets, fireplaces, and Samsung appliances. The master has a large walk in closet, a double sink vanity in the bathroom, and sliding doors leading out to a relaxing private terrace. Rooftop offers a full view of the NYC skyline. *not tandem parking*/ Energy Efficient (property comes with paid solar panels) Lots of natural sunlight all throughout. Conveniently located steps away from Central Ave Shopping District, Restaurants and Coffee Shops, Washington Park, and Congress St Lite Rail. Transportation to NYC, Hoboken, WTC, JSQ are steps away."
220015370,SOLD,"JC, Heights",88 THORNE ST,Condominium,1589,6494,"$825,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,0214,00059,,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$825,000","$800,000",$519.19,$519.19,8/24/2022,9/16/2022,10/17/2022,23,23,,10/17/2022,,,,"$7,932",2021,$243,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy and Summit Ave,"Newly constructed and tastefully styled 1589 square foot duplex condo located in the thriving Heights area of Jersey City. This welcoming and warm home has it all including 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bath, garage parking, amazing expansive private backyard, balcony, sleek chef's kitchen with quartz countertops, state of the art smart appliances, south-facing sunlit living room with oversized windows, beautiful HW floors, washer dryer room, central air, recessed lighting throughout and a security system. Main bedroom has a custom walk-in closet, a spacious balcony overlooking your private garden and ensuite bathroom with step-in rain shower and multi-jet spray system. 2nd full spa-like bathroom on the same level with bathtub. Lower level has a large bonus room, beautifully tiled half bath and direct access to the garage (with added storage/washer dryer room) and your private backyard perfect for entertaining, gardening, barbecuing or just relaxing. Short stroll to NYC bus, parks, playground, tennis and basketball courts, pool, dog run and to the many shops and restaurants in the burgeoning and lively Central Ave district which is currently undergoing major renovations. 15 minute walk to the elevator/steps to Hoboken, the 9th St Lightrail which connects to the Path train and Riverview Park offering amazing NYC skyline views and an impressive weekend farmer's market. Just a few blocks from the Central Avenue Special Improvement District (CASID). The 2 unit building completed construction in 2020 and came with a 10 year builders warranty and a tax abatement which expires in 2025. For tech lovers this home is wired for SMARTHOME capability. If you are seeking a modern spacious condo full of natural light with garage parking and a private outdoor yard this is the perfect home for you!  Video tour available."
230014205,SOLD,"JC, Heights",72 LAKE ST,Condominium,1544,1597,"$825,000",CONDO-COOP,,3 & R,2,"JC, Heights",07306,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$825,000","$825,000",$534.33,$534.33,8/24/2023,8/29/2023,10/13/2023,5,5,,10/13/2023,,,,,,$200,,Conventional,,,,,,Montrose & JFK,"High ceilings, high-end finishes and sky-high rooftop views help elevate these brand new homes to the next level. Situated on a quiet tree-lined street adjacent to Jersey City Heights Reservoir, each three-bedroom floor plan includes coveted private outdoor space, ensuite balcony and over 1,000 sq ft of roof deck, equipped with gas & water.  Modern and clean design echos throughout with beautiful oak hardwood floors, classic crown molding and all the smart home upgrade options. The dreamy upstairs space offers lofty appeal with a large glass Juliet balcony in the main living area, plus a full floor private rooftop with panoramic parkside views.  Kitchens excite with crisp shining white or matte midnight blue custom cabinets, gleaming waterfall quartz counters, tile backsplash, and top notch appliances. Freshly designed bathrooms feature dramatic floor to ceiling tile, glass shower or soaker tub and double vanity in the primary ensuite.  Beautiful brick facade offers excellent curb appeal on one of The Heights best streets. Located just off Pershing Field Park, and between JFK and Summit Ave, this home offers walkability to nearby shops, excellent parks, and easy NYC access."
220019909,SOLD,"JC, Heights",98 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1875,1597,"$825,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$825,000","$825,000",$440.00,$440.00,11/10/2022,12/5/2022,1/4/2023,25,25,,1/4/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave & JFK,"Dream a little dreamhome with this modern marvel in The Heights. Brand new construction home offers three bedrooms, loads of square footage, backyard, plus garage parking for the ultimate urban appeal.  To-the-ceiling Pella windows shine loads of natural light through to the open concept floorplan finished with classic design and modern upgrades like fresh oak hardwood floors, crown molding and smart home tech throughout. Downstairs duplex hosts bonus room with half bath, plus double glass door access to your own fully finished private backyard.  Contemporary eat-in kitchens offer clean white quartz waterfall island, counters and backsplash, plus seamless custom cabinetry and stainless LG appliances including wine fridge. Primary ensuites host glass doors to private balcony plus large built-out walk-in closets. Bathrooms feature elements like double vanity, glass shower with multihead system or soaker tub for added convenience. Designated utility area features stacking Samsung washer and dryer.  Glass and brick modern building with garage access is one block from Leonard Gordon Park, Citi bike station, and also main thoroughfare Summit Ave. Jersey City Heights is known for its eclectic vibe, great community, excellent schools and accessibility to NYC and surrounding areas."
