220015974,SOLD,"JC, Heights",121 SOUTH ST,Condominium,1367,1603,"$826,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02805,00027,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$826,000","$799,000",$604.24,$604.24,9/7/2022,9/20/2022,11/10/2022,13,13,,12/1/2022,,"$466,400",2021,"$7,451",2021,$170,,Conventional,,,,,,Central & Summit,"Welcome to luxury condominium living in the heart of the Heights!  This 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home will have you thinking you're in the suburbs as you stretch out in 1,367 square feet adorned with high-end finishes and custom touches abound.  From the living/dining area with cathedral ceilings to the stunning chef's kitchen, which is complete with a gas range and a stainless steel appliance package, this home has it all. Added custom beverage prep area is perfect for your morning coffee and boasts a built-in wine fridge and a floor-to-ceiling pantry cabinet for all of your food storage needs.  Both bathrooms are outfitted with Porcelanosa vanities, while the en-suite shower is equipped with a glass enclosure for a spa-like experience.  The main bedroom suite easily fits a king-sized bed and the oversized closet has been custom fitted with cabinetry to maximize your storage space.   Secondary bedrooms are being used as a nursery & office but can easily be converted to bedrooms with space for a queen bed in each. The private rooftop deck showcases NYC's striking views and has room for all of the necessities to supply the perfect vista for entertaining guests or simply enjoying meals outdoors. Construction was finished in late 2018, meaning this is your chance to become just the second owners of a home that's sure to satisfy for the foreseeable future.    "
