250003339,SOLD,"JC, Heights",13 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1422,6078,"$830,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,4402,24,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$830,000","$824,900",$583.68,$583.68,2/20/2025,2/25/2025,4/25/2025,5,5,,5/8/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave,"Welcome to 13 Manhattan Ave #3, a brand-new construction condo in the heart of Jersey City Heights, offering modern elegance, high-end finishes and a private rooftop. This spacious three-bedroom, two-bath home is designed for both comfort and convenience, featuring 10 ft ceilings and an open-concept layout that seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living area—perfect for entertaining. The kitchen is equipped with custom shaker cabinetry, quartz countertops, and a GE stainless steel appliance package, including a gas range and a wine fridge. New Anderson windows provide natural light that floods the space, highlighting the hardwood floors throughout. Thoughtfully designed custom closets provide optimal organization, and there is plenty of storage within the home. An in-unit washer and dryer adds everyday convenience, while central air and heat with Nest smart thermostats ensure year-round comfort. The master suite is generously sized and includes its own private balcony. This unit also includes a private rooftop spanning over 700 square feet, offering stunning views of NYC and Journal Square—perfect for enjoying sunsets and entertaining guests. A 10-year builder’s warranty offers peace of mind, making this an excellent opportunity for modern urban living. Located within walking distance to Pershing Field Park, this home is perfectly situated between Central and Palisade Avenue, offering easy access to shops, restaurants, and everyday conveniences. Commuters will appreciate the proximity to NJ Transit bus lines into Manhattan, with bus stops just a block away on Ferry St and Central Ave, as well as the 2nd Street Light Rail station. Reach out to schedule your private tour today!"
