220016665,SOLD,"JC, Heights",84 PATERSON ST,Condominium,1870,1653,"$837,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$837,000","$849,000",$447.59,$447.59,9/15/2022,1/25/2023,2/22/2023,132,132,,3/27/2023,,,,,,$333,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Summit Ave,"*Non-Tandem Parking* This ground up new construction redefines luxury condos. A short walk to Congress St Lite Rail Station, 84 Paterson sits in one of the best locations of Jersey City Heights close to Central Ave Shopping District, parks, direct buses into NYC, and amazing restaurants and coffee shops in each direction. Unit 1 is a duplex unit featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a bonus living area with powder room that leads out to an oversized backyard. 1 Car Parking (Not Tandem) included. Features include hardwood floors, custom trim, large spacious kitchen with Samsung stainless steel appliances and additional cabinetry, wine fridge, quartz countertop, coffered ceilings in the living room with an electric fireplace, lots of closet space throughout with custom shelving, in unit laundry, and modern fixtures. Master bedroom offers a sliding door to walkout to your private balcony, a large walk-in closet, and a master bathroom. Schedule a tour today!"
230009218,SOLD,"JC, Heights",138 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1886,1597,"$838,000",CONDO-COOP,,L&1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,2,2,8,,"$838,000","$835,000",$444.33,$444.33,6/5/2023,7/11/2023,8/21/2023,36,36,,8/21/2023,,,,,,$330,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin and Ferry,"Nestled on one of the most coveted streets in Jersey City Heights, this stunning brick brownstone feels like a single family home, offering private sanctuary and spacious living. Built in 1885 and meticulously gut-renovated in 2020, the over 1800 sq ft, 2-story layout boasts 2 full bedrooms with additional rooms like bonus family room, full laundry, utility and storage rooms, plus 2 full and 2 half baths. With an additional 725 sq ft of outdoor living space, the expansive backyard is complete with a multi-section patio, mature trees for elegant shade, and manicured landscaping.  The classic design of the home includes exposed brick accents and white oak flooring, while modern upgrades include Nest thermostat and custom automatic blinds. The contemporary eat-in kitchen hosts formal dining and elegant style with direct access to the backyard. Featuring waterfall quartz counters, sleek custom cabinetry, stainless LG appliances, a wine fridge, and thoughtfully curated pendant lighting, it is the perfect place to entertain guests.  The oversized floor-through bonus room is finished with wood tile for added convenience, and offers endless possibilities for flex space - currently set up as a family room and office. Not one, but two primary ensuites host large walk-in closets with built-ins, providing ample storage space. The stylishly finished bathrooms feature upgrades like floor-to-ceiling tile, penny tile flooring, brass fixtures, multi-systems glass shower or soaker tubs.  Located in the heart of Jersey City Heights, this unique property offers ideal access to walking distance to neighborhood favorites like Lo-Fi Bar, Choc’ o Pain French Bakery and Café, The Franklin Brunch and Dinner Restaurant, and Froth on Franklin Coffee House, plus other landmarks like 100 Steps Hoboken access, and unparalleled NYC views along the Palisade Cliffs. Owners are just blocks to the 2nd Street Light rail and Hoboken access, Riverview Fisk and Pershing Field Parks, Central Avenue main thoroughfare, and Port Authority bus stop. Nearby rental parking is potentially available."
240018696,SOLD,"JC, Heights",106 GRACE ST,Condominium,1725,6354,"$840,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,403,43,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$840,000","$863,000",$486.96,$486.96,9/20/2024,11/7/2024,1/9/2025,47,47,,1/10/2025,,"$148,200",2023,"$3,139",2022,$250,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Nelson Ave. & JFK Blvd.,"**NEW Construction** Amazing Opportunity to own this uniquely designed contemporary Condo in the Jersey City Heights section. This home offers a 3 Bed 3 Bath layout, plus major must haves like a private backyard and garage parking. Upon entrance you will find Hardwood floors, Recessed Lighting, and a neutral palette throughout. Light & bright Living/Dining Combo features trayed ceiling and modern gas fireplace. The Eat in Kitchen offers Black SS Appliances, Marbled quartz waterfall counters with eat-in peninsula island and modern white cabinetry. Down the hall the main Full Bath + 3 Bedrooms inc the Primary Suite. Primary boasts a WIC, sleek ensuite bath with Stall Shower & Balcony. Lower Level holds a large Rec Rm with Wet Bar and a 3rd Full Bath. Convenient in Unit laundry on this level too! Relax outdoors in your privately fenced in yard. Tandem Driveway & 1 Car Garage w/utility closets for storage. 10 Year Builder's Warranty and 5 Year Tax Abatement comes with this property. Live in the heart of Jersey City. This conveniently situated property is a few short blocks to Grove PATH, buses, and Light Rail. Enjoy the many eateries and shops nearby. Take in the fantastic views of the waterfront.  Don't wait, come and see for yourself! This one won't last!!"
220007028,SOLD,"JC, Heights",37 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1493,1597,"$840,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & 3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,4,0,2,7,,"$840,000","$849,000",$562.63,$562.63,4/21/2022,4/21/2022,8/5/2022,0,0,,8/5/2022,,,,,,,,FHA,,,,,,Central & Summit,"Big on both beauty and size, this brand new dreamhome was reconstructed from the ground up with modern luxury living at the heart. Brought to you by revered local builder, M2M Development are known for their chic design, attention to detail and quality craftsmanship.   This home offers a generous two-story layout with 1,490sqft, four bedrooms, two bathrooms, plus private storage and large private rooftop. Settled on a tree-lined street just one block from either Washington Park or Central and Summit Avenue, initial impressions echo an aristocratic era with light brick and mansard roof with dormer windows and trim.   Inside, light and grandeur spill into the modern and bright living space with oversized Andersen windows, light oak wide plank hardwood floors, and all the smart home technology expected today. The thoughtful split-level floorplan hosts a classic setup with open living on the first floor and bedrooms above, plus private access to the 395sqft roofdeck with unobstructed views of the NYC skyline and surrounding areas. Kitchen is finished with understated gray quartz counters, modern white custom cabinetry, brass fixtures, tile backsplash and pendant lighting. Primary bedrooms boast a large walk-in closet and sliding double glass doors to your own private balcony overlooking the backyard. Spa-inspired bathrooms offer elements such as floating double vanities, gorgeous glass showers, or blissful soaker tubs with matte black fixtures. Additional amenities include a dedicated utility area with new appliances, and large private basement storage area (250sqft).   Located in the heart of Jersey City Heights, this home is poised to sell with all the luxury fittings in walking distance to beautiful parks, vibrant community, excellent schools and easy NYC access.  *Photos are artistic renderings of unit, for reference of style. Final finishes & fixtures are subject to differ from artwork.*"
230009431,SOLD,"JC, Heights",123 PROSPECT ST,Condominium,1477,1597,"$840,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & R,2A,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$840,000","$849,000",$568.72,$568.72,6/7/2023,6/22/2023,8/1/2023,15,15,,8/1/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Lienau & Central,"Remarkable design and stylish sophistication shine in this newly renovated home including private outdoor and pre-paid parking in The Heights. Breathtaking brickwork, exposed beams and beautiful white oak floors combine with bay windows and bright open living for clean, simple design.    This three bed, two bath floorplan impresses with ultra-high 13ft ceilings, a sizable private balcony off the living room overlooking the front, plus a full-floor private roof deck with incredible cityscape views. Contemporary kitchen hosts custom matte black lower cabinets, clean natural wood uppers plus waterfall white quartz counters, tile backsplash, Frigidaire stainless appliances, and Kraüs gold faucet and fittings. Carefully curated pendant lighting, black matte window trim a striking exposed brick stairwell punctuate the property with artistry and style.   Bathrooms bring interest with elements such as double vanity,  herringbone or polished porcelain juniper tile feature walls, black pennytile floors, soaker tub or glass shower with cutout niche, or window for natural light. Primary en-suite boasts a showstopping matte black wainscotting feature wall, plus oversized walk-through or double closets.    Timeless brick building with classic front porch vibe rests on a tree-lined street in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Owners enjoy both walkability to surrounding Central Avenue, Pershing, Washington or Palisades Parks, plus nearby pre-paid parking for 1 year. Jersey City Heights is home to an eclectic art community, excellent schools, award-winning restaurants and businesses, plus easy NYC access."
210003016,SOLD,"JC, Heights",72 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,,1691,"$840,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2703,28,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$840,000","$799,000",,,2/5/2021,2/11/2021,4/1/2021,6,6,,4/1/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & Milton,"Created with exquisite taste and intelligent design, one of Jersey City Height’s top developers have completed two freshly renovated homes. This downstairs duplex plus den and backyard levels up daily lifestyle with ease and sophistication.  Experience ultimate curb appeal with alluring white brick facade, dark trim and protective enclosed front porch. Step inside to thoughtful finishes and top quality throughout -- wide plank hardwood floors, exposed brick walls, beautiful bay windows and elegant arched built-in dry bar to open the spacious floorplans. Chef-inspired kitchens impress with striking green custom cabinetry, black quartz waterfall countertops, built-in stainless appliances, brass fixtures and natural wood hood.   Massive master en-suite showcases seductive dark panelled accent wall plus sweeping french doors to private balcony perfect for al fresco coffee or cocktails. Distinctive zen-inspired bathrooms feature unique elements like black tile and floor-to-ceiling glass shower and faux wood or pattern tile floors. The downstairs unit boasts an additional full-sized den, powder bathroom, large private backyard, additional storage and parking.    Settled into a quiet, tree-lined street equidistant to Pershing Field, Leonard Gordon, Riverview Fiske and Washington Parks, this location also offers walkability to surrounding Central & Palisade Avenue for essential shopping needs. The Heights is a vibrant community with excellent schools, award-winning restaurants and shops plus easy NYC access!"
250025729,SOLD,"JC, Heights",10 SOUTH ST,Condominium,917,1597,"$840,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,403,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,2,0,1,4,,"$840,000","$843,000",$916.03,$916.03,1/2/2026,1/2/2026,3/20/2026,0,0,,4/1/2026,,,,,,,,Cash,,,,,,Palisade Ave and Ogden Avenue,"Discover an exceptional new collection of homes where historic character meets modern design.  10SouthSt.com. Rising up to four stories, these thoughtfully crafted residences capture the energy and sophistication of city living while offering a serene retreat at home.  Enjoy the convenience of a full-service elevator building with a secure lobby, intercom access, garage and handicap-accessible parking, and EV charging stations. Just three blocks from the Hoboken Light Rail, residents enjoy effortless access to Manhattan and beyond.  Inside, every detail has been considered—from European floor-to-ceiling windows and wide-plank white oak flooring to Gyp-Crete soundproofing that ensures quiet and comfort. Select homes include private balconies, dens, or roof decks designed for seamless indoor-outdoor living.  The interiors reflect a mid-century modern aesthetic with timeless craftsmanship, highlighted by granite waterfall islands, European cabinetry, Kohler fixtures, GE Café and Fisher & Paykel panel-door appliances, smart mirrors, and imported glass lighting. Open-concept kitchens flow into airy living spaces, creating the perfect backdrop for sophisticated urban life.  Private roof decks with full kitchens provide a refined setting for entertaining, complete with surround sound and green roof features.  For those seeking style, convenience, and connection, these residences reimagine Jersey City Heights living with an inspired blend of design, comfort, and modern amenities.  This home represents a 2 bedroom.  Parking is a separate cost."
250022441,SOLD,"JC, Heights",519 LIBERTY AVE,Condominium,2280,1713,"$840,000",CONDO-COOP,,multi,1,"JC, Heights",07307,1202,47,Heights,,,,,3,2,2,10,,"$840,000","$849,000",$368.42,$368.42,10/31/2025,12/6/2025,2/19/2026,36,36,,2/19/2026,,,,"$10,800",,$250,,VA,,,,,,Bleeker & North St,"Step into refined contemporary living with this oversized 2,300 sq. ft. ground-up new construction residence, built in 2021. Spanning three full floors of sophisticated design, this home is perfectly tailored for comfort, style, and convenience.  The open-concept layout is anchored by a modern chef’s kitchen, featuring sleek granite countertops, premium Samsung stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinetry designed for both function and elegance. Entertaining is effortless with seamless flow into expansive living and dining spaces that welcome natural light.  Upstairs, you’ll find large bedrooms, including a serene primary suite with a walk-in closet and spa-inspired finishes. Western exposures flood the home with light, offering beautiful sunset views every evening.  Enjoy the rare luxury of a private backyard retreat, perfect for gatherings or quiet relaxation, plus the convenience of garage parking included.  Located in the highly desirable Jersey City Heights, this property combines suburban comfort with urban accessibility. You’ll be just moments from parks, trendy restaurants, boutique shops, and top schools, with easy access to NYC via public transportation and quick connections to major highways.   This is more than a home—it’s a lifestyle of space, modern elegance, and unmatched convenience in one of Hudson County’s most sought-after neighborhoods."
230018700,SOLD,"JC, Heights",99 HAGUE ST,Condominium,1416,6078,"$840,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,402,15,,,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$840,000","$849,000",$593.22,$593.22,11/6/2023,1/22/2023,3/8/2024,0,0,,3/8/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Nelson & JFK Blvd,"Welcome to 99 Hague St, a stunning new construction condominium in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This residence includes garage parking, which will be a rare find in the near future stemming from a recent city ordinance change, rendering it an exceptional and prized possession for potential buyers in pursuit of hassle-free parking amidst the advancing urban development of Jersey City. This luxurious 3-bedroom, 2-bath condo boasts a plethora of features, including electric vehicle charging stations, an open floor layout, a vaulted living room ceiling, quartz countertops, a private rooftop deck, in-unit laundry, red oak hardwood floors, designer tiles, and modern fixtures. Step inside this breathtaking condo and experience the advantages of modern construction and understated luxury. The open floor layout provides ample space for entertaining guests or simply relaxing at home. The vaulted ceiling lends an airy, spacious feeling to the living areas, while the hardwood floors add warmth and elegance throughout. The chef's kitchen is a dream come true, featuring sleek quartz countertops, a collection of Samsung stainless steel appliances, and plenty of storage space. Prepare your favorite meals in style and enjoy the benefits of a modern kitchen. One of the most unique features of this property is the electric vehicle charging stations, making it the perfect home for environmentally-conscious individuals who want to reduce their carbon footprint.  As you make your way upstairs, you'll discover the private rooftop deck, offering breathtaking views. Imagine enjoying a morning coffee or evening cocktail as you take in the sights and sounds of the city around you. The private outdoor space is perfect for hosting friends and family or simply enjoying a moment of solitude. The designer tiles and modern fixtures throughout the condo are a testament to the high level of craftsmanship and attention to detail that went into this stunning property. Every inch of this condo is designed to offer the utmost in luxury and comfort. At 99 Hague St, you'll enjoy all the benefits of modern living, including a prime location in the heart of Jersey City. With easy access to public transportation, shopping, dining, and entertainment, this condo is the perfect place to call home. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this stunning new construction condominium your own! The property is eligible for a 5-year tax abatement.  "
250000555,SOLD,"JC, Heights",337 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1790,1603,"$840,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,4504,31,Heights,,,,,4,0,2,8,,"$840,000","$849,000",$469.27,$469.27,1/8/2025,2/28/2025,4/17/2025,51,51,,4/22/2025,,,,$0,,$348,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Ferry St and Franklin St,"Welcome to your dream home in the best location in Jersey City Heights! This new construction home offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and urban convenience. With three spacious bedrooms plus a versatile home office/den, you'll have plenty of room to live, work, and play. Step inside and be wowed by the high-end finishes throughout including a chef's kitchen complete with custom cabinetry with ample storage, a massive breakfast island, and panel-ready appliances that seamlessly blend with the sleek design. Whip up your culinary masterpieces while entertaining guests in style! Light hardwood floors and high ceilings create an airy, open atmosphere throughout the home. The primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat, while the additional bedrooms offer comfort and flexibility for family members or guests. The bathrooms feature designer fixtures and finishes and create a spa-like atmosphere. One of the standout features of this property is the finished private backyard - a rare gem in city living. This property boasts unparalleled ease of access to New York City, making your commute as breezy as a walk in the adjacent Riverview-Fisk Park. Whether you prefer the NJ Transit buses or the convenience of the 100 Steps to the 2nd Street Light Rail Station right at your doorstep, your connection to the city has never been smoother. The quality of construction is evident in every detail, ensuring that your investment will stand the test of time. 10 year home warranty included."
250009545,SOLD,"JC, Heights",221 LIBERTY AVE,Condominium,2085,1603,"$840,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,04601,00017,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$840,000","$849,000",$402.88,$402.88,5/14/2025,5/23/2025,7/16/2025,9,9,,7/16/2025,,,,$0,,$218,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Lake St & Carlton Ave,"Welcome to this stunning, new construction 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom condo that offers the spacious feel of a townhouse with modern design throughout its generous 2,085 square feet. This two-story home combines contemporary living with practical amenities in a fantastic Jersey City Heights location. The heart of this home features a gourmet kitchen with a show-stopping island that comfortably seats six, perfect for both everyday meals and entertaining. Samsung stainless steel appliances, a dedicated wine fridge, and custom cabinetry add both style and functionality to your culinary space. The primary bedroom offers a peaceful retreat complete with a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom. Step out onto your private balcony that spans across two bedrooms to enjoy spectacular sunset views after a long day. Two additional bedrooms provide comfortable space for family or guests. Outdoor living truly shines with a private fenced backyard—a rare find in urban living that creates your own personal sanctuary. The lower level boasts a massive recreation room with a half bath and is already prepared with plans for an additional kitchenette. Other notable features include a stylish built-in electric fireplace, custom lighting and thoughtful design touches throughout. Parking worries are eliminated with dedicated garage space for your vehicle. Located in a quiet neighborhood, you're just steps from the newly renovated Leonard Gordon Park, the Central Avenue shopping hub, and enjoy an easy commute to New York City via the Journal Square PATH train or direct bus service."
240018799,SOLD,"JC, Heights",116 HUTTON ST,Condominium,1700,5069,"$840,000",CONDO-COOP,,"1, 2",1,"JC, Heights",07307,3703,36,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$840,000","$840,000",$494.12,$494.12,9/23/2024,9/24/2024,10/25/2024,1,1,,10/25/2024,,,,"$13,482",24,$155,,Conventional,,,,,,Central and Summit,"Welcome to this stunning 3 bedroom/2.5 bath duplex condo with private backyard, offering the perfect blend of modern elegance and convenience. Nestled in a sought-after area of JC Heights just off Central Ave, this building underwent a full renovation less than 4 years ago! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a chic interior boasting impeccable attention to detail. The sunny and south facing living room exudes sophistication with stylish black and white marble flooring and accent wall, complemented by board-and-batten wall paneling that continues seamlessly up the staircase, adding a touch of timeless charm. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a chef's dream featuring waterfall quartz countertops, high end SS appliances, vented hood, pantry and coffee nook/bar with a built in wine fridge. The kitchen opens to a a dining area perfect for entertaining guests. Escape to the private oasis of the backyard easily accessed from the main level, complete with a mix of pavers and lush grass, offering the ideal setting for outdoor gatherings. This home is equipped with smart home technology throughout, allowing you to control lights, locks, thermostat, doorbell, and even the oven, all from the convenience of your phone. Enjoy privacy and comfort with top-down bottom-up cordless cellular blinds, allowing you to adjust natural light and maintain privacy with ease. All three bedrooms are generous in size and feature custom closets to accommodate all your storage needs. Retreat to the luxurious primary with walk-in custom closet and ensuite bathroom, boasting sleek finishes, dual floating vanity, makeup mirror, and linen closet, providing a spa-like experience right at home. With central A/C,  LED lighting, hardwood flooring, and  designated laundry closet with full size side by side washer and dryer, this duplex condo offers the epitome of modern living in a prime location. Parking is paid for by the seller for the first year!  Self managed HOA for low common charges! Easy access to NY transportation and close to so many amazing restaurants and shopping!  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite residence your own."
210004644,SOLD,"JC, Heights",118 CHARLES ST,Condominium,1518,6199,"$840,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02603,00039,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$840,000","$839,000",$553.36,$553.36,2/26/2021,3/5/2021,5/14/2021,7,7,,5/17/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & Kennedy,"Another Signature Luxury Condo by Blue Chip Living: Enjoy your privacy without giving up the perks of the city! Check out this brand new construction duplex that spares no expense in the heart of booming Jersey City. Open your private entry door to this captivating condo featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, modern open-concept living with a state of the art Chef’s Kitchen. This amazing unit also provides a private beautifully landscaped backyard and dedicated side by side garage parking. This unit features 10’ ceilings, 7’ solid-core doors and oversized Pella windows to flood the space with natural light and reduce noise transfer. Use the 1st Fl Den or one of the bedrooms as a dedicated office space without missing gourmet meals from your Chef’s kitchen. Fancy yourself to West Elm light fixtures, impeccable white high-gloss European Style cabinetry, stainless steel premium appliances and a Smart Home Refrigerator. The central island features a waterfall quartz countertop with a wine cooler and drawer microwave. The Master bedroom includes an en suite spa–like bathroom with rain showers, floating double vanity and an expansive walk–in closet. The master suite has 8‘ glass sliding doors leading out to a full width large balcony with picturesque views. Two generous bedrooms share a second bathroom featuring modern Cararra Porcelain slab tile, double vanity and soaking tub. Lower Level features a Family Room with a Powder room and Wet Bar to allow for easy entertainment. This Smart Home creates ease of living and efficiency through a central HVAC sys regulated by the Nest thermostat, Wi-Fi enabled lights, Smart doorbell, all integrated via a Smart home hub. This condo includes side by side (non tandem) private garage spot(s), which make for a commuters’ dream. The Property is located close to Congress St Light Rail, major highways, ferry, and PATH station. Make this your Dream Home Oasis today! *Eligible for 5 year tax abatement "
