220005170,SOLD,"JC, Heights",36 PATERSON ST,Condominium,1488,1724,"$842,500",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,01506,00038,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$842,500","$849,999",$566.20,$566.20,3/25/2022,5/2/2022,7/1/2022,38,38,,7/2/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Central & Passaic,"New construction luxury at it's finest. Welcome home to 36 Paterson St, the epitome of luxury and convenience. Travel though your bright and airy living room boasting high ceilings and 4” #1 red oak hardwood floors into your own chef's kitchen with a bevy of amenities. This sleek and modern kitchen is equipped with plentiful custom Fabuwood Nexus Kitchen cabinets, White Carrara Quartz countertops, vented hood and a full suite of high end stainless steel Samsung appliances. The master en-suite boasts high ceilings ,an oversized Porcelanosa bathroom, and a large custom closet, and This home features two other bedrooms and one and a half baths providing ample space for all your needs. Continue upstairs to your own private roof deck equipped with Sonos entertainment speakers perfect for entertaining family and friends. Recessed lights though out the entire condo, home entertainment wiring with 5.1 speakers,  Nest thermostat, and side by side garage parking completes the home. There are dedicated closets in the shared garage for extra storage. Just the pure luxury of this home will make it an enjoyable place to call home. Located minutes away fromWashington Park and less than a mile away from 9th street light rail.Should you want to travel to NYC this home is located just minutes away from the bus, light rail and all the transportation options making this the perfect address to call home."
240015344,SOLD,"JC, Heights",221 LIBERTY AVE,Condominium,2040,1639,"$845,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07306,04601,00017,,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$845,000","$869,000",$414.22,$414.22,8/6/2024,9/12/2024,11/1/2024,37,37,,11/6/2024,,,,"$10,617",2022,,,Conventional,,,,,,Lake st & Carlton Ave,"Welcome to 221 Liberty in the vibrant Jersey City Heights—a luxury condo offering an exceptional living experience on an oversized 29.17x138 lot. This brand-new, contemporary 4-bed, 2.5-bath home spans an impressive 2040 sq ft. Inside, you'll find a seamless open floor plan bathed in natural light from floor-to-ceiling windows. The expansive living room features a state-of-the-art Dimplex fireplace, perfect for cozy gatherings.  The gourmet kitchen is a highlight, with an extra-large island that seats up to 8, modern Samsung stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinetry. Bathrooms are designed as luxurious retreats with matte porcelain tiles, LED mirrors, and LED medicine cabinets.  The four spacious bedrooms offer versatile living options, including a potential home office. Two bedrooms open to a private balcony, while the master bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and an en-suite bath with elegant gray porcelain tiles and an LED anti-fog mirror.  Conveniently located just ten minutes from the JSQ Path Station and close to Central Avenue’s shops and dining, this condo offers a blend of luxury and practicality. Don’t miss the chance to make this exceptional property your new home!"
230001180,SOLD,"JC, Heights",118 BLEECKER ST,Condominium,1585,1419,"$845,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02101,00047,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$845,000","$849,000",$533.12,$533.12,1/20/2023,6/27/2023,8/29/2023,158,158,,8/30/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,South St & Paterson St,"Personalize the final touches on your brand new Home! Welcome to this spacious and sunlit new construction in the Jersey City Heights! This modern duplex is pre-designed for the latest in home technology and entertainment. Boasting wide plank solid hardwood floors throughout, 10ft ceiling, modern crown molding,  8ft custom doors in unit washer dryer, LED lighting, and private landscaped backyard! Pure white quartz counters with waterfall feature, custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and luxurious finishes provides an elevated ambiance in your home. This unit is comprised of 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, and also has an additional living room giving you ample space for entertainment and flexible living! Located in an unbeatable area of the Heights that is easily commutable and accessible to public transportation with direct bus lines to NYC Port Authority, Hoboken, and Downtown JC. The Hudson Light Rail Stations are also nearby as well as Pershing Field's indoor pool and ice skating rink being only a few blocks away. Riverview Park with its amazing views offers Farmers Market, movie nights, and neighborhood events! 1 car garage parking included! Call us for a private tour today."
240003613,SOLD,"JC, Heights",81 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1260,1713,"$845,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,4406,12,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$845,000","$849,000",$670.63,$670.63,2/27/2024,3/13/2024,4/24/2024,15,15,,4/29/2024,,,,$0,,$117,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton & Franklin,"Welcome to the epitome of modern urban living in Jersey City Heights! Unveiling a newly renovated 4-unit condo, this exquisite residence offers a seamless blend of sophistication and comfort. Nestled in the sought-after neighborhood, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom duplex boasts a private backyard, defining the perfect oasis in the heart of the vibrant community. Meticulously designed, the spacious living area unfolds seamlessly, merging the living, dining, and kitchen spaces into an inviting expanse, ideal for both entertainment and relaxation. Three generously sized bedrooms bathed in natural light, provide ample space for personalized style. Contemporary fixtures and elegant tile work adorn both bathrooms, with frameless shower doors adding a touch of modernity and creating a spa-like feel. The condo's clever use of space and thoughtfully crafted floor plan optimizes the expansive layout, ensuring every inch is functional and aesthetically pleasing. Step onto 4” Select Red Oak Hardwood Floors that span the unit, setting the stage for an elegant experience. The kitchen, a culinary haven, features Kraus kitchen sink & faucet, Jenn Air Appliances, and is graced with a peninsula and quartz countertops, embodying the perfect fusion of style and functionality. Solid core interior doors, extra-wide moldings & trims with crown molding throughout the house create an air of sophistication. The unit also features a dedicated backyard, low voltage with proficient brand speakers, custom closet designs, wall decor moldings, and claddings in the master bedroom. Located in the thriving Jersey City Heights neighborhood, renowned for its diverse community, shops, cafes, and cultural attractions, this residence offers easy access to transportation, making New York City just a breezy commute away. A shining example of luxury and convenience in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Welcome home!"
230008698,SOLD,"JC, Heights",89 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,1466,6199,"$845,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02702,00003,Heights,,,,,3,1,3,7,,"$845,000","$795,000",$576.40,$576.40,5/26/2023,6/20/2023,9/1/2023,25,25,,9/6/2023,,,,$0,,$125,2023,Cash,No,No,,,,Lincoln St. & Milton Ave.,"Brand New Unique Triplex Condo Townhouse, located in the heart of the highly desirable Jersey City Heights! Featuring 3 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, corner unit with an abundance of large windows drenched in natural sun light. Main living area with custom design metal railing, high ceilings with LED strip lighting make for a luxurious modern feel, sliding glass doors leading to balcony, contemporary fully equipped kitchen, with stainless steel appliances, high gloss white cabinetry, white quartz countertops and waterfall center island for additional storage, 3rd bedroom with a beautiful modern full bath and stand-up shower completes the floor. Lower-level flex room with private entrance, built-in wet bar, half bath perfect for family/living or home office, top floors main bedroom with sliding glass doors to a private balcony, wall to wall closet, generous 2nd bedroom, and 2 full baths, one with a tub and the other with a stand-up shower, bonus home office area. Hardwood floors, central A/C, washer and dryer room, private rooftop deck with adjacent wet bar and breathtaking views, a private backyard available for an additional fee. 1 private parking garage (not tandem) and plenty of storage. All major transportation at your fingertips, Close to all conveniences, parks, schools, library, restaurants, and more! Unpack and move in!"
210022330,SOLD,"JC, Heights",580 LIBERTY AVE,Condominium,3118,6199,"$845,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,00603,00012,Heights,,,,,4,0,4,10,,"$845,000","$859,000",$271.01,$271.01,9/24/2021,1/7/2022,3/28/2022,105,105,,3/29/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,North St and Leonard St,"Amazing opportunity to live in this brand new luxury 3118 sq. ft. 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath triplex located in the desirable Western Slope neighborhood in Jersey City Heights! Each gorgeous home features a sun drenched open concept floor plan, with a large living area, dining room and modern kitchen complete with quartz countertops and top-of-the-line Samsung appliances. You will fall in love with the large primary bedroom, complete with ensuite bath, enormous walk-in closet and private terrace that overlooks the tranquil backyard. There are two additional spacious bedrooms and a home office that is perfect for your private zoom meetings. Entertaining is a breeze in the large family room that leads to your gorgeous private backyard. Appointments include beautiful inlaid oak hardwood floors throughout, floor-to-ceiling Anderson windows, skylights, recessed LED lighting, high efficiency central heating and cooling and hookup for washer and dryer. Storage and space abound both inside and out of these well-designed homes. Garage parking for two cars. Buyers are eligible for 5-year tax abatement. 10 year limited home warranty provided by the developer. Close to Gordon Park with 5.7 acres, sports facilities, playground and dog run. 580 Liberty offers an easy commute to Port Authority, Penn Station, or downtown World Trade Center/ Financial district.  "
220021747,SOLD,"JC, Heights",58 GARRISON AVE,Condominium,2388,6199,"$848,888",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07306,,,,,,,,4,2,2,7,,"$848,888","$829,000",$355.48,$355.48,12/21/2022,12/30/2022,2/22/2023,9,9,,2/23/2023,,,,$0,,$125,,Conventional,,,,,,SIP & PAVONIA,"Open the door into this luxurious, newly restored 4 bedroom 2 full bath, 2 half-bath duplex unit gleaming with natural light and a huge, unique open concept layout designed by Blue Chip Living. This modern farmhouse style home is located within walking distance to Journal Square! Main floor features an oversized Living room with wall-to-wall bay windows and a sliding door which provides access to the patio bringing you to the great outdoors. This home features a dining area accented by an electric linear LED fireplace which flows into the beautiful chef’s kitchen with two tone shaker cabinets, pot filler, pantry closet, smart stainless-steel appliances, and a spacious waterfall quartz center island. Main level features the spacious main bedroom with a barn door walk-in closet and ensuite bath featuring spa like features and impeccable gold detail. An additional bedroom with a full bath and laundry room completes the main level. Additional main bedroom located upstairs with en suite half bath, barn door walk in closet along with another bedroom and stunning half bathroom. Upstairs also has a flex family entertaining room with cathedral ceilings complete with a reading nook. Other key features in this stunning home are hardwood floors throughout, an in-unit laundry hook up, and a paver patio to the backyard. Full smart home technology creates ease of living complete with Ring doorbell, Nest thermostat, Lighting Dimmer Switches accessible via smart phone. One car shared parking is included. All major transportation at your fingertips Close to all conveniences, major highways, minutes to Journal Square PATH terminal for a quick commute to NYC. Make this your Dream Home today! Property is Community Loan Eligible! Special LOW RATES in 5% RANGE, CONV With 5% Down Payment NO PMI AND BANK FEES. Eligible for 5 year tax abatement."
260005122,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",183 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1241,1750,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307-1111,3304,31,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,8,,,"$849,000",$684.13,,3/24/2026,,,16,,,3/24/2026,,,,,,$75,2026,,No,No,Yes,,,Liberty and Terrace,"Brand new from the ground up and distinguished by an extraordinary private backyard rarely found in Jersey City Heights, Unit 1 at 183 Zabriskie Street offers a standout blend of modern design, comfort, and indoor-outdoor living. This beautifully finished spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence spans approximately 1,241 square feet and showcases a bright open layout, oversized windows, wide-plank flooring, and a sleek contemporary kitchen with stylish cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, generous workspace, a dedicated wine bar area for added sophistication, and the everyday convenience of an in-unit washer/dryer and dishwasher. The bedrooms are well proportioned, the bathrooms are finished in a clean spa-like style, and custom storage adds functionality throughout. What truly sets this home apart, is the outdoor experience: a substantial, fully fenced private backyard with a manicured lawn, landscaped border, and dedicated patio area that creates a true extension of the living space—ideal for dining, lounging, entertaining, or simply enjoying a rare sense of privacy and greenery in the city. Set within a newly built boutique property close to transportation, parks, shops, and neighborhood favorites, this is Jersey City Heights living with a level of outdoor space and new-construction quality that is seldom available."
230000126,SOLD,"JC, Heights",71 RESERVOIR AVE,Condominium,1389,1597,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,3 & R,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$849,000","$849,000",$611.23,$611.23,1/4/2023,1/23/2023,3/17/2023,19,19,,3/17/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Lienau & Baldwin,"Brand new construction beckons with this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home including full private roof deck and EV charger garage parking in Jersey City Heights. Oversized windows illuminate the timeless style with red oak hardwood floors and crown molding, plus modern upgrades and smart home capabilities.  Spacious eat-in kitchen gleams with large island, white quartz counters and shaker cabinets, herringbone backsplash, stainless farm sink and appliances, including a coveted wine fridge. Head upstairs to the full-floor private roof deck with breathtaking 360 degree views including downtown NYC and surrounding parks. Shared garage parking with must-have EV charging ports adds the proverbial cherry on top.  Spacious bedrooms showcase plenty of natural light, with ample storage including a built-out walk-in ensuite closet. Beautifully finished bathrooms include floor to ceiling tile, including accent walls, glass showers, and vanities plus medicine cabinets for added convenience.  Settled on a tree-lined street just off Pershing Field Park and Reservoir, this home is perfectly poised for access to extended outdoor space, and key points of urban living. Easily access Central Avenue with surrounding shops and boutiques, 2nd Street Light Rail Station, and easy NYC access."
260003125,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",134 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1286,1597,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,4,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$849,000",$660.19,,2/23/2026,,,45,,,2/23/2026,,,,,,$351,,,,,,,,Franklin & Ferry,"Designed for both serenity and sophistication, this elevated home offers modern finishes, tree-top views and an unbeatable Heights location just 1 block to 2nd Street stairs and Lightrail station. A hidden haven in the Heights, this beautifully crafted 3 bed, 2 bath residence blends bespoke finishes with gorgeous private rooftop-shared with unit 3- for a rare retreat.   Wide plank floors ground the space, while natural light floods through the floor-to-ceiling windows illuminating the open floorplan. The kitchen offers clean lines and contemporary flair with modern white & blue cabinetry, gleaming quartz countertops, herringbone tile backsplash, sleek brass-accented fixtures and stainless steel appliances.  Both bathrooms are beautifully finished with floor-to-ceiling porcelain tile, herringbone floors, and luxurious rainhead multi-spray shower systems and soaking tub. One bedroom is shielded with privacy glass giving both sunshine and seclusion, while the primary ensuite showcases a full wall of glass for a gorgeous view & lots of natural light. Top it off with a brand new stacking LG washer and dryer for everyday ease and convenience.  Situated just one block from the 2nd Street Light Rail station, this home not only provides direct access to Hoboken and NYC connections, but also Riverview Fisk and Pershing Field Park and Reservoir. Jersey City Heights is known for its vibrant community, excellent parks and schools, boutique shops and restaurants and close proximity to NYC and surrounding areas."
260003003,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",146 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1310,1713,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2904,40,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,,"$849,000",$648.09,,2/20/2026,,,48,,,2/20/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Griffith St and Bowers St,"Welcome to 146 Sherman Avenue, Unit 2, a beautifully appointed 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo in the heart of Jersey City Heights.  This bright and spacious home features an open layout ideal for modern living and entertaining. The primary suite offers a private balcony — perfect for morning coffee or unwinding at the end of the day — while two additional bedrooms provide flexibility for guests, a home office, or a growing family.  Ideally located just moments from the vibrant shops and restaurants along Central Avenue and Palisade Avenue, and near the scenic Palisade cliffs and Washington Park, this home offers both convenience and charm. Commuters will love the easy access to NYC via nearby bus routes and light rail options.  A perfect blend of space, location, and lifestyle."
240016184,SOLD,"JC, Heights",988 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,2510,6706,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,1/2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2802,4,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$849,000","$849,000",$338.25,$338.25,8/16/2024,8/22/2024,10/17/2024,6,6,,10/23/2024,,"$440,900",2023,"$9,907",2023,$311,2024,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Bowers St and Lincolin St,"Welcome to 988 Summit Avenue, unit 1, a duplex style home boasting 2500 sqft of living space. This unit provides ample space throughout both floors. Floor 1 welcomes you into an open layout where the living room, dining room, and kitchen all meet. Enjoy an open floorplan along with a chef grade kitchen, shaker cabinets that are two-toned stacked to the ceiling, quartz counter tops, and waterfall design on each side of your floating island. The appliances are Samsung stainless steel with smart fridge and smart gas stove. This floor also has a half bathroom for the comfort of your guest. Entertain in the additional back room while hosting your guests or utilize it as a bedroom which walks out your private backyard. Floor 2 of this duplex home is breath taking. Every bedroom on the second floor contains a walk-in closet, with oversized guest bedrooms. Hidden in this the second floor is a grandeur master bedroom with a massive HIS/HER walk-in closet, and a chic master bathroom. This bathroom is styled with a floating tub and its own stand-up shower. Visualize floor to ceiling ceramic tile design along with a double vanity sink. Natural sunlight flows through the entire two floors of this unit. Features include Hardwood floors, custom trim, recess lighting, chic designer tiles throughout, coat closet, pantry closet, in unit laundry, and modern fixtures. Steps away from Pershing Field Park, amazing restaurants on Central Ave, close to NYC transportation, new upcoming reservoir where you can enjoy water activities. Schedule a tour today! "
240003716,SOLD,"JC, Heights",102 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1577,1603,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,,"JC, Heights",07307,00029,03404,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$849,000","$849,000",$538.36,$538.36,2/28/2024,3/8/2024,4/11/2024,9,9,,4/11/2024,,,,"$9,669",,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & JFK,"Ready to enjoy Spring in The Heights. Welcome home to 102 Zabriskie. Constructed in 2019, this top floor unit features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a private roof deck, and 1 car parking. The open concept living space boasts beautiful Wainscoting, high ceilings, large windows, and an electric fireplace. 5-inch cherry hardwood floors and custom crown-molding run throughout. The kitchen is home to stainless steel appliances, including a built-in microwave and refrigerator with a wine-fridge conversion, white quartz countertops, a farmhouse sink, and a Chef's hood. The island features a waterfall countertop and allows for extra seating and easy entertaining. The primary bedroom is home to a walk-in California Closet, en-suite with spa jets, and a private terrace, perfect for enjoying a morning coffee or a glass of wine. Two additional bedrooms boast custom closets and large windows, ideal for offices, guest rooms, or nurseries. Up the stairs you’ll find the expansive private roof deck with a beautiful pergola for shade on those hot summer days. Additional features include: private entrance, SOUNDPROOFING, color-changing lights, BONUS storage in the garage (2 closets), Ecobee smart thermostat, tankless hot water heater, recessed lighting, custom multi-operational shower heads, and more. Situated near Leonard Gordon and Manhattan Parks, you’ll have easy access to JFK and Summit Avenue bus routes. The Riverview Farmers Market and Jazz Festival kick off in May. Enjoy coffee and pastries at Dulce de Leche and become regulars at The Hutton and Ozu Foods. Come experience all the Heights has to offer. Welcome home!"
260004233,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",84 NELSON AVE,Condominium,1500,1623,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,0,3,8,,,"$849,000",$566.00,,3/11/2026,,,29,,,3/11/2026,,,,"$13,340",2025,,,,,,,,,North & Irving,"Welcome to 84 Nelson Ave, Unit 1, a beautifully designed 3-bedroom, 3-bath duplex condo built in 2023 that combines modern finishes, generous space, and exceptional natural light. From the moment you enter, the home feels bright and open thanks to soaring 10-foot ceilings and a dramatic picture-frame window at the front of the home that floods the living space with natural light and captures beautiful west-facing sunset views.  The main living level flows seamlessly between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting space that is equally suited for everyday living or entertaining guests. Upstairs, the primary suite offers a private retreat complete with a spacious walk-in closet, an elegant ensuite bathroom, and a private balcony—perfect for enjoying morning coffee or unwinding in the evening.  The lower level adds incredible flexibility to the home, offering a spacious bonus area finished with a wet bar and wine fridge along with a full bathroom, making it ideal for a media room, guest suite, home office, or additional living space.  Outdoor living is just as impressive, with a private backyard that has been fully upgraded with premium turf and low-voltage lighting, creating a beautiful, low-maintenance setting for relaxing or entertaining. The home also includes the rare convenience of non-tandem garage parking, central air, and in-unit laundry, adding everyday comfort to its modern design.  As an added benefit, the property qualifies for a First Time Homebuyer Program which is anyone who has not owned a home in the last 3 years. Minimum 5% down payment required. 30 yr fix  5.125 with 0 points, no PMI required if putting less than 20% down, bank fee waived. making this an exceptional opportunity for buyers seeking both value and lifestyle in a nearly new construction home."
260005868,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",146 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1310,1713,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2904,40,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,,"$849,000",$648.09,,4/2/2026,,,7,,,4/2/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Griffith St and Bowers St,"Step inside to an open-concept layout featuring generous natural light, hardwood floors, and a seamless flow perfect for both entertaining and everyday comfort. The contemporary kitchen is equipped with sleek cabinetry, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances, ideal for home chefs and hosting. Throughout the home, thoughtfully designed closet buildouts provide exceptional storage and organization, adding both functionality and style.  The spacious primary suite includes a stylish en-suite bathroom with premium finishes, while two additional well-proportioned bedrooms provide flexibility for guest space, a home office, or a growing household. Both bathrooms are tastefully appointed with modern tilework and high-quality fixtures.  The true highlight of this home is the private outdoor space—perfect for morning coffee, gardening, or al fresco dining. Whether you’re unwinding or entertaining, it’s a coveted extension of your living space.  Located just moments from Central Avenue shops, restaurants, parks, and transportation to NYC, this condo offers the perfect blend of convenience and comfort in one of the Heights’ most desirable neighborhoods. Don’t miss this opportunity to own a move-in-ready home with outdoor space in Jersey City Heights. Nearby parking is available for an additional fee."
220020878,SOLD,"JC, Heights",39 MONTROSE AVE,Condominium,1772,1419,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,04307,00020,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$849,000","$849,000",$479.12,$479.12,12/1/2022,1/4/2023,3/17/2023,34,34,,3/31/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Carlton Ave. & Beach St.,"Spacious and sunlit new construction makes its way to the Jersey City Heights! This modern duplex is pre-designed for the latest in home technology and entertainment. Boasting hardwood floors throughout, 8ft custom doors, high ceiling, crown molding, in unit washer dryer, LED lighting, and private backyard space! Pure white quartz counters with waterfall feature, custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and luxurious finishes provides an elevated ambiance in your home. This unit is comprised of 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, and also has an additional living room giving you ample space for entertainment and flexible living! Located in an unbeatable area of the Heights that is easily commutable and accessible to public transportation with direct bus lines to NYC Port Authority, Hoboken, and Downtown JC. The Hudson Light Rail Stations are also nearby as well as Pershing Field's indoor pool and ice skating rink being only a few blocks away. Riverview Park with its amazing views offers Farmers Market, movie nights, and neighborhood events! 1 car garage parking included! Call us for a private tour today, building is projected to be finished January 2023, 2 units available, unit #2 has a private roof deck."
260004350,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",22 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,1500,1750,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,,"$849,000",$566.00,,3/13/2026,,,27,,,3/12/2026,,,,"$14,280",,,,,,,,,,Central and Summit,"Welcome to this standout home in Jersey City Heights. This beautifully renovated 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath duplex condominium offers refined living with a private backyard and finished basement, all set on a quiet, tree-lined street just off Central Avenue.  Inside, the home is filled with thoughtful upgrades, including a custom built-in banquette in the living room—a true showpiece that adds both style and function. Wide-plank flooring runs throughout the home, complemented by central air and in-unit laundry for everyday comfort and convenience.  The modern kitchen makes a striking impression with custom blue/gray lower cabinetry, crisp white uppers, and elegant marbled quartz countertops. Both bathrooms are beautifully appointed with contemporary finishes such as floating custom vanities, pocket doors, oversized slab tile, and a sophisticated mix of brass and black fixtures. The spacious primary suite features two closets and a private balcony, perfect for morning coffee or unwinding in the evening. Outside, the hardscaped backyard provides a low-maintenance outdoor retreat ideal for entertaining, grilling, or simply relaxing. The finished basement offers flexible bonus space that can easily serve as a playroom, home gym, guest area, or office. The half bath is already equipped with plumbing lines for a future shower or tub, providing additional potential.  Located on a tree lined street and within walking distance of Central and Palisade Avenues for shopping, dining, and everyday essentials. Enjoy everything the Heights has to offer—excellent schools, award-winning restaurants, vibrant local businesses, and easy access to NYC. "
210002159,SOLD,"JC, Heights",65 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1146,6199,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03802,00007,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$849,000","$819,000",$740.84,$740.84,1/25/2021,2/22/2021,4/23/2021,28,28,,4/26/2021,,,,,,$225,2021,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"Featuring Another Signature Luxury brand new Construction by Blue Chip Living from the pages of Architectural Digest to the heart of booming Jersey City Heights , a business district, residential area, and transportation hub. Open your private entry door to this captivating condo featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a loft style open concept living space with cathedral ceilings, designer metal railings with exposed wood beam and oversized Pella windows and skylights that flood the space with natural light. The chef’s kitchen boasts impeccable white high-gloss European Style cabinetry, stainless steel premium appliances, modern porcelain backsplash, central island with a waterfall quartz, pendant lighting and drawer microwave with Ambient LED under-mounted lighting. The Master bedroom includes an en suite spa–like bathroom with matte black handware, floating vanity, an expansive walk–in closet and 8‘ x 8’ full glass sliding doors leading to your picturesque balcony. Two generous bedrooms share a second bathroom featuring modern Carrara Porcelain tile, floating vanity and soaking tub. Other perks include West Elm lighting, laundry room hook ups, central/heat/air, 7’ solid-core doors, private roof deck with NYC views and 1 tandem garage parking. Full smart technology home creates ease of living with Google Nest thermostat, August Smart Lock, Google Nest Doorbell, Google, Lutron Caseta Wireless Smart Lighting Dimmer Switch, My Q Smart Garage door with Amazon Key, all integrated via a Google Nest Hub all in one display accessible via smart phones. The Property is located close to Congress St Light Rail, major highways, ferry, and PATH station. Make this your Dream Home Oasis today! *Eligible for 5 year tax abatement."
