210001373,SOLD,"JC, Heights",433 LIBERTY AVE,Condominium,2100,298,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,L12,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02503,00030,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,14,,"$849,000","$879,000",$404.29,$404.29,1/15/2021,4/19/2021,6/17/2021,93,93,,6/18/2021,,,,$0,,$0,,Conventional,No,No,,,,btw Thorne & Lincoln,"Welcome to 433 Liberty Avenue – a rare offering of an oversized triplex! This newly constructed 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home with an additional family room is ideally located in the Western Slope neighborhood of Jersey City Heights. Fall in love with the thoughtfully crafted floor-through plan and stunning attention to detail. The main level features a boutique-style kitchen complete with quartz waterfall countertops and top-of-the-line Samsung appliances. Floor-to-ceiling window/doors open to a Juliet balcony. The open concept living space boasts custom trim and crown molding throughout. Here you will also find a custom-built, glass-encased wine cellar, capable of showcasing 200+ bottles. The main level continues to include 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a laundry room, and a full-length balcony extending off the master bedroom. Stairs lead down, opening into a 2nd family room with an additional full-length balcony, offering exceptional views. This level also features a designer half bathroom and garage access. A second lower level offers a bonus living area/bedroom and excess storage space. Glass doors open into a paved private backyard enclosed with dramatic, custom-built fencing and fully equipped with water, electric and entertainment hook-ups. Other design features include custom built-out closets, large format imported porcelain tile, Red Oak hardwood flooring, distinctive lighting, and modern finishings throughout. Unit 1 offers 2000 sq ft of living space, in addition to a private walk-out terrace/backyard, an oversized garage, and full-length balconies off the master bedroom and 2nd family room. More features include high efficiency HVAC system, security/ entertainment system, central vac system and much more! Additionally, buyers can look forward to winning with Jersey City’s 5-year “new construction” tax abatement; manufacture warranties, as well as a 10 year limited home warranty provided by the developer. Call or text the listing agent to schedule a tour. "
240000580,SOLD,"JC, Heights",27 LEONARD ST,Condominium,1325,1623,"$849,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,00504,00012,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$849,000","$849,000",$640.75,$640.75,1/10/2024,2/13/2024,4/10/2024,34,34,,4/10/2024,,,,,,$250,,Miscellaneous,,,,,,Central & Summit,"Experience luxury in this expansive condominium located in the highly coveted Jersey City Heights. This recently constructed 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo boasts non-tandem parking, a private rooftop deck with outdoor kitchen including gas, hot and cold water hookups, Trex decking and NYC views. The chef's kitchen, equipped with top-of-the-line Bertazzoni appliances, features quartz countertops, a Moen faucet with a waterfall design, European-style frameless cabinets, and 4 solid hardwood flooring. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen to the bright and spacious living room, creating an ideal setting for entertaining. Luxurious updates in the bathrooms include frameless shower doors, rain shower heads, and a double sink vanity. Modern design elements are present throughout the unit, which also offers energy-efficient full spray foam insulation, a separate private entrance and garage storage. Additional amenities include a central vacuum system, Andersen windows, Rheem HVAC, and sound-dampening rubber membrane between floors for enhanced sound insulation. Seize the opportunity to own this exceptional unit that combines style, functionality, and comfort."
