220000022,SOLD,"JC, Heights",25 WAVERLY ST,Condominium,1349,1691,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07306,,,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$850,000","$875,000",$630.10,$630.10,1/2/2022,1/27/2022,5/13/2022,25,25,,5/25/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Baldwin and Palisade,"Make yourself at home in this modern masterpiece. The newly finished luxury condo offers flowing three bedroom layout, plus coveted garage parking and private outdoor in Jersey City Heights.  Sunlight streams through oversized windows to showcase sophisticated style like matte black trim, fresh white oak hardwood floors and crown molding throughout. Contemporary eat-in kitchen offers sleek custom cabinets, waterfall quartz counters with seamless backsplash transition, plus stainless appliances and brushed nickel fixtures.  Primary en-suite features double glass doors leading to private terrace. Beautifully designed bathroom features double vanity with smart mirrors, and glass shower with multihead system. Follow the gorgeous glass staircase upstairs to the full floor private rooftop, fully finished with amazing NYC, Hoboken and downtown Jersey City views.  Add to this the ultimate must-have of garage parking, and this home offers the best of urban luxury. Settled on a tree-lined street in a quiet corner of The Heights, owners enjoy walkability to nearby parks, community, boutiques, schools and NYC access."
