220010913,SOLD,"JC, Heights",67 THORNE ST,Condominium,1600,1653,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02705,00014,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$850,000","$860,000",$531.25,$531.25,6/14/2022,6/24/2022,7/29/2022,10,10,,8/10/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Summet & Kennedy Blvd,"Location location location! Steps away from Central Ave Shopping District, 67 Thorne St redefines luxury condos. This ground up new construction offers 2 units with impeccable finishes, parking space, and private outdoor space. This duplex unit offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a bonus living area with powder room leading to a private size backyard. Features include Hardwood floors, custom trim, large spacious kitchen with Samsung stainless steel appliances and smart fridge, a wine fridge, quartz countertop, beautiful coffered ceilings in your living room plus an electric fireplace. Lots of closet space throughout with custom shelving, in unit laundry, and modern fixtures. Master bedroom offers a sliding door to walkout to your private balcony, a large walk-in closet, and a master bathroom with spa shower panel. Steps away from Washington Park, amazing restaurants on Central Ave, close to NYC transportation. Schedule a tour today!"
220008778,SOLD,"JC, Heights",124 IRVING ST,Condominium,1795,6139,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,703,57,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$850,000","$899,000",$473.54,$473.54,5/16/2022,8/12/2022,9/27/2022,64,64,,9/28/2022,,,,"$9,200",2022,,,Conventional,,,,,,NELSON & KENNEDY BLVD,"Back in the market!  TWO CAR GARAGE WITH PRIVET ENTRANCE. A MUST SEE!!! Welcome to 124 Irvins St unit 1.  New Construction Luxury 3 Bed 2.5 Bath Duplex  condo built with the highest standard of quality of living with your comfort in mind.  Your PETS would love playing while you are enjoying your BBQ in your privet backyard.   This duplex offers 1800 sqft of living space. WIDE Living Room & Dining Room with speakers, wine cooler, and cable ready for your enjoyment.   Premium SELET Red Oak Hardwood floors. Modern High Ceiling Kitchen Cabinets with extra storage. Smart Appliances and much more.   Live in one of the best locations in JC Heights only steps to public transportation.   Only one unit left on first floor! One parking per unit.  Not a tandem parking."
210009409,SOLD,"JC, Heights",415 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1300,6078,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02402,00021,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$850,000","$899,000",$653.85,$653.85,4/21/2021,5/27/2021,7/11/2021,36,36,,8/3/2021,,,,"$8,378",2020,$200,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress & South,"This gorgeous home has everything you're looking for and is located on the best street in town!    Oversized picture window as well as dual skylights equipped with custom Hunter blinds in the wide open layout floor plan floods your living space with natural light. The incredible kitchen features subway tile backsplash, farmhouse kitchen sink, marble countertops and stainless steel appliances including a wine fridge. Other incredible modern finishes in this home are upgraded lighting fixtures throughout, heated tiles in the bathroom floors and customized closets. Private storage closet in the garage and in-unit washer dryer. Looking for outdoor space? Master bedroom has a private terrace AND this unit comes with your own private roof deck with city views, plenty of space for grill and furniture sets, ideal for entertaining or relaxing on your own. This home is around the corner from the Lightrail, Hoboken, and only one block from NJ transit bus to Manhattan. Everything you need in the perfect spot of Jersey City Heights!"
260006236,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",50 COLUMBIA AVE,Condominium,1731,1702,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02602,00036,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,,"$850,000",$491.05,,4/8/2026,,,1,,,4/8/2026,,,,"$13,776",25,$0,,,,,,,,Lincoln & Thorne,"Welcome to 50 Columbia Ave, Jersey City – a stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom contemporary duplex condo offering 1,731 square feet of beautifully designed living space. Built in 2019, this home seamlessly blends modern sophistication with comfort, featuring hardwood floors, abundant storage throughout, recessed lighting, over 600 sq ft of private outdoor space.  The thoughtfully designed chef’s kitchen is a true centerpiece, complete with a spacious breakfast bar, Frigidaire Gallery stainless steel appliances, gas oven and stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, wine fridge and a convenient pantry. The renovated baths, including the primary ensuite, showcase sleek finishes and elegant touches. A cozy fireplace adds warmth and charm to the living space, while custom California closets in the bedrooms and customized built-ins in the foyer provide ample storage for effortless organization.  The home also boasts a flexible bonus room on the lower level ideal for a home gym, media room or guest bedroom with its own half bath. Enjoy the private backyard and garden – ideal for outdoor relaxation, dining al-fresco under the cedar pergola, or flexing your green thumb gardening. Parking is effortless with a covered garage space.  Year-round comfort is ensured with central AC and forced air heating, and the in-unit washer and dryer adds everyday convenience.   Located in a vibrant and thriving neighborhood, this move-in-ready home offers the perfect balance of modern living and outdoor retreat.   Located close to Washington Park, Pershing Field Park, and Leonard Park, the friendly neighborhood is home to many eclectic shops, cafes and markets. Only 1 block to JFK Blvd buses to NYC or Journal Square PATH and NJ Transit hub. Easy access to RT 1/9, Lincoln and Holland Tunnels, as well as the NJ Turnpike. Don’t miss this rare opportunity to make this exceptional condo your own!"
250004189,SOLD,"JC, Heights",376 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,2100,1623,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,2,1,2,6,,"$850,000","$850,000",$404.76,$404.76,3/5/2025,3/11/2025,6/27/2025,6,6,,7/9/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Ogden Ave & New York Ave,"Experience luxury living in this sun-drenched, spacious 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom apartment! This stunning unit boasts high cathedral ceilings, a skylight, and smart light switches throughout, seamlessly blending modern finishes with convenience.    Designed for privacy, both bedrooms are located on the same floor, separate from the main living areas, and each features a full en-suite bath and a walk-in closet for ultimate comfort and storage. The gourmet kitchen is equipped with quartz countertops, a double oven, and a dishwasher, while the in-unit washer and dryer add everyday ease.    Step outside to your private Trex roof deck, complete with a BBQ gas line and outdoor water faucet—perfect for entertaining!    Commuting is seamless with a 7-minute walk to the 2nd Street Light Rail Station, offering a quick 4-minute ride to the Hoboken PATH. A bus stop on the corner provides a direct route to Port Authority.    Enjoy the best of city living with shops, parks, and top-rated restaurants just a short walk away! Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity!"
210000129,SOLD,"JC, Heights",142 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1619,1707,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02904,00038,,,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$850,000","$825,000",$525.02,$525.02,1/4/2021,1/19/2021,3/22/2021,15,15,,3/24/2021,,,,,,$237,,Conventional,,,,,,*,"New Construction in a spectacular tree lined location.  This amazing high quality 3 bed, 2 bath condo features 1619 square foot of living space with deeded 2 car parking and private 1200 square foot of roof deck (gas-water-electric connections), kitchen containing quartz counter tops with waterfall island and Samsung black stainless steel appliances, wine fridge, Kohler plumbing fixtures, custom closets, high end finishes including crown moldings, central vacuum system, sprinkler system thru the entire home, aluminum railings, low voltage system (security camera, burglar alarm, video door bell, 5.1 channel home theater), elevated framing materials used for improved insulation and sound proof penetration and much more! *10 years builders warranty & 5 year tax abatement included. Very close to NY transportation (bus & rail), shopping, restaurants, parks, schools and much more! Will not last....come take a look!"
230001435,SOLD,"JC, Heights",277 COLUMBIA AVE,Condominium,2605,6706,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,603,00039 01,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$850,000","$899,000",$326.30,$326.30,1/25/2023,3/13/2023,4/11/2023,47,47,,4/13/2023,,,,$0,2022,$304,,FHA,,,,,,Leonard St and North St,"Brand New Construction triplex condo in prime Western Slope Section of Jersey City Heights. with 3 beds, 2.5 bath approx. 2605 square ft of living space. Featuring a Hardwood flooring, white modern kitchen, quartz counter tops with waterfall island and Samsung black stainless-steel appliances, wine fridge, Kohler plumbing fixtures, custom closets, high end finishes including crown moldings, aluminum railings, low voltage system, burglar alarm, video doorbell, 5.1 channel home theater, 1 indoor garage parking and private backyard. Also includes a 10 year's builder's warranty & 5 years tax abatement. Located just 2 blocks from JFK Blvd with buses to NYC withing 30 mins or toward Journal Path Station in 10 mins, 2 blocks from route 1/9 with easy access to both Lincoln and Holland Tunnels, all major highways such as route 3, 495, 95 and 80. Close to schools, parks and shopping."
210025040,SOLD,"JC, Heights",17 WAVERLY ST,Condominium,1617,1597,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07306,05803,00014,,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$850,000","$899,000",$525.66,$525.66,11/4/2021,12/6/2021,1/26/2022,32,32,,2/1/2022,,,,,,$193,,Conventional,,,,,,Palisade and Baldwin,"Fantastically located just off Palisade Avenue and a few blocks to Journal Square PATH Station, this newly converted Three Bedroom condominium has been designed and executed with the highest-quality materials and appliances. Influenced by the Scandinavian design tradition, the voluminous residence is furnished with wide plank light oak floors and abundant windows in every room creating bright and airy living spaces. The spectacular duplex home features two gorgeous bathrooms, a powder room, and a roof terrace with stunning views of the New York City skyline in all directions. The primary bedroom suite includes an en-suite bathroom, generous closets, and a romantic, South-facing balcony. The thoughtfully designed kitchen is adorned with Quartz countertops, custom cabinetry and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. The brand-new residence is further equipped with Central AC & Heat and washer & dryer. Enjoy an elevated standard of living in one of the most desirable neighborhoods in Jersey City!"
210002688,SOLD,"JC, Heights",101 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,,1691,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3803,11,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$850,000","$850,000",,,2/1/2021,2/9/2021,9/8/2021,8,8,,9/8/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith & Hutton,"One of Jersey City's finest builders is at it again! With an estimate completion of Summer 2021, these two new construction condominiums will quarrel over nothing except which wide open layout offers the best flow, and whose oversized outdoor space should host the next summer barbecue. This top floor 3 bed 2 bath home will be beautifully finished with absolute thoughtfulness and top-notch quality. Main floor living and dining area layout flows into chef-inspired kitchens finished with white marble waterfall island, inlay farm sink, Fabuwood cabinets, Samsung stainless steel appliances, must-have wine fridge, kohler fixtures and modern pendant lighting. Master suite and additional bedrooms boast ceiling fans, Pella windows, and custom walk-in closets, while bathrooms host high-end porcelain tiles, modern vanities and multiple shower heads. You'll be able hear a pin drop in this ultra-peaceful atmosphere, thanks to the extra-thick soundproofing, subfloor and insulation. A tech-lovers dream with every mod con, finishes include home entertainment wiring with 5.1 speakers, Ring doorbell, camera and security system, central vacuum and Nest thermostat. This top unit’s brag-worthy expansive roof deck with speakers, gas & water for ultimate entertaining (or your own private dance party) shows incredible NYC views! Steps from Riverview Fisk and Washington parks - as well as both 2nd St & 9th St Light Rail stations - this neighborhood is known for great schools and easy NYC access, all amid the eclectic and vibrant scene of Jersey City Heights. *Photos are of similar listing, different location*"
240019814,SOLD,"JC, Heights",193 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1822,298,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02203,00038,Heights,,,,,2,1,2,6,,"$850,000","$850,000",$466.52,$466.52,10/8/2024,10/15/2024,12/16/2024,7,7,,12/17/2024,,,,"$16,725",2024,$220,,Conventional,,,,,,South & Congress St,"Welcome home to 193 Hancock Ave! An incredible 1821 sqft duplex condo with very close proximity to the Congress St light rail and the highly rated PS 28 Christa McAuliffe school! Enter through your own separate entrance, upgraded with ProVia doors, into an open and modern space perfect for entertaining! The huge living room features coffered ceilings, handmade wainscotting, and crown molding. You will find abundant closet space, a half bath and a full size samsung washer/dryer. The open concept kitchen boasts a large marble double waterfall island with matching countertops, tastefully upgraded backsplash, under counter lighting, a pantry, high end appliances and vented hood. Additionally, the home is set up with an aquapure water filtration and softener system. Featuring two very large bedrooms with enough room to potentially create a 3rd bedroom, and spa-like en-suite bathrooms! The first floor bedroom leads out to a stunningly gorgeous updated backyard with patio, split levels, sprinkler system, hardwired lights and speaker jacks! Perfect for entertaining and pets. This home is truly ready for you with Anderson windows and sliders throughout, custom closet built-ins, simpli safe security camera, 3 zone split unit ac/heat and ethernet wired for your home office needs in the living room and 1st floor bedroom. Upstairs, the bedroom has its own outdoor space with a terrace overlooking your beautiful backyard. This location is amazing with abundant street parking, surrounded by restaurants, bars, cafes and some of JC Heights best businesses! You can enjoy Washington Park and Riverview Park nearby. Come and see this amazing home for yourself"
240021398,SOLD,"JC, Heights",337 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1400,1603,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,4,"JC, Heights",07307,4504,31,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$850,000","$899,000",$607.14,$607.14,10/31/2024,12/2/2024,1/22/2025,32,32,,1/22/2025,,,,$0,,$292,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Ferry St and Franklin St,"Welcome to your dream home in the best location in Jersey City Heights! This top floor, new construction, two-story home offers the perfect blend of modern luxury with the benefits of city convenience. Step inside and fall in love with light hardwood floors, high ceilings and private terrace off the living space creating an airy, open atmosphere throughout the home. Chef's kitchen complete with custom cabinetry with ample storage, a massive breakfast island, stainless steel appliances and a panel-ready dishwasher that seamlessly blends with the sleek design. Whip up your culinary masterpieces while entertaining guests in style! The primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat, while the additional bedrooms offer comfort and flexibility for family members or guests. The bathrooms feature designer fixtures and finishes and create a spa-like atmosphere. The best part? A massive two-sided private rooftop with NYC views, wet bar, gas and water lines makes this the best space to host gatherings or simply relax.  This property boasts unparalleled ease of access to New York City, making your commute as breezy as a walk in the adjacent Riverview-Fisk Park. Whether you prefer the NJ Transit buses or the convenience of the 100 Steps to the 2nd Street Light Rail Station right at your doorstep, your connection to the city has never been smoother.  The quality of construction in this home is evident in every detail, ensuring that your investment will stand the test of time. 10 year home warranty included. 1 PRE-PAID PARKING SPACE INCLUDED!"
