220017241,SOLD,"JC, Heights",23 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1500,5069,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,B,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$850,000","$875,000",$566.67,$566.67,9/26/2022,11/7/2022,12/16/2022,42,42,,12/19/2022,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Franklin / Ferry,"BUILDER IS OFFERING RATE BUY DOWN! Presenting 23 Manhattan, a new luxury construction home designed by one of Jersey City's most renowned builders, NKAY. This 3 bedrm, 2 bathrm home features an expansive open-concept living space with immaculate attention to detail, craftsmanship and design. The open concept chef's kitchen boasts premium Black Stainless Steel Samsung appliances and wine fridge, high-end designer cabinets, hand selected quartz waterfall counters/backsplash, farmhouse sink and pot filler. Throughout the home you'll notice smart home security, thermostat, speakers and doorbell. Master Bedroom has vaulted ceilings with custom built walk-in closets and plenty of natural light. Bathrooms include modern fixtures, smart mirror and floor to ceiling custom patterned porcelain tiles. Your private rooftop offers beautiful NYC views and is designed to entertain w/ speakers, lights and gas/water hook ups."
230009798,SOLD,"JC, Heights",265 GRIFFITH ST,Condominium,1573,1581,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3404,17,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$850,000","$899,000",$540.37,$540.37,6/13/2023,7/14/2023,9/14/2023,31,31,,9/14/2023,,,,,,$144,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave & Kennedy Blvd,"Welcome to 265 Griffith Street, Unit #2, located in the prestigious Jersey City Heights. This exceptional high-end new construction residence showcases impeccable finishes and boasts its own private roof deck, creating a truly luxurious living experience. Spanning 1,573.58 sq ft, this three-bedroom home offers a seamless blend of elegance and modernity. Step inside to discover an open and luminous floor plan adorned with lush weathered oak flooring and expansive Anderson windows that bathe the space in natural light. The modern kitchen features sleek quartz countertops, exquisite pendant lights, a built-in wine cooler, and an appliance package. Custom linen finished cabinetry adds a touch of sophistication, while smart video intercom and built-in speakers provide convenience and entertainment. As you explore the home, you'll find three generously-sized bedrooms, each equipped with private closets for optimal storage, and complete with a built-in laundry area. The primary bedroom offers a private balcony, a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom adorned with pastorelli porcelain tile and double vanity sinks, providing a haven of relaxation and tranquility. Ascend to the upper level to indulge in the ultimate outdoor retreat—a 1,090 sq ft private roof deck with breathtaking views of the New York City skyline. Whether you're hosting a summertime barbecue, enjoying evening cocktails, or simply unwinding with a good book, this meticulously crafted space offers the perfect ambiance. Quality decking, gas-grill ready connection, and built-in outdoor speakers further enhance the rooftop experience. Convenience is paramount with a dedicated parking spot in the garage and access to a storage area. 265 Griffith Street is just steps away from the local bus stops, providing easy transportation to and from NYC. Additionally, you'll find an array of shops and restaurants on Central/Palisade Avenue, ensuring a vibrant and fulfilling lifestyle. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail by one of Jersey City Height's most experienced developers, this residence exemplifies sophistication and quality. Take advantage of Jersey City's 5 Year 'New Construction' Tax Abatement, providing a substantial financial benefit for homeowners. Embrace the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own and immerse yourself in a lifestyle of unparalleled luxury and comfort."
250012609,SOLD,"JC, Heights",9 PIERCE AVE,Condominium,1953,1724,"$850,000",CONDO-COOP,,2&3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2105,27,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$850,000","$899,000",$435.23,$435.23,6/20/2025,8/15/2025,9/29/2025,56,56,,9/29/2025,,,,,TBD,,,Conventional,,,,,,Bleecker and South,"Discover refined living in this luxurious new condominium, ideally situated in Jersey City's vibrant Heights neighborhood. Spanning 1,953 square feet across two thoughtfully designed levels, this stunning residence offers 3 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 modern bathrooms.  Step inside to an inviting open-concept living and dining area, bathed in natural light and enhanced by sleek, contemporary finishes. Elegant hardwood floors flow throughout, leading to a gourmet kitchen that will delight any chef. This culinary haven boasts custom soft-close cabinetry, gleaming quartz countertops, a stylish backsplash, and a spacious breakfast bar that perfectly balances form and function.  The expansive primary suite is a serene retreat, featuring a large walk-in closet with custom shelving and a private en-suite bathroom for ultimate comfort. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms, and an office, offer ample closet space and versatile living options.  Two balconies and a private roof top terrace with a wet bar.  Nestled on a charming street, this exceptional home combines tranquility with urban convenience. Enjoy easy access to NYC transportation, popular neighborhoods, and a diverse selection of shops, restaurants, and cultural attractions. Plus, peace of mind comes standard with a 10-year builder's warranty.  Experience the perfect blend of style, comfort, and city living in this remarkable condominium.  "
