240017455,SOLD,"JC, Heights",28 GRACE ST,Condominium,1650,1724,"$851,999",CONDO-COOP,,1,A,"JC, Heights",07307,00504,00032,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$851,999","$849,999",$516.36,$516.36,9/5/2024,10/6/2024,11/21/2024,31,31,,11/22/2024,,,,"$10,325",2023,$235,2024,Conventional,No,No,,,,Central and Summit,"Welcome to 28 Grace St, a masterpiece of luxury and convenience. This stunning residence welcomes you with a bright and airy living room featuring soaring ceilings and custom stained white oak floors. The chef's kitchen is a modern marvel, showcasing custom white lacquer cabinets, Caesarstone countertops, a vented hood, and a full suite of high-end GE appliances. The master suite is a true retreat, offering high ceilings, an expansive Porcelanosa bathroom with floating vanities, ample closet space, and a tiled deck/terrace overlooking the serene backyard. The main level also includes two additional bedrooms and one other full bath, providing ample space for all your needs. travel to the lower level to discover a spacious rec room with a convenient half bathroom, seamlessly connecting to a beautiful backyard—ideal for entertaining or enjoying with your furry friends. The residence features large Anderson windows throughout, high ceilings, gleaming hardwood floors, 4 base moulding, and garage parking. One dedicated closet in the shared garage with custom shelving for extra storage.  Tech enthusiasts will appreciate the smart home features, including a Nest thermostat for remote temperature control and a smart lock on garage door. Additional conveniences include a package gate conveniently located under the outside stairs. Situated just minutes from Washington Park and less than a mile from the 9th Street Light Rail, this home provides easy access to NYC via bus and light rail. This exceptional property is a must-see—experience the luxury and convenience it has to offer!"
220010479,SOLD,"JC, Heights",9 IRVING ST,Condominium,1400,6199,"$852,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,804,23,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$852,000","$852,000",$608.57,$608.57,6/8/2022,7/19/2022,9/23/2022,41,41,,9/26/2022,,,,,,$250,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Summit Ave and John F. Kennedy Blvd,"Brand-new construction - spares no expense! Located in the heart of booming Jersey City Heights. Features include 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, modern open concept living, a fully equipped kitchen with state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances, a 5 burner stove, a convection oven, custom cabinets, and quartz countertops with a breakfast bar. The main bedroom with private en-suite bath and sliding glass doors that lead to your balcony, 2 generous sized bedrooms. Features include hardwood floors throughout, central air/heat, washer and dryer, and LED lighting. 1 tandem spot included. Minutes to Journal Square PATH and bus station, restaurants, shops, and all major highways and tunnels. Come and see for yourself why Jersey City was named the Sixth Borough of New York City. This property is eligible for a 5-year tax abatement."
230017130,SOLD,"JC, Heights",275 COLUMBIA AVE,Condominium,1674,1597,"$852,850",CONDO-COOP,,3&R,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,5,,"$852,850","$850,000",$509.47,$509.47,10/12/2023,10/17/2023,12/15/2023,5,5,,12/15/2023,,,,,,$196,,Conventional,,,,,,North St. & Leonard St,"Light streams in through the oversized Andersen windows illuminating the extra wide, open floorplan with classic crown molding and gleaming hardwood flooring throughout. White eat-in kitchen shows style with waterfall quartz counters & backsplash, custom shaker cabinets, pot-filler, apron sink, black Samsung appliances and wine fridge. A tech-lover’s dream wired for plenty of mod cons, including smart doorbell, smart thermostat, camera, security system. Set on a beautiful tree-lined street, this spacious three bedroom layout comes with coveted private outdoor and EV charger non-tandem parking.   Top unit includes full-size private rooftop with incredible cityscape views.   Bathrooms bring coveted upgrades like double-vanities, soaker tub with multi-system shower and niche, and glass shower. Primary ensuite hosts spacious built-out walk-in-closet for optimal storage and organization.   On a quiet tree-lined street of The Heights, and walking distance to JFK Blvd, Washington Park and 9th St Light Rail station, this neighborhood is known for great community, excellent schools and easy NYC access, all amid the eclectic and vibrant scene of Jersey City Heights.   "
240007622,SOLD,"JC, Heights",185 COLUMBIA AVE,Condominium,2668,6609,"$853,000",CONDO-COOP,,multi,1,"JC, Heights",07307,1203,51,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$853,000","$890,000",$319.72,$319.72,4/24/2024,7/9/2024,8/8/2024,76,76,,8/8/2024,,"$698,100",2023,"$12,619",2023,$200,2023,Conventional,No,No,,,,North Ave & Bleeker Ave,"Nestled in the heart of JC Heights, this exquisite duplex offers a unique blend of spaciousness, luxury, and convenience. Boasting an age of slightly more than one year, it presents an opportunity to indulge in urban living at its finest. With 3 levels of living space, 2 balconies, patio, 2-car tandem garage, a separate living area complete with a kitchenette, 2 laundry units, and more! The exterior showcases clean lines, a contemporary color palette, and large windows with panoramic views. The open-floor layout on the main floor seamlessly connects the LR, DR, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal setting for entertaining and relaxation alike. Gleaming hardwood floors exude warmth, while high ceilings elevate the sense of spaciousness. 2 balconies & cozy patio offer the perfect spaces to unwind. The gourmet kitchen stands as a masterpiece of both design & functionality. Adorned with top-of-the-line appliances, premium cabinetry, and sleek countertops, this culinary haven caters to both seasoned chefs & culinary enthusiasts. There are 3 well-appointed BRs. The master suite is complete with a lavish ensuite bath. The property features a unique offering - a separate living area with a kitchenette. From the high-end fixtures to the contemporary finishes, every element speaks of a sophisticated taste that is both timeless and modern. The convenience of an entire 2-car tandem garage and a driveway provides secure parking and storage."
230014550,SOLD,"JC, Heights",65 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,1975,1597,"$855,000",CONDO-COOP,,2+3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02702,00016,,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$855,000","$849,000",$432.91,$432.91,8/31/2023,9/16/2023,11/17/2023,16,16,,11/19/2023,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave and Milton Ave,"4 REAL Bedrooms, 2 full baths, powder room, rare balcony and private rooftop with amazing views!! The voluminous and light-filled residence is meticulously constructed with opulent modern finishes and materials. With oversized windows and 4” Red Oak hard wood floors throughout, every space of the home feels airy and serene. Elegantly designed with modern simplicity, the residence is further equipped with energy-efficient windows, washer and dryer, recessed LED lighting and fully built closets. The condo is located in a sought-after Jersey City Heights location close to parks, shops, renowned restaurants and public transportation. Taxes are TBD. HOA estimate$250 ***Check out the linked virtual tour!***"
230009138,SOLD,"JC, Heights",83 WAVERLY ST,Condominium,1627,1713,"$855,000",CONDO-COOP,,2nd,3,"JC, Heights",07306,04901,00027,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$855,000","$855,000",$525.51,$525.51,6/2/2023,6/21/2023,7/28/2023,19,19,,7/28/2023,,,,,TBD,$554,,Conventional,,,,,,Central & Oakland Ave,"Welcome home to your brand-new luxury condo! Last available unit in the newly completed PRINT HOUSE. Environmentally sustainable (built to LEED Silver certification) new construction on a quiet street in the booming Heights section of Jersey City. A real community feel with modern amenities!! Peace and quiet with everything you need only blocks away - including 13 acres of activities at Pershing Field (skating, tennis, kayaking, bird watching, swimming, etc...), shopping, supermarket, farmer’s market, eat and drink at coffee shops, artisanal shops, cafes, pubs, 5-star restaurants. This move-in ready condo features an open concept living space that extends directly to a huge 350 square foot outdoor space, seamlessly blending outdoor and indoor living. Light abounds through the numerous triple pane windows and doors, providing an abundance of natural light throughout the unit. Wait until you see the kitchen! Professional chef designed with quartz countertops, large island, SS Energy Star appliances, oversized pantry, and custom tile backsplash. Convenient for walking, biking or public transportation. Underground 2 car garage parking with electric vehicle charging station. Lower your energy bills & help the environment w/ high efficiency insulation, triple pane windows & doors, high efficiency multi-zone heating & cooling system with programmable thermostats, high efficiency LED lighting, EnergyStar rated white roof and a vegetated 'green’ roof, water conserving dual flush toilets. Sound attenuation helps while you work from home, read or just relax. Security conscious, need at home deliveries, no problem – remote smart access entry system to the building and residences. 5 year tax abatement approved July 2022.  Close to Journal Square, Hoboken & Downtown Jersey City."
250005726,SOLD,"JC, Heights",234 SOUTH ST,Condominium,1350,1597,"$855,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$855,000","$899,000",$633.33,$633.33,3/25/2025,4/22/2025,6/6/2025,28,28,,6/26/2025,,,,,,$226,,Conventional,,,,,,JFK and Pierce,"Nestled on a tree-lined street in The Heights, this brand new construction home brings the very best of modern luxury and ultimate lifestyle. The beautiful red brick building boasts a three bedroom home with must-have 1200 sq ft *private rooftop* and coveted garage parking.  Inside discover the epitome of modern elegance with red oak hardwood floors, high ceilings, oversized windows and crown molding throughout. This penthouse level home enchants with a full-story private rooftop offering panoramic views of the city skyline.   The showpiece kitchen beckons with neutral wood and white cabinets finished to the ceiling, white quartz counters, gleaming tile backsplash and an eat-in island adorned with paneled-wood finish and extra storage. Finishing touches include beautiful brass fixtures complemented by stainless appliances, including convertible hood and must-have wine fridge.  Bedrooms bring ample space, light and storage, plus a walk-in closet with built-ins featured in the primary ensuite. Wow-worthy bathrooms include touches like resort-inspired floor to ceiling tile, glass showers with multi-system sprays, and not one, but two double vanities.   This unbeatable location is just one block from Summit Avenue with bustling shops, restaurants and boutiques. Jersey City Heights is known for its excellent community, great schools, beautiful parks and easy access to NYC and surrounding neighborhoods. ."
220001868,SOLD,"JC, Heights",42 RAVINE AVE,Condominium,1700,1703,"$855,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,00017,05001,,42 RAVINE,,,,3,0,3,9,,"$855,000","$849,000",$502.94,$502.94,2/2/2022,2/11/2022,4/11/2022,9,9,,4/19/2022,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Webster Ave and Abbett Street,"NEW TO THE MARKET! Welcome to 42 Ravine Avenue, perfectly located in Jersey City Heights!  42 Ravine Ave consists of two brand new condominium residences that feel more like townhouses! Interior finishes include 4.5 inch white oak hardwood floors on the main level, custom moldings, cabinets as well as custom built in closets. Two zone central heat and air conditioning as well as a tankless hot water system and central vacuum throughout.  The spacious kitchen featuring a center island, Samsung black stainless steel appliances,  wine cooler, custom 42 cabinets with black metal hardware, quartz counters and subway tile backsplash.   Bathrooms feature Kholer fixtures, ceramic tile flooring and quartz counters. To top it off this residence features a private rear patio and direct access to a sun drenched front patio.  One parking space is included!"
250004368,SOLD,"JC, Heights",339 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1400,1603,"$855,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,4,"JC, Heights",07307,4504,30,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$855,000","$879,000",$610.71,$610.71,3/7/2025,4/1/2025,6/5/2025,25,25,,6/11/2025,,,,$0,,$256,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Ferry St and Franklin St,"Welcome to your dream home in the best location in Jersey City Heights! This top floor, new construction, two-story home offers the perfect blend of modern luxury with the benefits of city convenience. Step inside and fall in love with light hardwood floors, high ceilings and private terrace off the living space creating an airy, open atmosphere throughout the home. Chef's kitchen complete with custom cabinetry with ample storage, a massive breakfast island, stainless steel appliances and a panel-ready dishwasher that seamlessly blends with the sleek design. Whip up your culinary masterpieces while entertaining guests in style! The primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat, while the additional bedrooms offer comfort and flexibility for family members or guests. The bathrooms feature designer fixtures and finishes and create a spa-like atmosphere. The best part? A massive 767 sf private rooftop with gas and water lines.  The best space to host gatherings or simply relax.  This property boasts unparalleled ease of access to New York City, making your commute as breezy as a walk in the adjacent Riverview-Fisk Park. Whether you prefer the NJ Transit buses or the convenience of the 100 Steps to the 2nd Street Light Rail Station right at your doorstep, your connection to the city has never been smoother.  The quality of construction in this home is evident in every detail, ensuring that your investment will stand the test of time. 10 year home warranty included."
210022390,SOLD,"JC, Heights",48 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1600,5069,"$855,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,01505,00052,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$855,000","$850,000",$534.38,$534.38,9/27/2021,12/27/2021,3/14/2022,87,87,,3/14/2022,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Central Ave ---> Graham Street,"*New Construction Move-In Ready!!!* Built by one of Jersey City's premier builders with no expense spared.  Features include a massive roof deck that spans the entire unit's area, a 2 car heated garage, and an expansive open-concept living space. The marble waterfall island flows into a Chefs kitchen that includes premium stainless appliances and wine cooler with thoughtful arrangement for both entertainment and functionality. Unit includes 3 bedrooms and 2 baths with dedicated 2 car garage parking and private rooftop entertaining/leisure space with water and gas hookups. Master Bedroom has vaulted ceilings with custom walk in closets and tremendous natural light. Bathrooms include modern fixtures and vanity as well as multiple shower head showers lined with porcelain tiles.    "
210008280,SOLD,"JC, Heights",238 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,,1691,"$855,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3803,11,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$855,000","$855,000",,,4/8/2021,4/8/2021,9/9/2021,0,0,,9/9/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith & Hutton,"One of Jersey City's finest builders is at it again! With an estimate completion of Summer 2021, these two new construction condominiums will quarrel over nothing except which wide open layout offers the best flow, and whose oversized outdoor space should host the next summer barbecue. This duplex 3 bed 2.5 bath home will be beautifully finished with absolute thoughtfulness and top-notch quality. Main floor living and dining area layout flows into chef-inspired kitchens finished with white marble waterfall island, inlay farm sink, Fabuwood cabinets, Samsung stainless steel appliances, must-have wine fridge, kohler fixtures and modern pendant lighting. Master suite and additional bedrooms boast ceiling fans, Pella windows, and custom walk-in closets, while bathrooms host high-end porcelain tiles, modern vanities and multiple shower heads. You'll be able hear a pin drop in this ultra-peaceful atmosphere, thanks to the extra-thick soundproofing, subfloor and insulation. A tech-lovers dream with every mod con, finishes include home entertainment wiring with 5.1 speakers, Ring doorbell, camera and security system, central vacuum and Nest thermostat. Rec room to be completed with wet bar; backyard with outdoor speakers *and* fire pit! Steps from Riverview Fisk and Washington parks - as well as both 2nd St & 9th St Light Rail stations - this neighborhood is known for great schools and easy NYC access, all amid the eclectic and vibrant scene of Jersey City Heights. *Photos are of similar listing, different location*"
250020230,SOLD,"JC, Heights",85 BLEECKER ST,Condominium,1403,1724,"$855,300",CONDO-COOP,,2,3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$855,300","$899,000",$609.62,$609.62,10/1/2025,10/29/2025,1/23/2026,28,28,,1/27/2026,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,summit,"Welcome to this exceptional brand-new construction residence situated on one of Jersey City Heights’ most sought-after streets. Spanning an impressive 1,403 square feet, this thoughtfully crafted three-bedroom, two-bathroom with PRIVATE ROOF DECK home perfectly blends modern elegance with everyday comfort.  Step inside to a sun-drenched, open-concept living and dining area where soaring ceilings, light-finished 6 wide-plank hardwood floors, oversized Anderson windows, and an 8-foot custom entry door package create an immediate sense of style and sophistication. Anchoring the space is a bespoke electric fireplace, offering warmth and ambiance for both relaxing evenings and lively gatherings.  The chef’s kitchen is a true showpiece, designed for both function and flair. Outfitted with oversized custom soft-close cabinetry, a walk-in pantry, quartz countertops, and a designer tile backsplash, it is centered around a generous island perfect for casual dining and entertaining. A full suite of premium VIKING appliances completes the space, providing professional-grade quality for culinary enthusiasts.  Retreat to the primary suite oasis, featuring a custom walk-in closet and a spa-inspired en-suite bath with a contemporary rain shower and sleek designer finishes. Two additional well-proportioned bedrooms offer oversized custom closets and abundant natural light, ideal for guests, family, or a home office.  Ascend to your PRIVATE ROOF DECK—a rare luxury offering sweeping skyline views and ample room for outdoor dining, entertaining, or enjoying serene sunsets.  Additional highlights include garage parking availability, central heating and cooling, and premium finishes throughout.  Perfectly located, this home places you within moments of NYC transportation, neighborhood parks, local cafés, dining destinations, and cultural hot spots that define the vibrant Jersey City Heights lifestyle.  This is more than a residence—it’s an opportunity to experience elevated living in one of Jersey City’s most desirable neighborhoods.  GARAGE PARKING AVAILABLE."
260005660,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",15 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1284,1597,"$856,800",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$856,800",$667.29,,3/31/2026,,,9,,,3/31/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Central and Sherman,"This trio of brand-new residences blends modern craftsmanship together with rich design. Each home captures a signature balance of sophistication and warmth with curated lighting, high ceilings, and thoughtful layouts intended for everyday elegance.  Perfectly positioned near Pershing Field Park and Reservoir, plus nearby 2nd Street Light Rail, this address connects effortlessly to both PATH and ferry routes for seamless NYC access. The quiet tree-lined street brings the serenity of neighborhood living, with the charm and community of Jersey City Heights, Hoboken and beyond.  See Documents for Marketing Presentation."
240022961,SOLD,"JC, Heights",204 BOWERS ST,Condominium,1482,6706,"$857,500",CONDO-COOP,,2&3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2704,34,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$857,500","$869,000",$578.61,$578.61,11/26/2024,12/12/2024,1/31/2025,16,15,,2/3/2025,,,,"$12,223",,$127,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Milton Ave & Summit Ave,"Modern elegance with smart home features—this stunning 3-bedroom condo, nestled in the heart of the vibrant Heights neighborhood in Jersey City, could be your next home! The open-concept living area bathes in abundant natural light, creating an inviting space for relaxation and entertainment. The sleek white cabinetry in the kitchen houses Samsung appliances—including a wine fridge and a convenient pot filler. Quartz waterfall countertops add a touch of luxury, and the beautiful hardwood floors tie it all together! Three spacious bedrooms come with ample closet space. Primary bathroom features double vanity, smart mirrors and the glass shower has a multi-spray system. The unit includes a dedicated utility area with a Samsung washer and dryer, as well as a deeded 1-car parking spot in the tandem garage (complete with EV charging and a garage storage closet). Ascend to your full-size PRIVATE ROOFTOP and soak in breathtaking cityscape views! This property is conveniently located near restaurants, shops, public transportation and is in the center of three parks: Pershing Field Park, Riverview-Fisk Park and Washington Park. What are you waiting for? This home won't last in the market!"
250012126,SOLD,"JC, Heights",27 LEONARD ST,Condominium,1415,6078,"$859,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,504,12,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$859,000","$859,000",$607.07,$607.07,6/15/2025,7/25/2025,9/11/2025,40,41,,9/12/2025,,,,"$12,774",2024,$250,,Conventional,,,,,,Secaucus Rd and Leonard,"Discover high-end living in this spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bath condominium nestled in the sought-after Jersey City Heights neighborhood. Built with modern luxury in mind, this home includes the rare convenience of non-tandem parking and a private rooftop oasis complete with Trex decking, an outdoor kitchen, and panoramic NYC views perfect for entertaining or relaxing.The sleek chef's kitchen showcases premium Bertazzoni appliances, quartz countertops, a waterfall Moen faucet, and minimalist European-style cabinetry, all complemented by wide-plank hardwood floors. The open-concept layout flows effortlessly into a sun-filled living area, creating a welcoming and airy space for gatherings.Elegant touches continue into the spa-inspired bathrooms, featuring frameless glass shower doors, rainfall showerheads, and a double vanity. Designed for both style and efficiency, the home includes full spray foam insulation, sound-dampening layers between floors, Andersen windows, and a Rheem HVAC system for year-round comfort.Additional perks include a private entrance, dedicated garage storage, and a built-in central vacuum system. 2 Year Tax Abatement and 7 Year Builder's Warranty."
220012791,SOLD,"JC, Heights",112 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1614,1597,"$859,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,04503,00008,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$859,000","$825,000",$532.22,$532.22,7/14/2022,7/19/2022,9/12/2022,5,5,,9/13/2022,,,,"$9,359",2021,$275,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton and Franklin,"Beautifully crafted and meticulously constructed in 2019, this spacious garden duplex condominium residence is situated in an enviable location in the heart of the bustling Jersey City Heights. The residence offers 3 Bedrooms, 2 Full Bathrooms, a half bathroom, garage parking and a private oasis of a backyard. The lower living space has direct access to the deck leading to the backyard, and the chef’s kitchen is spacious and lavishly equipped. Custom trim work, modern finishes, hardwood and tile floors, and exceptional fixtures are found throughout. Further, the voluminous home features a laundry room, central AC & Heat, and abundant custom closets. Just a stone’s throw to parks, cafes, restaurants, markets, shops and entertainment, the gorgeous residence is conveniently located near all that Jersey City heights has to offer.  "
220012519,SOLD,"JC, Heights",138 LAKE ST,Condominium,2240,6452,"$860,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07306,04602,00032,,,,,,3,1,3,6,,"$860,000","$885,000",$383.93,$383.93,7/9/2022,9/23/2022,11/22/2022,76,76,,11/23/2022,,,,"$11,000",2022,$250,,Conventional,,,,,,Liberty and Kennedy,"BRAND NEW CONSTRUTION. Experience luxury like never before in this spacious condominium. From location to amenities this property has everything that you ever wanted in your home. This 3 bed 3.5 bath light filled home is a brand new construction. The first level starts with a spacious formal living area with a powder room, fireplace with bar & wine cooler and plenty of closets. The 2nd level has open concept kitchen with island, modern stainless steel appliances, shaker cabinets, dining area and family room. This level has bedroom #3 and a full bath with standing shower. 3rd level boasts of a master bed room, en-suite bath with double sinks and walk in closet, Bed room # 2 with a full bathroom  in the hallway and main floor laundry room completes this level.  A spacious roof top deck on the upper level is a major plus for relaxing, unwinding and entertaining after a hectic week. You'll have your own parking space and a shared front yard and patio. Rare opportunity, Don't miss it!!"
220017032,SOLD,"JC, Heights",230 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1249,1639,"$860,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02302,00001 02,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$860,000","$879,000",$688.55,$688.55,9/21/2022,9/29/2022,11/22/2022,8,8,,11/23/2022,,,,"$9,826",,,,Cash,,,,,,South St and Sherman Ave,"Welcome to Residence 2, located at 230 Sherman Ave. A meticulous 3-bedroom, 2 full bath smart home in the heart of Jersey City Heights! Be inspired when taking in the sights on an oversized, 1200 sqft private roof deck with panoramic views from Hudson Yards down to the World Trade Center, which has preinstalled gas/water/electric connections as well as Bluetooth enabled outdoor speakers for optimal use and entertaining. The interior home itself has a chef's kitchen outfit with a stunning waterfall quartz countertop, top tier Samsung package of black stainless steel appliances, Sharp under-counter microwave drawer, outside vented hood, and dual-zone wine fridge, matched with Kohler plumbing fixtures. No detail has been overlooked, with meticulous crown molding, a full building sprinkler system, a Ring security system equipped with video doorbell and outdoor security cameras, a Bluetooth enabled built-in 5.1 channel home theater, and a unified mesh Wifi network ensuring you never lose your broadband connection. The oversized primary bedroom is overrun with natural light, has his and her walk-in closets and a spa-like en-suite with a glass enclosed walk-in rain shower that exudes luxury. Additional amenities include central vacuum, custom closets throughout, commercial waterproof garage flooring and coaxial and ethernet ports in every room. This new construction build was developed by renowned Jersey City Heights developer, NKAY, known for their quality and credibility in the area and comes with a remaining 2-year new construction tax abatement and a 7-vear structural builder's warranty When it comes to location in The Heights, this residence is second to none with proximity to the 9th Street Light Rail, buses to Manhattan, top tier restaurants such as Corto, and Bread and Salt an Italian bakery opened by James Beard semi-finalist Rick Easton and walkability for the area that is unmatched. Couple this with heated garage parking, and this one has it all! One of the most desirable streets in all of Jersey City, come see why you will be calling 230 Sherman home."
240000578,SOLD,"JC, Heights",9 STAGG ST,Condominium,2106,6199,"$860,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07306,05401,00015,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$860,000","$865,000",$408.36,$408.36,1/10/2024,2/2/2024,4/5/2024,23,23,,4/5/2024,,,,"$6,714",2022,$267,,Conventional,,,,,,Liberty Ave & JFK,"Step into luxury living with this exquisite 3 bedroom, 2.5-bath residence, boasting an additional living area and an expansive rooftop deck (567 sq/ft), & parking (available for electric car charging)  that truly makes it feel like a home.  Experience the perfect blend of modern and classic design elements, featuring crown molding throughout, gleaming hardwood floors, Pella windows, and strategically placed ceiling fans throughout. The open-concept kitchen is a chef's dream, showcasing a sparkling quartz waterfall eat-in peninsula, stylish tile backsplash, custom shaker cabinets, a stainless farm sink, and Samsung appliances, including a wine fridge & vented stove. Enjoy the convenience of Kohler fixtures and modern pendant lighting, creating a sleek and inviting atmosphere complemented by an extra half bath adjacent to the main living area. The living area is adorned with a built-in floating electric fireplace, a centerpiece encased in a classic custom mantle.  Embrace smart living with upgraded features such as a Ring doorbell, security camera wiring, and a Nest thermostat & smart locks. The bathrooms offer a retreat with a marble double vanity and polished chrome fixtures. Additional features include a spacious laundry closet with Samsung washer and dryer, as well as a generously sized private basement storage area (440 sq/ft). Revel in the abundance of storage solutions and personalized closets within this home, ensuring both practicality and tailored organization to meet your lifestyle needs.  Ascend to the full-size rooftop deck (567 sq/ft), providing unobstructed east facing sunset views, creating an ideal space for entertaining or relaxation with ample space to BBQ .  Situated in a modern gray brick building on a picturesque tree-lined street in the serene corner of The Heights Western Slope, this residence is mere blocks from Leonard Gordon Park. Enjoy easy access to the JSQ PATH station, 2nd St Light Rail, and major roads, making commuting a breeze. Jersey City Heights is renowned for its strong community, exceptional schools, and seamless NYC access, surrounded by vibrant shops, restaurants, and parks. Don't miss the chance to call this stunning property home!   "
220015139,SOLD,"JC, Heights",82 PATERSON ST,Condominium,1870,1653,"$860,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,01405,00019 01,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$860,000","$875,000",$459.89,$459.89,8/18/2022,8/31/2022,10/14/2022,13,13,,10/18/2022,,,,,TBD,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Summit Avenue & Kennedy Blvd,"This ground up new construction redefines luxury condos. A short walk to Congress St Lite Rail Station, 82 Paterson sits in one of the best locations of Jersey City Heights close to Central Ave Shopping District, parks, direct buses into NYC, and amazing restaurants and coffee shops in each direction. Unit 1 is a duplex unit featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a bonus living area with powder room that leads out to an oversized backyard. Features include hardwood floors, custom trim, large spacious kitchen with Samsung stainless steel appliances and additional cabinetry, wine fridge, quartz countertop, coffered ceilings in the living room with an electric fireplace, lots of closet space throughout with custom shelving, in unit laundry, and modern fixtures. Master bedroom offers a sliding door to walkout to your private balcony, a large walk-in closet, and a master bathroom. Schedule a tour day!"
230008011,SOLD,"JC, Heights",99 HAGUE ST,Condominium,1697,6078,"$860,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,402,14,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,9,,"$860,000","$869,000",$506.78,$506.78,5/16/2023,9/11/2023,12/5/2023,118,118,,1/2/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Nelson & JFK Blvd,"Welcome to  99 Hague St, a luxurious new construction condominium in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This 3-bedroom, 3-bath duplex features an open floor layout, electric vehicle charging stations, 10 ft ceilings on the main level, Anderson windows, quartz countertops, in-unit laundry, red oak hardwood floors, designer tiles, and modern fixtures. As you enter the unit, you'll be greeted by a spacious entertaining area on the first floor, complete with a wet bar and direct access to a beautiful two-tiered backyard. This is the perfect space for hosting family and friends or simply relaxing outdoors. As you make your way up to the second floor, you'll discover the heart of the home - the kitchen and living room. The chef's kitchen features sleek quartz countertops, high-end appliances, and plenty of storage space, making it the perfect place to prepare your favorite meals. The open concept living room provides ample space for relaxation and entertainment, and the hardwood floors and designer tiles add warmth and elegance to the space. The second floor also includes three bedrooms, including a spacious master bedroom with a master bath. The master bedroom offers a peaceful retreat at the end of the day, while the master bath provides all the luxurious amenities you could want. This duplex unit is the perfect combination of modern luxury and practical living. With two floors of space, you'll have plenty of room to spread out and enjoy all that this beautiful condo has to offer. And with easy access to public transportation, shopping, dining, and entertainment, you'll be able to take advantage of everything that Jersey City has to offer. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this stunning new construction duplex your own. Schedule a showing today and experience all the benefits of modern living in one of the most sought-after areas of Jersey City. The property is eligible for a 5-year tax abatement. "
230008055,SOLD,"JC, Heights",16 ABBETT ST,Condominium,1442,6005,"$860,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,5008,1,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$860,000","$899,000",$596.39,$596.39,5/17/2023,5/23/2023,7/14/2023,6,6,,7/15/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Palisade & Central,"Luxury living awaits! Welcome to this expansive, gorgeously modern home located in one of Jersey City's Heights hottest locations! This new construction duplex has an open kitchen that is ideal for entertaining. It also has a half bath, private backyard and private garage with access on the main floor. The second floor boasts three bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. This exquisite condo is located on a quiet, tree lined street between Palisade Ave. and Central Ave. This chic, custom designed condo by NKAY Builders comes with a 10 year builders warranty and 5 yr. tax abatement (taxes must be independently verified by tax assessor) This property won’t last long! One member of selling LLC is an actively licensed NJ Real Estate Broker"
250022686,SOLD,"JC, Heights",99 THORNE ST,Condominium,1740,6541,"$860,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$860,000","$899,000",$494.25,$494.25,11/4/2025,11/19/2025,2/2/2026,15,15,,3/19/2026,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit and JFK,"Fully renovation beautiful and spacious three 3b/2b +finished basement/1 half bath unit located in desirable Jersey City Heights. This is a beautifully finished duplex featuring 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths with stylish double vanities, and a fully finished basement with a half bath, wet bar, and a bonus entertainment room. Enjoy brand-new stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, hardwood floors, and in-unit laundry. Step outside to your own private backyard, perfect for entertaining or relaxing. Located on a quiet block with easy access to NYC-bound buses and shoppings."
250012785,SOLD,"JC, Heights",104 POPLAR ST,Condominium,1803,1597,"$860,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$860,000","$879,000",$476.98,$476.98,6/24/2025,8/1/2025,10/22/2025,38,38,,10/22/2025,,,,"$13,844",,,,Conventional,,,,,,Nelson and JFK,"Step inside this thoughtfully crafted 2-story home where timeless style meets smart design. Set on a coveted tree-lined street in The Heights, this sun-drenched and spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home includes a bonus room, a private backyard, and coveted garage parking.  The bright and airy main level showcases oak hardwood floors, oversized windows and custom crown molding and millwork throughout. The open concept kitchen features gleaming quartz countertops with herringbone tile backsplash, an eat-in island, white shaker custom cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances including a farm sink. Downstairs, the bonus room includes a stylish wet bar with wine fridge—making indoor-outdoor living effortless. The double glass doors open to the private backyard area finished with pavers and fencing. A dedicated laundry area with full-size side-by-side Samsung washer & dryer adds utility and ease, while the private garage direct entry into the home gives the ultimate in convenience and function.  Upstairs, all three bedrooms are generously sized with fully built-out closets, including a walk-in for the primary ensuite. Beautiful bathrooms are luxuriously finished with floor-to-ceiling porcelain tile and multi-head shower systems—one with a glass-enclosed shower, the other with a deep soaking tub. Smart home features like wiring for surround sound, video intercom, camera security, and central vacuum enhance the experience, along with central air and an energy-efficient tankless water heater.  This home is a show-stopper from the street, with radiant red brick and stone facade, paver-lined driveway, and newly constructed exterior that blends classic charm with modern strength. Poplar Street is 2.5 blocks from Washington Park with sports facilities, playgrounds, walking paths, gardens, farmers markets and more. Owners enjoy easy access to the 9th street elevator and Lightrail with PATH, ferry and Hoboken connections. Jersey City Heights is known for its close-knit community, excellent schools, beautiful parks and easy access to NYC and surrounding areas."
250004869,SOLD,"JC, Heights",126 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1687,1686,"$860,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2C,"JC, Heights",07307,4503,17,Heights,,,,,1,0,1,6,,"$860,000","$850,000",$509.78,$509.78,3/14/2025,3/21/2025,4/30/2025,7,7,,4/30/2025,,,,"$13,509",,$690,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton & Franklin,"Experience the perfect blend of open-concept loft living while enjoying the privacy of a tucked away bedroom and separate den, currently used as a 2nd bedroom. This stunning home boasts soaring 13’ ceilings with exposed rafters, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere. The gorgeous kitchen features a large island, perfect for meal prep and gathering, seamlessly blending with the dining area and spacious living room complete with a cozy gas fireplace. A newly renovated bathroom adds modern elegance, while the terrace offers a space for outdoor relaxation. Enjoy the convenience of private garage parking along with additional basement storage. Located in a prime Heights location, it’s a commuter’s dream with easy access to all modes of transportation. Surrounded by top-rated bars, restaurants, and parks—this is city living at its finest."
250009054,SOLD,"JC, Heights",41 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1445,6199,"$860,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,01504,00010,,,,,,3,0,2,8,,"$860,000","$875,000",$595.16,$595.16,5/1/2025,5/2/2025,7/28/2025,1,0,,9/30/2025,,,,"$12,334",,$166,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave & Summit Ave,"Breathe in the beauty of this bright, tastefully finished, newer construction condominium in the heart of The Heights. Sought after 3 bedroom, 2 bath - 1445 sq ft grand, open floorplan complete with impressive private roof deck and panoramic NYC views. Tandem garage parking. Expansive open layout with plenty of room for living, dining, home office, entertaining or a growing family. The gorgeous living space has impressive high ceilings and oversized Pela windows. Enjoy all the features you desire.. crown molding, 4.25 hardwood floors & recessed lighting throughout. Gourmet chef's kitchens hosts oversized island with quartz countertops, modern appliances and - of course - a wine fridge. Generous bedrooms includes a walk-in closet in master bedroom. Zen inspired bathrooms are beautifully designed with soft-toned mosaic tile, and invigorating rain shower heads with multi jets and hand-held shower sprays. Modern upgrades with state-of-the-art surround sound, Schlage keyless entry, security camera, video intercom, and outdoor speakers. Location! Location! Settled just off Central Avenue, this lovely tree-lined street offers both a residential feel plus walkability to shopping and all the cool coffee shops and restaurants. Close proximity to schools, NYC access, and Washington Park with playgrounds, track fields, baseball fields, and tennis courts. Don't miss out on this luxurious condo! First time homebuyer program at 5.5% may be available for this property."
220012229,SOLD,"JC, Heights",9 FLOYD ST,Condominium,1620,1603,"$860,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07306,05403,00012,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$860,000","$875,000",$530.86,$530.86,7/6/2022,7/20/2022,9/14/2022,14,14,,9/14/2022,,,,"$9,871",2021,$179,,Conventional,,,,,,JFK Blvd & Spruce St,"Bright, spacious, luxury home in the JC Heights! 2020 new construction, located off Kennedy Blvd on a quiet street, less than a mile from the Journal Square path. Enter to a living room with a modern fireplace, strikingly high ceilings, flooded with natural light and high end finishes. Pass your dining area, open to a chef's kitchen with custom cabinetry, white quartz counters and high end Samsung appliances, including a smart fridge that syncs to your phone. The primary bedroom boasts an oversized modern bathroom, large closet, and balcony overlooking your private backyard. Featuring 2 other bedrooms and 1.5 baths providing ample space for your entertaining and living needs. Continue downstairs to an expansive rec room with marble floors that opens to a backyard oasis. Custom window treatments, gleaming hardwood floors, and a PRIVATE three car spacious garage equipped with an EV charger. Home is accompanied with smart appliances, thermostat, alarm system, wired speakers throughout, outdoor lighting, washer/dryer — it hits all the marks and then some! Take advantage of the 5 year tax abatement. Close to shopping, dining, parks, entertainment, schools, and transit. Must see!!  "
240023141,SOLD,"JC, Heights",197 GRIFFITH ST,Condominium,1675,5164,"$862,500",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$862,500","$875,000",$514.93,$514.93,12/3/2024,12/23/2024,2/10/2025,20,20,,2/11/2025,,,,,,$353,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave. and Central Ave.,"Welcome to luxury living with this custom designed, newly built 3 bedroom, 2 ½ bath condo nested within a prime location in Jersey City Heights! The downstairs duplex features a ground level expansive open-concept eat-in kitchen with a large peninsula island, waterfall quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. The dining and living room with a stylish bathroom lead to French sliding glass doors stepping out to a private backyard with a paver patio and white vinyl fence, ideal for entertaining. Upstairs greets you with beautiful, wide Red Oak hardwood floors and a spacious family room full of natural light. The master bedroom suite features a stunning full bathroom, large walk-in-closet, additional second closet, and sliding glass doors out to the balcony overlooking the backyard. Two additional sizable bedrooms, a full bathroom, washer and dryer, and ample closet space complete the second floor. Additional highlights include all new curtains and shades, 1 garage space, ZWave lighting system controlled by SmartThings Hub, warranties on all appliances and structures of the home, and a custom speaker system that connects directly with streaming apps. All within walking distance to convenient NYC transit access, vibrant shops, restaurants, parks, and schools! Specifically, right down the street from Riverview park where the famers market is! Eligible for a 5 year tax abatement."
230009200,SOLD,"JC, Heights",192 CONGRESS ST,Condominium,1707,6078,"$864,000",CONDO-COOP,,"1,2",1,"JC, Heights",07307,1402,34,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$864,000","$849,000",$506.15,$506.15,6/5/2023,6/20/2023,8/24/2023,15,15,,8/31/2023,,,,"$11,748",2022,$272,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit & Pierce,"Experience the perfect blend of luxury and modern living in this high-end, 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath Jersey City Heights home. With 10-foot ceilings and oversized windows, natural sunlight floods the open floor plan, complemented by remote-controlled blinds. The chef's kitchen is a standout, boasting high gloss modern cabinetry, a stainless steel Premium Samsung Appliance package, and a stunning waterfall Quartz countertop island. The master bedroom suite features a private terrace, designer walk-in closet, and a luxurious bathroom with high-end fixtures and a multi-jet glass-enclosed shower. Additional highlights include a lower level family room/den with a wet bar, and a private yard perfect for outdoor entertaining. Enjoy in-home laundry, hardwood floors, central A/C controlled by Nest, smart home technology, and indoor garage parking (NOT TANDEM). Conveniently located near shopping, highways, and transportation to NYC."
210024629,SOLD,"JC, Heights",103 THORNE ST,Condominium,1819,5464,"$865,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02603,00023,Downtown,103 Thorne,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$865,000","$877,000",$475.54,$475.54,10/29/2021,2/10/2022,4/6/2022,104,104,,4/7/2022,,,,"$8,173",2021,$176,2021,Conventional,No,No,,,,JFK Blvd & Summit Ave,"Newly built home in the vibrant Heights neighborhood in Jersey City. This 3 Bedroom / 2.5 Bath home is located directly off the major commercial hub of Central Ave with plenty of shopping and dining options along with bus routes directly to Manhattan. JSQ Path station is also not far. The home is built on lot line with adjacent property on left side, which makes it wider (22ft, instead of most other new build homes that are typically only 20ft wide). This additional 2ft width for the entire 65ft length of the building adds substantial width and square footage to the livable space for this home. Importantly, this home also offers an extra large NON-TANDEM covered parking garage included within it. Non-Tandem means both condo owners park their vehicle in garage without one having to move its own vehicle to make way for the other. This home on 1st level comes with its own full backyard, a rear patio/balcony, own private alley, and a large recreation room with its own half bath on the ground floor, with direct access to garage as well the backyard. Craftfully designed kitchen features Samsung appliances, quartz counters, and bonus cabinets. This home will be bright all year long having large windows and own private balcony looking in to the yard. Too many things to list. Easy distance to work, grocery, shopping and restaurants. This is a website, a visit is better. This is a great move-in ready opportunity to take advantage of the long term benefits of the Heights and Jersey City magnet schools. Hurry ! Won't last. See listing phone number provided below. HOA fee & property tax estimated."
230014549,SOLD,"JC, Heights",65 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,2643,1597,"$865,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02702,00016,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$865,000","$849,000",$327.28,$327.28,8/31/2023,9/13/2023,11/7/2023,13,13,,11/8/2023,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave. and Milton Ave.,"Newly gut-renovated and completely reimagined condominium duplex residence, 3 bedrooms 2/1 baths with full finished basement and private backyard! The voluminous and light-filled residence is meticulously constructed with opulent modern finishes and materials. With oversized windows and 4” Red Oak hardwood floors throughout, every space of the home feels airy and serene. Elegantly designed with modern simplicity, the residence is further equipped with energy-efficient windows, washer and dryer, recessed LED lighting and fully built closets. The condo is located in a sought-after Jersey City Heights location close to parks, shops, renowned restaurants and public transportation. Taxes are TBD. HOA estimate $250.***Checkout the linked virtual tour!***"
220017919,SOLD,"JC, Heights",104 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,1627,1597,"$865,000",CONDO-COOP,,  3&4,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$865,000","$875,000",$531.65,$531.65,10/6/2022,10/25/2022,12/19/2022,19,19,,12/19/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,JFK & Milton Ave,"Magazine-worthy modern marvel is move-in ready in The Heights. Brand new construction by one of Jersey City’s top builders offers three bedrooms, wide layout giving extra square footage, rooftop, plus garage parking for the ultimate urban appeal.  Extra-high Pella windows shine loads of natural light through to the open concept floorplan finished with classic design and modern upgrades like fresh oak hardwood floors, crown molding, high ceilings, and smart home tech throughout. Upstairs unit showcases a gorgeous glass staircase leading to the private rooftop with breathtaking 360 cityscape views.   Contemporary eat-in kitchens offer clean white quartz waterfall island, counters and backsplash, plus seamless custom cabinetry and stainless GE appliances including wine fridge. Primary ensuites host glass doors to private balcony plus large built-out walk-in closets. Bathrooms feature elements like double vanity with smart mirrors, glass shower with multihead system or soaker tub for added convenience. Designated utility area features stacking Samsung washer and dryer.  Modern brick building with 2-car non-tandem parking is less than one block from Summit Avenue, and walking distance to both Washington and Leonard Gordon Parks for ultimate urban escape. Jersey City Heights is known for its eclectic vibe, great community, excellent schools and accessibility to NYC and surrounding areas."
220012210,SOLD,"JC, Heights",151-153 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1711,1419,"$865,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,101,"JC, Heights",07307,03804,00014,Heights,,,,,2,1,2,5,,"$865,000","$899,000",$505.55,$505.55,7/6/2022,6/9/2022,8/22/2022,0,0,,8/26/2022,,,,,,$237,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton St. & Griffith St.,"Welcome home to The Webster Flats! This 6 unit ground up new construction condominium building brings a new meaning to LIVE PLAY WORK  all within the comfort of your own home! This expansive space provides you with 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, soaring 10 ft ceilings, backyard space, high end stainless steel appliances, full sized WhirlPool washer/dryers, Resideo alarm system, Aiphone home intercom system, and the Honeywell Pro Series thermostat. Entertainment becomes easy with your built in Sonos Ceiling speaker system prewired throughout the living room and primary bedroom. The enormous multi purpose space in the front of the home provides you with ample room for an office, art studio/gallery, creative space, at home business, workshop, boutique, or an expansive living space! Details like the solid oak hardwood floor in Herringbone pattern, Kohler fixtures, black and white tiled bathrooms, and highly efficient recessed lighting throughout all create a tranquil atmosphere for you to relax, live, work, and have fun, all at the same time. Parking is in the next door gated and monitored lot. The Jersey City Heights gets even better with its newest addition, this package is complete with a 10 year new home warranty and a 5 year tax abatement to be filed with JC.  50% closed. "
250012786,SOLD,"JC, Heights",72 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,1509,1597,"$865,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & R,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$865,000","$899,000",$573.23,$573.23,6/24/2025,9/11/2025,11/20/2025,79,79,,11/20/2025,,,,"$14,614",,$175,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit and Milton,"Created with exquisite taste and intelligent design, this recently renovated home in the heart of the Heights sets a new standard for city living. Showcasing sky-high ceilings, skylights and a panoramic rooftop, this three bedroom home levels up daily lifestyle with ease and sophistication. Work in NYC? Commuting is a breeze with multiple options to get into the city - Access the path in JSQ via the 83 NJ Transit bus or by Citi Bike; alternatively, head straight into Midtown Manhattan via the 119 NJ Transit Bus on Central Ave.  Experience ultimate curb appeal with alluring white brick facade, dark trim and protective enclosed front porch. Step inside to thoughtful finishes and top quality throughout -- wide plank hardwood floors, exposed brick walls, beautiful bay windows and elegant arched built-in dry bar to open the spacious floorplans. Chef-inspired kitchens impress with striking green custom cabinetry, black quartz waterfall countertops, built-in stainless appliances, brass fixtures and natural wood hood.  Massive primary ensuite showcases seductive dark panelled accent wall plus sweeping french doors to private balcony perfect for al fresco coffee or cocktails. Custom California Closets & Shade Store electronic shades also elevate this luxury bedroom. Distinctive zen-inspired bathrooms feature unique elements like black tile and floor-to-ceiling glass shower and faux wood or pattern tile floors. Head upstairs for a fully finished rooftop with unobstructed cityscape and NYC rooftop views.  Located on a quiet, tree-lined street equidistant to Riverview-Fisk, Washington and Pershing Field-Reservoir Parks, this location also offers walkability to surrounding Central, Summit & Palisade Avenue for essential shopping needs. The Heights is a vibrant community with excellent schools, award-winning restaurants and shops plus easy NYC access!"
240010046,SOLD,"JC, Heights",129 POPLAR ST,Condominium,1800,1676,"$865,000",CONDO-COOP,, 1, 1,"JC, Heights",07307,00703, 00007,,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$865,000","$865,000",$480.56,$480.56,5/23/2024,6/24/2024,10/15/2024,18,13,,2/10/2025,,,,,,,,VA,,,,,, Irving St & Grace St," Duplex with Backyard. Experience modern living with this stunning luxury condo in the heart of Jersey City. Perfectly blending state-of-the-art smart technology with elegant design, this 1,800 sq ft residence offers both convenience and sophistication.  Welcome to your new home at 129 Poplar, where 2 new construction condos await your purchase, either together or separately, in one of the most sought-after sections of Jersey City Heights. This unit boasts generous floorplans, 10-foot ceilings, Base and Crown Molding. Stunning kitchens feature beautiful quarts counters and an Island, Samsung stainless steel appliances, and an in-built microwave. Other features include oak hardwood flooring throughout, central HVAC, Samsung appliances, and a garage with 2-car parking with EV charging.   Unit 1 features 1800 Sq. Feet of spacious living w/ 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and recreation room. Private balcony and your backyard. Experience the pinnacle of luxury living, charter schools are within walking distance. A 10-year construction warranty and a 5-year tax abatement further only enhance the appeal of your new home. Must See !!"
250000631,SOLD,"JC, Heights",339 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1400,1603,"$865,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,4504,31,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,5,,"$865,000","$875,000",$617.86,$617.86,1/9/2025,3/25/2025,5/27/2025,75,75,,5/27/2025,,,,$0,,$257,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Ferry St and Franklin St,"Welcome to this stunning two-story duplex condo that seamlessly blends modern luxury with urban convenience. This newly constructed 1,400-square-foot residence offers three bedrooms and three full bathrooms, thoughtfully designed across two levels of living space. Step inside to discover soaring ceilings and expansive windows that flood the interior with natural light while framing breathtaking views of the New York City skyline. The high-end finishes throughout showcase meticulous attention to detail, creating an atmosphere of refined elegance. One of this home's most captivating features is the private rooftop space – a perfect urban oasis for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet moments while taking in panoramic city views. The quality of construction is evident in every corner, from the premium materials to the sophisticated design elements.  This property boasts unparalleled ease of access to New York City, making your commute as breezy as a walk in the adjacent Riverview-Fisk Park. Whether you prefer the NJ Transit buses or the convenience of the 100 Steps to the 2nd Street Light Rail Station right at your doorstep, your connection to the city has never been smoother."
