210012842,SOLD,"JC, Heights",107 JEFFERSON AVE,Condominium,1605,1659,"$865,000",CONDO-COOP,,"1,2",1,"JC, Heights",07306,5706,11,Heights,TBD,,,,3,1,2,9,,"$865,000","$899,000",$538.94,$538.94,5/27/2021,6/4/2021,10/8/2021,8,8,,10/9/2021,,,,"$6,450",2021,,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Central Ave and Oakland Ave,"Wake up to a bright airy day in this ultra-modern living space where the morning sunlight pours through the living room’s floor-to-ceiling windows providing a view of a lush outdoor space in place of the nosey neighbor. Walk across polished Select 5 ¼ inch flooring with pre-fabbed hickory to a brand new European contemporary state-of-the-art kitchen. Become the gourmet chef you always dreamed of with stainless steel smart appliances, incandescent quartz countertops, cabinets dressed in glossy white and a prep island that keeps you in constant contact with your guests in the living room as they enjoy the warmth of the infrared wall mounted fireplace with wireless capacity ensuring precise climate/ambience control to match any mood. A liquor bar counter replaces the outdated pantry of the 70s and leads you to a private study, laundry room with energy efficient washer/dryer. Prepare for a busy day ahead in lavatories drenched in pearl white Carrara marble, his and hers vanities, jacuzzi jets that will soothe all your troubles away. The spacious rooms including a master’s with a walk-in closet and barn door on guard sets up a restful night for the hardworking Professional in any light. A halo pendant chandelier illuminates a short stroll to the Rec room where a wet bar awaits with a wine cooler accompanying quartz counters, barn sink and ample space for entertaining. End your day by the fire pit, beautiful backyard with luscious green yard that pairs well with ruby fencing for the ultimate private getaway with which checks all the right marks for this Chateau disguised in Condominium attire! Also ask about the Tax Abatement."
260005391,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",1003 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,1630,1725,"$865,000",CONDO-COOP,,1st,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,1,2,6,,,"$865,000",$530.67,,3/26/2026,,,14,,,3/26/2026,,,,,,$351,,,,,,,,Bowers & Charles Street,"Brand-new construction 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence offering 1,630 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space with a private backyard—rare for new construction in The Heights. This boutique home was crafted for today’s urban lifestyle, blending modern luxury, functionality, and exceptional natural light. The open-concept layout features a chef’s kitchen with Bosch stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, custom designer cabinetry, and an oversized island ideal for both entertaining and everyday living. Wide-plank white oak hardwood floors run throughout, complemented by high ceilings and windows on three exposures, filling the home with sunlight. Additional highlights include in-unit LG washer and dryer, central air and forced-hot-air heating, and well-proportioned bedrooms with ample storage. The private backyard offers a true outdoor extension of the home—perfect for dining, gardening, or relaxing. Ideally located just one block from Central Avenue’s vibrant retail and dining corridor, with award-winning restaurants, cafes, and daily conveniences at your doorstep. Easy and direct access to NYC via bus, Light Rail, and nearby PATH connections. A rare opportunity to own a spacious, outdoor-enhanced new construction home in one of Jersey City’s most dynamic neighborhoods."
220016533,SOLD,"JC, Heights",119 SOUTH ST,Condominium,1672,5845,"$865,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02085,00028,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$865,000","$859,000",$517.34,$517.34,9/14/2022,11/7/2022,12/11/2022,54,54,,12/13/2022,,,,"$7,757",2021,$257,,Cash,,,,,,Central and Passaic,"Simply stunning, 3 bedroom/2.5 bathroom duplex with a private backyard and parking. Newly constructed only 2 years ago, this impeccable home offers over 1672 sq ft of living space and a landscaped, private yard. The main floor features an expansive living/dining area with a chef's kitchen complete with Quartz counters & breakfast bar, Carrara marble backsplash, SS appliances and plentiful cabinets. All three bedrooms are on the main floor with the primary bedroom offering a walk in closet & private balcony overlooking the yard. The en-suite bathroom has custom tile and an upgraded vanity. The lower level opens to a sprawling family room with custom built-ins and direct access to the backyard. The backyard is truly an urban oasis, offering privacy and space, with professional landscaping and a separate patio area. This floor also has an additional half bath and in-home laundry. The garage can be accessed from this level, where you will find a tandem parking spot and a private storage room. Ideally located in the center of the burgeoning Heights area of Jersey City,  just steps to parks, restaurants, shops and schools and providing easy excess to all forms of transportation with the bus to NYC on the corner and a short walk to the Light Rail station."
230013985,SOLD,"JC, Heights",19 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1465,6199,"$865,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,04402,00021,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$865,000","$839,000",$590.44,$590.44,8/21/2023,9/18/2023,10/20/2023,28,28,,10/23/2023,,,,"$10,047",,,,Conventional,,,,,,Sherman Ave & Central,"Situated in the heart of booming Jersey City Heights this 3 bedroom 2 bath condo offers a unique blend of contemporary design and comfort all with modern city living! Enjoy an open-concept layout that seamlessly integrates the naturally sunlit drenched living room with two skylights and cathedral ceiling creating a loft style feel, the dining area, and kitchen, all blending and creating a perfect space for entertaining and relaxation! The kitchen features Premium Samsung stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, waterfall center island with breakfast bar seating, and white subway tile backsplash. Spacious primary bedroom suite with walk-in closet, sliding doors to balcony, en-suite modern bath with a stand-up shower, porcelain tiles. Two additional good size bedrooms, complete with closets and a full bath with jacuzzi tub and shower. Central A/C and Heating System, double door entry foyer for added privacy, Hardwood Floors throughout, Washer/Dryer Room with premium large washer dryer as an added convenience, and a private roof deck great for entertaining and relaxation. Smart technology with Nest thermostat and keyless entry for seamless living and one tandem parking spot complete this home. Short block to Central Ave, close to all shops, the business district, restaurants, Pershing field park with tons of amenities, light rail and shuttle bus to JSQ PATH make this a commuter’s dream! A perfect place to call home, just move in and unpack!"
220005171,SOLD,"JC, Heights",36 PATERSON ST,Condominium,1720,1724,"$867,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,01506,00038,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$867,000","$875,000",$504.07,$504.07,3/25/2022,4/7/2022,5/16/2022,13,13,,6/9/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Central and Passaic,"New construction luxury at it's finest. Welcome home to 36 Paterson St, the epitome of luxury and convenience. Travel though your bright and airy living room boasting high ceilings and 4” #1 red oak hardwood floors into your own chef's kitchen with a bevy of amenities. This sleek and modern kitchen is equipped with plentiful custom Fabuwood Nexus Kitchen cabinets, White Carrara Quartz countertops, vented hood and a full suite of high end stainless steel Samsung appliances. The master en-suite boasts high ceilings ,an oversized Porcelanosa bathroom, and a large custom closet, and This home features two other bedrooms and one and a half baths providing ample space for all your needs. Continue downwards via the staircase to your own expansive rec room with a half bathroom that opens up to a gorgeous backyard, perfect for hosting or for your furry friends. Recessed lights though out the entire   condo, home entertainment wiring with 5.1 speakers,  Nest thermostat, and side by side garage parking completes the home. There are dedicated closets in the shared garage for extra storage. Just the pure luxury of this home will make it an enjoyable place to call home. Located minutes away fromWashington Park and less than a mile away from 9th street light rail. Should you want to travel to NYC this home is located just minutes away from the bus, light rail and all the transportation options making this the perfect address to call home."
210022606,SOLD,"JC, Heights",31 BLEECKER ST,Condominium,2485,1691,"$869,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,3,6,,"$869,000","$869,000",$349.70,$349.70,9/29/2021,10/12/2021,12/23/2021,13,13,,12/23/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave & Summit Ave,"Newer construction compliments classic style and modern finishes in this almost 2,500sq ft stunner in Jersey City Heights. Beautiful red brick gives great first impressions with soffits and exterior molding. The two story, three bedroom and three and a half bath home comes complete with backyard, close proximity to Central Ave, Washington Park and 9th St Light Rail, and rental parking nearby.  Grand foyer welcomes through double glass etched doors through to timeless crown molding, wide plank hardwood floors and wainscoting continuing throughout the main floor and upstairs living areas. Lofty open floorplan comes complete with stonework fireplace and mantle, bright white eat-in kitchen, and formal dining or living space. Features include waterfall quartz counters, tile backsplash, custom shaker cabinets, samsung refrigerator, and Bosch under-cabinet microwave.   Smarthome features include modern conveniences like security cameras and alarm system. Expansive bedrooms showcase not one, but two primary bedrooms, each with large ensuite bath, sliding double doors leading to the big backyard or oversized balcony, plus his and hers custom closets. Bathrooms boast double vanity, exquisite tile work, glass shower and separate soaker tub. Additional bedroom also includes ensuite bath, plus large windows for lots of natural light.    Huge balcony upstairs gives excellent views to the fully finished, low maintenance backyard complete with storage shed. Settled into Jersey City’s hottest neighborhood, the Heights is known for its vibrant community, eclectic artistic scene, excellent schools and easy NYC access. "
220001355,SOLD,"JC, Heights",185 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1700,1597,"$869,000",CONDO-COOP,,1+2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02205,00036,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$869,000","$874,000",$511.18,$511.18,1/20/2022,1/24/2022,3/24/2022,4,0,,3/24/2022,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers St. and South St.,"Impeccably designed and newly constructed with the highest level of craftsmanship, this spacious Three Bedroom Condominium leaves nothing to be desired. The overall atmosphere of the residence furnished with 5” red oak hardwood floors, recessed lighting and black metal hardware and fixtures throughout is serene and warm. This voluminous duplex residence boasts 1700sf of generous indoor living space, three uniquely designed bathrooms including a powder room, an in-garage tandem Parking Space and a second living room downstairs with a wall of glass doors leading out to a 400sf walled private backyard. The primary bedroom suite features an en-suite bathroom adorned with elegant tiles, a private balcony over looking the garden and a fully built-out walk-in closet. Each additional bedroom is in excellent proportions with ample closets. The stunning chef’s kitchen is equipped with custom two-tone cabinetries, Samsung stainless steel appliances, beautifully tiled backsplash and a peninsula with waterfall Quartz countertops. This stunning brand-new residence is further outfitted with Central AC, Nest Thermostat and Doorbell, washer and dryer, and Pella windows. Ideally located in the highly sought-after Jersey City Heights just a few blocks to cafes, restaurants, shops and services on Palisade Avenue and Central Avenue, Riverview Fisk Park and transportations to Manhattan, Hoboken, Journal Square and Downtown Jersey City ,this expertly constructed new condominium residence is not to be missed."
260005338,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",547 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1211,1724,"$869,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2305,28,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$869,000",$717.59,,3/26/2026,,,14,,,3/26/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,South & Bowers,"Welcome to Unit 2 at 547 Palisade Avenue, a beautifully appointed 1,211 sq ft open-concept home in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This modern residence features natural hardwood floors, abundant sunlight, and a layout designed for both comfort and versatility. The chef’s kitchen is equipped with Bosch and Samsung appliances, custom cabinetry, and a large island ideal for meal prep and entertaining. A private deck directly off the kitchen creates seamless indoor–outdoor living. The spacious primary bedroom offers flexibility rarely found in the Heights, with room for an office nook, reading lounge, or additional custom closet build-outs to suit your storage needs. Secondary bedrooms are well-sized with ample natural light and storage options. Located on highly desirable Palisade Avenue, this home places you moments from neighborhood cafés, boutiques, and the green spaces of Riverview-Fisk Park and Leonard Gordon Park. Commuting is effortless—just 0.2 miles to the 9th Street Light Rail, with bus routes steps away for quick access to Hoboken, Downtown Jersey City, and Manhattan."
230003246,SOLD,"JC, Heights",273 COLUMBIA AVE,Condominium,2382,1597,"$870,000",CONDO-COOP,,L/1/2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,9,,"$870,000","$875,000",$365.24,$365.24,2/28/2023,4/26/2023,7/17/2023,57,57,,7/17/2023,,,,,,$303,,Conventional,,,,,,Leonard St & North St,"Photos are of similar property! Estimated completion is 4/1/23.   Light streams in through the oversized Andersen windows illuminating the open floorplan with classic crown molding and gleaming hardwood flooring throughout. White eat-in kitchen shows style with waterfall quartz counters & backsplash, custom shaker cabinets, pot-filler, apron sink, black Samsung appliances and wine fridge. A tech-lover’s dream wired for plenty of mod cons, including smart doorbell, smart thermostat, camera, security system.   First unit *triplex* offers nearly 2400 sq ft and not one, but two lower level bonus rooms; one with wet bar, half bath and gorgeous sliding glass doors to the fully finished private backyard.   Bathrooms bring coveted upgrades like double-vanities, soaker tub with multi-system shower and niche, and glass shower. Primary ensuite hosts spacious built-out walk-in-closet for optimal storage and organization.   On a quiet tree-lined street of The Heights, and walking distance to JFK Blvd, Washington Park and 9th St Light Rail station, this neighborhood is known for great community, excellent schools and easy NYC access, all amid the eclectic and vibrant scene of Jersey City Heights.   "
230020919,SOLD,"JC, Heights",865 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,2200,1724,"$870,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,04303,00015,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,6,,"$870,000","$899,000",$395.45,$395.45,12/19/2023,12/29/2023,2/14/2024,10,10,,2/15/2024,,,,,,,TBD,Conventional,No,No,,,,Manhattan & Carlton Ave.,"Introducing a Stunning New Construction Condo in the Heart of Jersey City Heights. This newly constructed home, ideally located just a mere 5-minutes from the Journal Square PATH station, presents an exceptional living experience. From the moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and airy open layout that effortlessly combines modern elegance with comfort. The first level of this exquisite condo boasts a generously sized living room bathed in natural light, thanks to its floor-to-ceiling windows. These windows also provide access to a charming Juliet balcony, where you can savor the providing breathtaking scenery and stunning views of Pershing Field Park. The living room seamlessly flows into a modern kitchen equipped with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances and an abundance of sleek cabinetry, making it a culinary enthusiast's dream. Travel through the home where you'll discover two spacious bedrooms that offer both comfort and versatility. with one of the rooms providing access to your very own private backyard, perfect for entertaining or just relaxing. Travel upstairs to the 2nd level solely designed for the master bedroom. The master suite, a true retreat, provides a dedicated office/den space, large windows that flood the room with light, and a master bath that is elegantly designed with porcelain tiles, double vanity and illuminating/defog mirror creating a spa-like oasis within your own home. This charming unit offers both functionality and versatility with an expansive 814 square foot storage basement, providing ample space to cater to various needs. The basement boasts a full bathroom, adding to its convenience and potential. Beyond the exceptional features of this condo, its location is a true gem. Situated just 5 minutes away from the Journal Square PATH station, commuting to New York City or other destinations is a breeze. Moreover, the property is strategically positioned directly in front of Pershing Field Park, providing breathtaking scenery and stunning views of the iconic New York City skyline. For those seeking a vibrant neighborhood experience, simply take a short one-block stroll to Central Avenue, where you'll discover an array of restaurants, cultural attractions, and the bustling energy that defines this dynamic community. This new construction condo embodies the perfect blend of modern luxury, convenience, and urban living. Don't miss your opportunity to call this exceptional residence your own and experience the best of Jersey City Heights living. This property has a 5 year Tax Abatement- call JC tax assessor's office for more details."
220010980,SOLD,"JC, Heights",126 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1655,5845,"$870,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2E,"JC, Heights",07307,04503,00017,Heights,Hugo Lofts,,,,1,0,1,6,,"$870,000","$870,000",$525.68,$525.68,6/15/2022,8/8/2022,9/27/2022,54,54,,9/28/2022,,,,"$12,123",2022,$552,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton and Franklin,"Living where you love means coming home to this stylish, one-of-a-kind large loft residence at the Hugo Pronti Artist Loft. This former suitcase factory is located in one of the hottest neighborhoods in Jersey City. Living is easy in this impressive, generously-sized 1,655 square foot corner loft residence. Delight in the expansive living area graced by 13 foot original timber-beam ceiling with industrial-aged steel supports and enveloped in exposed brick walls. The home radiates warmth through it's hardwood flooring, gas fireplace, and tiled 21.5'x12.6' private terrace. There is a large primary sleeping area with an additional work area that can easily be transformed into a second bedroom. There are 7 massive windows approximately 5'x9' throughout this spacious residence, allowing natural light to flow from the east and south-west from morning to early evening. Be Awed by the design and layout of the home, and be WOWED by the 34'7 x 12'5 Sunroom which faces south, it is currently being used as an additional sitting area and guest quarters. The home comes with a private detached garage for a vehicle and an approximate 5'6 x 14'10 private storage space in the building's basement. This is a pet-friendly, 28-unit loft building with elevator, bike area, a laundry area, and a video entrance/security system. Transit options include: NYC Bus service located 2 blocks away on Palisade. Light Rail station accessible in about 8 minutes. Riverview Fisk Park within 3 blocks and has a host of recreational activities, playground, seasonal farmers market and expansive views of NYC and the Hudson River. (See floor plan and alternative floor plan to add bedrooms)."
210019273,SOLD,"JC, Heights",250 CAMBRIDGE AVE,Condominium,,1691,"$870,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3803,11,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$870,000","$855,000",,,1/15/2021,1/18/2021,8/12/2021,3,0,,8/13/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith & Hutton,"One of Jersey City's finest builders is at it again! With an estimate completion of Summer 2021, these two new construction condominiums will quarrel over nothing except which wide open layout offers the best flow, and whose oversized outdoor space should host the next summer barbecue. This duplex 3 bed 2.5 bath home will be beautifully finished with absolute thoughtfulness and top-notch quality. Main floor living and dining area layout flows into chef-inspired kitchens finished with white marble waterfall island, inlay farm sink, Fabuwood cabinets, Samsung stainless steel appliances, must-have wine fridge, kohler fixtures and modern pendant lighting. Master suite and additional bedrooms boast ceiling fans, Pella windows, and custom walk-in closets, while bathrooms host high-end porcelain tiles, modern vanities and multiple shower heads. You'll be able hear a pin drop in this ultra-peaceful atmosphere, thanks to the extra-thick soundproofing, subfloor and insulation. A tech-lovers dream with every mod con, finishes include home entertainment wiring with 5.1 speakers, Ring doorbell, camera and security system, central vacuum and Nest thermostat. Rec room to be completed with wet bar; backyard with outdoor speakers *and* fire pit! Steps from Riverview Fisk and Washington parks - as well as both 2nd St & 9th St Light Rail stations - this neighborhood is known for great schools and easy NYC access, all amid the eclectic and vibrant scene of Jersey City Heights. *Photos are of similar listing, different location*"
210022329,SOLD,"JC, Heights",580 LIBERTY AVE,Condominium,3118,6199,"$870,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,1,"JC, Heights",07307,00603,00012,Heights,,,,,4,0,4,10,,"$870,000","$859,000",$279.03,$279.03,9/24/2021,1/21/2022,3/28/2022,119,119,,3/29/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,North St and Leonard St,"Amazing opportunity to live in this brand new luxury 3118 sq. ft. 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath triplex located in the desirable Western Slope neighborhood in Jersey City Heights! Each gorgeous home features a sun drenched open concept floor plan, with a large living area, dining room and modern kitchen complete with quartz countertops and top-of-the-line Samsung appliances. You will fall in love with the large primary bedroom, complete with ensuite bath, enormous walk-in closet and private terrace that overlooks the tranquil backyard. There are two additional spacious bedrooms and a home office that is perfect for your private zoom meetings. Entertaining is a breeze in the large family room that leads to your gorgeous private backyard. Appointments include beautiful inlaid oak hardwood floors throughout, floor-to-ceiling Anderson windows, skylights, recessed LED lighting, high efficiency central heating and cooling and hookup for washer and dryer. Storage and space abound both inside and out of these well-designed homes. Garage parking for two cars. Buyers are eligible for 5-year tax abatement. 10 year limited home warranty provided by the developer. Close to Gordon Park with 5.7 acres, sports facilities, playground and dog run. 580 Liberty offers an easy commute to Port Authority, Penn Station, or downtown World Trade Center/ Financial district.  "
230001871,SOLD,"JC, Heights",204 BOWERS ST,Condominium,1923,1597,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$875,000","$875,000",$455.02,$455.02,2/2/2023,2/2/2023,3/3/2023,0,0,,3/5/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Milton Ave & Summit Ave,"Reputed builders, NKay Construction, do it again with these freshly renovated, modern, move-in ready homes in The Heights. Set on a beautiful tree-lined street, each spacious three bedroom layout comes with coveted private outdoor and EV charger non-tandem parking.    Stylish finishes and top-level craftsmanship shine with classic crown molding, rich hardwood floors and large Pella windows. Eat-in kitchens showcase sparkling waterfall quartz counters, farm sink, shaker cabinets, blue accent shiplap, and black Samsung appliances including pot filler and added wine fridge. Smarthome features include ring doorbell, camera and security system, and nest thermostat.   The downstairs duplex hosts a bonus room finished with wet bar, additional half bath and sliding glass doors leading to the private backyard finished with pavers and landscaping.  Bathrooms boast extras like beautiful blue double vanity, herringbone tile, glass shower with multi-spray system, matte black fixtures and smart mirrors.  All units have a dedicated utility area with Samsung washer and dryer, plus tandem EV charging garage tandem parking.  Newly refinished tan brick and grey paneled building is situated less than one block from Summit Ave, and equidistant to both Washington and Pershing Field Parks. Jersey City Heights is known for its great community, excellent schools and easy NYC access, with vibrant shops, restaurants and parks!"
220005634,SOLD,"JC, Heights",27 LEONARD ST,Condominium,1718,1713,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,00504,00012,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$875,000","$899,000",$509.31,$509.31,4/1/2022,4/29/2022,5/27/2022,28,28,,6/1/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Central and Summit,"Welcome to this luxurious 1700+ sq foot condo in the highly sought after Jersey City Heights! This 3 bed 2 bath condo is all new construction and features a beautiful and serene private backyard. The custom chef’s kitchen is complete with Bertazzoni appliances, quartz countertops with waterfall Moen faucet, European style frame less cabinets and 4 solid hardwood flooring. The open floor plan in the kitchen and bright spacious living room allow for great entertainment space. The beautifully updated bathroom boasts frameless shower doors and rain shower head as well as a double sink vanity. This unit features a modern design throughout, energy efficient full spray foam insulation, separate private entrance, additional private storage and parking spot in the attached garage! Plus, a central Vacuum system, Andersen windows, Rheem HVAC, sound dampening rubber member between floors for sound insulation. Don’t miss the opportunity to own this fabulous unit!"
230015325,SOLD,"JC, Heights",339 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1400,1597,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2A,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$875,000","$875,000",$625.00,$625.00,9/13/2023,9/27/2023,11/17/2023,14,14,,11/17/2023,,,,,,$260,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin and Ferry,"Rental parking available nearby!   Manhattan finishes and modern luxury are move-in ready in Jersey City Heights. No expense has been spared in these exquisite residences, where high-end finishes and top-of-the-line amenities await. Situated just one block away from the 2nd street lightrail station and stairs to Hoboken, and a mere two blocks from Riverview Fisk Park, you'll enjoy easy access to both The Heights and the vibrant neighborhood of Hoboken.  Step inside the three bed, two bath residences with warm hues emanating from the chestnut stained wide-plank oak flooring, high ceilings and large sliding glass doors seamlessly connecting your private outdoor space. The flowing floorplan culminates with the designer kitchen showcasing natural wood themes and a large, eat-in island with waterfall white quartz counters. Features include matte black and ribbed glass custom cabinetry, quartz tile backsplash, stainless Bertazzoni appliances plus built-in wine fridge and pull out microwave, and polished off with matte black fixtures and carefully curated white and gold pendant lighting. Step outside the oversized sliding glass doors to your own private oversized outdoor deck, ideal for everyday enjoyment or entertainment.   Modern upgrades throughout include built-in surround sound speakers and video entry. Bedrooms host stunning white wainscoting feature walls or exquisite gold foiled cherry blossom wallpaper for romantic detail. Bathroom design offers floor to ceiling tile with soaker tub and shower combo including disability access, or double vanity with smart mirrors, and glass shower with multi-system and marbled porcelain tile. Primary ensuite hosts a built-out walk-in closets while each unit includes a dedicated utility room with stacking LG washer and dryer.  This ground up, new construction brick building - built in 2022 - offers a secure entrance on a perfectly positioned tree-lined street in Jersey City Heights. This area is known for its excellent community, boutique restaurants and shops, excellent schools, great parks and easy NYC access."
240015355,SOLD,"JC, Heights",380 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1503,1597,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,4,0,3,7,,"$875,000","$875,000",$582.17,$582.17,8/6/2024,9/16/2024,11/18/2024,41,41,,12/2/2024,,,,,,$507,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"Find the ultimate contemporary urban living in the vibrant Heights neighborhood! This newly constructed 3-unit building boasts a secure entrance on a tree-lined street with access to surrounding Hoboken and NYC access.   This unit presents a two-story, 4 bed, 3 bath floorplan, with the separate floor primary ensuite giving access to a large private roof deck and breathtaking city views. This unit *also* includes basement storage!  Modern design and upgrades emanate throughout each home, with wide plank light oak floors and carefully curated lighting. White kitchens feature sleek quartz counters, tile backsplash, an eat-in island, sleek custom cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. Bathrooms bring luxury with floor-to-ceiling tile, shower and soaker tub options, sleek vanities and polished chrome fixtures. The dedicated utility/laundry room gives maximum flexibility and convenience in your daily routine, hosting stacking Samsung washer and dryer. Storage is maximized with excellent closet space, including large walk-ins in each primary ensuite.   Situated just one block from Riverview Fisk Park with breathtaking Manhattan views, and the Hoboken stairs leading to the 2nd Street Lightrail, this location is offers the ultimate urban luxury lifestyle. The Heights is known for its vibrant community, excellent parks and schools and easy access to NYC and surrounding neighborhoods."
240015356,SOLD,"JC, Heights",211 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1792,1597,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,2&3,2L,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,5,1,2,9,,"$875,000","$875,000",$488.28,$488.28,8/6/2024,8/15/2024,10/10/2024,9,9,,10/10/2024,,,,,,$377,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Griffith,"Set your sights on this stunning two-story home set on a sought-after block in Jersey City Heights. Combining classic design and modern amenities, the open floorplan is flooded with light illuminating the hardwood floors, neutral color palette and classic crown molding throughout. With five bedrooms, two and a half baths, and an additional bonus room, this home offers spacious living, sophistication and style.  The kitchen is a contemporary twist on a classic design, with waterfall quartz countertops and matching backsplash, custom Luna white and Indigo fabuwood cabinetry that stretches to the ceiling, complemented by exposed shelving. The space is completed with Samsung appliances, gold fixtures and fittings plus matte black pendant lights over the eat-in peninsula perfect for quick meals and easy gathering.  The primary ensuite is conveniently located on the first floor, and features a dark matte feature wall with elegant wainscoting plus a fully finished, oversized walk-in closet. Upstairs hosts a loft-style bonus room ideal for play, home office, gym or more, and also includes an ideally located utility closet with a stacking brand new Samsung washer and dryer. Bathrooms are equally impressive with elements like double vanities, porcelain tile showers with niches, multi-system fixtures, or hexagon-tiled floor.  Just steps from the Riverview Fisk Park with panoramic NYC views, and the Hoboken stairs and 2nd Street Light Rail, the location is absolutely impeccable. Jersey City Heights is known for its bespoke arts scene, excellent schools and parks, incredible community, and easy NYC access. "
240019562,SOLD,"JC, Heights",49 GRACE ST,Condominium,1654,1713,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,A,"JC, Heights",07307,802,6,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$875,000","$975,000",$529.02,$529.02,10/3/2024,12/11/2024,12/18/2024,69,69,,12/20/2024,,,,,,$340,,Cash,,,,,,Poplar St & Central Ave,"Discover modern urban living in this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom duplex with a private backyard, situated in the vibrant and sought-after Jersey City Heights neighborhood. This exquisite residence offers a seamless blend of sophistication and comfort. Meticulously designed, the spacious living area unfolds seamlessly, merging the living, dining, and kitchen spaces into an inviting expanse, ideal for both entertainment and relaxation. Three bedrooms bathed in natural light, provide ample space for personalized style. Contemporary fixtures and elegant tile work adorn the bathrooms, with full glass shower doors adding a touch of modernity and creating a spa-like feel. The condo's clever use of space and thoughtfully crafted floor plan optimizes the expansive layout, ensuring every inch is functional and aesthetically pleasing, equipped with sound dampening hardwood floors, Marvin windows, and a central vacuum system. The kitchen, a culinary haven, features Bertazzoni appliances, vented hood, built-in microwave and is graced with an island and quartz countertops, embodying the perfect fusion of style and functionality. Located in the thriving Jersey City Heights neighborhood, renowned for its diverse community, shops, cafes, and cultural attractions, this residence offers easy access to transportation, making New York City just a breezy commute away. A shining example of luxury and convenience in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Welcome home!"
220006001,SOLD,"JC, Heights",151-153 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1372,1419,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,301,"JC, Heights",07307,03804,00014,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,6,,"$875,000","$885,000",$637.76,$637.76,4/6/2022,4/18/2022,6/22/2022,12,12,,6/22/2022,,,,$0,2021,$213,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton St & Griffith St,"The Jersey City Heights gets even better with its newest addition, The Webster Flats! This 6 unit condominium building brings a new meaning to LIVE PLAY WORK  all within the comfort of your own home! This expansive space provides you with 3 large bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, soaring 10 ft ceilings, 1 private terrace, high end stainless steel appliances, Zephyr wine fridge, full sized WhirlPool washer/dryers, Resideo alarm system, Aiphone home intercom system, and the Honeywell Pro Series thermostat. The master bedroom includes a custom walk in closet as well as a double sink vanity in the bathroom. Entertainment becomes easy with your built in Sonos Ceiling speaker system prewired throughout the living room and master bedroom. Details like the solid oak hardwood floor in Herringbone pattern, Kohler fixtures, black and white tiled bathrooms, and highly efficient recessed lighting throughout all create a tranquil atmosphere for you to relax, work, and have fun, all at the same time. Your package is complete with a 10 year home warranty and a 5 year tax abatement to be filled with J.C. Visit www.TheWebsterFlats.com for more information."
