240021015,SOLD,"JC, Heights",84 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1940,1713,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,1$2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,3701,51,Heights,,,,,4,0,3,11,,"$875,000","$875,000",$451.03,$451.03,10/25/2024,11/2/2024,12/27/2024,8,8,,12/27/2024,,,,"$17,392",2024,$308,,Conventional,,,,,,Central and Summit,"Welcome to 84 Manhattan Ave #1, a truly exclusive residence in a boutique 3-unit condominium, ideally located in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This expansive 1,940 sq ft, 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home has been thoughtfully and meticulously designed, with every detail carefully crafted to offer an unparalleled living experience. High-end finishes and a sophisticated layout define this stunning residence.  At the heart of the home is the open Chef’s kitchen, a true standout that boasts quartz countertops, sleek custom cabinetry, and top-of-the-line Bertazzoni appliances. The kitchen’s refined design seamlessly integrates with the home’s elegant 5.25 wide plank oak flooring, creating a sense of warmth and style throughout the living spaces.  The spa-inspired bathrooms are designed to evoke tranquility, offering a serene retreat where luxury meets modern sophistication. With high-quality fixtures and chic finishes, they provide the perfect space for unwinding and relaxation.  One of the most distinctive features of this home is its spacious private backyard, one of the largest in Jersey City Heights. This rare outdoor space is ideal for entertaining, dining al fresco, or enjoying quiet moments of personal leisure. It provides a peaceful escape while being just steps away from all the conveniences of urban living.  Perfectly located near Pershing Field, Central Avenue’s vibrant shopping and dining scene, and with easy access to NYC transit, this home is the epitome of refined luxury, offering not only spacious living but also unmatched value in one of the most sought-after areas of Jersey City Heights. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly unique property in a premier neighborhood."
210024138,SOLD,"JC, Heights",25 WAVERLY ST,Condominium,1573,1691,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07306,,,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$875,000","$899,000",$556.26,$556.26,10/21/2021,11/3/2021,3/21/2022,13,13,,5/4/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Baldwin and Palisade,"Make yourself at home in this modern masterpiece. The newly finished luxury condo offers two floors, three bedrooms, plus coveted garage parking and private outdoor in Jersey City Heights.   Sunlight streams through oversized windows to showcase sophisticated style like matte black trim, fresh white oak hardwood floors and crown molding throughout. Contemporary eat-in kitchen offers sleek custom cabinets, waterfall quartz counters with seamless backsplash transition, plus stainless appliances and brushed nickel fixtures.  Main floor living hosts three bedrooms and two full baths, including the primary en-suite with double glass doors and balcony overlooking the private backyard. Beautifully designed bathroom features double vanity with smart mirrors, and glass shower with multihead system. Follow the gorgeous glass staircase downstairs to a beautiful bonus family room complete with wet bar and wine fridge, powder room and sliding glass door for access to the backyard as well. Private outdoor living space hosts brand new white fencing, fresh lawn and paver patio, perfect for entertainment or personal enjoyment.  Add to this the ultimate must-have of garage parking, and this home offers the best of urban luxury. Settled on a tree-lined street in a quiet corner of The Heights, owners enjoy walkability to nearby parks, community, boutiques, schools and NYC access."
210026512,SOLD,"JC, Heights",68 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1431,1691,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$875,000","$875,000",$611.46,$611.46,12/2/2021,12/13/2021,3/4/2022,11,11,,3/8/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton & Griffith,"Modern, bright and brand new remodeled luxury living awaits in the heart of the Heights. This three bedroom home is equipped with loads of square footage, plenty of private outdoor space, and highly coveted parking garage. Light floods through large windows to showcase modern design and thoughtful finishes with wide plank white oak floors, matte black windows and all the smart home upgrades you need. A gorgeous glass floating staircase is truly a show-stopping key feature, allowing both sophistication and open air concept.  Upstairs leads to your own full floor roofdeck with unobstructed 360 degree views of NYC and beyond for much-needed fresh air and friendly gathering space. Bright white kitchens shine with seamless marbled quartz backsplash, counters and waterfall island, plus sleek custom cabinets, and stainless appliances and hood. Primary en-suites boast balcony with sliding glass doors, plus walk-in closet. Each well-designed bathroom features double vanity with smart mirrors, plus features like oversized glass shower with multiple shower system, or porcelain tile finished to the wall and soaker tub.  Tandem garage parking is the cherry on top of this impeccably planned property. Set in a sweet spot of Jersey City Heights, owners enjoy walkability to essential shops, Riverview Fisk and Pershing Field parks, light rail and easy NYC access."
