240009906,SOLD,"JC, Heights",391 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1222,6199,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,5,503,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,Gallery Lofts,,,,2,0,2,6,,"$875,000","$899,000",$716.04,$716.04,5/23/2024,6/26/2024,7/29/2024,34,34,,7/31/2024,,,,"$10,100",2022,$530,,Cash,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"This impressive two-bedroom, two-bathroom layout offers spectacular views of The Greatest City in the World and the added convenience of dedicated parking. Designed with sophistication and elegance, the residence features timeless selections with a touch of European flair: Bertazzoni appliances, porcelain slab countertops, imported porcelain tile, Mittel Cucine cabinets from Italy, and Kohler fixtures. The unit also boasts a private outdoor space with stunning NYC views, providing a perfect blend of luxury and convenience in this modern masterpiece. Unit 503 is a proud part of Gallery Lofts, a building less than five years old, constructed with steel and concrete, and located in the blossoming Jersey City Heights"
240006647,SOLD,"JC, Heights",185 TERRACE AVE,Condominium,1898,1639,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02002,00011,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$875,000","$875,000",$461.01,$461.01,4/10/2024,4/20/2024,6/14/2024,10,10,,6/14/2024,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Thorne and Bleeker,"Experience urban sophistication in Jersey City Heights. Welcome to the pinnacle of contemporary living in this newly constructed residence. Spanning 1898 sq ft, across three floors, this trophy triplex home seamlessly combines spaciousness, elegance, and convenience while offering an ideal urban sanctuary for those craving a balanced lifestyle. Step inside to discover an expansive open concept living and dining area thoughtfully designed for modern comfort and entertaining. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring ample cabinetry, sleek quartz countertops, and premium stainless steel appliances. This stately home features three generously proportioned bedrooms. An oversized primary bedroom suite includes a full en suite bath and direct access to an additional 517 sqft living/recreational room floor, which walks out to the private backyard. Nestled in Jersey City Heights, this property offers the best of both worlds – easy access to the city center and a peaceful retreat from the urban hustle. With major highways like 1&9 and RT 3 just minutes away, commuting is effortless. Additionally, benefit from a 5-year tax abatement."
260005393,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",1003 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,1407,1725,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,2nd,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$875,000",$621.89,,3/26/2026,,,14,,,3/26/2026,,,,,,$303,,,,,,,,Bowers & Charles Street,"Brand-new construction 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence offering 1,407 square feet of thoughtfully designed open living space that leads out to your private 300 sqft deck—an exceptional feature rarely found in The Heights. This boutique home was designed for modern urban living, combining refined finishes, functional layout, and abundant natural light. The open-concept floor plan showcases a chef’s kitchen with Bosch stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, custom designer cabinetry, and generous prep and seating space—ideal for entertaining or everyday living. Wide-plank white oak hardwood floors flow throughout, complemented by high ceilings and windows on three exposures, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. Additional highlights include in-unit LG washer and dryer, central air and forced-hot-air heating, and spacious bedrooms with excellent storage. The private deck offers a true outdoor retreat—perfect for dining, lounging, and hosting—extending the living experience well beyond the interior. Ideally situated just one block from Central Avenue’s vibrant shopping and dining corridor, with award-winning restaurants, cafes, and everyday conveniences nearby. Easy access to NYC via bus, Light Rail, and nearby PATH connections makes commuting effortless. A rare opportunity to own a rooftop-level new construction home in one of Jersey City’s most sought-after neighborhoods."
