220003310,SOLD,"JC, Heights",126 CHARLES ST,Condominium,1573,1691,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$875,000","$875,000",$556.26,$556.26,2/25/2022,3/18/2022,5/4/2022,21,21,,5/4/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,JFK and Summit Ave,"Modern style plus magnificent design are move-in ready in The Heights! The newly finished luxury home offers flowing three bedroom layout, coveted garage parking and private roof on a tree-lined street walking distance to Summit Ave and surrounding parks.  The open glass stairwell grabs immediate attention as you walk into the light, bright and airy space aloft treetops in the urban landscape. Sunlight streams through oversized windows to showcase matte black trim, exotic hardwood floors and crown molding throughout. Contemporary kitchen open to large living and dining area with sleek white custom cabinets, waterfall quartz counters including oversized eat-in island, seamless transition backsplash and stainless appliances.  Spacious bedrooms offer plenty of closet space, with the primary en-suite featuring double glass doors to the private balcony. Beautifully designed bathrooms features elements like double vanity with smart mirrors, stunning porcelain tile and glass shower with multihead system.   Head upstairs to the full floor private rooftop with panoramic NYC and 360 degree views. Add to this the ultimate must-have of garage tandem parking, and this home offers the best of urban luxury.   Jersey City Heights is well known for its vibrant community, eclectic shops, walkability to nearby parks and easy NYC access"
210006689,SOLD,"JC, Heights",99 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,,1691,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3603,7,,,,,,3,0,4,7,,"$875,000","$899,000",,,3/21/2021,4/8/2021,7/19/2021,18,18,,7/20/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave & Sanford Pl,"Classic elegance and grandeur extend through these beautifully re-constructed condominiums in one of the sweetest spots of Jersey City Heights. Majestic ceilings and tall floor-to-ceiling trim and crown molding welcome in the top unit with three stories, three bedrooms, four full baths plus loft suite and private deck. Above the glass door foyer opens into a grand flowing living area plus kitchen with warm walnut hardwood floors, tall windows and luxurious crown molding throughout. The main floor back room offers entry onto the large private deck. Upstairs hosts two beautiful bedrooms including master suite and laundry landing, then onward to the added loft space and extra bath above. Bathrooms relax with classically neutral tones and floor-to-ceiling marbled porcelain tile.   The stylish street view shows beautiful dark grey siding and classic white gable cornice settled into the tree-lined residential street. Sherman Place is walking distance to Central Avenue with essential shops and vibrant community, as well as Riverview Fisk Park with sports facilities, play areas, walking paths and excellent NYC skyline vistas."
210022388,SOLD,"JC, Heights",46 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1,5069,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,01505,00051,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$875,000","$850,000","$875,000.00","$875,000.00",9/27/2021,10/27/2021,12/24/2021,30,30,,12/12/2021,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Central Ave --> Jersey City,"Incredible New Construction development built by one of Jersey City's most renowned builders, to be completed in October 2021. This beautifully architected home has immaculate attention to detail, craftsmanship and design, and offers an expansive open-concept living space. The marble waterfall island flows into a Chefs kitchen that includes premium stainless appliances and wine cooler with thoughtful arrangement for both entertainment and functionality. Unit includes 3 bedrooms and 2 baths with dedicated 2 car garage parking and private rooftop entertaining/leisure space. Master Bedroom has vaulted ceilings with custom walk in closets and tremendous natural light. Bathrooms include modern fixtures and vanity as well as multiple shower head showers lined with porcelain tiles. Rooftop includes gas and water hook up. Photos are of similar listing, different location."
210002161,SOLD,"JC, Heights",65 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1362,6199,"$875,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03802,00007,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$875,000","$849,000",$642.44,$642.44,1/25/2021,4/14/2021,6/3/2021,79,79,,6/4/2021,,,,,,$225,2021,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"Featuring another Signature Luxury brand new construction by Blue Chip Living from the pages of Architectural Digest to the heart of booming Jersey City Heights a business district, residential area and transportation hub. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath duplex has a modern open living space with 10’ ceilings and oversized Pella windows that flood the space with natural light. Impeccable white high-gloss European Style cabinetry, stainless steel premium appliances, modern porcelain backsplash, central island featuring a waterfall quartz countertop and drawer microwave with Ambient LED under-mounted lighting. The Master bedroom includes an en suite spa–like bathroom with matte black hardware, floating double vanity with Ambient LED lighting and an expansive walk–in closet. The master suite has 8‘ x 8’ glass sliding doors leading out to a full width large balcony. Two generous bedrooms share a second bathroom featuring modern Carrara Porcelain slab tile, double vanity and soaking tub. Lower Level features a Family Room, Powder room and Wet Bar to allow for easy entertainment and leads to a private, beautifully landscaped backyard. Other perks include West Elm light fixtures, laundry room hook ups, central/heat/air, 7’ solid-core doors, 1 tandem garage parking. Full smart technology home creates ease of living with Google Nest thermostat, August Smart Lock, Google Nest Doorbell, Lutron Caseta Wireless Smart Lighting Dimmer Switch, My Q Smart Garage door with Amazon Key, all integrated via a Google Nest Hub all in one display and accessible via smart phones. The Property is located close to Congress St Light Rail, major highways, ferry, and PATH station. Make this your Dream Home Oasis today! *Eligible for 5 year tax"
250015895,SOLD,"JC, Heights",31 RAVINE AVE,Condominium,1657,6078,"$878,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,05009,00001,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$878,000","$898,000",$529.87,$529.87,8/4/2025,9/16/2025,10/27/2025,43,43,,10/27/2025,,,,"$14,618",'24,$617,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Ferry St & Booraem Ave,"Luxury Living in the Heart of Jersey City Heights — Welcome to 31 Ravine Avenue. Set in one of Jersey City's most sought-after neighborhoods, The Ravine Avenue Condo Collection delivers the perfect blend of modern luxury, thoughtful design, and everyday functionality. This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence boasts a stylish open layout, high-end finishes, and rare perks that are hard to find in the Heights. Step into your chef’s kitchen featuring custom waterfall quartz countertops, a sleek breakfast bar, rich shaker-style cabinetry, a glass tile backsplash, and a full suite of stainless steel appliances — all designed to impress and built to perform. Downstairs, enjoy the versatility of a spacious duplex-level family room, perfect for movie nights, a home office, or playroom setup. The private landscaped backyard offers a tranquil outdoor retreat for relaxing or entertaining. Additional highlights include garage parking, modern bathrooms with designer finishes, and easy access to parks, shops, dining, and transportation to NYC. This is more than a home — it’s a lifestyle upgrade in the hottest part of Jersey City. Come see what sets this space apart."
220005579,SOLD,"JC, Heights",294 GRIFFITH ST,Condominium,1900,1623,"$879,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,3403,45,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,10,,"$879,000","$879,000",$462.63,$462.63,3/31/2022,5/12/2022,9/20/2022,42,42,,9/20/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,JFK & Milton Ave,"Welcome to 294 Griffith St! Don’t wait to get into this brand new luxury condominium in Jersey City Heights! This new construction condo offers 2 floors of living, 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths, one garage parking space with electric vehicle charging stations, and a large family room leading out to a beautiful backyard. The open floor layout boasts 10 ft ceilings and floor-to-ceiling windows that will drench the living areas with sunlight all day. You’ll appreciate plenty of cabinet space in your state-of-the-art kitchen, with Samsung stainless steel appliances, and a quartz countertop. Features include in-unit laundry, Hardwood floors, stylish designer tiles, recess lighting, pantry closet, custom trim, and modern fixtures. The Master bedroom offers a large walk-in closet, a master bathroom with a double sink vanity, and a sizable private balcony overlooking your backyard. The lower level features a summer kitchen and family room that leads out to your backyard where you can enjoy entertaining on those warm summer nights. Conveniently located right off JFK Blvd and only two blocks from Central Ave for an easy commute to NYC and access to shopping, restaurants, schools, and daycare. The developer is open to allowing owners to choose their finishes and the property is eligible for a 5-year tax abatement."
260004942,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",99 THORNE ST,Condominium,1621,6541,"$879,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,C3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,,"$879,000",$542.26,,3/20/2026,,,20,,,3/20/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Summit and JFK,"Fully renovation beautiful and spacious three 3b/2b unit located in desirable Jersey City Heights. This sunlit top-floor residence offering 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths with elegant double vanities, and a private rooftop deck with sweeping skyline views. Extra storage room available in the basement. Outfitted with brand new Viking stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, hardwood floors, and in-unit laundry, this home seamlessly blends luxury and convenience. Located on a peaceful street with easy access to NYC-bound buses and shoppings."
260001482,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",3447 JOHN F KENNEDY BLVD,Condominium,1429,1597,"$879,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,2602,19,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,8,,,"$879,000",$615.12,,1/28/2026,,,71,,,1/28/2026,,,,$0,,,,,No,No,No,,,Bowers St and Lincoln St,"NYC Views direct from unit plus a massive private rooftop for this home! Four brand new construction homes in prime Jersey City Heights location. 3447 JFK Blvd are exclusive residences featuring modern design, high-end finishes, and open-concept layouts. The living room is anchored by a sleek linear fireplace, flanked by custom built-in shelving with warm wood accents.  Wide-plank hardwood loots, oversized windows, and designer lighting fixtures flood the space with natural light.  The chef’s kitchen boasts custom cabinetry, stone backsplash, stainless-steel appliances, gas range, wine fridge and a quartz waterfall island.  Spa-inspired bathrooms include floating vanities, designer tile, and walk-in showers with custom niches.  Every home offers a spacious primary suite with large private patio, perfect for indoor-outdoor living.  Units 3 and 4 include private rooftop terraces with breathtaking NYC skyline views. 1 storage space included.   Ideally located near shopping, dining, transportation, and all the conveniences of city living.  Whether you’re upgrading your lifestyle or making a smart investment, this is luxury that delivers value."
210025621,SOLD,"JC, Heights",53 PROSPECT ST,Condominium,1614,1691,"$880,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$880,000","$875,000",$545.23,$545.23,11/15/2021,12/31/2021,3/31/2022,46,46,,4/9/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Palisade Ave & Central Ave,"Perfectly positioned top floor unit with full private roof deck is newly finished by one of Jersey City's top builders. Spacious and stylish three bed and two bath layout showcases high-end finishes and modern style expected with Nkay Construction.   Wide open floorplan offers hardwood flooring throughout, ceiling fans, Pella windows, and custom walk-in closets. No expense was spared in the chef-inspired kitchen with sparkling quartz waterfall counters, stainless steel apron sink, Fabuwood cabinets, Samsung stainless appliances including must-have wine fridge, Kohler fixtures and modern pendant lighting. A tech-lover’s dream with every mod con, including ring doorbell, camera and security system, central vacuum and nest thermostat.  Blocks from Pershing Field Park and walking distance to 2nd St Light Rail station - this neighborhood is known for great community, excellent schools and easy NYC access, all amid the eclectic and vibrant scene of Jersey City Heights."
210026986,SOLD,"JC, Heights",83 WAVERLY ST,Condominium,1480,5745,"$880,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,H,"JC, Heights",07306,,,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$880,000","$879,000",$594.59,$594.59,12/11/2021,2/1/2022,8/14/2022,52,52,,8/22/2022,,,,,,,,Cash,No,No,No,,,Oakland and Central,"Million dollar view from your aproximately 1142 sq. ft. ROOFTOP DECK. Eco friendly/environmentally sustainable new construction condo. Located on a quiet street in the booming Heights section of Jersey City. This spectacular modern condo boasts an open Floor plan, 9 ft. ceilings and ceiling to floor windows. Let the sun shine in! The kitchen is the heart of the home and this one is every chef’s dream. stainless steel appliances, subway tile backsplash and stone countertops. 2 bedroom and 2 full baths. Help your wallet and the environment with high efficiency insulation on the interior of all exterior walls and the roof, triple pane windows, high efficiency multi-zone heating & cooling system with programmable thermostats, high efficiency LED lighting, EnergyStar rated white roof and a vegetated “green” roof, water conserving dual flush toilets and a rain water harvesting and recycling system used for flushing toilets. Enjoy the peace & quiet provided by sound attenuating insulation on the interior wall partitions while you work from home, read or just relax in your Kohler deep soaking tub. Low or non-toxic building materials were used for construction and approximately 90% of all construction was diverted from landfill & recycled materials. This spectacular condo is located just blocks from whatever you need - from the many activities at Pershing Field Park to shopping, farmer’s markets, schools, public transportation and much more. Enjoy the old and new eateries from cafes & pubs to 5 star restaurants. This unit is approximately 1480 sq. ft. complete with outdoor space, indoor parking with electric vehicle charging station, bicycle & stroller storage. Close proximity to Journal Square, Hoboken and Downtown Jersey City. Washer/ Dryer hookup in unit. 1 covered parking space included. Come see for yourself. Photos are Virtually Staged, finishes are subject to change. Construction will be complete approximately 1/31/2022."
260005392,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",1003 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,1581,1725,"$880,000",CONDO-COOP,,3rd,3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$880,000",$556.61,,3/26/2026,,,14,,,3/26/2026,,,,,,$340,,,,,,,,Bowers & Charles Street,"Brand-new construction 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence offering 1,581 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space, crowned by a private rooftop deck—an exceptional feature rarely found in The Heights. This boutique home was designed for modern urban living, combining refined finishes, functional layout, and abundant natural light. The open-concept floor plan showcases a chef’s kitchen with Bosch stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, custom designer cabinetry, and generous prep and seating space—ideal for entertaining or everyday living. Wide-plank white oak hardwood floors flow throughout, complemented by high ceilings and windows on three exposures, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. Additional highlights include in-unit LG washer and dryer, central air and forced-hot-air heating, and spacious bedrooms with excellent storage. The private roof deck offers a true outdoor retreat—perfect for dining, lounging, and hosting—extending the living experience well beyond the interior. Ideally situated just one block from Central Avenue’s vibrant shopping and dining corridor, with award-winning restaurants, cafes, and everyday conveniences nearby. Easy access to NYC via bus, Light Rail, and nearby PATH connections makes commuting effortless. A rare opportunity to own a rooftop-level new construction home in one of Jersey City’s most sought-after neighborhoods."
240013312,SOLD,"JC, Heights",97 NORTH ST,Condominium,1700,1499,"$882,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,01505,00024,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$882,000","$999,000",$518.82,$518.82,7/10/2024,9/23/2024,11/1/2024,75,75,,11/1/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,,,,,Summit & Central,"Are you ready to enjoy your Private Roof Deck, “New Construction on a spectacular tree lined block. This amazing high quality 3 bed, 2 bath condo features wide open layout offers the best flow this top floor 3 bed 2 bath home beautifully finished with absolute thoughtfulness and top-notch quality. Main floor living and dining area layout flows into chef-inspired kitchens stainless steel appliances, must-have wine fridge, Kohler fixtures and modern pendant lighting. Master suite has a private terrace Pella windows, sliding door and custom walk-in closets, while bathrooms host high-end tiles, double sinks modern vanities you’ll not be able hear a pin drop in this ultra-peaceful atmosphere, thanks to the extra-thick soundproofing, subfloor and insulation, this unit also comes with your own private roof deck with NYC views, sink, water, gas, electric, plenty of space for grill and furniture sets, ideal for entertaining or relaxing on your own while enjoying This home is around the corner from the Light rail, Hoboken, and NJ transit bus to Manhattan. Everything you need in the perfect spot of Jersey City Heights!"
230009101,SOLD,"JC, Heights",197 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1302,6494,"$883,500",CONDO-COOP,,2,2A,"JC, Heights",07307,03805,00021,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$883,500","$899,000",$678.57,$678.57,6/2/2023,9/14/2023,11/17/2023,104,104,,11/19/2023,,,,,,$233,,Conventional,,,,,,Corner of Hutton St.,"Welcome home to this beautiful and bright 3BR/2 BA newly renovated condo in one of the most rapidly growing areas of Jersey City. Modern, elegant features mix with warm, rich finishes to create a space that is brimming with high-contrast urban chic.  The spectacular layout, with both a corner living room and primary bedroom, allows for a flood of natural light from Eastern, Western, and Southern exposures. Wide-plank white oak floors and oversized windows add to the open and airy feel of this loft-style unit.  Custom designed kitchen by Kuche-Cucina boasts sleek Samsung black stainless steel appliances and waterfall quartz countertops.  Unwind for the night in your spacious primary bedroom with private balcony and walk-in closet. Luxuriate in your en-suite spa-like bath enveloped in woodsy warm tones with double vanities and a porcelain tiled rainfall shower.  1 assigned parking spot and 221sf private storage room included.  Just a short walk to spectacular Riverview-Fisk Park and some of the Heights' hottest spots like Corto, The Franklin, Bread and Salt, Fox and Crow, Choc au Pain and more. Be a part of the most exciting growth in Jersey City!"
230014682,SOLD,"JC, Heights",45 BOORAEM AVE,Condominium,1420,6199,"$885,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,05005,00009,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$885,000","$899,000",$623.24,$623.24,9/5/2023,2/23/2024,7/17/2024,171,171,,7/19/2024,,,,,,$250,,Conventional,,,,,,Palisade Ave,"Gorgeous, NEW, and Ideally located in the heart of the Jersey City Heights.    Beautiful, Modern, and Stylish with quality design and craftsmanship. This residence makes a strong first impression welcoming you with soaring ceilings, a wide-open floor plan, exposed brick, and bay windows. The versatile space provides options for laying out furniture and creating rooms that work for you.   The very large open concept kitchen is both an elegant showpiece and a welcoming are to gather with family and friends. The kitchen is custom designed to exude a sleek, upscale look and feel, while offering comfort and functionality. A hard-to-find separate dining room space is appreciated by those who like to entertain. Perfect for your next dinner party!   Primary bedroom featuring a terrace, walk in closet, and a large bathroom check all the boxes. Two well sized guest bedrooms, a stylish guest bathroom, and great closet space complete this home.   True hardwood flooring all throughout, excellent natural light, floor to ceiling tiled baths, attractive fixtures and lighting.   Bike and Stroller room on the ground level plus a Personal Private Storage Room.   Location, Location, Location! Walk to coffee shops, restaurants and grocery store. Easy breezy transportation into NYC, Hoboken, JSQ, and Downtown JC.       "
240003309,SOLD,"JC, Heights",337 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1400,5069,"$885,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,4504,31,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,6,,"$885,000","$899,000",$632.14,$632.14,2/21/2024,6/3/2024,7/8/2024,103,103,,7/9/2024,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Ferry St and Franklin St,"Presenting 337 Palisade Ave Unit 3, Palisade Ave's newest New Construction Luxury Condo. This 3 Bedroom, 3 Bathroom residence offers quality, high end interior design all located conveniently to transportation, Jersey City Restaurants and Riverview Fisk Park.       Your first floor enters to an open concept Living / Dining Room and Kitchen area. Your kitchen includes top line panel ready appliances, custom natural tone cabinetry, custom quartz countertops and waterfall island, designer pendant lights, pantry and plenty of storage space. Completing your first floor is a full bath and bedroom / office.   Your second floor offers Main Bedroom which is filled with natural light and complete privacy. Complete with true custom walk in closet, your main bathroom offers double sink / vanity, matte black top of line shower fixtures and rainfall shower head.   Second floor is complete with 2 additional bedrooms and full bathroom. This home is perfectly fit for entertaining with your oversized rooftop with NYC and Jersey City views.  Property comes with 5 Year Tax Abatement and 10 Year warranty."
240004290,SOLD,"JC, Heights",60 PATERSON ST,Condominium,1500,5069,"$885,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,1403,18,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$885,000","$899,000",$590.00,$590.00,3/7/2024,4/8/2024,5/17/2024,32,32,,5/18/2024,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit ave and Pierce ave,"Presenting 60 Paterson Unit B, a Brand-New Luxury Duplex. This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom residence offers quality, smart home capabilities and the perfect blend between Modern and Dark / Natural tones.  Your first floor enters to an open concept Living / Dining Room and Kitchen. Your kitchen includes top line appliances, custom two-tone cabinetry, custom quartz countertops / backsplash and dark wood island accent, designer pendant lights all framed by oversized Andersen windows, letting in plenty of natural light while providing maximum privacy.  Your Main Bedroom is filled with natural light through your triple wide Andersen Window. Complete with custom closets, your main bathroom offers double sink / vanity, matte black top of line shower fixtures and rainfall shower head. Main floor is complete with 2 additional bedrooms, full bathroom and Laundry. Your Private Full Length Rooftop is perfectly fit for entertaining, stainless steel outdoor kitchen with pizza oven / sink and grill, outdoor lighting, trex flooring and turf section adding the perfect greenery to your outdoor space. Garage features non-tandem parking. Property comes with 5 Year Tax Abatement and 10 Year warranty."
250016696,SOLD,"JC, Heights",28 BEACON AVE,Condominium,1301,5069,"$885,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07306,5903,29,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$885,000","$890,000",$680.25,$680.25,8/14/2025,9/1/2025,11/7/2025,18,18,,11/7/2025,,,,$0,,$216,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Palisade Ave and Baldwin Ave,"Seller to contribute $10k towards closing costs! --- Nestled in the highly sought-after Jersey City Heights neighborhood, this completely reimagined and meticulously redesigned boutique building offers three exceptional units that seamlessly blend elevated luxury with modern convenience—including one year of pre-paid parking, just a one-minute walk away.   This sun-drenched 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence features refined finishes and thoughtful design. The timeless red brick façade, complemented by bold black accents, delivers standout curb appeal. Inside, high ceilings, white oak flooring, recessed lighting, and floor-to-ceiling windows create a bright and airy living space.   At the heart of the home, the chef’s kitchen makes a bold statement with sleek two-tone cabinetry, quartz waterfall countertops and full-height backsplash, pot filler, and a suite of top-of-the-line smart Samsung appliances. Sleek finishes and thoughtful design make the space as functional as it is beautiful -- perfect for both everyday cooking and effortless entertaining.   The primary suite features double closets and a spa-inspired en-suite bath with double vanities, designer fixtures, and a high-end smart toilet. Step out onto your private balcony and enjoy the tranquil setting—perfect for morning coffee or an evening drink—your personal escape from the bustle of city life. Two additional bedrooms provide flexibility for children, guests, or a home office, served by a stylish full bathroom.   Walk up to your private roof deck and begin your day with a quiet cup of coffee as the city stirs awake below. More than just outdoor space, this is your personal sanctuary in the sky. Let your child—or furry little ones—roam freely in the fresh air, host weekend brunches or sunset BBQs with friends, or simply unwind with a glass of wine and a good book as the skyline glows at dusk. With panoramic views of the Empire State Building, Midtown Manhattan, Downtown Jersey City, and Journal Square, this expansive rooftop retreat sets the stage for elevated living—from sunrise to starry nights.  Engineered for energy efficiency and modern comfort, the home includes spray foam insulation, Andersen high-performance windows, and a full fire sprinkler system. Smart home features include a Honeywell thermostat, Ring doorbell, keyless entry, and Wi-Fi–enabled appliances throughout. A dedicated private storage room on the lower level provides space for bikes, strollers, and any other storage needs.   Commuting to NYC is effortless—take the NJ-119 bus directly to Midtown Manhattan; hop on a Citibike or NJ-83 bus to Journal Square PATH or simply enjoy a 15-minute walk to the station. The neighborhood is alive and amazing with many local favorites—restaurants, cafes, shops—and beloved parks like Pershing Field, offering walking trails, multiple sports fields, playgrounds, an ice rink, and a seasonal heated pool.  Opportunities likes this are rare--schedule your private showing!!"
220005024,SOLD,"JC, Heights",151-153 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1562,1419,"$885,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,202,"JC, Heights",07307,03804,00014,,,,,,3,0,3,6,,"$885,000","$885,000",$566.58,$566.58,3/23/2022,4/18/2022,5/6/2022,26,26,,6/14/2022,,,,$0,2021,$216,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton St. & Griffith St.,"Welcome home to The Webster Flats! This 6 unit ground up new construction condominium building brings a new meaning to simple elegance! This expansive space provides you with 3 large bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms (2 master suits, one with its own private terrace), soaring 10 ft ceilings, high end stainless steel appliances, full sized WhirlPool washer/dryers, Resideo alarm system, Aiphone home intercom system, and the Honeywell Pro Series thermostat. The primary bedroom includes a custom walk in closet as well as a large custom bathroom, and private terrace. Entertainment becomes easy with your built in Sonos Ceiling speaker system prewired throughout the living room and master bedroom. Details like the solid oak hardwood floor in Herringbone pattern, Kohler fixtures, black and white tiled bathrooms, and highly efficient recessed lighting throughout all create a tranquil atmosphere for you to relax, work, and have fun, all at the same time. Welcome home to The Webster Flats! This 6 unit ground up new construction condominium building brings a new meaning to LIVE PLAY WORK  all within the comfort of your own home! This expansive space provides you with 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, soaring 10 ft ceilings, backyard space, high end stainless steel appliances, full sized WhirlPool washer/dryers, Resideo alarm system, Aiphone home intercom system, and the Honeywell Pro Series thermostat. Entertainment becomes easy with your built in Sonos Ceiling speaker system prewired throughout the living room and primary bedroom. The enormous multi purpose space in the front of the home provides you with ample room for an office, art studio/gallery, creative space, at home business, workshop, boutique, or an expansive living space! Details like the solid oak hardwood floor in Herringbone pattern, Kohler fixtures, black and white tiled bathrooms, and highly efficient recessed lighting throughout all create a tranquil atmosphere for you to relax, live, work, and have fun, all at the same time. Parking is in the next door gated and monitored lot. The Jersey City Heights gets even better with its newest addition, this package is complete with a 10 year new home warranty and a 5 year tax abatement to be filed with JC.  Visit www.TheWebsterFlats.com for more information. Please also check out unit 101 (1,711 sqft) priced at $899,000 that comes with designated work/commercial space!"
210009671,SOLD,"JC, Heights",11 CAMBRIDGE AVE,Condominium,,1691,"$885,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,3803,11,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$885,000","$899,000",,,4/23/2021,4/23/2021,10/1/2021,0,0,,10/4/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"One of Jersey City's finest builders is at it again! With an estimate completion of Summer 2021, these two new construction condominiums will quarrel over nothing except which wide open layout offers the best flow, and whose oversized outdoor space should host the next summer barbecue. This duplex 3 bed 2.5 bath home will be beautifully finished with absolute thoughtfulness and top-notch quality. Main floor living and dining area layout flows into chef-inspired kitchens finished with white marble waterfall island, inlay farm sink, Fabuwood cabinets, Samsung stainless steel appliances, must-have wine fridge, kohler fixtures and modern pendant lighting. Master suite and additional bedrooms boast ceiling fans, Pella windows, and custom walk-in closets, while bathrooms host high-end porcelain tiles, modern vanities and multiple shower heads. You'll be able hear a pin drop in this ultra-peaceful atmosphere, thanks to the extra-thick soundproofing, subfloor and insulation. A tech-lovers dream with every mod con, finishes include home entertainment wiring with 5.1 speakers, Ring doorbell, camera and security system, central vacuum and Nest thermostat. Rec room to be completed with wet bar; backyard with outdoor speakers *and* fire pit! Steps from Riverview Fisk and Washington parks - as well as both 2nd St & 9th St Light Rail stations - this neighborhood is known for great schools and easy NYC access, all amid the eclectic and vibrant scene of Jersey City Heights. *Photos are of similar listing, different location*"
210000128,SOLD,"JC, Heights",142 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1798,1707,"$885,500",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02904,00038,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$885,500","$875,000",$492.49,$492.49,1/4/2021,1/19/2021,3/1/2021,15,15,,3/1/2021,,,,,,$263,,Conventional,,,,,,*,"New Construction in an spectacular tree lined location.  This amazing high quality 3 bed, 2.5 bath condo features: 1798 square foot of living space with deeded 2 car parking and private back yard space (gas-water-electric connections), kitchen containing quartz counter tops with waterfall island and Samsung black stainless steel appliances, wine fridge, Kohler plumbing fixtures, custom closets, high end finishes including crown moldings, central vacuum system, sprinkler system thru the entire home, aluminum railings, low voltage system (security camera, burglar alarm, video door bell, 5.1 channel home theater), elevated framing materials used for improved insulation and sound proof penetration and much more! *10 years builders warranty & 5 year tax abatement included. Very close to NY transportation (bus & rail), shopping, restaurants, parks, schools and much more! Will not last....come take a look!"
260005335,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",545 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1650,1724,"$889,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02305,00029,Heights,,,,,4,0,3,10,,,"$889,000",$538.79,,3/26/2026,,,14,,,3/26/2026,,,,,,$529,,,,,,,,South St. & Bowers,"This beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom, with bonus studio, duplex residence offers a one-of-a-kind opportunity for the new owner to generate income while living in a luxury new construction by renting out either the upstairs or downstairs part of the home. With a prime location across from Riverview Park, located on the coveted Palisade Ave of Jersey City, this condo offers the convenience of nearby shopping, dining, and public transportation, making it an ideal choice for those who value accessibility. Buyers can customize the unit layout and some finishing options. Additional entertainment space with a separate entrance above the garage can be deeded to the unit for an additional cost.  The open floor plan and abundant natural light complemented by the solid 5 wide hardwood oak flooring throughout, and 8-foot solid wood doors creates a sense of grandeur. This home offers a contemporary design and high-end finishes that are sure to impress. Custom kitchen cabinets designed with both style and functionality in mind, provide ample storage space and a sleek, modern look. Chic and ornate fixtures atop premium Calcutta quartz counter tops. State-of-the-art stainless steel appliances complete the modern kitchen. Each bathroom, layered with elegant Porcelanosa tiles, creating a spa-like retreat within your own home. Buyer's can choose from their preferred choice of tiles for a limited time.   *photos include the other units to showcase other finishing options*"
260002500,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",131 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1800,6685,"$889,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,3601,3,,,,,,3,0,3,6,,,"$889,000",$493.89,,2/12/2026,,,56,,,2/12/2026,,,,"$12,457",2025,$150,,,,,,,,kennedy Blvd & Central Ave,"Beautifully designed 1,800 sq ft duplex unit built in 2021, spanning the entire first and second floors of a modern condo home in desirable Jersey City Heights. The first floor features a spacious, versatile open area perfect as a playroom, home office, guest room, or creative space, complete with a convenient half bathroom and direct access to a private backyard—ideal for relaxing or entertaining. Upstairs, enjoy a bright, open-concept kitchen, living, and dining area with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, hardwood floors, and soaring ceilings. Three generously sized bedrooms and two full bathrooms complete the upper level, including a serene primary suite with en-suite bath and ample closet space. Additional highlights include in-unit washer/dryer, central heating and cooling, and one tandem garage parking spot. The building is shared with only one other unit, providing privacy and a quiet environment. Located near parks, schools, shopping, dining, and NYC transit options. Tenant pays gas and electricity."
260003409,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",3447 JOHN F KENNEDY BLVD,Condominium,1429,1597,"$889,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,4,"JC, Heights",07307,2602,19,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,8,,,"$889,000",$622.11,,2/27/2026,,,41,,,2/27/2026,,,,$0,,,,,No,No,No,,,Bowers St and Lincoln St,"NYC Views direct from unit plus a massive private rooftop with direct views for this home! Four brand new construction homes in prime Jersey City Heights location. 3447 JFK Blvd are exclusive residences featuring modern design, high-end finishes, and open-concept layouts. The living room is anchored by a sleek linear fireplace, flanked by custom built-in shelving with warm wood accents.  Wide-plank hardwood loots, oversized windows, and designer lighting fixtures flood the space with natural light.  The chef’s kitchen boasts custom cabinetry, stone backsplash, stainless-steel appliances, gas range, wine fridge and a quartz waterfall island.  Spa-inspired bathrooms include floating vanities, designer tile, and walk-in showers with custom niches.  Every home offers a spacious primary suite with large private patio, perfect for indoor-outdoor living.  Units 3 and 4 include private rooftop terraces with breathtaking NYC skyline views. 1 storage space included. Ideally located near shopping, dining, transportation, and all the conveniences of city living.  Whether you’re upgrading your lifestyle or making a smart investment, this is luxury that delivers value."
220011284,SOLD,"JC, Heights",580 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1098,1692,"$890,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,501,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,The Riveview,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$890,000","$890,000",$810.56,$810.56,1/1/2022,1/30/2022,6/9/2022,29,0,,6/20/2022,,,,,,$343,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress and South,"Step inside and immediately feel at ease in this unit. BRAND NEW GROUND UP CONSTRUCTION at The Riverview offers impeccable comfort and convenience, situated on Palisade Avenue, at the heart of the neighborhood’s exciting retail/dining corridor. Choose from two- and three-bedroom residences in this intimate 13-unit building, crafted to meet your every need. The well-proportioned units are carefully constructed with today’s most in-demand elements. Flow-through rooms and thoughtful appointments combine for luxurious comfort. Expansive energy-efficient insulated windows frame the interiors with abundant natural light. Elegant top-line finishes include wide plank flooring, granite countertops and premium Fischer-Paykel appliances. Thoughtfully curated amenities bring ease to today’s busy lifestyles. A package room, 12-car parking garage with electric chargers and ground-level bike storage are among the building’s many essential comforts designed to enhance your lifestyle. Make this inspired collection of pet-friendly condominiums home. 10-year New Home Warranty, Manufacturer’s Warranty on all appliances and systems, and tax abatement. Photos are of model unit."
220010222,SOLD,"JC, Heights",254 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,2333,1568,"$890,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02302,00013,,,,,,3,0,3,8,,"$890,000","$886,900",$381.48,$381.48,6/6/2022,6/22/2022,8/29/2022,16,16,,8/29/2022,,,,"$9,504",2021,$304,,Conventional,No,No,,,,South and Congress,"Price Improvement to $886,900! 2,333 Square Feet of Living PLUS Private Yard, Balcony, Large Bonus Room and Parking for 2 Cars!   Spacious, open, and impeccably maintained 3 bedroom, 3 FULL bath home with 2 floors of living. Large , open kitchen with granite and stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet storage space, built-in sidebar and room for formal dining. Open living room with Juliet balcony. Master bedroom suite with master bathroom, walk-in closet and private balcony. 2 additional nice bedrooms with great closet space. Enjoy all of the extras!!!! Huge Bonus Room, Yard & Garage! Spacious bonus room is large enough to use as a family room with a fitness area. It is complete with a full bathroom and extra closets to also work as a guest/nanny suite. Beautiful, serene,  & private yard that is the perfect spot for a relaxing day in the shade or summertime entertaining! Hardwood floors, washer/dryer and large garage with extra storage. Driveway/Garage/Backyard are deeded to unit 1 alone, and not shared.List of property improvements are attached."
240006654,SOLD,"JC, Heights",146 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1400,1603,"$890,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,00011,04504,,,,,,2,1,2,4,,"$890,000","$899,000",$635.71,$635.71,4/10/2024,4/19/2024,6/10/2024,9,9,,6/10/2024,,,,"$16,740",,$200,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Ferry,"Ultra private 2 bed, 3 bath two-story home in the coveted Riverview Arts neighborhood of Jersey City Heights, mere blocks from the steps to Hoboken and the 2nd Street Light Rail, restaurants and businesses on Franklin Street and Palisade and Central Avenues, and beautiful Riverview Park. This stunning residence boasts a separate entrance, a 600 SQ FT PRIVATE 2 car garage with 4 storage closets, and a 625+ sq ft EXCLUSIVE backyard featuring patio pavers as well as green space, creating a secluded oasis in the middle of an exciting neighborhood. The first floor is built for entertaining and makes indoor/outdoor hosting a breeze. The spacious kitchen boasts gorgeous Lusso Cuccia cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, quartz waterfall countertops, and a tasteful tile backsplash. Lovely porcelain tile runs throughout this floor and a half bath completes this thoughtfully designed interior space. Right off the kitchen, double doors open up to your private backyard where you can grill, lounge, or entertain. Back inside and up the beautiful staircase you’ll find a spacious living room with white crown molding, oak hardwood floors, and rounded wall corners. This floor features two bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and in-unit laundry. The second bedroom is perfect for a guest room, nursery, or office. The primary is home to a large walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom. Additional features include high ceilings throughout, video intercoms, WiFi EcoBee thermostats, Anderson windows, GE Gallery and Sharp appliances, porcelain tile and oak hardwood floors. Close to The Franklin, The Alps (brand new wine bar), LoFi, Choc O Pain Bakery & Cafe, Froth on Franklin, Alessio’s Cafe, Green Pear Heights, and opening soon: La Milpa. Come enjoy all the Heights has to offer. Welcome home!"
240007253,SOLD,"JC, Heights",89 IRVING ST,Condominium,1373,6199,"$890,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,704,24,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$890,000","$899,000",$648.22,$648.22,4/18/2024,5/15/2024,8/20/2024,27,27,,8/22/2024,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,JFK and Nelson,"Nestled within the vibrant Jersey City Heights neighborhood, this spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo with parking boasts an unparalleled blend of modern elegance and comfortable living.  Upon entering discover an open-concept layout, with the living room and dining room seamlessly flowing and filled with natural light from the wall of windows creating a bright atmosphere perfect to entertain. The sleek and contemporary kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, equipped with stainless steel appliances, a quartz waterfall center island, ample storage, and stylish finishes. Retreat to the private quarters, where three generously sized bedrooms offer serene sanctuaries for rest and rejuvenation along with two modern baths. The master suite boasts a luxurious en-suite bathroom, providing a spa-like oasis with a stand-up shower, to unwind after a long day. Ascend to the rooftop deck and experience the perfect setting for al fresco dining, morning yoga sessions, or simply soaking in the breathtaking vistas. Additional highlights of this beautiful residence include hardwood floors, and in-unit laundry for added convenience. Conveniently located in Jersey City Heights, residents enjoy easy access to an array of trendy restaurants, shops, parks, and transportation options, ensuring a vibrant urban lifestyle. Eligible for 5 year tax abatement and special interest rate program 5.875% with no PMI and 5% down! Schedule your private tour today and discover the epitome of modern city living!"
230000118,SOLD,"JC, Heights",46 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1925,1597,"$890,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & 3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$890,000","$890,000",$462.34,$462.34,1/4/2023,1/27/2023,3/20/2023,23,23,,3/24/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Sherman Ave & Central Ave,"French townhouse meets fully upgraded dreamhome with this newly renovated home including private rooftop one block from Central Avenue and Pershing Field Park. The extra-wide building size allows for added spaciousness in the two-story, three bedroom plus loft layout. Rental parking has also been secured just two blocks away!  Country chic elements inspire throughout like white oak hardwood floors, exposed wood and metal banister stairwell and light airy design. Open floorplan kitchen boasts waterfall quartz counters, modern white and matte gray custom cabinetry, pennytile backsplash, gold fixtures and exposed accent shelves. Sliding barn doors reveal a centrally located laundry area for convenience.  Stunning matte black wainscotting accent wall adds drama to the dreamy primary ensuite. Ultra-stylish bathrooms showcase herringbone tile, double vanity, sophisticated black tile shower with gold accents. Upstairs loft space boasts exposed beams and vaulted ceilings, plus access to the private 782 sqft rooftop with surrounding city views.   This fully restored home hosts a wrap-around porch on a tree-lined street for excellent curb appeal, all in the heart of Jersey City Heights. The Heights is known for its excellent shops and boutiques, eclectic vibe and community, expansive parks and easy Hoboken and NYC access."
260004901,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",104 POPLAR ST,Condominium,1310,6270,"$890,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$890,000",$679.39,,3/19/2026,,,21,,,3/19/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Nelson Ave and JFK BLVD,"Move right into this stunning condo! Featuring three bedrooms, two baths, parking for two cars, wide crown molding, hardwood floors, custom kitchen and an island with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and a wine cooler. Gorgeous spa-like baths with multi jets and shower sprays. Pella transom windows for generous natural light, tankless hot water system, central vacuum, camera security and video intercom door bell. Private 750 square foot rooftop terrace with sound speakers, electric, water and gas line increasing your outdoor enjoyment and eastern NYC view and mountain vistas to the west. Located in JC Heights on a residential city street and low HOA. Conveniently close to NYC transportation, bus to Journal Square PATH or a stroll through the park to the Light Rail Station."
250019676,SOLD,"JC, Heights",642 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1633,1623,"$893,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,4,"JC, Heights",07307,01703,00057,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$893,000","$899,000",$546.85,$546.85,9/23/2025,11/14/2025,1/16/2026,52,52,,1/19/2026,,,,"$13,380",23,$540,25,Conventional,,,,,,Congress & Paterson Plank,"Welcome to the penthouse at 642 Palisade Ave, a spacious 1,633 sq. ft. 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in a boutique condo building with a dedicated parking spot. Perched on the top floor, this residence offers sweeping views of the Manhattan skyline and the Hudson River, providing a striking backdrop for everyday living.  The open and airy layout is designed to maximize light and space, with modern finishes that blend comfort and style. In addition to the generous living space, this home includes a full-size private parking spot and basement storage, adding convenience and practicality that’s rare to find.  Jersey City Heights is a diverse, traditional neighborhood situated atop the New Jersey Palisades, known for its hilly terrain, historic Victorian homes, a bustling Central Avenue shopping district and scenic views of the Manhattan skyline. It offers a small-town community feel with local parks, a variety of businesses, and an arts district.  Unit 4 combines the exclusivity of penthouse living with the warmth of a close-knit neighborhood, the perfect blend of city energy and community charm. Located just a short stroll to the 9th Street/Congress Street Light Rail Station, elevator to Hoboken and River View Fisk Park."
230008476,SOLD,"JC, Heights",35 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,2060,1597,"$894,800",CONDO-COOP,,2&R,2,"JC, Heights",07307,01504,00013,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,5,,"$894,800","$875,000",$434.37,$434.37,5/23/2023,5/23/2023,5/23/2023,0,0,,5/23/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Milton Ave & Summit Ave,"Reputed builders, NKay Construction, do it again with these freshly renovated, modern, move-in ready homes in The Heights. Set on a beautiful tree-lined street, each spacious three bedroom layout comes with coveted private outdoor and EV charger non-tandem parking.    Stylish finishes and top-level craftsmanship shine with classic crown molding, rich hardwood floors and large Pella windows. Eat-in kitchens showcase sparkling waterfall quartz counters, farm sink, shaker cabinets, blue accent shiplap, and black Samsung appliances including pot filler and added wine fridge. Smarthome features include ring doorbell, camera and security system, and nest thermostat.   Upstairs units includes full-size private rooftop with incredible cityscape views.   Bathrooms boast extras like beautiful blue double vanity, herringbone tile, glass shower with multi-spray system, matte black fixtures and smart mirrors.  All units have a dedicated utility area with Samsung washer and dryer, plus tandem EV charging garage tandem parking.  Newly refinished tan brick and grey paneled building is situated less than one block from Summit Ave, and equidistant to both Washington and Pershing Field Parks. Jersey City Heights is known for its great community, excellent schools and easy NYC access, with vibrant shops, restaurants and parks!"
240019105,SOLD,"JC, Heights",104 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1734,1724,"$895,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03404,00030,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$895,000","$949,000",$516.15,$516.15,9/26/2024,10/10/2024,11/6/2024,14,14,,11/19/2024,,,,$0,2024,$275,2024,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave. & Kennedy Blvd.,"Builder is also offering a 1% credit to buyer for closing costs / rate buydown / remodel on this chic new construction duplex offering 3 large bedrooms, 2 ½ baths, private back yard, and uncommon side-by-side garage parking (not tandem) in the desirable Jersey City Heights. This south-facing home is bathed with natural sunlight. luxurious design features highlighted by 5'' wide solid plank oak hardwood flooring throughout its spacious 1,730+ square feet of open layout. 10-foot ceilings, 8-foot custom doors, and sliding glass balcony and patio door to a private backyard provide you with a home that's both warm and welcoming.  The home is equipped with all the modern amenities including in-unit laundry, central AC, and heat/ The chef's kitchen is equipped with a hidden vented hood, high-end stainless steel appliances wrapped in ceiling-high custom cabinetry draped in white Calcutta quartz countertops, and backsplash. Custom closets and ample storage make everyday living comfortable. The ground floor family room with a wet bar makes entertaining a breeze.  Available EV charging facilities, 5-year tax abatement, and a 10-year builder's warranty ensure peace of mind with your investment. Contact to schedule a private tour and take the first step towards securing your bright, new home today.  "
220004173,SOLD,"JC, Heights",198 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1696,1691,"$895,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$895,000","$899,000",$527.71,$527.71,3/10/2022,3/16/2022,4/29/2022,6,6,,5/17/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers & South St,"High ceilings, high windows and high-end finishes illuminate this newly finished dreamhome in Jersey City Heights. Complete with radiant hardwood floors, crown molding and carefully curated design, this three bedroom home includes coveted garage parking and plentiful private outdoor for the ultimate lifestyle upgrade.  Two-story layout provides traditional floorplan on main floor. Head downstairs to the additional bonus room with half bath and sliding glass door entrance to the beautiful backyard with lawn, pavers and white fence.  Modern and stylish eat-in kitchens offer striking black quartz waterfall counters with seamless backsplash transition, contrasting custom white cabinets, pendant lighting and top-of-the-line stainless appliances including hood. Primary en-suite features double glass doors to private balcony, while bathrooms feature double vanity with smart mirrors, and glass shower with multihead system.  To top it off, this home offers access to the coveted garage for tandem parking. Walking distance to both Washington Park with sports facilities, dog run, playgrounds and walking trails, and Central Avenue for essential shops and vibrant community, this home offers the best of urban living. Settled on a tree-lined street in a quiet corner of The Heights, this neighborhood is known for its walkability to nearby parks, boutiques, schools and NYC access."
230009333,SOLD,"JC, Heights",110 CARLTON AVE,Condominium,1650,1724,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,04203,00026,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$899,000","$899,000",$544.85,$544.85,6/6/2023,7/17/2023,8/30/2023,41,41,,8/30/2023,,,,,,$205,,Conventional,No,No,,,,JFK and Liberty Ave,"Welcome home to this remarkable new construction luxury oversized condo nestled in the prestigious Jersey City Heights neighborhood. This extraordinary 1650 sq ft home offers a truly unparalleled living experience with features such as a private rooftop equipped with Bluetooth speakers and water/gas connections providing a secluded outdoor oasis. This expansive space is perfect for entertaining guests, hosting gatherings, or simply relaxing in the fresh air. Travel downstairs where you'll be immediately captivated by the spacious and thoughtfully designed open layout. The exquisitely designed kitchen features top-of-the-line Samsung stainless steel appliances, soft-close cabinets and quartz countertops/backsplash. Travel through the home to find three generously sized bedrooms and one office, each bedroom offers large closets and motorized ceiling fans. The spacious master suite offers a full bathroom adorned with beautifully large Brooklyn porcelain tiles, and  the large walk-in closet provides ample storage. The master bedroom also boasts access to a private 500 sq ft deck overlooking the backyard. The attention to detail extends throughout the residence with solid wood European doors, Grade one 4-inch hardwood floors and custom tile art. A full-size Samsung washer and dryer is also included to ensure the utmost convenience and efficiency for your laundry needs. Immerse yourself in an immersive audio experience with surround sound Bluetooth speakers installed throughout the home. Additionally, the inclusion of a built-in central vacuum system adds a touch of modern convenience, simplifying your cleaning routine. Other features included 8K HDMI, LAN and central cooling/heating. The shared garage features 1 side by side parking spot and a 60 amp car charger port installed, allowing for easy electric vehicle charging. Situated in the desirable Jersey City Heights, this new construction luxury condo offers an unparalleled living experience. With its sophisticated design, high-end finishes, and array of impressive features.**5 year Tax abatement"
