260005736,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",42 GRACE ST,Condominium,1450,6638,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,,"$899,000",$620.00,,4/1/2026,,,8,,,4/1/2026,,,,"$9,950",,,,,,,,,,Central Ave. & Leonard St.,"Just Listed in Prime Jersey City Heights w. the largest private roof deck on market! Experience elevated living in this newer construction 3-bedroom, 2-bath full floor condo located just off scenic Washington Park in the heart of Jersey City Heights. The home features a complete private rooftop deck  and 1 car garage parking NON-Tandem! With sleek porcelain pavers and built-in surround sound—perfect for relaxing or entertaining with skyline views. The chef’s kitchen features timeless white shaker cabinets, Frigidaire Gallery appliances, a wine fridge, and quartz countertops. Designer bathrooms are outfitted with Italian tile, vessel vanities, handheld fixtures, and rain shower heads. Additional perks include custom built-out closets, in-unit security features, and surround sound in both the living room and rooftop. With its prime location off Central Avenue and refined timeless design, this Jersey City gem offers the ideal blend of luxury and convenience. Special rates and grant programs offered through preferred lender - inquire for details."
260002882,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",81-83 HUTTON ST,Condominium,1251,1597,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,203,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,2,0,2,5,,,"$899,000",$718.63,,2/19/2026,,,22,,,3/18/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Cambridge & Central,"Welcome to Everton House. A nine-residence elevator building in Jersey City Heights, distinguished by curtain-wall glass imported from Spain, creating light-filled interiors with sweeping views of New York City. Everton House offers two, three, and four-bedroom residences, with select homes featuring private outdoor spaces and all residents enjoying access to a shared rooftop. Interiors are defined by dramatic ceiling heights and thoughtfully considered layouts. Kitchens are outfitted with JennAir appliances, including signature Black Obsidian interiors and a built-in coffee system. Primary bathrooms feature radiant heated floors, delivering a refined, spa-like experience. Additional amenities include garage parking with EV charging, a Swiftlane smart entry system, and a dedicated mail and package room designed for modern convenience.  Renderings showcase select units and are for illustration only; actual unit details may vary."
240023319,SOLD,"JC, Heights",294 PATERSON PLANK RD,Condominium,0,1713,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,1703,25,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$899,000","$899,000",,,12/5/2024,12/12/2024,2/5/2025,7,7,,2/7/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Paterson Plank and Ogden,"Welcome to the epitome of modern urban living in Jersey City Heights! Nestled in the sought-after Ogden Ave, this 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom duplex boasts a private outdoor space and parking, defining the perfect oasis in the heart of the vibrant community. Meticulously designed, the spacious living area unfolds seamlessly, merging the living, dining, and kitchen spaces into an inviting expanse, ideal for both entertainment and relaxation. Four large bedrooms bathed in natural light, provide ample space for personalized style. Contemporary fixtures and elegant tile work adorn the bathrooms, adding a touch of modernity and creating a spa-like feel. The condo's clever use of space and thoughtfully crafted floor plan optimizes the expansive layout, ensuring every inch is functional and aesthetically pleasing. The kitchen, a culinary haven, features stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops, embodying the perfect fusion of style and functionality.  Located in the thriving Jersey City Heights neighborhood, renowned for its diverse community, shops, cafes, and cultural attractions, this residence offers easy access to transportation, making New York City just a breezy commute away. A shining example of luxury and convenience in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Welcome home!"
250000663,SOLD,"JC, Heights",35 PATERSON ST,Condominium,2050,6706,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,2/3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,1507,4,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,8,,"$899,000","$899,000",$438.54,$438.54,1/10/2025,1/20/2025,2/21/2025,10,10,,2/24/2025,,"$387,600",2023,,2023,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Passaic and Central Avenue,"Welcome to 35 Paterson St LLC, unit 2 this 4 bedroom 2.5 bathrooms, is a duplex style home boasting approximately 2050 sqft of living space. This unit provides ample space throughout both floors. Floor 1 of unit 2 welcomes you into an open layout where the living room, dining room, and kitchen all meet. Enjoy an open floorplan along with a chef grade kitchen, two-toned cabinets, quartz counter tops, and waterfall design along with quartz backsplash design. The appliances are Samsung stainless steel with smart fridge and smart gas stove. The living room has coffered ceiling design and wainscoting wall design. This floor also has a half bathroom perfect for when entertaining guest. Floor 2 of unit 2 has 4 bedrooms along with 2 full bathrooms. This floor also contains a family room with cathedral ceilings drenched in natural lighting. The master bedroom has a chic master bathroom, visualize floor to ceiling ceramic tile design along with a double vanity sink, neighboring a walk-in closet. Enjoy some fresh air in your balcony right off of your master bedroom. This unit has its own private roof top with stunning city views. Features include Hardwood floors, custom trim, recess lighting, chic designer tiles throughout, coat closet, in unit laundry, and modern fixtures. Steps away from restaurants on Central Ave, close to NYC transportation, parks, houses of worship and schools."
220000031,SOLD,"JC, Heights",68 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1696,1691,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$899,000","$899,000",$530.07,$530.07,1/2/2022,2/3/2022,5/6/2022,32,32,,5/6/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton & Griffith,"Modern, bright and brand new remodeled luxury living awaits in the heart of the Heights. This three bedroom home is equipped with loads of square footage, plenty of private outdoor space, and highly coveted parking garage. Light floods through large windows to showcase modern design and thoughtful finishes with wide plank white oak floors, matte black windows and all the smart home upgrades you need. A gorgeous glass floating staircase is truly a show-stopping key feature, allowing both sophistication and open air concept.  In this downstairs duplex, the lower floor hosts a bonus room with wet bar and half bath, plus double sliding door access to the fully finished backyard, ideal for entertainment or added living. Bright white kitchens shine with seamless marbled quartz backsplash, counters and waterfall island, plus sleek custom cabinets, and stainless appliances and hood. Primary en-suites boast balcony with sliding glass doors, plus walk-in closet. Each well-designed bathroom features double vanity with smart mirrors, plus features like oversized glass shower with multiple shower system, or porcelain tile finished to the wall and soaker tub.  Tandem garage parking is the cherry on top of this impeccably planned property. Set in a sweet spot of Jersey City Heights, owners enjoy walkability to essential shops, Riverview Fisk and Pershing Field parks, light rail and easy NYC access."
240018026,SOLD,"JC, Heights",414 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1307,6078,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,A,"JC, Heights",07307,1704,34,,,,,,3,0,2,5,,"$899,000","$899,000",$687.83,$687.83,9/12/2024,10/9/2024,11/15/2024,27,27,,11/19/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,North and Congress,"Discover unparalleled elegance and modern living at 414 New York Ave, a premier collection of 4 luxury condominiums, in a brand-new construction boutique building, on a tree-lined street, in the heart of vibrant Jersey City. Stunning Unit A, features 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offering sleek contemporary design and high-end finishes throughout. Enjoy a spacious open-concept layout with expansive floor-to-ceiling windows that bathe the home in natural light throughout the day. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, showcasing premium CAFE stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, brass fixtures and exquisite quartz countertops. Residents will appreciate the upscale amenities, including private backyard and private storage. Located in a thriving neighborhood with easy access to dining, shopping, parks and public transit, this condo offers the perfect blend of luxury and convenience. Experience the epitome of refined urban living at 414 New York Ave."
220008914,SOLD,"JC, Heights",126 CHARLES ST,Condominium,1573,1691,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$899,000","$875,000",$571.52,$571.52,5/18/2022,5/16/2022,5/16/2022,0,0,,5/18/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,JFK and Summit Ave,"Modern style plus magnificent design are move-in ready in The Heights! The newly finished luxury home offers flowing three bedroom layout, coveted garage parking and private roof on a tree-lined street walking distance to Summit Ave and surrounding parks.  The open glass stairwell grabs immediate attention as you walk into the light, bright and airy space aloft treetops in the urban landscape. Sunlight streams through oversized windows to showcase matte black trim, exotic hardwood floors and crown molding throughout. Contemporary kitchen open to large living and dining area with sleek white custom cabinets, waterfall quartz counters including oversized eat-in island, seamless transition backsplash and stainless appliances.  Spacious bedrooms offer plenty of closet space, with the primary en-suite featuring double glass doors to the private balcony. Beautifully designed bathrooms features elements like double vanity with smart mirrors, stunning porcelain tile and glass shower with multihead system.   Head upstairs to the full floor private rooftop with panoramic NYC and 360 degree views. Add to this the ultimate must-have of garage tandem parking, and this home offers the best of urban luxury.   Jersey City Heights is well known for its vibrant community, eclectic shops, walkability to nearby parks and easy NYC access"
230000121,SOLD,"JC, Heights",71 RESERVOIR AVE,Condominium,1849,1597,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$899,000","$899,000",$486.21,$486.21,1/4/2023,1/4/2023,1/4/2023,0,0,,1/4/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Lienau & Baldwin,"Brand new construction beckons with this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home including private backyard and EV charger garage parking in Jersey City Heights. Oversized windows illuminate the timeless style with red oak hardwood floors and crown molding, plus modern upgrades and smart home capabilities.  Spacious eat-in kitchen gleams with large island, white quartz counters and shaker cabinets, herringbone backsplash, stainless farm sink and appliances, including a coveted wine fridge. Shared garage parking with must-have EV charging ports adds the proverbial cherry on top.  Spacious bedrooms showcase plenty of natural light, with ample storage including a built-out walk-in ensuite closet. Beautifully finished bathrooms include floor to ceiling tile, including accent walls, glass showers, and vanities plus medicine cabinets for added convenience.  Settled on a tree-lined street just off Pershing Field Park and Reservoir, this home is perfectly poised for access to extended outdoor space, and key points of urban living. Easily access Central Avenue with surrounding shops and boutiques, 2nd Street Light Rail Station, and easy NYC access."
210008278,SOLD,"JC, Heights",238 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,,1691,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,3803,11,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$899,000","$899,000",,,4/8/2021,4/8/2021,9/10/2021,0,0,,9/10/2021,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith & Hutton,"One of Jersey City's finest builders is at it again! With an estimate completion of Summer 2021, these two new construction condominiums will quarrel over nothing except which wide open layout offers the best flow, and whose oversized outdoor space should host the next summer barbecue. This duplex 3 bed 2.5 bath home will be beautifully finished with absolute thoughtfulness and top-notch quality. Main floor living and dining area layout flows into chef-inspired kitchens finished with white marble waterfall island, inlay farm sink, Fabuwood cabinets, Samsung stainless steel appliances, must-have wine fridge, kohler fixtures and modern pendant lighting. Master suite and additional bedrooms boast ceiling fans, Pella windows, and custom walk-in closets, while bathrooms host high-end porcelain tiles, modern vanities and multiple shower heads. You'll be able hear a pin drop in this ultra-peaceful atmosphere, thanks to the extra-thick soundproofing, subfloor and insulation. A tech-lovers dream with every mod con, finishes include home entertainment wiring with 5.1 speakers, Ring doorbell, camera and security system, central vacuum and Nest thermostat. Rec room to be completed with wet bar; backyard with outdoor speakers *and* fire pit! Steps from Riverview Fisk and Washington parks - as well as both 2nd St & 9th St Light Rail stations - this neighborhood is known for great schools and easy NYC access, all amid the eclectic and vibrant scene of Jersey City Heights. *Photos are of similar listing, different location*"
260003613,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",974 SUMMIT AVE,Condominium,1898,1725,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,4th,406,"JC, Heights",07307,2801,5.01,Heights,Lincoln Manor,,,,3,0,3,7,,,"$899,000",$473.66,,3/3/2026,,,37,,,3/3/2026,,,,"$20,648",2025,$725,,,,,,,,Corner of Summit Ave and Lincoln St.,"RARE: Sun-drenched corner triplex in elevator building. On-site deeded parking included.   At 1900 sq ft, this stunning home has 3 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, open plan dining and living, separate den, generous storage on all floors including a walk in closet, and windows on three sides. Features include hardwood floors, central A/C with smart vents, quartz countertops, high end GE Cafe appliances (including smart tech induction vented range with Wi-Fi cooking access), MOEN disposal, tankless water heater, and vented washer/dryer.   Shared roof deck with sweeping 360 degree views of New York City, exercise room with Peloton bike, ButterflyMX smart intercom, and more. One deeded parking spot included. Smart home features include Yale smart locks, Nest thermostat. Verizon FiOS ready.   Located on the corner of Summit and Lincoln, Lincoln Manor is one block away from Central Avenue's shopping and dining. Close to several parks and steps away from NYC buses. Must see!"
260003159,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",160 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,1350,5069,"$899,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,4903,3,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$899,000",$665.93,,2/24/2026,,,44,,,2/24/2026,,,,$0,,,,,No,No,Yes,,,Prospect and Reservoir,"Seller offering up to 2 years of fenced in parking at 156 Central Ave!  Welcome to 160 Central Ave Unit 2, a premier high-end new construction condo from NKAY Developers in the heart of Jersey City Heights, conveniently located across from Pershing Field Park. This second floor unit features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, balcony, and secure rental parking just 2 doors down. Sleek kitchen is designed with top of the line stainless steel Bosch appliances including dual zone wine fridge, quartz waterfall counters and backsplash, oversized stainless steel sink, two-tone custom cabinetry, pot filler, stylish gold hardware and fixtures, and high-end pendant lighting. West facing living and dining room are complete with a fireplace framed with custom millwork, oversized Andersen windows, and a large closet under the stairs for additional storage. Main bedroom suite faces east and offers ample natural light from the sliding glass door to the balcony. The bedroom boasts a custom millwork accent wall with dual pendant lighting, and walk-in closet with high-end custom built-in shelving and cabinets. Ensuite bathroom offers an oversized double vanity, floor-to-ceiling large format tiles, dramatic warm accent lighting, and a top of the line waterfall shower, complete with sprayer and jets. Each of the additional 2 bedrooms feature high end custom built-in closets. Washer/dryer in unit add to the convenience of the home.  The home is equipped with a smart doorbell, keyless entry, Legrand smart dimmers, and energy-efficient Nest thermostats. The exterior facade has been designed with modern yet timeless features, exterior lighting, professional landscaping, and a fenced-in front yard. The property comes with a 10-year warranty. Please note that square footage is approximate. Amazing location is just steps from tons of restaurants, shopping, transit options to the city, and the 13-acre park with a trail/path, reservoir, multiple sport fields, heated pool, ice rink, and much more!    "
