250005271,SOLD,"JC, Heights",51 PROSPECT ST,Condominium,1400,1707,"$949,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,5802,9.02,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$949,000","$949,000",$677.86,$677.86,3/19/2025,3/31/2025,6/4/2025,12,12,,6/5/2025,,,,"$11,467",2023,$250,,Conventional,,,,,,*off Palisade Ave.,"Welcome to the East Side of Jersey City Heights—prime location! This spectacular 3-bedroom and 2-bath condominium, nestled in a quiet and relaxing neighborhood, offers modern luxury and high-end finishes throughout.  The sleek, contemporary kitchen boasts quartz countertops with a waterfall island and Samsung black stainless steel appliances, including a wine fridge. The primary suite features an ensuite bath and two walk-in closets. Elegant hardwood floors flow throughout, complementing the fireplace and crown moldings that add an extra touch of sophistication.  This home is packed with premium features including: 5.1 channel home theater surround sound, in-unit washer/dryer, ring security camera, central vacuum system and sprinkler system throughout.  Enjoy the ultimate rooftop experience with your private 1,200 sq. ft. deck offering stunning NYC views, gas-water-electric connections and 2-channel surround sound—perfect for entertaining.  Parking is hassle-free with two dedicated spaces (one in the garage, one outside; NON-tandem with Unit 1). Located in close proximity to NYC transportation (bus & rail), shopping, dining, schools and parks; this home truly has it all. Builders warranty included.  Schedule your appointment today!  "
230008533,SOLD,"JC, Heights",112 CARLTON AVE,Condominium,2228,1724,"$949,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,04203,00026 01,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$949,000","$949,000",$425.94,$425.94,5/24/2023,6/4/2023,8/31/2023,11,11,,9/6/2023,,,,,,$235,,Conventional,No,No,,,,JFK and Liberty Ave,"Welcome home to this remarkable new construction luxury oversized condo in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This stunning 2,228 sq ft home offers an exceptional blend of modern elegance and thoughtful design. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious open layout boasting 12-inch ceilings and large triple pane European tilt and turn windows offering a spacious and airy ambiance that enhances the overall sense of luxury. The exquisitely designed kitchen features top-of-the-line Samsung stainless steel appliances, soft-close cabinets and quartz countertops and backsplash. Travel through the home to find three generously sized bedrooms and one office, each bedroom offers large closets and motorized ceiling fans. The spacious master suite offers a full bathroom adorned with beautifully large porcelain Brooklyn tiles and custom vanities, creating a spa-like retreat within your own home. The large walk-in closet provides ample storage and the attached office can be made into an extra closet for his and hers. The master bedroom also boasts access to a private 500 sq ft deck overlooking your private backyard. Travel down stairs where you will find a captivating and spacious rec room with a half kitchen, full bathroom and access to your own private backyard equipped with water/gas connections, ideal for entertaining guests or enjoying leisurely activities. The attention to detail extends throughout the residence with solid wood European doors and Grade one 4-inch hardwood floors. A full-size Samsung washer and dryer is also included to ensure the utmost convenience and efficiency for your laundry needs. Immerse yourself in an immersive audio experience with surround sound Bluetooth speakers installed throughout the home. Additionally, the inclusion of a built-in central vacuum system adds a touch of modern convenience, simplifying your cleaning routine. Other features included 8K HDMI, LAN and central cooling/heating. The shared garage features one side by side parking spot and a 60 amp car charger port installed, allowing for easy electric vehicle charging. Situated in the desirable Jersey City Heights, this new construction luxury condo offers an unparalleled living experience. With its sophisticated design, high-end finishes, and array of impressive features. ** 5 year tax abatement"
250000015,SOLD,"JC, Heights",30 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1650,5069,"$949,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,1505,43,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$949,000","$949,000",$575.15,$575.15,1/2/2025,2/18/2025,4/2/2025,47,47,,4/2/2025,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Summit and Central ave,"Welcome to 30 Graham Unit 2, one of NKAY Developer’s latest High End New Construction Duplex Projects in Sought After Enclave of Jersey City Heights. This New Construction Unit features 3 bedroom and 2 full bath. First floor's layout offers direct flow between your Kitchen and Living Room / Dining Room. Kitchen designed w. Top Line Stainless Steel Thermador appliances, unique black & white quartz counters with matching waterfall island, backsplash and Two Tone Custom Cabinetry. Your LR and DR are complete with fireplace framed with custom millwork and oversized Andersen Windows. Your Main Bedroom Suite offers ample sunlight through multiple large windows, custom millwork accent wall with dual pendant lighting, walk in closets with custom built in shelving and cabinets. Main Bathroom Suite offers double vanity and dramatic floor to ceiling dark tiled shower with warm accent lighting and top line sprayer and jets. Completing your first floor is 2 large bedrooms with custom built in closets, Full Bathroom, laundry room with High Efficiency Samsung Washer / Dryer and Custom Coat Nook for additional storage.   Your upper floor is complete with full length / width private roof deck with Gas / Electric / Water Hook ups, with panoramic NYC Views. Home is complete with Oversized Side By Side Parking Garage, Smart Camera, Smart Doorbell, Smart Keypad Entry and High Voltage EV Charging Ports. Exterior facade has been designed with Modern Features yet a timeless design as well, paver driveway and professional landscaping complete your outdoor space. Property comes with 10 year warranty. Please note that sqft is approx. PROPERTY QUALIFY FOR LOW INTEREST RATE PROGRAM FROM PREFERRED LENDER. Property may qualify for 5 Year Tax Abatement!"
230000249,SOLD,"JC, Heights",46 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,2597,1597,"$949,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,4,1,3,7,,"$949,000","$949,000",$365.42,$365.42,1/5/2023,1/5/2023,3/22/2023,0,0,,3/22/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Sherman Ave & Central Ave,"French townhouse meets fully upgraded dreamhome with this newly renovated home including private backyard one block from Central Avenue and Pershing Field Park. The extra-wide building size allows for added spaciousness in the two-story, four bedroom three and a half bath layout.  Country chic elements inspire throughout like white oak hardwood floors, exposed wood and metal banister stairwell and light airy design. Open floorplan kitchen boasts waterfall quartz counters, modern white and matte black custom cabinetry, pennytile backsplash, gold fixtures and exposed accent shelves. Sliding barn doors reveal a centrally located laundry area for convenience.  Stunning matte black wainscotting accent wall adds drama to the dreamy primary ensuite. Ultra-stylish bathrooms showcase herringbone tile, double vanity, sophisticated black tile shower with gold accents.   This fully restored home hosts a wrap-around porch on a tree-lined street for excellent curb appeal, all in the heart of Jersey City Heights. The Heights is known for its excellent shops and boutiques, eclectic vibe and community, expansive parks and easy Hoboken and NYC access."
230005096,SOLD,"JC, Heights",123 PROSPECT ST,Condominium,2923,1597,"$949,000",CONDO-COOP,,L & 1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,2,1,2,10,,"$949,000","$949,000",$324.67,$324.67,3/30/2023,4/14/2023,6/27/2023,15,15,,6/27/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Lienau & Central,"This fully renovated home brings impeccable design and sophistication to this perfectly located, tree-lined street one block off Central Avenue, Pershing Field Park and Reservoir. Breathtaking brickwork, exposed beams and beautiful white oak open stairs combine with bay windows and light oak floors to create bright open living with simple, clean design.   Possibilities are endless with nearly 3,000 sq ft, 2-story, lower unit. Enter into the open floorplan living, kitchen and dining area, and onward to two bedrooms, two full baths and an added den with access to the private yard. Head down to the extra large basement for the additional living space with built-in shelves, two bonus rooms, half bath, office, utility room with side-by-side LG washer and dryer, storage room and additional backyard access.   Contemporary kitchens impress with custom matte black lower cabinets, clean natural wood uppers plus waterfall white quartz counters, tile backsplash, Frigidaire stainless appliances, and Kraüs gold faucet and fittings. Carefully curated pendant lighting, black matte window trim and brick accents punctuate the property throughout.  Bathrooms bring interest with elements such as double vanity,  herringbone or polished porcelain juniper tile feature walls, black pennytile floors, soaker tub or glass shower with cutout niche, or window for natural light. Primary en-suite boasts a showstopping matte black wainscotting feature wall, plus oversized walk-through or double closets.   Timeless bricks building with classic front porch vibe rests on a tree-lined street in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Both homes offer ideal walkability to surrounding Central Avenue for all essential shopping needs, plus nearby Pershing, Washington or Palisades Parks. Jersey City Heights is home to an eclectic art community, excellent schools, award-winning restaurants and businesses, plus easy NYC access."
