240023323,SOLD,"JC, Heights",58 WAVERLY ST,Condominium,1618,6706,"$949,000",CONDO-COOP,,2&3,2,"JC, Heights",07306,5805,13,Heights,,,,,4,1,3,8,,"$949,000","$949,000",$586.53,$586.53,12/5/2024,12/24/2024,2/27/2025,19,19,,2/28/2025,,,,"$13,000",,$275,,Conventional,,No,,,,Baldwin and Oakland,"This stunning 4-bed, 3.5-bath condo is a true gem, spanning approximately 1,618 sq ft of living space. The unit occupies the 2nd and 3rd floors, offering abundant natural light and a spacious feel. Inside, you'll find beautiful hardwood floors, chic tiles, and walk-in closets in each bedroom. The kitchen boasts waterfall quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of cabinet space. The master bathroom features a double sink vanity and a frameless shower. Step out onto your own private, spacious balcony for a breath of fresh air and relaxation. Located just one block from Palisade Ave with direct NYC bus access and close to JSQ PATH, this condo is convenient to all local amenities and commuting routes. Don't miss out on this idyllic and stylish home!"
210023788,SOLD,"JC, Heights",42 RAVINE AVE,Condominium,1774,1703,"$949,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,00017,05001,,42 RAVINE,,,,3,1,2,10,,"$949,000","$949,000",$534.95,$534.95,10/15/2021,10/21/2021,12/22/2021,6,5,,12/22/2021,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Webster Ave and Abbett Street,"NEW TO THE MARKET! Welcome to 42 Ravine Avenue, perfectly located in Jersey City Heights!  42 Ravine Avenue consists of two brand new condominium residences that feel more like townhouses! Interior finishes include 9ft ceilings, 4.5 inch white oak hardwood floors, custom moldings, cabinets as well as custom built in closets. Two zone central heat and air conditioning as well as a tankless hot water system and central vacuum throughout.  The spacious kitchen featuring a center island, Samsung black stainless steel appliances,  wine cooler, custom 42 cabinets with black metal hardware,  quartz counters and subway tile backsplash.   Bathrooms feature Kholer fixtures, ceramic tile flooring and quartz counters. To top it off this residence features a rear deck right off the kitchen and direct access to its own  650sf private roof deck featuring 2x2 porcelain tiles and NYC views.  Two rear driveway parking spaces are included!"
260005804,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",206 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1250,1750,"$949,900",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,,"$949,900",$759.92,,4/1/2026,,,8,,,4/1/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,South & Bowers,"Unparalleled luxury awaits you in Jersey City Heights’ newest condominium project. 206  Sherman Ave is situated on a charming tree-lined street in the heart of everything Jersey City Heights has to offer. Comprised of three stunning 3-bedroom homes, all with private outdoor space and spectacular custom finishes throughout. As you approach 206 Sherman Ave, you are greeted by a gorgeous brick exterior, black-framed bay windows, and a modern cornice blending old-world charm with modern style. Each home is bathed in an abundance of natural light through floor-to-ceiling east, south, and west-facing windows, highlighting a luxurious open-concept layout with white oak wide-plank hardwood flooring and thoughtfully curated finishes throughout. The kitchens all feature light Oak cabinetry, bronze hardware and fixtures, a top-of-the-line Café luxury appliance package, quartz countertops, and backsplash. Complimenting the kitchen is a wet bar with a beautiful stone countertop and backsplash, a beverage center, oak-faced cabinetry, and floating shelves. The primary spa-like en-suite bathroom is an elegant retreat with beautiful custom finishes, a dual vanity, a glass-enclosed shower, and even a towel warmer for that extra luxurious touch. Wake up and enjoy your morning coffee on your private, direct-access terrace right from each primary bedroom. The 2nd and 3rd bedrooms are generous in size and feature custom closet systems. Additional highlights include fully customized closets throughout, a full-size washer & dryer, LED lighting throughout with dimmers & smart lighting, central A/C, app-based thermostats, high ceilings, surround sound system, music system in each primary bedroom, and a centralized iPad smart control interface. Unit 1 enjoys a private 710s/f landscaped yard, and Unit 3, a 900+s/f roof deck with gorgeous views of NYC and the ever-changing Jersey City Skyline. Building features include a video door phone/intercom system and a 24-hour CCTV surveillance system. Conveniently located near Fisk & Washington Parks, restaurants, cafes, coffee shops, farmer’s markets, and grocery stores. Easy access to Hoboken and the NJ Transit Light Rail to the PATH and ferries via the 9th Street Elevator, making commuting to NYC seamless. Jersey City Heights is known for its artistic roots, vibrant community, and sweeping Manhattan skyline views."
230017975,SOLD,"JC, Heights",17 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1641,1603,"$949,900",CONDO-COOP,,"1,2",1,"JC, Heights",07307,04402,00022,,,,,,3,1,2,10,,"$949,900","$949,900",$578.85,$578.85,10/25/2023,11/16/2023,12/15/2023,22,22,,12/15/2023,,,,"$12,015",2022,$218,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Avenue & Sherman Avenue,"Enjoy the best The Heights has to offer - new construction duplex living (2021 and remodeled in 2023) with ample indoor and outdoor space, parking, privacy, and close proximity to everything that makes The Heights the most wonderful and fastest growing neighborhood in Jersey City!  Welcome to 17 Manhattan #1 - a 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath, 1641 sqft condo with thoughtful upgrades, modern SMART amenities, and sleek finishes.  The open and spacious home is enhanced by its high ceilings and light wide oak flooring. Windows surround the living room/dining room and kitchen- with an extra row of transom windows to the north, and east-facing windows bringing natural light into every corner of the home. The kitchen is outfitted with white quartz counters and shaker cabinets, a custom island with under-mount microwave and additional storage, and top-of-the-line stainless steel Samsung SMART appliances.  The kitchen also has a large pantry, gorgeous vented hood and porcelain farm sink, a built-in food disposal, and added coffee/cocktail bar.  Beyond the kitchen, you'll find the first of many custom storage spaces.  The laundry room is just off of the kitchen - with a 2nd pantry/add'l storage. As you head to the primary suite, you'll pass 2 equal sized bedrooms with custom closet systems (both fit a queen sized bed), a guest bath, and two hall closets. The primary bedroom easily fits a king sized bed, and the walk-in closet is larger than other homes with similar floor plans. The primary bath offers a double sink vanity and spa-like shower with jetted shower heads. And sliding glass doors lead to the bedroom's private balcony which overlooks the home's lush backyard oasis.  Head downstairs to the bonus flex space - with additional custom storage system and its own half bath.  And walk out onto your patio and private fenced-in backyard.  This home sits on an oversized lot, so if this backyard seems larger than most, you'd be right!  And for more wow, this home comes with 2 deeded GARAGE parking spaces (not in-tandem to your neighbor's space), and everything from the RING doorbell and security, to indoor and outdoor lights, garage door, and appliances - all can be controlled from your phone.  Nothing has been missed.  Move right in and immediately feel like you're home."
260000562,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",78 BEACON AVE,Condominium,2200,6199,"$949,999",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07306,5906,18,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,7,,,"$949,999",$431.82,,1/14/2026,,,85,,,1/14/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Laidlaw & Hopkins,"Eligible for a 5-year tax abatement and a special interest rate program with 5.375% (no PMI) and only 5% down, this home offers an incredible opportunity to experience the best of modern city living. Nestled in the vibrant Jersey City Heights neighborhood, 78 Beacon Ave presents over 2000 square feet, stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom new construction condo that perfectly blends modern design with everyday comfort — complete with a private yard. Upon entry, you’re welcomed into an open-concept living and dining area filled with natural light from an expansive wall of windows, porcelain tile, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere ideal for relaxing or entertaining. The modern European style kitchen features a sleek quartz waterfall island, stainless steel appliances, ample storage, and sophisticated finishes making it a true centerpiece for all gatherings. The lower level provides exceptional versatility, featuring a fourth bedroom and full bathroom — perfect for guests or extended family or an au pair. The upper-level features hardwood floors and offers three spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms, including a serene primary suite with a spa-like en-suite bath featuring a glass-enclosed shower and contemporary fixtures. Additional highlights include in-unit laundry for everyday convenience and plenty of closet space for all your storage needs. Located in Jersey City Heights, residents enjoy easy access to an array of local shops, trendy restaurants, parks, and transportation options — offering the perfect balance of neighborhood charm and urban convenience. Credit for 1 year free parking is being offered!"
220017033,SOLD,"JC, Heights",230 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1945,1639,"$950,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02302,00001,,,,,,3,1,2,9,,"$950,000","$949,000",$488.43,$488.43,9/21/2022,9/28/2022,11/22/2022,7,7,,11/23/2022,,,,"$10,987",2021,,,Conventional,,,,,,South St & Sherman Ave,"Welcome to Residence 1. located at 230 Sherman Ave. An oversized, nearly 2,000sqft, 3-bedroom, 2.5 bath DUPLEX in the heart of Jersey City Heights! With the feeling and space often hard to find in single family homes, Residence 1 gives you the multi-floor living and private backyard that make even suburban families jealous! The interior home itself has a chef's Kitchen outfit with a stunning waterfall quartz countertop, top tier Samsung package of black stainless-steel appliances, Sharp under-counter microwave drawer, outside vented hood, and dual-zone wine fridge, matched with Kohler plumbing fixtures. No detail has been overlooked, with meticulous crown molding, a full building sprinkler system, a Ring security system equipped with video doorbell, outdoor security cameras and indoor alarm system, a Bluetooth enabled built.in 5.1 channel home theater, and an united mesh WiFi network ensuring you never lose your broadband connection. The oversized primary bedroom is overrun with natural light. has his and her walk in custom closets and a spa-like en-suite with a glass enclosed walk-in rain shower that exudes luxury. But the real differentiator is the massive bottom floor, fitted with a wet bar with a built-in beverage refrigerator and direct access  to a private backyard, which features Bluetooth enabled outdoor speakers and a preinstalled gas line for grilling. This home will make entertaining family and friends more fun than you could have imagined. Additional amenities include central vacuum, custom closets throughout, commercial waterproof garage flooring and coaxial and ethernet ports in every room. This new construction build was developed by renowned Jersey City Heights developer, NKAY, known for their quality and credibility in the area and comes with a remaining 2-year new construction tax abatement and a 7-year structural builder's warranty. When it comes to location in The Heights, this residence is second to none with proximity to the 9th Street Light Rail, buses to Manhattan, top tier restaurants such as Corto, and Bread and Salt an Italian bakery opened by James Beard semi-finalist Rick Easton and walkability for the area that is unmatched. Couple this with heated garage parking, and this one has it all! One of the most desirable streets in all of Jersey City, come see why you will be calling 230 Sherman home. "
230009530,SOLD,"JC, Heights",110 CARLTON AVE,Condominium,2228,1724,"$950,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,04203,00026 01,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$950,000","$949,000",$426.39,$426.39,6/8/2023,6/14/2023,8/31/2023,6,6,,9/1/2023,,,,,,$235,,Conventional,No,No,,,,JFK and Liberty Ave,"Welcome home to this remarkable new construction luxury oversized condo in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This stunning 2,228 sq ft home offers an exceptional blend of modern elegance and thoughtful design. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious open layout boasting 12-inch ceilings and large triple pane European tilt and turn windows offering a spacious and airy ambiance that enhances the overall sense of luxury. The exquisitely designed kitchen features top-of-the-line Samsung stainless steel appliances, soft-close cabinets and quartz countertops and backsplash. Travel through the home to find three generously sized bedrooms and one office, each bedroom offers large closets and motorized ceiling fans. The spacious master suite offers a full bathroom adorned with beautifully large porcelain Brooklyn tiles and custom vanities, creating a spa-like retreat within your own home. The large walk-in closet provides ample storage and the attached office can be made into an extra closet for his and hers. The master bedroom also boasts access to a private 500 sq ft deck overlooking your private backyard. Travel down stairs where you will find a captivating and spacious rec room with a half kitchen, full bathroom and access to your own private backyard equipped with water/gas connections, ideal for entertaining guests or enjoying leisurely activities. The attention to detail extends throughout the residence with solid wood European doors and Grade one 4-inch hardwood floors. A full-size Samsung washer and dryer is also included to ensure the utmost convenience and efficiency for your laundry needs. Immerse yourself in an immersive audio experience with surround sound Bluetooth speakers installed throughout the home. Additionally, the inclusion of a built-in central vacuum system adds a touch of modern convenience, simplifying your cleaning routine. Other features included 8K HDMI, LAN and central cooling/heating. The shared garage features one side by side parking spot and a 60 amp car charger port installed, allowing for easy electric vehicle charging. Situated in the desirable Jersey City Heights, this new construction luxury condo offers an unparalleled living experience. With its sophisticated design, high-end finishes, and array of impressive features. ** 5 year tax abatement"
240022561,SOLD,"JC, Heights",104 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1546,1724,"$950,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03404,00030,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$950,000","$950,000",$614.49,$614.49,2/1/2024,2/2/2024,5/2/2024,1,0,,11/19/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave. & Kennedy Blvd.,"Builder is also offering a 1% credit to buyer for closing costs / rate buydown / remodel on this chic new construction duplex offering 3 large bedrooms, 2 ½ baths, private back yard, and uncommon side-by-side garage parking (not tandem) in the desirable Jersey City Heights. This south-facing home is bathed with natural sunlight. luxurious design features highlighted by 5'' wide solid plank oak hardwood flooring throughout its spacious open layout. 10-foot ceilings, 8-foot custom doors, and sliding glass balcony and patio door to a private backyard provide you with a home that's both warm and welcoming.  The home is equipped with all the modern amenities including in-unit laundry, central AC, and heat/ The chef's kitchen is equipped with a hidden vented hood, high-end stainless steel appliances wrapped in ceiling-high custom cabinetry draped in white Calcutta quartz countertops, and backsplash. Custom closets and ample storage make everyday living comfortable. The ground floor family room with a wet bar makes entertaining a breeze.  Available EV charging facilities, 5-year tax abatement, and a 10-year builder's warranty ensure peace of mind with your investment. Contact to schedule a private tour and take the first step towards securing your bright, new home today.  "
250010602,SOLD,"JC, Heights",44 BLEECKER ST,Condominium,1650,5069,"$950,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,1502,13,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$950,000","$999,000",$575.76,$575.76,5/28/2025,7/29/2025,9/18/2025,62,62,,11/26/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central and Summit,"Welcome to 44 Bleecker Unit 2, a new construction 3 bedroom 2 bath luxury duplex condo built by Medna Developers. The first floor offers an expansive open-concept living space with a chef's kitchen, showcasing premium Samsung SS Smart appliances, waterfall quartz countertops, and two-tone cabinetry. The kitchen flows into a soaring living and dining room with 12-foot high ceilings, lined with oversized Pella windows that let in abundant sunlight, complemented by custom designer pendant lighting. The primary bedroom includes a custom floor-to-ceiling accent wall, built-in closets with a mirrored section, accent pendant lighting, a balcony, and a luxurious ensuite bathroom. Completing the first floor are two additional bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a laundry room. The rooftop provides the perfect space for entertainment, offering direct views of NYC. The garage features true side-by-side parking and an EV charging outlet. The property comes with a 10-year builder warranty and may be eligible for a 5-year tax abatement. Ask about our Low Interest Rate First Time Home Buyer Program"
240000104,SOLD,"JC, Heights",60 PATERSON ST,Condominium,0,5069,"$950,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,A,"JC, Heights",07307,1403,18,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$950,000","$975,000",,,1/3/2024,1/19/2024,2/20/2024,16,16,,2/22/2024,,,,$0,,,,Cash,,,,,,Summit ave and Pierce ave,"Presenting 60 Paterson Unit A, a Brand-New Luxury Duplex. This 4 Bedroom, 2.1 Bathroom residence offers quality, smart home capabilities and the perfect blend between Modern and Dark / Natural tones.  Your first floor enters to an open concept Living / Dining Room and Kitchen. Your kitchen includes top line appliances, custom two-tone cabinetry, custom quartz countertops / backsplash and dark wood island accent, designer pendant lights all framed by oversized Andersen windows, letting in plenty of natural light while providing maximum privacy.  Your Main Bedroom is filled with natural light through your triple wide Andersen Window. Complete with custom closets, your main bathroom offers double sink / vanity, matte black top of line shower fixtures and rainfall shower head. Main floor is complete with 2 additional bedrooms, full bathroom and Laundry. Your Ground level is perfectly fit for entertaining, with powder room, sliding glass doors which enter to your private backyard finished with paver patio and grass backyard. Garage features non-tandem parking. Property comes with 5 Year Tax Abatement and 10 Year warranty."
240015559,SOLD,"JC, Heights",288 GRIFFITH ST,Condominium,1839,1597,"$950,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$950,000","$950,000",$516.59,$516.59,8/8/2024,9/23/2024,11/19/2024,46,46,,12/2/2024,,,,,,,,Cash,,,,,,JFK and Summit,"Design and destination delight in this stunning duplex with private backyard and side-by-side garage parking in Jersey City Heights (so you can park your SUV with ease!). This recent construction offers a seamless blend of contemporary design and functional living with a spacious 3 bed + den, + rec room, 2.5 bath floorplan.   Natural light bathes the marble floors and striking accent wall that captivates as you step inside the spacious open concept living area. Modern amenities abound with additions like ceiling fans from Atlas Fan Co. and Oxygen Lighting, plantation shutters by Interior Motif, and central vacuum system. The white eat-in kitchen boasts sleek modern cabinetry, Bertazzoni stainless steel appliances including a dual-fuel range, plus an oversized white waterfall quartz island, complemented by matching counters and backsplash.    The downstairs den is equipped with an all-important wet bar, and provides direct access to a beautifully designed private backyard. This outdoor oasis, curated by A Small Green Space, features a patio, professional landscaping, lighting, and an irrigation system—perfect for entertaining or unwinding in style.    Upgrades await around every corner, like the custom shelving, lighting, Murphy bed and additional soundproofing in the spare bedroom or office. All bedroom closets have been custom outfitted by Interior Motif, while the primary ensuite hosts a private balcony, plus custom Hunter Douglas black-out power-roller shades. Bathrooms bring beauty with double vanity, glass showers, Kohler medicine cabinets and chair-height toilets. Last but not least, owners enjoy the luxury of side-by-side garage parking and additional storage space.   Located on a tree-lined street just off JFK Blvd, this home offers easy access to the lush greenery of Leonard Gordon, Washington, and Pershing Field Parks. Jersey City Heights is known for its vibrant community, eclectic vibe, excellent schools and parks, and proximity to NYC and surrounding areas. Experience the perfect blend of city living and serene surroundings in this exceptional property."
240024004,SOLD,"JC, Heights",124 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1768,1597,"$950,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$950,000","$989,000",$537.33,$537.33,12/18/2024,1/14/2025,3/7/2025,27,27,,3/7/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,JFK & Summit,"This property qualifies for a Temporary Interest Rate Buydown with an estimated savings to the buyer in excess of $10k.   Step into sophisticated luxury with this stunning, brand-new home featuring three bedrooms, bonus room, private backyard and garage parking in The Heights. Light streams in through the oversized windows bringing loads of natural light to the contemporary classic design. Features like the striking bamboo accent wall, crown molding and white oak floors help elevate the open floor plan.   This home features a spacious two-story layout with the downstairs bonus room hosting a wet bar and wine fridge, plus additional half bath. Step outside the sliding glass doors to the private backyard beautifully finished with pavers and landscaping. Upstairs, the kitchen is finished with waterfall black quartz counters and backsplash, modern custom cabinets in white or natural wood cabinets with under-lighting, high-end stainless appliances. Pendant lighting adds a touch of elegance, while matte black fixtures, including a pot filler, add sophistication and style.    The primary ensuite enamors with a white wainscotting feature wall with bedside sconce lighting. The side-by-side walk-in closets are fully finished offering ultimate storage and convenience. Bathrooms include extras like double vanity, smart mirror, glass shower, and black porcelain tile.    Situated on a quiet street in Jersey City Heights, this home is near the newly renovated Leonard Gordon Park and neighborhood favorites like The Hutton Restaurant and Bar and Dulce de Leche Bakery. The Heights is known for its eclectic arts scene, excellent community and schools, peaceful parks, and easy access to NYC and surrounding areas."
220001642,SOLD,"JC, Heights",29 RESERVOIR AVE,Condominium,1518,283,"$950,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,05801,00005,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$950,000","$929,900",$625.82,$625.82,1/28/2022,2/4/2022,3/16/2022,7,7,,3/22/2022,,,,,,$193,,Conventional,,,,,,Webster & Palisade ave,"Welcome to another Brand New Construction Luxury Condo brought to you by Blue Chip Properties located on the East Side of the highly regarded Jersey City Heights residential area. This 1,518 sq ft. 3 bedroom, 2 bath home boasts a modern open concept living space, 12’ ceilings and oversized windows that flood the space with natural lighting. Entertain and Relax on your oversized 700 + sq ft private rooftop oasis, equipped with gas, electric and plumbing connections for an outdoor kitchen while you enjoy the marvelous panoramic views of NYC.  Featuring High-gloss European Style cabinetry, stainless steel premium appliances, modern porcelain backsplash, Central Island featuring a waterfall quartz countertop and drawer microwave with Ambient LED under-mounted lighting. The Master bedroom includes an en suite spa inspired bathroom with floating double vanity and Ambient LED lighting. The master suite has 8‘ x 8’ glass sliding doors leading out to a full width large balcony along with an expansive walk-in closet. Two generous bedrooms share a second bathroom featuring modern Carrera Porcelain slab tile, double vanity and soaking tub.  Blue Chip Properties’ other signature upgrades include West Elm light fixtures, laundry room hook ups, central HVAC, 8’ solid-core doors, 1 car garage parking fitted with electric vehicle (EV) charger. Full smart home technology complements the modern design with integrated lights, thermostat, smart lock, switches and video doorbell which are all voice activated using a central display screen and also accessible remotely via a smartphone. This property is located on a quiet tree lined street in the Riverview Arts District, close to Shops, Restaurants, Congress St Light Rail, Hoboken, Downtown Jersey City, major highways, and PATH station. Make this your Dream Home today! *Eligible for 5 year tax."
