230003862,SOLD,"JC, Heights",251 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1920,1727,"$955,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307, 2204,29,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$955,000","$899,000",$497.40,$497.40,3/9/2023,3/16/2023,4/21/2023,7,7,,4/22/2023,,,,"$13,449",22,$298,,Conventional,,,,,,South & Congress,"Have it all in this amazing duplex on Sherman Ave....Tandem parking, large private yard, 2 floors, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 1920 square feet living space & top of the line finishes define this exceptional home. Contemporary open floor plan with dream kitchen featuring an extra large breakfast with quartz counters & pendant lighting, chevron tile backsplash, gas stove with griddle and super stylish range hood, bib sink, DW & microwave. Secluded primary suite has 2 walk in closets, built-in seating and storage running below the distinctive bay window, spa inspired bathroom with double sinks & multi jet frameless shower. The media/family room leads to the exclusive yard  & is complete with a wet bar, storage & 1/2 bath. Fantastic for indoor/outdoor entertaining! Hardwood & tile floors,  custom closets & window treatments throughout, CAC, side by side washer/dryer,  recessed lighting & ceiling fans.  Ideal Heights location, super close to the Congress St. elevator, hip restaurants & cafes, and parks."
230021064,SOLD,"JC, Heights",191 HUTTON ST,Condominium,1474,1603,"$959,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03602,00017,,191 Hutton Street,,,,3,0,2,12,,"$959,000","$969,000",$650.61,$650.61,12/26/2023,3/1/2024,4/22/2024,66,66,,4/22/2024,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Sanford Pl and Summit Ave,"3 PARKING SPACES INCLUDED!!! 191 Hutton Street features spacious living with 3 over sized bedrooms pus an office!  Get ready for MORE parking (3 CARS), MORE storage ( 2 PRIVATE STORAGE ROOMS) and MORE outdoor space (DIRECTLY OFF LIVING ROOM AND KITCHEN)! Welcome to this upscale one of a kind residence located in desirable Jersey City Heights.  With an attention to detail, Belfiore Builders has gone above and beyond to outfit all 3 bedrooms with custom built-in closet systems which maximize your storage options.  You will immediately notice the 10ft ceilings and abundance of sun light!   Kitchen features custom cabinets, quartz counters, herring bone tile backsplash, wine fridge, double hung LG ThinQ oven and over sized island.  With southern exposure and an abundance of sunlight, your kitchen and living room lead directly out to you amazing private terrace where you can dine al fresco and entertain your guests. Get ready for the most parking available in the Heights!  This residence comes with the ability to park 3 vehicles in your garage plus a bonus 2 private storage rooms!  FIVE year tax abatement in place!   This home is in close proximity to shopping, parks, restaurants and transportation to NYC!"
250021244,SOLD,"JC, Heights",203 HUTTON ST,Condominium,2005,1724,"$960,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & 3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3602,11,Heights,,,,,5,1,3,8,,"$960,000","$979,000",$478.80,$478.80,10/14/2025,11/13/2025,12/15/2025,30,30,,12/15/2025,,,,$0,,$180,2025,Cash,,,,,,Summit Ave. & Sanford Place,"Experience the perfect blend of elegance and modern convenience in this exceptional residence in Jersey City Heights. This home boasts over 2,000 square feet of exquisitely designed living space, making it a true gem in the real estate market. Step into a spacious haven featuring 5 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, soaring 10-foot ceilings and 8-foot custom doors. The open-concept chef's kitchen has new stainless steel appliances, custom white quartz countertops, and a full-size washer and dryer. Elegant 5 wide solid oak flooring flows seamlessly throughout the home, creating a comfortable and inviting atmosphere.  Each bathroom has smart mirrors, adding a touch of tech-savvy sophistication. Enjoy private moments on your front and back bedroom balconies or relish the breathtaking New York City views from your expansive 1,000 sqft roof deck.  This prime location offers a serene lifestyle: a 5-minute stroll from Pershing Field Park and a mere 35-minute commute to the World Trade Center. The convenience of this location ensures you can enjoy the best of both worlds - a peaceful retreat and easy access to the city. Large closets with ample storage ensure clutter-free living, while central heat and air conditioning provide year-round comfort. Owner will pay for 2-years of rental parking. This building has a 10-year builder warranty and the builder will file for a 5-year tax abatement.   Elevate your lifestyle in the highly desirable Jersey City Heights area. Schedule your 203 Hutton St Unit 2 tour today and make this extraordinary property your new home."
210009069,SOLD,"JC, Heights",502 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1624,1702,"$960,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,301,"JC, Heights",07307,02401,00001.01,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$960,000","$929,000",$591.13,$591.13,4/16/2021,4/21/2021,6/30/2021,5,5,,6/30/2021,,,,"$10,800",,$411,,Conventional,,,,,,Palisade and Bowers,"***Virtual Tour Available*** Best Value in Jersey City – over 1600 sqft 3 bedroom / 2 bath with parking & NYC views! This unit features large living space, open chef's kitchen with dinning area,  large living room with NYC views, super bright unit facing southeast, master suite features walk in closet and private bath with heated floors. This luxury condo includes custom closets, custom electronic blinds, NYC and river southeast views and much more. Unit is still under builder warranty - in mint condition!"
240017618,SOLD,"JC, Heights",122 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1575,1724,"$960,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,302,"JC, Heights",07307,04504,1,Heights,The York,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$960,000","$994,000",$609.52,$609.52,9/6/2024,10/3/2024,12/16/2024,27,27,,12/18/2024,,,,,,$484,,Conventional,,,,,,Ferry St & Franklin St,"This concrete and steel new construction at 122 New York Ave is a testament to modern architecture, offering residents a tranquil retreat with unobstructed views of the Manhattan skyline atop The York's expansive roof deck. The building's design is both contemporary and functional, featuring a range of high-end amenities that cater to every aspect of urban living. Closets and additional cabinets can still customized upon the buyer's request.  Residents enjoy the convenience of an indoor climate-controlled garage with bike storage, ensuring their vehicles and bicycles are kept secure and protected from the elements. The expansive communal rooftop deck is a standout feature, providing a space to relax and entertain while taking in the stunning cityscape. Each of the 9 finely appointed homes is accessible via a chic lobby, with the elevator opening directly to a landing with only two units per floor, ensuring privacy and exclusivity. The spacious condominiums span approximately 1,545 square feet, with an open floor layout that includes 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Attention to detail is evident throughout, from the Bosch stainless steel appliances and Cuccina kitchen cabinetry in the chef's kitchen to the in-unit gas washer/dryer and in-ceiling speakers managed by a Sonos amplifier. The living areas are adorned with 5 wide French oak plank hardwood floors, while the bathrooms feature Porcelanosa tile and plumbing fixtures, LED lighting, and heated floors in both bathrooms, for ultimate comfort. The builder has prioritized a soundproofed environment, utilizing advanced materials such as sound channels, sound clips, Quiet Rock, green/noise proofing compound, and foam insulation to create a peaceful sanctuary. The York's prime location offers easy access to public transportation, with Palisade Ave just a block away, providing direct bus lines to NYC Port Authority, Hoboken, and Downtown JC. The Hudson Light Rail Stations are also conveniently close. Residents can take advantage of nearby Pershing Field's indoor pool and ice skating rink, as well as Riverview Park for community events. Visit theyorkjc.com for more information!"
230019796,SOLD,"JC, Heights",197 GRIFFITH ST,Condominium,1675,1692,"$960,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,1,2,10,,"$960,000","$899,000",$573.13,$573.13,11/27/2023,12/6/2023,2/5/2024,9,9,,2/19/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave & Central Ave,"Jersey City Height’s own Blackstone Builders delivers another beautiful ground-up new-construction boutique condo project! This one is a stunning two residence building custom designed and carefully crafted on a quiet block in the heart of this well-loved neighborhood. --- The downstairs duplex welcomes you with its expansive open-concept kitchen, living room and dining room with large French sliding glass doors leading to 900 sq ft private outdoor space that boasts both a grass yard and paver patio. Backyard enjoyment was carefully considered: the time and expense were taken to bring the central HVAC condenser unit onto the roof creating a quiet urban oasis even with the A/C running inside. --- Loaded with Smart Home features such as a lighting system powered by ZWave technology controlled by SmartThings Hub, Yale W-Fi locks, Ring Elite Doorbells, Lift Master WiFi Garage Door Opener with Security Camera, and a custom designed speaker system that directly connects with streaming apps without being interrupted by phone calls. --- The kitchen is a chef’s delight with high-end stainless-steel appliances, custom vented hood, well-made cabinets, waterfall quartz countertop, and subway backsplash. For entertaining and living convenience there is a stylishly finished bathroom on this first level. Waiting upstairs is a spacious family room with a large set of windows as well as two spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom. Wide Red Oak Hardwood flooring, and a full size washer dryer are just the small details in this gorgeous home. The third master bedroom is the cherry on top with its large walk-in closet, beautifully finished ensuite bathroom, and sizable balcony overlooking the backyard. Garage parking completes the unit. --- Situated just steps from Jersey City’s bustling Central Ave loaded with a myriad of shops, restaurants, bars, cafes, gyms, and yoga studios. Of course, there is the unparalleled access to Downtown Jersey City, Hoboken, New York City and points west in New Jersey bringing the best of the region within grasp. No better way to bring in the New Year than in your just built home!"
240007298,SOLD,"JC, Heights",48 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1600,1623,"$962,500",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,1505,52,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$962,500","$945,000",$601.56,$601.56,4/19/2024,5/12/2024,6/11/2024,23,23,,6/11/2024,,,,"$13,200",2024,$155,2024,Conventional,,,,,,Central and Summit,"Gorgeous 3 bedroom 2 bath home with 2 car garage parking and private roofdeck! No detail has been overlooked in this two years young home, crafted by one of Jersey City's premier builders. Upon entry, you're greeted by an expansive open-concept living space flooded with natural light, perfectly complemented by the oversized south-facing windows. The chef's kitchen is a culinary delight, featuring a stunning quartz waterfall island and premium black stainless steel appliances, including a wine cooler, farmhouse style sink, and a convenient pot filler. This home offers three spacious bedrooms, including a luxurious primary bedroom retreat with custom walk in closets, and stunning ensuite bathroom with double vanity, makeup mirrors, and spa-like walk in rain shower with bench, nook, and full body jets. LED lighting throughout, Nest-powered central air, tankless hot water heater, central vac system, and built-in speakers are just a few of the thoughtfully added features. The crown jewel of this residence is the massive roof deck, spanning the entire footprint of the unit, offering a private outdoor oasis with breathtaking city views. Complete with water and gas hookups and speaker system, this rooftop haven is ideal for outdoor entertaining or simply unwinding after a long day. Additional highlights include an attached heated two-car garage with room for extra storage (not tandem with your neighbor!), ensuring comfort during colder months. Benefit from the remaining 2.5 years on the tax abatement, providing significant savings, and enjoy peace of mind with 7.5 years remaining on the new construction warranty! Nestled in a coveted JC heights neighborhood close to restaurants,  Washington Park, shopping, and easy commuting option to NYC , this home offers a rare opportunity to experience contemporary luxury living in Jersey City. Don't miss your chance to make this exquisite residence your own!"
