es indoor WIDE garage TANDEM parking shared with unit 1, ensuring hassle-free access, and two deeded storage closets for added convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this sophisticated and meticulously designed condo your new home. Nestled on a street adorned with beautiful historic preserved homes and within walking distance to Pershing Field Park, this home encapsulates the best of urban living. Residents will appreciate its proximity to NYC transportation, neighboring districts, and an array of shops, restaurants, and cultural attractions."
