240002415,SOLD,"JC, Heights",33 CARLTON AVE,Condominium,1746,6078,"$975,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,4702,8,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$975,000","$1,075,000",$558.42,$558.42,2/1/2024,2/1/2024,3/20/2024,0,0,,5/5/2024,,,,,,$290,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit and Montrose,"Introducing: The Carlton, where Location meets Luxury!! 2 years in the making, “33 Carlton Ave”, the Pershing Field Gem, is a collection of two ultra-luxurious brand new condominiums, brought to you by the Jersey City’s Top builder, Kuber Construction, in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This exquisite property is an epitome of comfort, space and modern design. Elevate your standards of living with these massive, meticulously designed, duplex homes, featuring designer finishes throughout, White Oak flooring, Recessed Lighting, Crown and Baseboard Moulding, Central HVAC, Nest Thermostat, Ring Doorbell, Camera Security, Pella Awning Windows, 10-foot ceilings, 8-foot doors and contemporary Matte black fixtures, on an oversized 25’ x 125’ lot, steps from Pershing Field Park(the most famous 13.5 acres park).  Immerse yourself in an impressive audio experience with surround sound WIFI/Bluetooth speakers installed throughout this smart home.  Expansive Unit 1 condominium spans over ~2,222 square feet, spread across two separate floors, offering oversized 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and a coveted private rooftop deck. Step inside this thoughtfully crafted home, and be greeted by an open and airy layout that seamlessly integrates a spacious living and dining area. The sophisticated living room features Brooklyn-Style BRICK TV wall with integrated ultra-thin electric fireplace, pine wood walnut paneling, modern LED lighting fixture, pre-wired wifi-speakers for entertainment, and oversized black windows allowing abundance of natural light throughout the day. The living/dining room seamlessly flows into the sophisticated chef’s kitchen showcasing an abundance of dramatic yin-yang glossy cabinetry with fine white/black modern trim, elegant quartz countertops, electrifying glossy black drop-ceiling filled with spotlights and integrated pendant lighting, Samsung Bluetooth Refrigerator, 5-burner Gas/Oven range, Pot Filler, Wine Cooler, Microwave, Dishwasher, Stainless Steel Sink, making it a culinary enthusiast's dream kitchen. The master-suite, a true retreat, provides a dedicated office/den space, also boasts access to a private balcony overlooking the serene backyard. The elegantly designed Ensuite Master Bathroom, equipped with Rain Shower, Waterfall and Panel style unique porcelain tiles, white high-gloss double vanity, SOAKING EUROPEAN BATH TUB, creates a spa-like experience. Master bedroom also features Custom Walk-In Closet finished with solid wood barn-door that seamlessly glides on a black metallic rail. This magnificent condominium that rivals Manhattan standard luxury, provides two additional queen size bedrooms, a second bathroom and a laundry room with full-size LG washer and dryer units. Travel downstairs to the lower level, where you'll discover treasured  private entertainment space with kitchenette and outdoor space. Each unit offers Exclusive Non-Tandem Garage Parking for our new homeowners looking to take advantage of covered parking in R1 zone, without hassling the neighbors.   Settled on a prestigious tree-lined, quiet, residential, extra wide street of Jersey City Heights, one block from Pershing Field Park, adjacent to Jersey City Reservoir No. 3, and bustling Central avenue, provides an unparalleled living experience. Located just 5 minutes away from the Journal Square PATH station, commuting to New York City is a breeze. Walking distance to boutique shops, restaurants, cafés and parks, this home is ideally located for a balance of urban living and secluded sanctuary. Jersey City Heights is known for its tight-knit community, great schools and easy access to NYC. **10-Year Builders Warranty, Eligible for 5 yr. tax abatement"
220020913,SOLD,"JC, Heights",21 WAVERLY ST,Condominium,2197,1581,"$975,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,Unit 1,"JC, Heights",07306,05803,00012,,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$975,000","$975,000",$443.79,$443.79,12/2/2022,12/8/2022,2/2/2023,6,6,,2/3/2023,,,,,,$200,,Conventional,,,,,,Baldwin ave & Palisade Ave,"BRAND NEW PROFESSIONALLY DESIGNED with a Private Back Yard in the heart of Jersey CIty Heights - Take this opportunity to live on one of the most sought after street in The Historical Heights Arts District.  Indulge in this impeccably designed brand new Duplex Condominium that boasts over 2,197 total square feet.  As you walk through the front door, you are greeted with a separate formal entry foyer, down the hall is a beautifully designed marble inlay powder room.  Just beyond the powder room is a separate home office which can be used as a 4th bedroom with a custom built in closet.  The first floor of this unit also occupies a very spacious living space with a living room dining room combo and a modern kitchen that is beautifully designed with a large center waterfall island, black on trend quartz counter tops, full black marble backsplash, two tone high end cabinets.  The kitchen also has an ample size separate pantry.  Just beyond the kitchen is the private back yard that can be accessed with large sliding glass doors with built in speakers outdoors and inside.  In addition, the first floor has 3 very large storage closets with custom built ins for all your storage needs.    Walk up to the second floor where you have a great size primary bedroom with large windows that lets in abundant amount of natural light, very large walk in primary closet with custom closet system and a complete walled tiled bathroom with double vanity.  There are two additional secondary bedrooms that share an enormous Jack and Jill bathroom that has a large double vanity with a separate shower and open shelving.  Every closet in this unit is equipped with custom closet built ins.  Other features include large size window where light fills the entire unit, gleaming oak hardwood floors, extra large crown and base moldings, in unit laundry with washer/dryer, 10 foot ceilings on both floors.  Additionally, the buyer can also take advantage of Jersey City’s 5 Year ‘New Construction’ Tax Abatement. 21 Waverly will provide you with the incomparable opportunity to live in Modern Luxury within an urban redeveloping area such as the Riverview Art District of Jersey City Heights. You will be within steps from parks, cafes, shops, and restaurants along with public transportation like NJ transit, the light rail, and the NY/NJ PATH, which will get you into Manhattan in minutes."
220021317,SOLD,"JC, Heights",83 CONGRESS ST,Condominium,1800,5069,"$975,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 - 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2204,20,Heights,,,,,4,0,3,8,,"$975,000","$995,000",$541.67,$541.67,12/12/2022,1/2/2023,2/20/2023,21,21,,2/20/2023,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Central / Palisades,"Welcome to 83 Congress, a Luxurious New Construction 4 bedroom 3 full bath duplex unit designed by one of Jersey City's top Home Builders, Blue Chip Properties, known for their unique interior design, high end finishes and quality craftsmanship. This home is a minutes walk to Congress St Light Rail, Washington Park, Riverview Park and Central/Palisade shops! Your main floor enters to an open concept Dining Room / Living Room featuring 10 ft high walls lined with Andersen windows and natural light. Your Chef's kitchen features Top-Line two tone cabinetry, smart stainless-steel appliances, pot filler, waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash and accent lighting.   Main level features Primary bedroom designed with wooden accent wall, modern bedside lighting, barn door walk in-closet and private balcony. Your ensuite bath has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience. Two additional bedrooms, full bath and laundry room hookups complete your main level.   Your ground floor level includes full bath and oversized bedroom / entertaining room, which features wet bar and direct access to your private patio and tree lined backyard. Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Ring doorbell, Google thermostat, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smart phone. Garage features non-tandem parking and High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit. The ground level bedroom creates for the perfect Airbnb option. Property is Eligible for Low Rate Loan options and comes with 5 Year Tax Abatement and 10 year warranty."
240018954,SOLD,"JC, Heights",12 IRVING ST,Condominium,1752,6199,"$975,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,00803,00030,Heights,,,,,4,0,3,8,,"$975,000","$969,000",$556.51,$556.51,9/25/2024,1/29/2025,4/11/2025,126,126,,4/16/2025,,,,,,$175,,Conventional,,,,,,Central & Summit,"Modern, sleek elegance is this 4-bedroom, 3 full bath condo with parking, where luxury living awaits its new owner in the booming Jersey City Heights close to the amazing Washington Park with tons of activities. This stunning new construction unit boasts an open concept layout where the spacious, brightly lit living expands into the dining room and chefs kitchen making for a seamless flow for entertaining and everyday living! The fully equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, abundant cabinet space and a spacious island, making it the perfect hub for culinary creativity. The primary bedroom is generously sized with large windows, providing a private retreat where you can unwind and recharge. Ensuite bath that embodies spa-like elegance, complete with a separate glass-enclosed stand-up shower, contemporary vanity with sleek countertops, and premium fixtures and an adjacent walk-in closet. Additional two bedrooms with large windows that flood the space with natural light, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere and a full contemporary bathroom with double vanity complete the main level. The lower-level flex space ideal for family room, home office, or 4th bedroom. all finished with wet bar and another full bathroom. The rare bonus of a private yard is another perk that this condo has to offer allowing for a tranquil oasis for relaxation, gardening, and outdoor gatherings. Additional features include an in-unit washer and dryer, hardwood floors throughout and porcelain floors on lower level, non-tandem garage parking with plenty of storage. Location is key, ideally situated in the Heights, offering easy access to local dining, shopping, and entertainment. Commuting to Manhattan is a breeze with minutes to Congress St. Light Rail, Journal Square PATH and bus station all major highways and tunnels. Don't miss the opportunity to call this exquisite new construction condo your home. Contact today to schedule a viewing and experience urban luxury at its finest. Home qualifies for the Community Loan Program with low interest rate, no PMI and low down payment!"
