220013722,SOLD,"JC, Heights",43 PROSPECT ST,Condominium,1902,1598,"$980,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,05802,00012 02,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$980,000","$999,999",$515.25,$515.25,7/28/2022,8/17/2022,10/5/2022,20,20,,10/6/2022,,,,"$9,521",21,$273,,Conventional,,,,,,Palisade Ave & Baldwin Ave,"Welcome home to this spectacular luxury “Newer Construction”Duplex Condo built in 2020. Spacious 3 Bed / 2.5 Bath offers generous 1902 SqFt of living space and has an open floor layout with ultra modern finishes. Main floor offers contemporary kitchen with white wolf nexus cabinets, high quality quarts countertops, waterfall island, top of the line stainless steel appliances, built in wine fridge, custom closets, crown molding throughout, 4 inch stained red oak hardwood floors, central vacuum, surround system, sprinkler system, aluminum railing, low voltage smart security camera, burglar alarm, video doorbell and etc. Lower level offers an open floor rec/family room, wet bar with built in wine cooler, half a bath and in suite washer and dryer. This home also offers extra insulation and soundproof penetration with Homasote sub flooring, spray foam insulation between joints, 5/8 inch sheetrock, High end quality porcelain in the kitchen and bathrooms, Kohler plumbing fixtures and commercial waterproof garage flooring with extra storage space. Also it offers 2-3 car indoor/outdoor private parking and exclusive landscaped backyard with stone pavers, fire pit, outdoor speakers and gas line for grilling. This home comes with a remaining 8-Year structural builders warranty and a 3-year tax abatement from the City of Jersey City. Short distance to JSQ Path, next to 2nd St Light Rail and Hoboken PATH, bus on the corner, shopping and supermarket few blocks away, park, school and more. Hurry up, don’t miss this amazing opportunity to own this beauty!!"
