240019879,SOLD,"JC, Heights",159 HOPKINS AVE,Condominium,1800,1186,"$985,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07306,,,,,,,,3,0,3,6,,"$985,000","$1,075,000",$547.22,$547.22,2/15/2024,8/9/2024,10/4/2024,176,0,,10/8/2024,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit ave & Central Ave,"Welcome to your new home at 159 Hopkins, where 2 new construction condos await your purchase, either together or separately, in one of the most sought out sections of Jersey City Heights. This unit boasts generous floorplans, 10-foot ceilings, Base and Crown Molding. Kitchens feature beautiful quarts counters and Island, black LG stainless steel appliances, microwave, and wine cooler. Other features include oak flooring throughout, central HVAC, Samsung Washer/Dryer and garage with 2 car parking and electrical charging. Unit 1 features 1800 Sq. Feet of spacious living w/ 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and recreation room. Private balcony overlooking backyard. Experience the pinnacle of luxury living where you will enjoy nearby Riverview Park and a plethora of other recreational activities. A 10-year construction warranty and a 5-year tax abatement further only enhance the appeal of your new home. Owner is a licensed NJ Realtor. Pictures are virtually staged"
250014319,SOLD,"JC, Heights",28 CAMBRIDGE AVE,Condominium,1401,6036,"$985,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,4405,11,,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$985,000","$999,000",$703.07,$703.07,7/15/2025,10/22/2025,12/8/2025,99,99,,12/10/2025,,,,$0,,$202,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton and Franklin,"Welcome to this beautifully crafted, newly developed 3-bedroom, 2-bath condo in the heart of Jersey City Heights, complete with a private rooftop deck offering breathtaking views of the NYC skyline. As you enter, you're immediately greeted by an abundance of natural light streaming through expansive windows, creating an open and airy atmosphere throughout the home. The spacious living areas are enhanced by thoughtful finishes, including wide-plank hardwood floors and 10-ft ceilings that add to the feeling of openness. The kitchen features sleek, modern appliances, elegant quartz countertops, and stylish cabinetry, making it the perfect space for cooking and entertaining. The primary suite offers a serene retreat, with ample closet space and an en-suite bathroom with a private balcony. The two additional bedrooms are generously sized, ideal for family, guests, or a home office. With its light-filled interiors and stunning design, this condo offers a bright, inviting space for those who appreciate both style and comfort.  Located Just 1 mile from the Congress Street Light Rail and the JSQ PATH Station, this home provides the perfect blend of convenience and elegance."
260000799,SOLD,"JC, Heights",146 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1500,1713,"$986,000",CONDO-COOP,,3&4,3,"JC, Heights",07307,2904,40,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$986,000","$999,000",$657.33,$657.33,1/16/2026,1/16/2026,2/27/2026,0,0,,3/3/2026,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith St and Bowers St,"Welcome to 146 Sherman Ave, Unit 3, an elevated 3-bed, 2-bath condo crowned with a private rooftop deck showcasing breathtaking NYC skyline views. This top-floor residence offers an airy, sun-filled layout with hardwood floors, oversized windows, and a seamless open-concept design perfect for modern living. The contemporary kitchen features sleek cabinetry, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances, creating the ideal space for cooking, hosting, and gathering.  The primary suite includes a beautifully finished en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub and generous custom built closet space, while two additional bedrooms provide versatility for guests, a home office, or a nursery. Both bathrooms are outfitted with high-end fixtures and stylish tilework for a clean, modern aesthetic.  The standout feature of Unit 3 is the exclusive private roof deck, a rare retreat with panoramic views of the Manhattan skyline. Perfect for summer lounging, outdoor dining, or hosting unforgettable gatherings, this rooftop oasis elevates your lifestyle in every way.  Situated in the heart of Jersey City Heights, you're moments from Central Avenue’s vibrant shops and eateries, local parks, and convenient transportation to NYC.  Experience luxury living with unmatched skyline views. Unit 3 at 146 Sherman Ave is truly one of a kind."
220000686,SOLD,"JC, Heights",104 LAIDLAW AVE,Condominium,1940,1653,"$990,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07306,05706,00037,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$990,000","$965,000",$510.31,$510.31,1/12/2022,1/19/2022,6/3/2022,7,7,,6/6/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Central & Oakland Avenue,"Location location location! Get in early on this new luxury condominium just steps away from Central Ave Shopping District. This ground up new construction offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a bonus oversized recreational room and half bathroom, with two car garage parking spaces. Experience an open floor layout drenched in natural lighting. The living room has floor to ceiling windows, adorned with exposed wooden beams. This unit stands out with larger bedrooms than your normal new construction. Enjoy the ample cabinet space in your state of the art kitchen, with Samsung stainless steel appliances and smart fridge, a wine fridge, quartz countertop. Features include Hardwood floors, custom trim, recess lighting, chic designer tiles throughout, coat closet, pantry closet, in unit laundry, and modern fixtures. Master bedroom offers a sliding door to walk out to your private oversized balcony, a large walk-in closet, and a master bathroom which includes a double sink vanity. Entertain in your oversized private backyard. Steps away from Pershing Field Park, amazing restaurants on Central Ave, close to NYC transportation, new upcoming reservoir where you can enjoy water activities. Schedule a tour today!"
210021925,SOLD,"JC, Heights",430 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1900,72,"$990,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,02404,00040,Heights,Hubson Court,,,,3,2,2,9,,"$990,000","$924,000",$521.05,$521.05,9/20/2021,9/25/2021,12/10/2021,5,5,,12/10/2021,,,,"$12,814",2020,$325,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Congress & South St.,"Spectacular Ogden Avenue views!  Rare, sought-after, 4-story townhome with garage. This vibrant neighborhood is convenient to Riverview Park, shopping and restaurants.   Enter this home from the maturely-landscaped front courtyard or drive right into the attached garage.   The first level is comprised of an office/den/family room, a half-bath and laundry with radiant heat floors and tons of storage.  Up one flight is the open concept living and dining area, a large, handsomely-renovated eat-in kitchen with a six burner Blue Star range, large farm sink, stainless appliances, radiant heat floor and abundant storage.   There is also a half-bath on this level.  Glass sliders invite you onto the private terrace.  The third floor has the main ensuite plus two additional bedrooms and another full bath.  The bathrooms have been tastefully designed and renovated.   There is a 4th floor, heated and cooled solarium with breathtaking, panoramic views of the New York skyline.  Additionally, there is a shared gated courtyard with picnic, play and garden areas.    Choose your means of transportation into Manhattan with the elevator to the Hoboken light rail just 1 1/2 blocks away or the corner bus to the Port Authority.  Other features of this home include oak flooring, 2-zone heating, central air-conditioning, recessed lighting, newer windows and parking for 2 cars.                   "
240010077,SOLD,"JC, Heights",95 RESERVOIR AVE,Condominium,1859,1597,"$990,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$990,000","$999,000",$532.54,$532.54,5/28/2024,6/5/2024,7/29/2024,8,8,,7/31/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Lienau & Central Ave,"Make your move to modern luxury with this brand new, two-story, three bed, two and half bath home with bonus room, garage and private backyard in The Heights. Contemporary classic design echoes throughout with finishes like crown molding and white oak floors giving a light, bright and airy feel. The wide glass fireplace serves as the focal point, with space above ideal for television or artwork, while the oversized windows bring in loads of natural light.  The open floor plan showcases the kitchen finished with waterfall white quartz counters, modern custom cabinets with natural wood accents, and stainless appliances including a farm sink and microwave drawer. Pendant lighting adds a touch of elegance, while matte black fixtures, including a pot filler, add sophistication and style. Entertain effortlessly in the downstairs bonus room and living area, complete with a wet bar and wine fridge. Then step outside to the private backyard oasis, featuring pavers, white fencing, and lush landscaping.  Spacious bedrooms provide ample light and closet space, while the primary ensuite boasts a deep blue wainscotting feature wall, plus lavish bathroom with double vanity, smart mirror, and glass shower with black porcelain floor-to-ceiling tile. Additional bathrooms include intricate tiling, spacious vanities, and bathtub shower combo. Convenient amenities include coveted garage parking with EV charger capabilities, and a stacking Samsung washer and dryer.  Settled in the heart of Jersey City Heights, owners are one block to Pershing Field Park and Reservoir, and near to shops, boutiques and the 2nd Street Light Rail. The Heights is known for its eclectic arts scene, excellent community and schools, peaceful parks and easy access to NYC and surrounding areas. "
240001509,SOLD,"JC, Heights",112 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1937,1598,"$990,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03404,00034,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$990,000","$975,000",$511.10,$511.10,1/25/2024,2/6/2024,5/1/2024,12,12,,5/1/2024,,,,"$10,171",2023,,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave & Kennedy Ave.,"Looking for modern day conveniences while still enjoying the city life? Look no more! Welcome to this 1900+SQFT home duplex condo with a private walk-out backyard. Spacious 3 bedroom/ 2.5 bathroom plus bonus space that can be used as a family room/ office/ gym/ or playroom.  Fully equipped kitchen features modern white sleek cabinetry, top of the line stainless steel appliances, built in wine fridge, quartz countertops, and a large breakfast island. Kitchen overlooks the expansive living room/ dining room space. Master bedroom features an ensuite, walk-in closet, and private balcony. Additional home features include recessed lighting throughout, hardwood floors, and in-unit washer/dryer. Conveniently located close to restaurant shops, parks, schools, and NYC public transportation. Did we mention one garage parking included? "
250002910,SOLD,"JC, Heights",144 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1919,1613,"$990,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2205,9,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$990,000","$1,060,000",$515.89,$515.89,2/13/2025,6/11/2025,7/23/2025,118,118,,7/24/2025,,,,"$13,053",2024,$195,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Central ave and Palisade ave,"Enjoy luxury living in this fantastic area of Jersey City Heights! This spacious duplex condo will make you feel right at home, featuring 2 levels of living space, 1,919 SQFT and Central Air & and beautiful fenced-in back yard.  Enter the first floor and find an open family room with half bath, washer and dryer, sliding door to the backyard, with one car garage. Walk up to the second floor where you’ll be welcomed by open concept living room/kitchen/dining area, 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, stainless steel appliances, wood floors throughout, recessed lighting and lots of natural light.  Conveniently located walking distance to Congress Light rail, Central Ave shops, banks, restaurants, cafes, stores, local and NYC transportation, a stone’s throw to Hoboken & Journal Square, schools and houses of worship & parks. The property is currently rented for $5k per month.  The monthly HOA is $194.75 to cover insurance and water. Don’t miss out this great opportunity to own this gorgeous condo! "
240022694,SOLD,"JC, Heights",246 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1900,1692,"$994,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 + 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2306,12,Heights,,,,,4,0,3,9,,"$994,000","$1,049,000",$523.16,$523.16,11/21/2024,3/7/2025,4/15/2025,106,106,,4/23/2025,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,South and Bowers,"With a true mother-in-law suite complete with a full bathroom, kitchenette, separate entrance, and private backyard, this one-of-a-kind home, crafted by a trusted builder, is a luxurious, oversized, brand-new boutique condo located in the heart of Jersey City. ----- At nearly 2,100 interior square feet, 246 Webster, Unit A offers dynamic living space in a vibrant community. The property’s main level features a well-appointed, traditional three-bedroom, two-bath layout. The large kitchen, bathed in natural light from a north-facing picture window, is finished with a granite waterfall countertop, custom cabinets, and a designer wood-paneled Fisher & Paykel appliance package. ------- Down the hallway, there are two spacious bedrooms, a high-tech laundry room, and a full bath with Porcelanosa tiles, a tasteful vanity, and modern fixtures. At the end of the hall lies the master bedroom, complete with an ensuite bathroom, a glass-enclosed shower, a double vanity, a walk-in closet, and a small balcony. ----- The home is fully connected with smart controls including door and doorbell, lighting, and speakers.  --- All of this, plus the bonus apartment downstairs, makes this home a must-see. Surrounded by the vibrant life and culture that make The Heights highly sought after, 246 Webster is truly a condo apart from the rest. "
260005204,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",373 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1465,5069,"$995,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$995,000",$679.18,,3/25/2026,,,15,,,3/25/2026,,,,$0,,,,,No,No,Yes,,,Bowers and Congress,"2-YEAR FREE PARKING. RATE BUY DOWN WITH RATES AS LOW AS 4.875%. Terms and eligibility apply-- please inquire for details. MOMENTS FROM CONGRESS ST LIGHT RAIL STATION AND RIVERVIEW FISK PARK. Welcome to 373 New York Avenue, Jersey City — Blue Chip Properties’ most iconic and sought-after project to date. This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom duplex home is located in the highly desirable New York Avenue enclave, known for its close proximity to the 9th Street Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park, Hoboken, and the gourmet dining scene of Palisade Avenue. Designed with timeless interior finishes, high-end fixtures, and meticulous craftsmanship, this residence also offers cutting-edge modern technology for elevated daily living.  The main entrance opens to a grand open-concept dining and living area with soaring ceilings, oversized Andersen energy-efficient windows, abundant natural light, and a statement-making realistic flame fireplace. The chef’s kitchen is outfitted with designer two-tone cabinetry, Thermador appliance package with paneled refrigerator and dishwasher, 5 burner range, and heating drawer.  The oversized double waterfall quartz island showcases luxurious West Elm accent lighting, along with porcelain backsplash with a convenient Pot Filler, and an externally vented hood. Flowing seamlessly from the kitchen is your entertainment zone featuring a wet bar with custom cabinetry, backlit designer backsplash, and wine fridge.   The primary suite is a serene retreat featuring custom warm wood-tone millwork, bedside pendant lighting, a walk-in closet with built-ins. The spa-like ensuite bath showcases modern natural tones, an oversized double vanity, soaking tub, warm pendant lighting, and a luxurious shower with multiple Kohler body sprays and rainfall showerhead. The two additional bedrooms include custom-finished closets and share a beautifully appointed full bath with double vanity and floor-to-ceiling tiles. A separate laundry room with top-of-the-line washer and dryer completes this unit.   This fully equipped smart home includes a Google Nest doorbell, security cameras, Google Smart Hub, smart thermostat, touchscreen light switches, dimmers, and more — all seamlessly controlled via smartphone, along with a security camera system. The home is completed with Blue Chip Properties’ signature exterior facade and professional landscaping. Property includes a 10-year builder’s warranty. Square footage is approximate. Offsite parking is available, inquire further."
240010923,SOLD,"JC, Heights",240 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1818,1707,"$995,100",CONDO-COOP,,1 - 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02302,00006,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$995,100","$995,000",$547.36,$547.36,6/6/2024,7/2/2024,9/23/2024,26,26,,9/24/2024,,,,"$13,707",2023,$370,,Conventional,,,,,,*,"Welcome to the East Side of Jersey City Heights; prime location!  This spectacular 3 bed, 2.5 bath condo situated in a very quiet neighborhood features 1818 square feet and two levels of living space, modern kitchen containing quartz counter tops with waterfall island and Samsung black stainless steel appliances, master bedroom with full bath and walk in closet, hardwood floors, wine fridge, custom closets, high end finishes including crown moldings, central vacuum system, sprinkler system thru the entire home, 5.1 channel home theater surround sound, Ring security camera, family room with wet bar leading to a private back yard having gas-water-electric connections and 2 channel surround sound, washer/dryer, deeded garage parking and much more!  Close proximity to New York transportation (bus & rail), shopping, restaurants, parks (Washington and Riverview) and schools (including PS 28 Christa McAuliffe - Prek4 thru 8th).  Builders warranty. Schedule your appointment now!   "
230008685,SOLD,"JC, Heights",134 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1926,6199,"$998,888",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,04302,00011,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$998,888","$998,888",$518.63,$518.63,5/26/2023,6/1/2023,7/14/2023,6,6,,7/14/2023,,,,$0,,$175,2023,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Summit Ave. and Sanford Pl.,"Inspired from the pages of architectural digest, we bring you our newest listing… a nearly 2000 sqft, 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home with 1 car non-tandem parking designed and custom built by Blue Chip Living. It is perfectly situated on Manhattan Avenue in the heart of Jersey City Heights!  Boasting a contemporary design, luxurious features, and great location, this unit offers the pinnacle of modern living. Enter inside and be greeted by an inviting open floor plan with 12 foot high ceilings that seamlessly blends style and functionality. The spacious living area is bathed in natural light, creating an airy ambiance, ideal for both relaxation and entertaining all leading into the dining area which opens to the gourmet modern kitchen, which is a chef's dream, featuring stainless steel appliances, sleek quartz countertops, and ample storage space.     The primary bedroom is a private sanctuary complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom featuring a stand-up shower, a generous walk-in closet and a sliding door leading to the private balcony! Down the hall are an additional three good sized bedrooms all with closet space for storage needs, complete with another full bath with double vanity. This unit also features a side by side laundry room, and a half bath. Beyond the interior, this home presents an outdoor haven with private roof deck access. Enjoy al fresco dining or simply unwind on the serene roof deck, perfect for creating unforgettable memories with family and friends.  This home includes smart home technology which creates ease of living with Ring doorbell, Nest thermostat and Smart Fridge to name a few. One car Parking with EV charger port is included with this unit. Located on Manhattan Avenue, you'll have the best of both worlds – a residential setting combined with easy access to the vibrant energy of Jersey City.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary unit by Blue Chip Living your own. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and experience the epitome of luxury!"
