230020155,SOLD,"JC, Heights",130 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,1740,1724,"$999,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03502,00021,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$999,000","$1,075,000",$574.14,$574.14,12/4/2023,12/21/2023,2/1/2024,17,17,,2/2/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Kennedy and Sanford,"Welcome to this exquisite Brand New Construction luxury condo, ideally situated on one of the most coveted streets in JC Heights. This meticulously designed residence spans an impressive 1740 square feet across two floors, offering three bedrooms and 2.5 baths. As you step into this thoughtfully crafted home, you are greeted by an open and airy layout that seamlessly integrates a spacious living and dining area. The interior is adorned with contemporary accents, featuring high ceilings, light-finished 6 wide plank hardwood flooring, Anderson windows, a custom-built electric fireplace, and 8-foot custom entry doors throughout, creating a welcoming ambiance. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, boasting 60-inch sleek custom soft-closing cabinets, a walk-in pantry closet, quartz countertops, a stylish backsplash, and a spacious center island. The kitchen is equipped with a full suite of VIKING appliances, ensuring both functionality and sophistication. The generous Primary Bedroom is a true retreat. It includes two spacious closets and one walk-in, a private balcony overlooking the serene of your private backyard, and an en-suite bathroom featuring floor-to-ceiling custom tiling, a glass-enclosed rain shower, and double vanity sinks. In addition to the lavish Primary Bedroom, this luxury condo boasts two additional spacious bedrooms, each adorned with ample living space and large closets. Travel downstairs to discover a spacious rec room with a full wet bar kitchen, providing seamless access to your private yard—an ideal space for entertaining guests and creating lasting memories. As a testament to convenience and luxury, this exceptional property also includes indoor WIDE garage TANDEM parking shared with unit 2, ensuring hassle-free access, and two deeded storage closets for added convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this sophisticated and meticulously designed condo your new home. Nestled on a street adorned with beautiful historic preserved homes and within walking distance to Pershing Field Park, this home encapsulates the best of urban living. Residents will appreciate its proximity to NYC transportation, neighboring districts, and an array of shops, restaurants, and cultural attractions."
240002412,SOLD,"JC, Heights",33 CARLTON AVE,Condominium,1746,6078,"$999,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,4702,8,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$999,000","$999,000",$572.16,$572.16,2/8/2024,2/19/2024,5/3/2024,11,11,,5/5/2024,,,,,,$290,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit and Montrose,"Introducing: The Carlton, where Location meets Luxury!! 2 years in the making, “33 Carlton Ave”, the Pershing Field Gem, is a collection of two ultra-luxurious brand new condominiums, brought to you by the Jersey City’s Top builder, Kuber Construction, in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This exquisite property is an epitome of comfort, space and modern design. Elevate your standards of living with these massive, meticulously designed, duplex homes, featuring designer finishes throughout, White Oak flooring, Recessed Lighting, Crown and Baseboard Moulding, Central HVAC, Nest Thermostat, Ring Doorbell, Camera Security, Pella Awning Windows, 10-foot ceilings, 8-foot doors and contemporary Matte black fixtures, on an oversized 25’ x 125’ lot, steps from Pershing Field Park(the most famous 13.5 acres park).  Immerse yourself in an impressive audio experience with surround sound WIFI/Bluetooth speakers installed throughout this smart home.  Expansive Unit 2 condominium spans over ~1,746 square feet, spread across two separate floors, offering oversized 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and a coveted private rooftop deck. Step inside this thoughtfully crafted home, and be greeted by an open and airy layout that seamlessly integrates a spacious living and dining area. The sophisticated living room features Brooklyn-Style BRICK TV wall with integrated ultra-thin electric fireplace, pine wood walnut paneling, modern LED lighting fixture, pre-wired wifi-speakers for entertainment, and oversized black windows allowing abundance of natural light throughout the day. The living/dining room seamlessly flows into the sophisticated chef’s kitchen showcasing an abundance of dramatic yin-yang glossy cabinetry with fine white/black modern trim, elegant quartz countertops, electrifying glossy black drop-ceiling filled with spotlights and integrated pendant lighting, Samsung Bluetooth Refrigerator, 5-burner Gas/Oven range, Pot Filler, Wine Cooler, Microwave, Dishwasher, Stainless Steel Sink, making it a culinary enthusiast's dream kitchen. Adjacent to the living/dining room is a thoughtfully designed powder room, adding convenience and sophistication to the living space. The master-suite, a true retreat, provides a dedicated office/den space, also boasts access to a private balcony overlooking the serene backyard. The elegantly designed Ensuite Master Bathroom, equipped with Rain Shower, Waterfall and Panel style unique porcelain tiles, white high-gloss double vanity, SOAKING EUROPEAN BATH TUB, creates a spa-like experience. Master bedroom also features Custom Walk-In Closet finished with solid wood barn-door that seamlessly glides on a black metallic rail. This magnificent condominium that rivals Manhattan standard luxury, provides two additional queen size bedrooms, a second bathroom and a laundry room with full-size LG washer and dryer units. Travel upstairs to the upper level, where you'll discover treasured 632 SQFT of private outdoor space, whether its sipping your morning coffee on a secluded terrace, or taking in the sunset, or enjoying the views of Pershing Field and NYC skyline, this rooftop is set to making lasting memories. Each unit offers Exclusive Non-Tandem Garage Parking for our new homeowners looking to take advantage of covered parking in R1 zone, without hassling the neighbors.   Settled on a prestigious tree-lined, quiet, residential, extra wide street of Jersey City Heights, one block from Pershing Field Park, adjacent to Jersey City Reservoir No. 3, and bustling Central avenue, provides an unparalleled living experience. Located just 5 minutes away from the Journal Square PATH station, commuting to New York City is a breeze. Walking distance to boutique shops, restaurants, cafés and parks, this home is ideally located for a balance of urban living and secluded sanctuary. Jersey City Heights is known for its tight-knit community, great schools and easy access to NYC. **10-Year Builders Warranty, Eligible for 5 yr. tax abatement"
240001346,SOLD,"JC, Heights",431 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1700,1597,"$999,000",CONDO-COOP,,2+3,4,"JC, Heights",07307,03902,00028,,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$999,000","$1,099,000",$587.65,$587.65,1/23/2024,2/16/2024,4/19/2024,24,24,,4/24/2024,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith st. and Hutton st.,"Experience the breathtaking New York City skyline from your own private rooftop in this unique, newly renovated 1,700 sqft top-floor residence, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, along with an exclusive 126 sqft rooftop terrace. The residence boasts an open living area, flooded with natural light and adorned with high-end finishes, creating the perfect ambiance for both entertaining and relaxation. Nestled in a charming brick building on Palisade Avenue, this home is just steps from Riverview Fisk Park and a block from the 2nd Street Light Rail station, offering easy access to Hoboken. Enjoy the vibrant community and easy access to cafes, restaurants, shops and services. Additional dedicated storage place in the basement. Taxes are TBD. ***Check out the linked virtual tour!***"
240024393,SOLD,"JC, Heights",334 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,2400,1713,"$999,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-3,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2305,22,,,,,,3,2,2,10,,"$999,000","$1,100,000",$416.25,$416.25,1/2/2025,2/19/2025,3/25/2025,48,48,,4/1/2025,,,,"$10,426",2023,$289,,VA,,,,,,South St & Bowers St,"**RESERVED RENTAL PARKING, LESS THAN TWO BLOCKS AWAY** 334 New York Avenue redefines modern luxury living, offering a spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom layout with private roof deck, right across the street from Riverview Park. The main floor features an open-concept living and dining area, complemented by a beautifully designed chef’s kitchen boasting sleek quartz countertops, a pot-filler, premium stainless steel appliances including a Thermador range, under-counter microwave, vented range hood, wine fridge, ample cabinetry, and a wrap-around breakfast bar. The upper floor houses the serene primary suite with an en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet, along with generously sized additional bedrooms and a full bath. Outdoor enthusiasts and entertainers will adore the expansive private roof terrace. Reserved rental parking is conveniently available less than two blocks away. With over 1,700 square feet of living space, stylish finishes, and thoughtful details throughout, this condo is the epitome of urban elegance in Jersey City. Additional features like extra storage closets, a dedicated utility area, and premium flooring throughout provide both luxury and convenience in one of Jersey City’s most desirable neighborhoods. Enjoy close proximity to your NYC commute via light rail and NJ Transit bus, as well as all the shops, restaurants, and entertainment The Heights has to offer."
