260003108,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",100 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1600,1597,"$999,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,,"$999,000",$624.38,,2/23/2026,,,45,,,2/23/2026,,,,,,$492,,,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"1 car rental spot pre-paid for 1 year!   Stay safe!  Step into elevated design and modern convenience with these three ground up new construction 3 bedroom + office/den, 2.5 bath units with private outdoor space in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Set on Webster Avenue with a striking white brick exterior, this home is bathed in natural light, highlighting a spacious open-concept layout with premium Legno Bastone wide-plank hardwood flooring and high-end finishes.  The oversized windows frame a beautifully designed kitchen featuring modern sage green and natural light oak custom cabinetry, white quartz waterfall countertops, and a matching backsplash. Premium Fisher & Paykel appliances bring both style and functionality, making this space perfect for cooking and entertaining.  The primary ensuite bathroom is a luxurious retreat with elegant gold accents, and a glass-enclosed shower with a multi-spray system and rain head. Additional features include ample closet space & brand-new washer and dryer.  Located just one block from popular cafés and restaurants like Froth on Franklin and The Franklin, the best of The Heights is at your doorstep. The 2nd Street stairs to Hoboken provide quick access to the Light Rail, PATH, and ferry, making commuting to NYC effortless. Known for its vibrant community, excellent parks and schools, and stunning skyline views, Jersey City Heights continues to be one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in the area."
240014131,SOLD,"JC, Heights",122 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1665,1724,"$999,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,402,"JC, Heights",07307,04504,00001,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$999,000","$999,000",$600.00,$600.00,7/19/2024,7/19/2024,7/22/2024,0,0,,7/29/2024,,,,,,,,Cash,,,,,,Ferry St. & Franklin St.,"The York presents a remarkable opportunity to experience luxurious living in Jersey City Heights. This concrete and steel new construction at 122 New York Ave is a testament to modern architecture, offering residents a tranquil retreat with unobstructed views of the Manhattan skyline. The building's design is both contemporary and functional, featuring a range of high-end amenities that cater to every aspect of urban living. Residents can enjoy the convenience of an indoor climate-controlled garage with bike storage, ensuring their vehicles and bicycles are kept secure and protected from the elements. The expansive communal rooftop deck is a standout feature, providing a space to relax and entertain while taking in the stunning cityscape. Each of the 9 finely appointed homes is accessible via a chic lobby, with the elevator opening directly to a landing with only two units per floor, ensuring privacy and exclusivity. The spacious condominiums span approximately 1,545 square feet, with an open floor layout that includes 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Attention to detail is evident throughout, from the Bosch stainless steel appliances and modernized cabinetry in the chef's kitchen to the in-unit gas washer/dryer and in-ceiling speakers managed by a Sonos amplifier. The living areas are adorned with 5 wide French oak plank hardwood floors, while the bathrooms feature Porcelanosa tile and plumbing fixtures, LED lighting, and heated floors for ultimate comfort. The builder has prioritized a soundproofed environment, utilizing advanced materials such as sound channels, sound clips, Quiet Rock, green/noise proofing compound, and foam insulation to create a peaceful sanctuary. The York's prime location offers easy access to public transportation, with Palisade Ave just a block away, providing direct bus lines to NYC Port Authority, Hoboken, and Downtown JC. The Hudson Light Rail Stations are also conveniently close. Residents can take advantage of nearby Pershing Field's indoor pool and ice skating rink, as well as Riverview Park for community events. For those interested in exploring this exceptional property and scheduling a private showing, please visit theyorkjc or contact the listing agent. Don't miss the chance to embrace the epitome of luxury at The York in Jersey City Heights."
230009793,SOLD,"JC, Heights",265 GRIFFITH ST,Condominium,1932,1581,"$999,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,3404,17,,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$999,000","$999,000",$517.08,$517.08,6/13/2023,7/27/2023,9/27/2023,44,44,,9/27/2023,,,,,,$177,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave & Kennedy Blvd,"Welcome to 265 Griffith Street, Unit #1, a stunning new construction duplex residence boasting exquisite finishes and its own private backyard. This exceptional 1,932.67 sq ft home offers a unique blend of luxury and functionality, featuring three-bedrooms plus an office or family room. Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the open and bright first floor plan adorned with lush weathered oak flooring and Anderson windows that flood the space with natural light. The modern kitchen is a chef's dream, showcasing sleek quartz countertops, elegant pendant lights, a built-in wine cooler, and an appliance package. Custom linen finished cabinetry adds a touch of sophistication, while built-in speakers and a smart video intercom system provide convenience and entertainment. The main entrance welcomes you with high ceilings and leads you to three generously-sized bedrooms, each equipped with private closets for optimal storage, and complete with a built-in laundry area. The primary bedroom offers a private balcony, an en-suite bathroom adorned with pastorelli porcelain tile, and double vanity sinks for a touch of luxury. Descending to the lower level, you'll discover a versatile office/entertainment room featuring a wet bar and beverage fridge, as well as a full bathroom. Through sliding doors, you'll be transported to a private backyard, perfect for relaxation and outdoor gatherings, enhanced by built-in outdoor speakers and gas-grill ready connection. Convenience is paramount with a dedicated parking spot in the garage and access to a storage area. 265 Griffith is just steps away from the local bus stops, providing easy transportation to and from NYC. Additionally, you'll find an array of shops and restaurants on Central Avenue, ensuring a vibrant and lively lifestyle. Meticulously crafted by one of Jersey City Height's most experienced developers, this home is truly a masterpiece. Furthermore, take advantage of Jersey City's 5 Year 'New Construction' Tax Abatement, offering an excellent financial incentive for homeowners. Embrace the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own, and experience a lifestyle of unparalleled comfort and sophistication."
210022552,SOLD,"JC, Heights",230 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1788,1702,"$999,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03904,00014,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$999,000","$995,000",$558.72,$558.72,9/29/2021,9/30/2021,12/13/2021,1,1,,12/17/2021,,,,,,$229,2021,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Griffith St & Franklin St,"This is it -- the final home to be offered at 230 Ogden Avenue. Discreetly tucked away on the most exquisite and private block of the most sought after street in Jersey City Heights, Residence 2 at 230 Ogden Avenue is a 1,788 SF three bedroom, two-and-a-half bathroom with parking for two cars that has been purpose-built to showcase jaw-dropping, panoramic views of the Hudson River and New York City with a wrap-around balcony and floor-to-ceiling windows. Perched on the edge of the Palisades, the open-concept living, dining and entertaining area is framed on one end by an open kitchen with richly stained shaker millwork, under-cabinet lighting, granite countertops and a full suite of stainless steel appliances, and on the other by mesmerizing views of New York City that magically stretch from the Upper West Side to the Verrazano Bridge. The city's most iconic buildings are seemingly an outstretched hand away and perhaps even more astonishing when experienced year-round from the private covered balcony. The palatial owner's suite offers southern exposure, three closets -- including two walk-in closets -- and a welcoming en-suite spa bathroom with oversized glass-enclosed walk-in shower, deep soaking tub and a double vanity. It is complemented by two generously sized bedrooms, crisply appointed bathroom with tub, and a perfectly located powder room. Life at home in Residence 2 is further enhanced by central air, ecobee3 lite smart thermostat with Amazon Alexa or Google Assistant integration, gas fireplace and full-size side-by-side washer/dryer. Benefiting from an ideal Jersey City Heights location with incredible walking access to a vibrant, evolving network of local shopping that includes grocery stores, farmer's markets and destination-worthy restaurants, bars and coffee shops, The Penthouse at 230 Ogden Avenue is also as commutable as can be -- it is within two blocks of multiple bus lines that service both New York City (Port Authority) and Hoboken Terminal (PATH, NY Waterway Ferry, NJ Transit), and an easy stroll to the 2nd Street Light Rail station which services Hoboken Terminal and points throughout downtown Jersey City and beyond. Riverview-Fisk Park, renowned for its panoramic views of New York City and impressive farmer's market, and Pershing Field Park, known for its running track, numerous ball fields and swimming pool, are each a short walk away. Taxes to be determined."
250018822,SOLD,"JC, Heights",245 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1715,6199,"$999,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & 3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,03903,00052,,,,,,2,1,2,9,,"$999,000","$1,050,000",$582.51,$582.51,9/12/2025,12/4/2025,1/23/2026,83,83,,2/2/2026,,,,"$16,095",,$275,,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith St & Franklin St,"Private Garage parking, Private Roof Deck & Stunning NYC views on Ogden Ave! Don’t miss out on this spectacular, one-of-a-kind duplex situated on one of Jersey City Heights’ most sought-after streets. 245 Ogden Avenue #2 offers residents an expansive, light filled home with soaring 19-foot ceilings, copious oversized windows, and Brazilian wood floors. With 1715 square-feet of living space and high-end features, the modern design of this home provides the perfect urban oasis. Spread over two levels this condominium home features a bright, open layout which encompasses a spacious dining area, a powder room, and a beautifully updated contemporary kitchen. The kitchen has everything you need with chic cabinetry providing plentiful storage, quartz countertops, stylish pendant lighting, an undermount sink, stainless steel appliances – including a smart refrigerator and free standing gas range – and a quartz breakfast bar. The spacious living room is bathed in natural light with an airy atmosphere, and built-ins that provide storage, the living room is the ideal place to relax and entertain. The expansive, primary bedroom suite is the perfect, private place to revitalize. Effortlessly relax at the end of a long day in your roomy master bedroom with a custom walk in closet, a terrace to sip your morning coffee & ensuite that contains a soaking Jacuzzi tub-shower, double vanity with undermount sinks. The second bedroom has plentiful space to accommodate a queen-sized bed, desk and additional furniture while containing two, oversized closets for storage. The second full bathroom provides a tub-shower and stylish vanity to rejuvenate. Prepare to be impressed by the home’s stunning, large, private roof deck that allows owners to entertain with ease. Magnificent views of the NYC skyline, the deck offers plenty of space to set up a grill, lounge chairs, & outdoor dining table to host gatherings. Roof deck offers your very own green house to satisfy your green thumb. Residents will appreciate the home’s very own private garage parking with plenty of storage plus a second parking space on the driveway. Location! Location! Live in this vibrant community near public transit, including a bus to NYC and Light Rail. The home is also located 100 steps to Hoboken, half a block from Riverview Fisk Park which hosts the Sunday Farmer's Market, and near all the cool  bakeries, coffee shops, and restaurants. Come experience this amazing home today! This condo may qualify for a 5.375 interest rate.     "
250001669,SOLD,"JC, Heights",198 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1394,6712,"$999,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,3,,"$999,000","$999,950",$716.64,$716.64,1/17/2025,3/3/2025,4/4/2025,45,37,,6/4/2025,,,,"$13,391",,,,Conventional,,,,,,South St.,"This meticulous sun-filled home features extra large windows, and an expansive living area that flows seamlessly, integrating the living, dining, and kitchen spaces into one inviting layout. Complete with a fully modern chef's kitchen with a vented hood and built-in microwave draw, it is outfitted with high-gloss custom cabinetry, gleaming black granite countertops, and a large, inviting breakfast bar. The primary bedroom includes en-suite bath with double vanities, LED mirrors, glass enclosed shower with multi-head system, walk-in closet and a private balcony. This unit has a rooftop with spectacular views of New York City. Unit boasts 2 additional bedrooms, 4 inch hardwood floors throughout, upgraded lighting, and a custom electric fireplace. HOA fee $120 per month. Tax abatement for 2 years."
230005062,SOLD,"JC, Heights",305 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,2600,6199,"$999,900",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02306,00050,,,,,,3,1,3,9,,"$999,900","$974,900",$384.58,$384.58,3/30/2023,4/7/2023,5/4/2023,8,8,,5/5/2023,,,,"$14,155",22,$270,23,Conventional,,,,,,South and Bowers,"Massive 2,600s/f 3 bedroom/3.5 bathroom duplex home in the heart of Jersey City Heights. The main living floor of this recently built home features an expansive living/dining area with half bathroom, perfect for entertaining and an open concept kitchen that boasts a top-of-the-line stainless steel appliance package, luxurious quartz countertops, large island and an abundance of cabinet storage. Adjacent to the main living space is an 18’ x 24’ bedroom with an En-suite full bathroom complete with a dual vanity, separate shower and bathtub, ample closet space and direct access to a private 18’ x 22’ fenced in yard with paver patio and privacy fence. The second level of the home features a generous primary suite complimented by generous closets and built-ins, an En-suite spa-like bathroom with rain fall shower, separate tub and dual vanity. As an added bonus, the primary suite has a private 77s/f direct access balcony that overlooks the yard. Third bedroom also features a direct En-suite bathroom with tub and great closet storage. As an added bonus, there is a 24’ x 17’ multi-purpose room with fireplace (perfect for family-room, playroom, home office or den). Additional highlights include central A/C, custom tiling throughout, recessed lighting, washer/dryer, high ceilings, smart home features, and off-street parking. Located in the heart of the Riverview Arts District of Jersey City Heights, you will find easy access to restaurants, coffee shops, Washington Park and Riverview Park (1 block away) with amenities such as tennis courts, dog runs, children’s play areas, picnic areas, views of NYC, Farmer’s markets and so much more! Located 1 block from the NJ Transit bus to Port Authority and 4 blocks to the 9th and Congress LightRail station to the Hoboken PATH."
230016285,SOLD,"JC, Heights",155 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1610,1686,"$999,999",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,05101,00021,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$999,999","$970,000",$621.12,$621.12,9/28/2023,10/3/2023,11/29/2023,5,5,,11/29/2023,,,,"$12,199",2022,$236,2022,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Palisade Ave,"Welcome to this exceptional 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom condo with multi-floor living, boasting a modern and luxurious lifestyle in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Built in 2019, this pristine residence offers a perfect blend of contemporary design and thoughtful custom features that make it a truly unique offering. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the spaciousness and elegance of this 1610-square-foot home. The open-concept living area is bathed in natural light, creating a welcoming atmosphere perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. One of the standout features of this condo is the custom private backyard, accessible directly from the lower living area. This outdoor oasis provides a tranquil escape from the bustling city life, ideal for hosting gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying some fresh air. The primary bedroom is a true retreat with a custom walk-in closet that offers ample storage. The ensuite primary bathroom is equally impressive with modern fixtures and finishes, ensuring your daily routines are both convenient and indulgent. The lower level of this condo boasts a custom-designed bar in the spacious living room, making it an excellent space for socializing. Whether you're mixing cocktails or watching your favorite sports, this area is sure to become a favorite hangout spot. This home also features the convenience of garage parking with direct access to the condo and the in-unit washer and dryer on the main floor provide added convenience for your daily chores. Located on one of the most desirable streets in Jersey City Heights, you'll find yourself in a vibrant and diverse community. Conveniently close to all public transportation options, allowing for an easy commute to Manhattan and other parts of Jersey City. Parks and restaurants are just a stone's throw away, providing endless opportunities for outdoor recreation and culinary exploration."
220020997,SOLD,"JC, Heights",183 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1755,6078,"$999,999",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,4,0,3,10,,"$999,999","$995,000",$569.80,$569.80,12/4/2022,1/16/2023,3/3/2023,43,43,,3/3/2023,,,,$0,2023,$150,,Conventional,,,,,,South street and Bowers Street,"Welcome to 183 Sherman Avenue, a luxury new construction development built by one of Jersey City’s top local developers, Blue Chip Properties, a company known for their unique design esthetic, high end finishes and quality workmanship.   Unit One is one of a kind custom duplex condo featuring an open concept kitchen, living, and dining space that is illuminated with direct sunlight coming through the oversized Anderson windows.   The Chefs Kitchen features two tone high-gloss European Style cabinetry, premium stainless steel smart appliances, modern porcelain backsplash, central island with waterfall quartz countertop, pot filler, custom lighting, and hidden drawer microwave.   The primary bedroom is highlighted by a wooden feature wall with modern accent lighting, an en suite spa-like bathroom, walk-in closet and a large balcony overlooking the private backyard. This makes for a perfect place to relax after a busy day.   Other key features include custom 8 ft doors throughout the entire property, matte black hardware, hardwood floors, Washer and dryer hookups, Designer Lighting fixtures and Smart Home Technology. Ease of living is created using the Ring doorbell, Nest thermostat, Lighting Dimmer Switches, etc. (all accessible via smartphone).   There are 2 levels of living space for a total of 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, a private outdoor backyard and custom wet bar. The ground level bedroom has a walkout entrance giving you easy access to the backyard and street.   Non-tandem garage parking with a high voltage EV Charger outlet is included. Low HOA fees. Easy access into NYC via bus or train.  Congress street light rail station is a 5 min walk, walking distance to both Washington Park and Riverview- Fisk Park.    The Ground Level bedroom can be a great Airbnb option as Jersey City is the most visited Airbnb’s in the state of NJ.  The Ultimate Jersey City Heights Experience!   Property is eligible for a 5 year tax abatement. Schedule your appointment today."
230019390,SOLD,"JC, Heights",376 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1613,6546,"$999,999",CONDO-COOP,,2 & 3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,02404,00019,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$999,999","$1,049,000",$619.96,$619.96,11/16/2023,11/16/2023,12/29/2023,0,0,,1/4/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,South & Bowers St,"Come find out for yourself why Jersey City has been nicknamed the Sixth Borough of New York City.  From the diverse community to the endless restaurants and nightlife to the multiple parks, playgrounds, and museums … there is quite literally something for everyone in this city.      Check out this newly renovated duplex – from the modern open concept living space to the private terrace with incredible views of the NYC skyline this condo offers it all.  Located in one of most desirable Jersey City Height blocks you can find yourself minutes away from Journal Square PATH, bus stations, and all major highways and tunnels.      Opening the door to this spacious and luxurious condo you find a fully equipped kitchen – from the stainless-steel appliances to custom white cabinets and quartz counter tops – you are captivated instantly.  Offering 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, the main bathroom features a double sink vanity, tub, and standup shower.  You will find two generous sized bedrooms both drenched in natural light. The top floor features a 3rd bedroom loft – endless amounts of space for entertaining and relaxing with stunning views of NYC. Open the doors to your roof top deck and bring the city view into your home! This unit has some fantastic features such as hardwood floors throughout, center air/heat, washer and dryer, and LED lighting.  Stop by for a tour, and we promise you will not be disappointed!"
240019899,SOLD,"JC, Heights",248 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1800,1623,"$999,999",CONDO-COOP,,2&3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$999,999","$1,099,000",$555.56,$555.56,10/8/2024,3/10/2025,5/9/2025,153,152,,5/12/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers & Griffith,"Introducing 248 New York Ave, a brand-new luxury condo in a boutique two-unit building, offering 1,800 square feet of sophisticated living across two beautifully designed levels. This spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home boasts an open floor plan with soaring high ceilings and is flooded with natural light throughout, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere.  The main level features two expansive living spaces perfect for entertaining, a state-of-the-art kitchen with top-of-the-line finishes, and sleek, modern baths. Upstairs, step out to your private rooftop terrace with stunning city views and hookups for water, gas, and electricity—ideal for outdoor entertaining, dining, or relaxing under the stars.  This home is equipped with central air and an on-demand hot water system for year-round comfort and efficiency. Located just one block from River-Fisk View Park, this prime Jersey City Heights location offers easy access to parks, shops, dining, and transportation.  Experience modern luxury with the convenience of city living in this exceptional condo—don’t miss your chance to make it yours!"
240004401,SOLD,"JC, Heights",88 PROSPECT ST,Condominium,2577,1724,"$999,999",CONDO-COOP,,2-3,2,"JC, Heights",07305,05006,00023,Heights,,,,,4,1,3,7,,"$999,999","$999,999",$388.05,$388.05,3/8/2024,3/20/2024,6/3/2024,12,12,,6/4/2024,,,,$0,,$0,0,Conventional,,,,,,Lienau Pl & Webster Ave.,"Step into modern luxury with this exquisitely renovated sun-drenched condo featuring high ceilings that elevate the sense of space and sophistication. This residence offers over 2400 sq’ of luxurious open floor plan, with four incredibly large bedrooms, each equipped with closets customizable to buyers' needs. The main level boasts an on-suite, perfect for accommodating extended family members, ensuring both privacy and convenience. With 3.5 baths, this home provides ultimate comfort and convenience.  The living and entertaining space is truly remarkable, featuring an open layout that seamlessly blends style and functionality. An approximately 1200 square-foot large roof deck adds to the allure, creating the perfect setting for both intimate gatherings and larger celebrations with family and friends. Nestled near Pershing Field, residents have the convenience of year-round indoor ice skating and access to an indoor swimming pool, ensuring endless activities for the whole family.  Beyond the doorstep, this home is surrounded by the best Jersey City has to offer – from convenient transportation options to a diverse array of restaurants, vibrant nightlife, and trendy shops. Commute with ease from this strategically located property, as it provides seamless access to transportation hubs. Embrace the perfect blend of contemporary living and neighborhood charm, making this residence an ideal choice for those seeking both comfort and convenience in the heart of Jersey City.  *Rental parking available.*  **The images shown are for illustration purposes only and may not be an exact representation of the product. Images depict Unit 2 which have similar finishes.**"
240013310,SOLD,"JC, Heights",97 NORTH ST,Condominium,1900,1499,"$999,999",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,01505,00024,,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$999,999","$999,999",$526.32,$526.32,7/10/2024,7/25/2024,9/9/2024,15,15,,9/9/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,,,,,Summit & Central," Are you Ready to enjoy summer in The Heights? Welcome home to 97 North Street. Step into this stunning Brand-New Construction luxury condominium, perfectly positioned on one of JC Heights' most sought-after streets. Spanning across two levels, this meticulously crafted residence boasts three bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Upon entry, you'll be greeted by an inviting, light-filled space that merges a spacious living and dining area. The interior is adorned with modern touches, including high ceilings, 6 wide plank hardwood flooring, Pella windows, a custom electric fireplace, gourmet kitchen quartz countertops, a stylish backsplash, and a sizable center island. Equipped with all stainless-steel appliances, The Primary Bedroom offers a true sanctuary, complete with two closets, including a walk-in, a private balcony overlooking the tranquil backyard, and a bathroom featuring floor-to-ceiling custom tiling, a glass-enclosed shower, and double vanity sinks. In addition, this meticulously designed condo includes two more spacious bedrooms, each boasting ample living space and large closets. Descend to the lower level to find a generous rec room with a full wet bar kitchen, connecting to the private yard—a perfect space for entertaining guests. This home sits conveniently within Summit and Central, minutes from Hoboken, Congress St Light Rail, gourmet restaurants, variety of shops and cultural attractions. 5 Year Tax Abatement."
220018940,SOLD,"JC, Heights",97 LAIDLAW AVE,Condominium,1686,1603,"$999,999",CONDO-COOP,,2&3,3,"JC, Heights",07306,05705,00014,Heights,,,,,4,0,2,7,,"$999,999","$1,050,000",$593.12,$593.12,10/25/2022,1/6/2023,2/17/2023,73,73,,2/17/2023,,,,$0,,$628,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave & Oakland Ave,"97 Laidlaw Ave is a collection of five timeless new construction condominium homes consisting of three and four bedrooms, two and three bath homes. Unit 3 is absolutely unique and is the only duplex home in the building with direct access to private rooftop from inside home. This stunning home features three bedrooms plus a den/home office, two baths and includes THREE private outdoor spaces. Enjoy two terraces and massive private rooftop space with NYC views accessible directly from your unit.  Full-service kitchen designed to flow smoothly into and out of the living area features Frigidaire appliances in slate, two-toned matte cabinetry with custom integrated cabinet lighting, Himalayan White Granite waterfall countertops and floating wall shelves. This elegant space with dining area is perfectly suited for casual dining as well as entertaining. Luxurious bathrooms offering you a spa-like retreat with an assortment of carefully selected materials and textures that are exceptional including Roca Piasentina silver polished large format tiles throughout, 60'' double vessel sink on a floating vanity, 30'' natural oak vanities, showers with horizontal niche and integrated led lighting, fixed glass enclosed shower with rain shower head and more. Every home offers unparalleled detail from expansive open floor plan living spaces and high-end finishes to massive private balconies, exclusive backyards, elevator, garage parking and deeded rooftop spaces with NYC views.  97 Laidlaw Ave sits in prime location only a few short blocks from Pershing Field Park and only one block to the Central Ave shopping district. Commute with ease to NYC via NJ Transit buses right on Central Ave or a quick 15 minute walk to the JSQ PATH train. City-bikes located one block from the property. Offering you larger living spaces at desirable price points while maintaining close proximity to NYC, these one-of-a-kind new construction homes are so luxurious you’ll never want to leave!  Property eligible for 5 year tax abatement."
220011506,SOLD,"JC, Heights",249 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1500,1603,"$999,999",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,03903,00050,,,,,,3,1,2,9,,"$999,999","$899,987",$666.67,$666.67,6/23/2022,6/29/2022,8/11/2022,6,6,,8/16/2022,,,,"$11,200",2021,$190,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Griffith,"Welcome Home to the most sought after Ogden Ave address in the Heart of JC Heights.  Rare 3br Duplex condo in a 3 year old new construction 2 Family building with Large 450sqft Private Backyard, and Parking included.   The main home level features large kitchen/living room concept with dining area.  Chef Kitchen includes Professional Samsung Stainless Steal Appliances, high-end fixture's, Caesar stone Quartz kitchen counter tops with elegant white cabinets. Primary bedroom suite has large walk in closet and private terrace overlooking private backyard.  Two other equal size bedrooms.  Central AC, hardwood floors throughout and in unit large laundry room. 1st floor level has large Rec room, half bath and direct access to Yard and Garage. This PRIME Ogden location is just 1 block from River View Fisk Park, 100 steps down to Hoboken & Light rail station, Palisade Ave with shopping, dining and Bus stop to NYC/PATH."
260005336,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",545 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,2300,1724,"$1,019,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1A,"JC, Heights",07307,02305,00029,Heights,,,,,4,0,4,10,,,"$1,019,000",$443.04,,3/26/2026,,,14,,,3/26/2026,,,,,,$529,,,,,,,,South St. & Bowers,"Located directly across from Riverview Park on sought-after Palisade Avenue in Jersey City Heights, this newly constructed four-bedroom, three-bath duplex residence with a bonus recreation space offers a flexible layout designed for modern city living; providing versatility for buyers seeking both lifestyle and long-term value. The home features an open-concept main living area filled with natural light, complemented by 5-inch wide oak hardwood flooring throughout and solid 8-foot interior doors. The contemporary kitchen is designed with both form and function in mind, featuring custom cabinetry, Calacatta quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Bathrooms are finished with Porcelanosa tile, creating a clean and refined design throughout the residence. Right on Palisade Avenue, the home is steps from neighborhood cafés, restaurants, and shops, with convenient access to public transportation providing an easy commute to Downtown Jersey City and New York City. Garage parking may be available.  *photos include the other units to showcase other finishing options*"
220012583,SOLD,"JC, Heights",580 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1534,1692,"$1,019,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,503,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,The Riveview,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$1,019,000","$1,075,000",$664.28,$664.28,11/29/2021,11/29/2021,6/23/2022,0,0,,7/11/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress and South,"Step inside and immediately feel at ease in this unit. BRAND NEW GROUND UP CONSTRUCTION at The Riverview offers impeccable comfort and convenience, situated on Palisade Avenue, at the heart of the neighborhood’s exciting retail/dining corridor. Choose from two- and three-bedroom residences in this intimate 13-unit building, crafted to meet your every need. The well-proportioned units are carefully constructed with today’s most in-demand elements. Flow-through rooms and thoughtful appointments combine for luxurious comfort. Expansive energy-efficient insulated windows frame the interiors with abundant natural light. Elegant top-line finishes include wide plank flooring, granite countertops and premium Fischer-Paykel appliances. Thoughtfully curated amenities bring ease to today’s busy lifestyles. A package room, 12-car parking garage with electric chargers and ground-level bike storage are among the building’s many essential comforts designed to enhance your lifestyle. Make this inspired collection of pet-friendly condominiums home. 10-year New Home Warranty, Manufacturer’s Warranty on all appliances and systems, and tax abatement. Photos are of model unit."
250021774,SOLD,"JC, Heights",619 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1558,5069,"$1,020,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07306,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$1,020,000","$1,049,000",$654.69,$654.69,10/21/2025,11/20/2025,2/2/2026,30,30,,2/2/2026,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Congress & North St,"Seller offering $20K concession towards closing costs!  Welcome to 619 Palisade Avenue unit 1, a premier high-end new construction condo from NKAY Developers in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Conveniently located on Palisade Avenue, just steps from Light Rail and Riverview Fisk Park. This unit features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, 1 half bath, and a private backyard. The entryway sets the tone with custom built-in millwork, providing a stylish functional drop zone for coats and everyday essentials. Custom designed kitchen offers  top of the line stainless steel Thermador appliances including wine fridge, XL quartz waterfall counters and backsplash, oversized stainless steel sink, two-tone custom cabinetry, pot filler, stylish gold hardware and fixtures, and high-end pendant lighting. Open-Concept living and dining room are complete with a fireplace framed with custom millwork and oversized Andersen. Main bedroom suite offers ample natural light and boasts a luxurious accent wall with dual pendant lighting, walk in custom closet with custom built-in shelving and drawers and frosted glass doors and walk-out backyard. Ensuite bathroom offers clean design with white tile and porcelain slabs as well as oversized double vanity, dramatic warm accent lighting, and a top of the line waterfall shower, complete with sprayer and jets and soaking tub. Each additional bedroom features high end custom built-in closets and common bathroom. Washer/dryer in unit add to the convenience of the home. The home is also equipped with a smart doorbell, keyless entry, Legrand smart dimmers, and energy-efficient smart thermostats. The exterior facade has been designed with modern yet timeless features, exterior lighting, professional landscaping, and a fenced-in front yard. This property comes with a 10-year warranty and may qualify for a 5 year tax abatement. Highly sought after location being steps from new restaurants, shopping, palisade ave bus stop, Congress st light rail, Riverview Fisk park and much more! Please note that square footage is approximate. Off-site parking available."
250002086,SOLD,"JC, Heights",32 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1550,5069,"$1,025,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,1505,44,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$1,025,000","$1,099,000",$661.29,$661.29,1/31/2025,2/9/2025,3/27/2025,9,9,,6/19/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central and Summit Ave,"*** Welcome to 32 Graham, Blue Chip Properties’ latest New Construction unit to date. This Luxury 3 bedroom 2 full bath duplex unit, which was designed with timeless interior design, top line finishes and fixtures, quality craftsmanship and modern technological features. This home sits on sought after Graham Street for it's close proximity to Congress St Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park, Central Ave and Palisade Ave gourmet restaurants!  Your main floor opens to an oversized open concept Dining & Living featuring RARE 12 ft high walls lined with oversized Andersen Energy Efficient windows, natural light, floor to ceiling glass accent wall and realistic flame fireplace.  Your Chefs kitchen features top of line designer - two tone cabinetry, Thermador Stove, Thermador Heating Drawer, Thermador Panel Ready Fridge, pot filler, pantry, oversized double waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash and externally vented hood vent. The kitchen is further enhanced by the West elm accent lighting and OVERSIZED window for plenty of natural sunlight within your kitchen.  Main level features Large Primary bedroom designed with custom millwork, bedside pendant lighting, walk-in-closet with custom built-ins and large picturesque private balcony with views of Manhattan. Your ensuite bath has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience and offers double vanity, warm pendant lighting, Shower with multiple jets and shower head.  Two additional bedrooms with finished custom closets and Oversized full bath with Double Vanity and floor to ceiling lime wash tiles, laundry room with Top Line Washer / Dryer complete your main level.  Your upper floor level enters from a recessed lit staircase which includes a wet bar backed with custom backsplash, recessed lighting and wine fridge. This leads out to an oversized rooftop with SOME OF THE BEST NYC VIEWS in the heights, gas / electric and water hookups making it perfect for entertaining and creating memories.  Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Security Cameras, Google Smart Hub, Smart Thermo and Smart Touch Screen Switches, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smartphone.  Garage features RARE SIDE BY SIDE parking and a separate Level 2 High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit and security camera. Home is complete with exterior facade and recessed driveway lighting and landscaping. Property comes with 10 year warranty and may qualify for 5 Year Tax Abatement . Please note that sqft is approx."
240019048,SOLD,"JC, Heights",198 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1696,1713,"$1,025,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2301,10,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,11,,"$1,025,000","$999,000",$604.36,$604.36,9/26/2024,10/5/2024,12/13/2024,9,9,,12/13/2024,,,,"$13,754",,$235,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers & South St,"Introducing this bright and spacious 1696 SF 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom duplex, located on a quiet, tree-lined street in the Riverview Arts District of Jersey City Heights. This meticulous sun-filled home features large windows, and an expansive living area flows seamlessly, integrating the living, dining, and kitchen spaces into one inviting layout. Complete with a fully modern chef’s kitchen with a vented hood and built-in microwave draw, it is outfitted with high-gloss custom cabinetry, gleaming granite countertops, and a large, inviting breakfast bar.  The primary bedroom includes en-suite bath with double vanities, smart mirrors, glass enclosed shower with multi-head system, walk-in closet and private balcony with views on NYC and the Empire State Building.  Unit boasts 2 additional spacious bedrooms, hardwood floors throughout, upgraded lighting, custom window treatments adorning every window including stylish bamboo blinds and designer white linen floor-length blackout drapes. With full size washer/dryer, central heating/AC, and an abundance of closets and storage space.  Lower level includes versatile flex space with half bath suitable for guest room, play space, or second living area, opening through sliding glass doors to private, spacious backyard complete with lawn, pavers, and fence ideal for any lifestyle!  Close proximity to Riverview Fisk Park, local shops, restaurants, farmers' markets, and cafes and convenient to all NYC transportation, including buses, elevator to light rail, PATH, ferry, NJ Turnpike, you name it!"
240018114,SOLD,"JC, Heights",527 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,1652,6078,"$1,025,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,B,"JC, Heights",07307,804,28,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$1,025,000","$1,075,000",$620.46,$620.46,9/13/2024,9/23/2024,11/6/2024,10,10,,11/7/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,North and Irving,"Welcome to 527 Central Ave, a collection of exclusive two ultra-luxurious, brand new condominiums, offering rare views of Washington Park, on an oversized 25' x 106' lot, in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Elevate your standards of living with these massive, meticulously designed, duplex homes, featuring designer finishes throughout, White Oak flooring, Recessed Lighting, Crown and Baseboard Moulding, Central HVAC, Nest Thermostat, Ring Doorbell, Camera Security, Pella Windows, 10-foot ceilings, 8-foot doors and contemporary Matte black fixtures.  Immerse yourself in an impressive audio experience with surround sound WIFI/Bluetooth speakers installed throughout this smart home.  Unit 2 condominium duplex features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a coveted private rooftop deck with stunning views of NYC Downton, Midtown as well as Washington Park. The bright contemporary open concept living and dining room featuring oversized windows facing the park, Brooklyn-Style BRICK TV wall with integrated ultra-thin electric fireplace and 5 pre-wired wifi/bluetooth speakers for entertainment. Flowing seamlessly into the massive chef’s kitchen, offering an abundance of yin-yang glossy cabinetry, quartz countertops, Samsung Appliances, integrated Pot Filler, Wine Cooler, Microwave, Dishwasher, Stainless Steel Sink, making this a culinary enthusiast's dream kitchen. The luxurious master-suite boasts access to a private balcony overlooking the serene backyard. This magnificent condominium  provides two additional queen size bedrooms, a second bathroom and a fully equipped laundry room. The unit also offers Exclusive NON-TANDEM Garage Parking to our new homeowners.  Settled on a quiet block of Central Ave, enjoy an unparalleled living experience with shops, restaurants, banks and cafés at your doorsteps. Located at 3 mins walk from Bus 119 and 225, arrive into NYC Port Authority in under 30 mins. Jersey City Heights is known for its tight-knit community, great schools and easy access to NYC. **10-Year Builders Warranty, Eligible for 5 year Tax Abatement.. Property qualifies for CENSUS TRACT program, with interest rates offered in the mid-high 5’s, making this investment even more attractive."
260005206,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",373 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1464,5069,"$1,025,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$1,025,000",$700.14,,3/25/2026,,,15,,,3/25/2026,,,,$0,,,,,No,No,Yes,,,Bowers and Congress,"2-YEAR FREE PARKING. RATE BUY DOWN WITH RATES AS LOW AS 4.875%. Terms and eligibility apply-- please inquire for details. MOMENTS FROM CONGRESS ST LIGHT RAIL STATION AND RIVERVIEW FISK PARK. Welcome to 373 New York Avenue, Jersey City — Blue Chip Properties’ most iconic and sought-after project to date. This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is located in the highly desirable New York Avenue enclave, known for its close proximity to the 9th Street Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park, Hoboken, and the gourmet dining scene of Palisade Avenue. Designed with timeless interior finishes, high-end fixtures, and meticulous craftsmanship, this residence also offers cutting-edge modern technology for elevated daily living.  The main entrance opens to a grand open-concept dining and living area with soaring ceilings, oversized Andersen energy-efficient windows, abundant natural light, and a statement-making realistic flame fireplace. The chef’s kitchen is outfitted with designer two-tone cabinetry, Thermador appliance package with paneled refrigerator and dishwasher, 5 burner range, and heating drawer.  The oversized double waterfall quartz island showcases luxurious West Elm accent lighting, along with porcelain backsplash with a convenient Pot Filler, and an externally vented hood. Flowing seamlessly from the kitchen is your entertainment zone featuring a wet bar with custom cabinetry, backlit designer backsplash, and wine fridge.   The primary suite is a serene retreat featuring custom warm wood-tone millwork, bedside pendant lighting, a walk-in closet with built-ins. Sliding glass doors open directly to the private backyard, blending indoor comfort with outdoor living. The spa-like ensuite bath showcases modern natural tones, an oversized double vanity, soaking tub, warm pendant lighting, and a luxurious shower with multiple Kohler body sprays and rainfall showerhead. The two additional bedrooms include custom-finished closets and share a beautifully appointed full bath with double vanity and floor-to-ceiling tiles. A separate laundry room with top-of-the-line washer and dryer completes the main level.  This fully equipped smart home includes a Google Nest doorbell, security cameras, Google Smart Hub, smart thermostat, touchscreen light switches, dimmers, and more — all seamlessly controlled via smartphone, along with a security camera system. The home is completed with Blue Chip Properties’ signature exterior facade and professional landscaping. Property includes a 10-year builder’s warranty. Square footage is approximate. Offsite parking is available, inquire further."
250001865,SOLD,"JC, Heights",44 BLEECKER ST,Condominium,1865,5069,"$1,025,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,1502,13,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$1,025,000","$1,099,000",$549.60,$549.60,1/29/2025,2/7/2025,4/7/2025,9,9,,4/7/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central and Summit,"Welcome to 44 Bleecker, Unit 1, a new construction 3 bedroom 3 full bath luxury duplex condo built by Medna Developers. The first floor features an expansive open-concept living space with a chef's kitchen, showcasing premium GE CAFE Appliances, waterfall quartz countertops, and two-tone cabinetry. The kitchen flows into a living and dining room lined with oversized Pella windows that let in abundant sunlight, enhanced by custom designer pendant lighting. The primary bedroom includes a custom floor-to-ceiling accent wall, built-in closets with a mirrored section, accent pendant lighting, a balcony, and a luxurious ensuite bathroom. Completing the first floor are two additional bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a laundry room. The ground floor provides the perfect space for entertainment, featuring both interior and exterior living areas. The interior includes a full bathroom, a wet bar, a recreation room, direct access to the garage, and a private side entrance. The backyard is one of the largest in the Heights, featuring professional landscaping, custom stone and turf design, and a custom wood fence for ultimate privacy. The garage offers true side-by-side parking and an EV charging outlet. The property comes with a 10-year builder warranty and may qualify for 5 Year Tax Abatement. Ask about our Low Interest Rate First Time Home Buyer Program"
250007045,SOLD,"JC, Heights",43 CHARLES ST,Condominium,1750,5069,"$1,029,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2803,7.02,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$1,029,000","$1,099,000",$588.00,$588.00,4/10/2025,4/10/2025,5/6/2025,0,0,,5/6/2025,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central and Summit,"  Welcome to 43 Charles, Blue Chip Properties’ highest end New Construction unit to date. This 3 bedroom 2 full bath duplex unit spans an impressive 1,750 sqft, which was designed with timeless interior design, top line finishes and fixtures, quality craftsmanship and modern technological features. This home sits conveniently within Summit and Central, minutes from Hoboken, Congress St Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park and Palisades gourmet restaurants!  Your main floor enters to an oversized open concept Dining & Living featuring 12 ft high walls lined with oversized Andersen windows, natural light and realistic flame fireplace. Your Chefs kitchen features top of line designer - two tone cabinetry, Thermador Stove, Thermador Heating Drawer, Panel Ready Fridge, pot filler, pantry, oversized double waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash and West elm accent lighting.   Main level features Primary bedroom designed with custom millwork, bedside pendant lighting, walk in-closet with custom built ins and large picturesque private balcony. Your ensuite bath has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience and offers double vanity, warm pendant lighting, shower with multiple jets and rain fall shower head.  Two additional bedroom with finished custom closets and ensuite bath, laundry room with Top Line Washer / Dryer complete your main level.  Your upper floor level enters from a recessed lit staircase which includes wet bar backed with custom backsplash, recessed lighting and wine fridge. This leads out to an oversized rooftop with turf and NYC views, gas / electric and water hook ups making it perfect for entertaining and creating memories.   Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Security Cameras, Google Smart Hub, Smart Thermo and Smart Touch Screen Switches, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smart phone. Garage features non-tandem parking and separate Level 2 High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit. Home is complete with exterior facade and recessed driveway lighting and landscaping. Property comes with 10 year warranty. Please note that sqft is approx. Property may qualify for 5 Year Tax Abatement!"
250006302,SOLD,"JC, Heights",28 CAMBRIDGE AVE,Condominium,1601,6036,"$1,030,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,4405,11,,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$1,030,000","$1,075,000",$643.35,$643.35,4/2/2025,5/9/2025,7/1/2025,37,37,,7/2/2025,,,,$0,,$205,,Cash,,,,,,Hutton and Franklin,"Step into this newly developed 3-bedroom, 2.5 bath condo, where modern design meets comfort and convenience. With soaring high ceilings and an abundance of natural light, the open concept living areas create an inviting and airy atmosphere perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. The chef-inspired kitchen features sleek white quartz countertops, contemporary cabinetry, and top-of-the-line appliances. The expansive living and dining spaces flow seamlessly into each other, providing ample room for gathering with family and friends. The primary suite offers a serene retreat, complete with a luxurious en-suite bath. The additional bedrooms are generously sized, offering versatility for a home office, guest room, or family space. One of the standouts features of this home is, the bonus room and private yard, a rare find that provides an outdoor oasis for lounging, gardening, or enjoying the fresh air. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or enjoying a quiet moment, this private outdoor space is your personal sanctuary. Located Just 1 mile from the Congress Street Light Rail and the JSQ PATH Station, this home provides the perfect blend of convenience and elegance. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity!"
220004897,SOLD,"JC, Heights",124 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1545,1419,"$1,035,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,301,"JC, Heights",07307,04504,1,Heights,The York,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$1,035,000","$1,040,000",$669.90,$669.90,3/22/2022,4/29/2022,10/21/2022,38,38,,10/18/2022,,,,,,$484,,Conventional,,,,,,Ferry St & Franklin St,"A tranquil oasis is awaiting you in the Jersey City Height with unobstructed Manhattan views! Don't miss this rare opportunity to see and live in The Jersey City Heights newest development - The York! With serene private terraces and direct elevator access to a the huge communal deck; this elevator building optimizes every square foot of the floor plan and includes two communal rooftop decks, a large garage, and a bike rack on the 1st floor. Radiant and inviting, this airy condominium entails 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with approximately 1,550 sq ft of living space. Equipped with chef's kitchen, Bosch stainless steel appliances, modernized cabinetry, in-unit washer/dryer, and in-ceiling speakers managed by Sonos amplifier. 5 wide plank oak hardwood floors throughout, Porcelanosa tile and plumbing fixtures, LED lighting and heated bathroom floors create a true luxurious experience. The builder spared no cost in making this home sound proofed by using sound channels and sound clips, Quietrock, green/noise proofing compound, and even foam insulation, dampening the noise. This rare Heights location is easily commutable and accessible to public transportation being only 1 block from Palisade Ave; with direct bus lines to NYC Port Authority, Hoboken, and Downtown JC. The Hudson Light Rail Stations are only minutes away as well as Pershing Field's indoor pool and ice skating rink being only 3 blocks away. Riverview Park with its amazing views offers Farmers Market, movie nights, and neighborhood events. Garage parking available. 5 year new construction tax abatement. Please contact listing agent for private showing!"
250003772,SOLD,"JC, Heights",98 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1595,1597,"$1,049,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$1,049,000","$1,049,000",$657.68,$657.68,2/27/2025,4/2/2025,5/15/2025,34,33,,5/15/2025,,,,,,$460,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"Step into elevated design and modern convenience with this newly constructed 3 bedroom, 2 bath with parking, storage and a private rooftop in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Set on a corner lot with a striking red brick exterior, this home is bathed in natural light, highlighting a spacious open-concept layout with premium flooring and high-end finishes.  The oversized windows frame a beautifully designed kitchen featuring modern black and natural light oak custom cabinetry, white quartz waterfall countertops, and a matching backsplash. Premium Bertazzoni appliances bring both style and functionality, making this space perfect for cooking and entertaining.  The primary ensuite bathroom is a luxurious retreat with floor-to-ceiling picket pattern tile, elegant gold accents, and a glass-enclosed shower with a multi-spray system and rain head. Additional features include ample closet space, a separate utility room with a brand-new washer and dryer, and dedicated storage for added convenience.  This unit comes with a coveted parking space and access to a private rooftop, providing a perfect outdoor escape with sweeping city views.  Located just one block from popular cafés and restaurants like Froth on Franklin and The Franklin, the best of The Heights is at your doorstep. The 2nd Street stairs to Hoboken provide quick access to the Light Rail, PATH, and ferry, making commuting to NYC effortless. Known for its vibrant community, excellent parks and schools, and stunning skyline views, Jersey City Heights continues to be one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in the area."
250003292,SOLD,"JC, Heights",414 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1509,6078,"$1,055,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,2,"JC, Heights",07307,1704,34,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,6,,"$1,055,000","$1,075,000",$699.14,$699.14,2/20/2025,3/18/2025,5/23/2025,26,26,,8/13/2025,,,,"$1,641",,$228,,Conventional,,,,,,North and Congress,"Welcome to 414 New York, where luxury meets location! Situated on the most desirable streets of Jersey City Heights, this boutique condominium building offers sophistication and comfort. This brand new construction property is built on a unique 37.5’ x 100’ lot featuring WIDER FLOOR PLANS with tons of natural sunlight, seamlessly flowing through the massive windows. The Finest Unit 2 Duplex, features a total of 3 Bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms, TWO PRIVATE BALCONIES, Rooftop Deck, NON-TANDEM Garage Parking (a RARITY in the future), and a PRIVATE BASEMENT STORAGE UNIT.  with a total of 1,509 SQFT of livable space. The two sets of interior stairs gives this unit a lofty feel. As you enter the main floor through the hallway, you will be greeted by the gorgeous open-concept living dining room, shedding tons of light through the oversized floor to ceiling windows. The 23’ WIDE living room features a beautiful TV wall with wood panel work and shelving, 60-inch electric fireplace, 5 SONOS speakers, and a private balcony facing the quiet tree-lined street. The gourmet kitchen is fitted with high-end GE CAFE appliances, White Quartz Countertops Pot Fillers, Wine Cooler, Garbage Disposal and tons of custom cabinetry for all your kitchen storage needs. The 892 SQFT of living floor, also features, One Full Bedroom, One Full Bathroom and fully equipped laundry outfitted with Samsung Washer and Dryer. As you walk up the stairs, you will enter into the 617 SQFT of the second floor featuring a gorgeous Master Bedroom with a private balcony with New York views, a custom built walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom, offering privacy from the rest of the home. To the left of the Master is the third bedroom and the third full bathroom. As you walk up another set of stairs, you will enter your own private 25’ wide roofdeck offering stunning New York City views, ready to be turned into your private oasis. Located one block from Washington Park, One block from Palisade Ave with tons of dining, one block from Bus 123, 119 and 5mins to Ninth street Light Rail, close proximity to Tessa and Franklin Middle School, makes this property ideal for all generations."
240000111,SOLD,"JC, Heights",34 LEONARD ST,Condominium,1719,6199,"$1,055,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,00503,00035,,,,,,4,0,3,8,,"$1,055,000","$1,099,888",$613.73,$613.73,1/3/2024,1/15/2024,3/8/2024,12,12,,3/13/2024,,,,,,$175,2023,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave & Central Ave,"Amazing opportunity for first time home buyer interest rate as low as 5.75% and mansion tax paid by developer! Brand New construction, this property features a distinctive parking garage, a  future rarity resulting from a recent city ordinance change making it an uncommon and valuable asset for prospective buyers in search of convenient parking in the evolving urban Jersey City landscape ahead. Luxurious 4 bedroom 3 full bath duplex unit designed and built by Jersey City’s very own Blue Chip Properties, known for their modern design, high end finishes and quality craftsmanship. Enjoy the spacious and sun-drenched open concept living area and dining area featuring 10 ft high walls lined with Anderson windows. The chefs modern kitchen is fully equipped with top of the line Thermador appliances, pot filler, quartz countertops, a waterfall center island with breakfast bar perfect for entertaining. Main level features a primary bedroom designed with custom millwork, bedside pendant lighting, walk in-closet and large picturesque private balcony. The ensuite bath has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience. Two additional bedrooms with finished custom closets, full bath and laundry room complete your main level. Ground floor level includes a full bath and oversized bedroom or entertaining room, which features wet bar and large closet for added storage. This level leads out to the tree lined private backyard with professional landscaping, paver patio and accent lighting making it perfect for entertaining and creating memories. Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Google thermostat and smart hub, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smart phone. Garage features non-tandem parking and separate Level 2 High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit. Property comes with 5 Year Tax Abatement and 10 year warranty. Home qualifies for the Community Loan Program with low interest rate, no PMI and low down payment! Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the epitome of modern city living presented by Blue Chip Living!"
250000148,SOLD,"JC, Heights",183 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1755,1623,"$1,059,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2205,37,,,,,,4,0,3,7,,"$1,059,000","$1,079,000",$603.42,$603.42,1/3/2025,2/3/2025,3/31/2025,31,31,,3/31/2025,,,,"$14,791",2024,$257,,Conventional,,,,,,South & Bowers,"NEARLY NEW and ready for you! This 2 level luxurious condo in JC Heights has so much to offer! Enter into your open floor plan living, dining and kitchen area with an expansive picture window providing an abundance of natural light. The kitchen features gorgeous marble countertops, island with breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances including dishwasher & smart fridge. Three bedrooms on the main floor including a primary suite with a massive walk-in closet, en suite bathroom, and floor to ceiling sliding doors to your private terrace. The main floor also features a washer and dryer in-unit as well as a second full bathroom for guests. Downstairs you will find the entrance to your garage parking spot, non-tandem for ease and convenience, complete with electric charger! The lower level is set up for a spacious family room, but could easily be transformed to a fourth bedroom or any kind of additional space you may need, also includes a wet bar with a wine fridge and a wine rack, and floor to ceiling sliding doors to your private outdoor oasis. The backyard is completely private and newly landscaped, ideal for entertaining or just relaxing in the fresh air. All this in the growing hub of Jersey City Heights, around the corner from some of the best restaurants in Hudson County, Riverview-Fisk Park, and easy transit to Manhattan - door to door to Port Authority in under 20 minutes! Approximately 3 years left on tax abatement. This unit will not last so schedule your showing today!"
250014072,SOLD,"JC, Heights",244 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1400,1713,"$1,075,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2302,8,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$1,075,000","$1,100,000",$767.86,$767.86,7/10/2025,7/23/2025,8/22/2025,13,13,,8/22/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers & Griffith,"Nestled in the vibrant heart of Jersey City Heights, 244 Sherman #2 is a stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo that perfectly blends modern luxury with everyday convenience. One of its most sought-after features is the non-tandem garage parking, which includes individual EV chargers for each unit owner, providing unparalleled ease and accessibility in this bustling urban neighborhood.  Step inside and discover an expansive open-concept living and dining area, thoughtfully designed for both relaxation and entertaining. This inviting space boasts a cozy built-in fireplace and dedicated TV hookups, making it ideal for movie nights or gathering with friends. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring elegant two-tone cabinetry and paneled appliances that create a seamless, sophisticated look. It's fully equipped with a professional-grade Wolf range, a Bosch built-in microwave, a convenient pot filler for culinary tasks, and undercabinet lighting that beautifully illuminates the matching stone backsplash.  The spacious primary bedroom offers a private retreat, complete with a large closet and an ensuite bathroom. Indulge in the luxurious primary bath, which boasts a double vanity, a sleek lit mirror, and a modern glass-enclosed shower. The second full bathroom is equally well-appointed, featuring a comfortable tub. Beyond the beautiful aesthetics, this unit provides practical living solutions with abundant storage throughout and a full-size washer and dryer, ensuring all your needs are met.  Experience the pinnacle of urban living with your very own private roof deck. This incredible outdoor space is an entertainer's delight, featuring a fully equipped outdoor kitchen that's perfect for al fresco dining. From this elevated vantage point, you'll be treated to breathtaking, unobstructed New York City views, offering a spectacular backdrop for everyday moments and special occasions alike.  244 Sherman #2 offers an unparalleled living experience in Jersey City Heights, combining sophisticated design with ultimate comfort and convenience, all within a vibrant and accessible community."
240006226,SOLD,"JC, Heights",81 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1778,1713,"$1,075,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & 3,4,"JC, Heights",07307,4406,12,,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$1,075,000","$1,100,000",$604.61,$604.61,4/4/2024,4/30/2024,6/24/2024,26,26,,6/27/2024,,,2022,$0,,$166,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton & Franklin,"Welcome to the epitome of modern urban living in Jersey City Heights! Unveiling a newly renovated 4-unit condo, this exquisite residence offers a seamless blend of sophistication and comfort. Nestled in the sought-after neighborhood, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom duplex boasts a private roof deck, defining the perfect oasis in the heart of the vibrant community. Meticulously designed, the spacious living area unfolds seamlessly, merging the living, dining, and kitchen spaces into an inviting expanse, ideal for both entertainment and relaxation. Four generously sized bedrooms bathed in natural light, provide ample space for personalized style. Contemporary fixtures and elegant tile work adorn both bathrooms, with frameless shower doors adding a touch of modernity and creating a spa-like feel. The condo's clever use of space and thoughtfully crafted floor plan optimizes the expansive layout, ensuring every inch is functional and aesthetically pleasing. Step onto 4” Select Red Oak Hardwood Floors that span the unit, setting the stage for an elegant experience. The kitchen, a culinary haven, features Kraus kitchen sink & faucet, Jenn Air Appliances, and is graced with a peninsula and quartz countertops, embodying the perfect fusion of style and functionality. Solid core interior doors, extra-wide moldings & trims with crown molding throughout the house create an air of sophistication. The unit also features a dedicated roof deck, low voltage with proficient brand speakers, custom closet designs, wall decor moldings, and claddings in the master bedroom. Located in the thriving Jersey City Heights neighborhood, renowned for its diverse community, shops, cafes, and cultural attractions, this residence offers easy access to transportation, making New York City just a breezy commute away. A shining example of luxury and convenience in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Welcome home!"
260005333,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",34 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,2005,1713,"$1,075,000",CONDO-COOP,,multi,2,"JC, Heights",07307,4403,41,Heights,,,,,4,2,3,9,,,"$1,075,000",$536.16,,3/26/2026,,,14,,,3/26/2026,,,2024,"$5,024",2026,$225,,,,,,,,Sherman ave & Central Ave,"Welcome to 34 Manhattan Ave #2, a sprawling and meticulously designed 4-bedroom, 3-full, and 2-half bath condominium that redefines luxury living in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This multi-level residence seamlessly blends high-end custom finishes with the rare privilege of two distinct private outdoor retreats. From the moment you step inside, the home’s open-concept heart unfolds into an entertainer’s dream. The designer kitchen is a masterpiece of form and function, featuring white wood soft-close cabinetry, striking waterfall countertops with a breakfast bar, and a full suite of Samsung stainless appliances, complete with a vented hood, over-range pot filler, in-cabinet drawer microwave, and a dedicated wine fridge. Under-cabinet lighting and a tiled backsplash accentuate the space, while custom West Elm lighting in the living room leads you directly to your private backyard sanctuary.  The second level is thoughtfully laid out to accommodate the modern lifestyle, currently featuring two versatile bedrooms utilized as a high-end home gym and a professional office. The gym-configured bedroom serves as a secondary suite, boasting a private Juliet balcony and an ensuite bathroom with a glass-enclosed shower. This floor also includes a well-appointed hallway bathroom with a soaking tub and the ultimate urban convenience: a dedicated laundry area with full-sized, stacked Samsung washer and dryer units. Throughout the home, custom window treatments from The Shade Store provide both privacy and a polished aesthetic.  Ascending to the third floor, you’ll find the primary retreat, a true sanctuary designed for ultimate relaxation. The primary suite is anchored by a custom-built walk-in closet and a private Juliet balcony, with elegant West Elm lighting overhead. Its spa-like ensuite bathroom features a massive glass-enclosed shower with a built-in bench and a sleek double vanity. This level is rounded out by a fourth bedroom (currently used as an office) and a convenient hallway half-bath, ensuring every inch of the home is utilized for maximum comfort.  The crowning jewel of this residence is found just one flight up: a private roof deck offering breathtaking, unobstructed views of the New York City skyline. Whether you are hosting summer gatherings against the backdrop of Manhattan or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this outdoor space is a rare find in the Heights. With its sophisticated custom upgrades and expansive floor plan, 34 Manhattan Ave #2 offers a truly elevated living experience in one of the city's most vibrant neighborhoods. Parking available nearby for an additional fee.   "
250013861,SOLD,"JC, Heights",262 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1997,1713,"$1,075,000",CONDO-COOP,,2-3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2306,19,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$1,075,000","$1,075,000",$538.31,$538.31,7/9/2025,7/18/2025,9/11/2025,9,9,,9/16/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Sherman Ave & New york Ave,"Experience unparalleled modern living in this exquisite unit at 262 Webster Avenue, nestled in the vibrant and highly sought-after Jersey City Heights with 3 bedrooms and large den that can be legally a fourth bedroom with a closet installation. This thoughtfully designed residence offers a perfect blend of sophistication and comfort, ideal for those seeking a premium lifestyle. Step inside to discover immaculate hardwood floors that flow seamlessly throughout the open and airy layout. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring top-of-the-line Samsung stainless steel appliances, sleek countertops, and ample cabinetry, making meal preparation a delight. The highlight of this stunning home is the private master bedroom suite. This serene retreat boasts a spacious walk-in closet for all your wardrobe needs and a luxurious ensuite bathroom complete with a modern glass-enclosed shower, providing a spa-like experience. The master suite also offers access to a private terrace, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or a quiet evening under the stars. Beyond the unit, residents will enjoy access to a spectacular roof deck, offering breathtaking panoramic views of the city skyline – an ideal spot for entertaining or simply unwinding. Located in the desirable Jersey City Heights, 262 Webster Avenue offers convenient access to a myriad of local amenities. Enjoy strolls through picturesque parks like Riverview-Fisk Park with its stunning Manhattan views, explore the diverse culinary scene on Central Avenue, or easily commute to NYC with excellent transportation option. Parking available nearby for an additional fee."
250002719,SOLD,"JC, Heights",34 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1550,5069,"$1,075,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$1,075,000","$1,099,000",$693.55,$693.55,2/11/2025,2/18/2025,5/6/2025,7,7,,5/6/2025,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central Ave and Summit,"Welcome to 34 Graham, Blue Chip Properties’ latest New Construction unit to date. This Luxury 3 bedroom 2 full bath duplex unit, which was designed with timeless interior design, top line finishes and fixtures, quality craftsmanship and modern technological features. This home sits on sought after Graham Street for it's close proximity to Congress St Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park, Central Ave and Palisade Ave gourmet restaurants!  Your main floor opens to an oversized open concept Dining & Living featuring RARE 12 ft high walls lined with oversized Andersen Energy Efficient windows, natural light, floor to ceiling glass accent wall and realistic flame fireplace.  Your Chefs kitchen features top of line designer - two tone cabinetry, Thermador Stove, Thermador Heating Drawer, Thermador Panel Ready Fridge, pot filler, pantry, oversized double waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash and externally vented hood vent. The kitchen is further enhanced by the West elm accent lighting and OVERSIZED window for plenty of natural sunlight within your kitchen.  Main level features Large Primary bedroom designed with custom millwork, bedside pendant lighting, walk-in-closet with custom built-ins and large picturesque private balcony with views of Manhattan. Your ensuite bath has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience and offers double vanity, warm pendant lighting, Shower with multiple jets and shower head.  Two additional bedrooms with finished custom closets and Oversized full bath with Double Vanity and floor to ceiling lime wash tiles, laundry room with Top Line Washer / Dryer complete your main level.  Your upper floor level enters from a recessed lit staircase which includes a wet bar backed with custom backsplash, recessed lighting and wine fridge. This leads out to an oversized rooftop with SOME OF THE BEST NYC VIEWS in the heights, gas / electric and water hookups making it perfect for entertaining and creating memories.  Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Security Cameras, Google Smart Hub, Smart Thermo and Smart Touch Screen Switches, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smartphone.  Garage features RARE SIDE BY SIDE parking and a separate Level 2 High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit and security camera. Home is complete with exterior facade and recessed driveway lighting and landscaping. Property comes with 10 year warranty and may qualify for 5 Year Tax Abatement . Please note that sqft is approx."
250011737,SOLD,"JC, Heights",100 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1732,1597,"$1,080,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$1,080,000","$1,099,000",$623.56,$623.56,6/10/2025,7/18/2025,9/19/2025,38,38,,9/19/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"Seller to contribute $20k towards closing costs! *See your agent for details* 1 car rental spot pre-paid until June 2026!  Step into elevated design and modern convenience with this ground up new construction 3 bedroom + office/den, 2.5 bath unit with private rooftop in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Set on Webster Avenue with a striking white brick exterior, this home boasts 10 foot ceilings & is bathed in natural light, highlighting a spacious open-concept layout with premium Legno Bastone wide-plank hardwood flooring and high-end finishes.  The oversized windows frame a beautifully designed kitchen featuring modern sage green and natural light oak custom cabinetry, white quartz waterfall countertops, and a matching backsplash. Premium Fisher & Paykel appliances bring both style and functionality, making this space perfect for cooking and entertaining.  The primary ensuite bathroom is a luxurious retreat with elegant gold accents, and a glass-enclosed shower with a multi-spray system and rain head. Additional features include ample closet space & brand-new washer and dryer.  Located just one block from popular cafés and restaurants like Froth on Franklin and The Franklin, the best of The Heights is at your doorstep. The 2nd Street stairs to Hoboken provide quick access to the Light Rail, PATH, and ferry, making commuting to NYC effortless. Known for its vibrant community, excellent parks and schools, and stunning skyline views, Jersey City Heights continues to be one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in the area."
230011405,SOLD,"JC, Heights",9 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1695,1597,"$1,080,000",CONDO-COOP,,2&3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$1,080,000","$1,100,000",$637.17,$637.17,7/10/2023,7/12/2023,2/8/2024,2,2,,2/8/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Sherman and Central,"3 UNITS AVAILABLE! Renderings are of unit 1, but finishes will be similar.  Embrace the art of elegant living with these exquisite residences in Jersey City Heights. Comprised of three two-story homes, each includes ultra-luxe designer finishes, coveted private outdoor space, and exclusive non-tandem parking. Quality craftsmanship and exceptional style echo throughout the white brick building settled on a prestigious tree-lined street one block from Pershing Field Park and Reservoir and bustling Central avenue.  Interior finishes elevate with white oak select grade floors, designer lighting by West Elm, Nest thermostat, and pre-wiring for entertainment. Kitchens are curated by My House Kitchens and showcase dramatic black or elegant white Caesarstone quartz waterfall countertops, Fabuwood Modern Shaker Cabinets with under lighting, matte black fixtures including pot filler, and stainless appliances. Residents bask in treasured outdoor space, whether sipping their morning coffee on a secluded terrace, or taking in the sunset and NYC skyline from a private rooftop.   Bedrooms bring ample space, light and storage with large windows and walk-in-closets. Spa-inspired bedrooms indulge with impressive details like imported Turkish bathroom vanities, imported Italian porcelain floor-to-ceiling tiles, glass showers or soaker tubs and top-of-the-line fixtures.   Walking distance to boutique shops, restaurants, cafés and parks, these homes are ideally located for a balance of urban living and secluded sanctuary. Jersey City Heights is known for its tight-knit community, great schools and easy access to NYC. Brought to you by talented local builder, M2M Development, these homes bring unparalleled elegance and superior design."
260003115,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",105 LAIDLAW AVE,Condominium,1652,1597,"$1,080,000",CONDO-COOP,,"1,2,3",2,"JC, Heights",07306,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,,"$1,080,000",$653.75,,2/23/2026,,,45,,,2/23/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Oakland & Central Ave,"  Set amid a striking new four-unit development in The Heights, this 1,600+ sq ft residence redefines modern living, bold style and curated comfort. Spanning two levels with floor to ceiling windows on three sides, this 3 bedroom, 3 bath home also includes a private roofdeck for the elevated indoor and outdoor living.   Step into a sun-soaked open floorplan with warm hardwood floors and a slatted modern staircase illuminated by LED treads. The kitchen commands attention with a waterfall white quartz island, seamless backsplash, matte black and natural wood custom cabinetry, and premium stainless appliances including a wine fridge. Matte black pendant lighting and fixtures finish the look, including a pot filler for precision and poise.  Retreat to the primary ensuite designed to impress with soft grey wood-panelling, striking light fixture, and a spa-inspired bath. Bathroom finishes include elements like matte black vessel sinks, vertical tile to the ceiling, glass-enclosed multi-spray shower or soaker tub, and accent lighting in the shower niche. Additional upgrades abound with extras like Bose surround sound speakers throughout the home, or the magazine-worthy powder room with floating vanity and artistic wallpaper.  Two blocks to Reservoir #3 or Pershing Field Park, and easy access to the 2nd Street Lightrail Station with Hoboken and NYC access, this location offers comfort, community and convenience. Set on a tree-lined street in Jersey City Heights, this quiet neighborhood is known for its artistic community, boutique shops and restaurants, excellent parks and schools and crystal clean Manhattan views."
260004952,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",433 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,1643,6638,"$1,095,000",CONDO-COOP,,4TH,PH4,"JC, Heights",07307,1508,20,,The James,,,,3,1,2,6,,,"$1,095,000",$666.46,,3/20/2026,,,20,,,3/20/2026,,,,,,$644,,,,,,,,Bleeker & South St,"*1 year free parking* A rare penthouse with direct elevator entry into your residence, a private balcony off the living room with direct World Trade Center views, and access to a roof deck with sweeping Manhattan panoramas. Boutique luxury just 20 minutes to Manhattan in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This one-of-one 3-bed, 2.5-bath condominium features sun-soaked, open-concept living with wide-plank chevron oak floors and floor-to-ceiling windows. Enjoy your chef’s kitchen with quartz countertops, premium stainless appliances, and sleek integrated panels. Spa-inspired baths showcase elegant porcelain finishes, matte-black fixtures, and heated floors. Smart conveniences include Ecobee thermostats, Swiftlane video intercom, keyless entry, and built-in speakers. Moments to neighborhood shops, parks, cafés, restaurants, and transit - including the 9th Street Light Rail - this penthouse blends bespoke design, modern sophistication, and exceptional accessibility to NYC. *Please reach out to our preferred lender at cross co mortgage for grant options from $15k-22k"
230003856,SOLD,"JC, Heights",355 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,2482,1581,"$1,099,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,02303,00038,,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$1,099,000","$1,099,000",$442.79,$442.79,3/9/2023,4/8/2023,6/5/2023,30,30,,6/8/2023,,,,,,$200,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress St & South St,"LOCATION ! LOCATION! LOCATION! Welcome to 355 New York Ave, Unit #1, a high-end new construction 4 bedroom duplex residence with exquisite finishes, with its own unique private backyard. This one of a kind 2,482 sq ft home is a 4 bedroom (3 bedroom + office) featuring an open & bright first floor plan with lush weathered oak flooring throughout, Anderson windows, chef's kitchen equipped with modern quartz countertops and luxurious pendant lights, built-in wine cooler, dedicated coffee station, Samsung appliance package, custom linen finished cabinetry; along with built-in speakers and smart video intercom. As you walk towards the back of the home, you will find your office/entertainment room with a powder room, which through the sliding doors leads you to a 479 sq ft landscaped private oasis backyard with built-in outdoor speakers. As you head upstairs, you are greeted with high ceilings and three sizable bedrooms, with three walk-in-closets and built-in laundry. Two of the bedrooms share a jack-and-jill bathroom, while the master bedroom provides an en-suite bathroom finished with pastorelli porcelain tile and double vanity sinks. 355 New York is in a fantastic location in the Riverview Arts District of The Heights; steps to the vibrant Washington Park, minutes walk to the Hoboken Light Rail & local bus stops to and from NYC, shops & restaurants on Central/Palisade Avenue. Carefully crafted by one of Jersey City Height's most experienced developers! Additionally, you can also take advantage of Jersey City’s 5 Year ‘New Construction’ Tax Abatement"
230019424,SOLD,"JC, Heights",45 BOORAEM AVE,Condominium,2673,6199,"$1,099,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & G,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,8,,"$1,099,000","$1,099,000",$411.15,$411.15,11/17/2023,2/20/2024,6/12/2024,95,95,,6/5/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,,,,Palisade Ave,"PRICE IMPROVEMENT! **OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY ** 1-3PM   Pristine 2 Level Condo offering 4 bedrooms 3 bathrooms and just about 2673 square feet.   This beautiful condo welcomes you with soaring ceilings, a very large, wide-open floor plan, exposed brick, bay windows and tremendous natural light.  The versatile space provides options for laying out furniture and creating rooms that work for you. The spacious open concept kitchen is an elegant showpiece that is sure to impress. Custom designed to offer a sleek, upscale look while offering comfort and functionality.   Primary bedroom offers direct access to the private outdoor patio, a walk in closet, and a large ensuite bathroom. Two well sized guest bedrooms, a stylish guest bathroom, with great closet space.   The lower level is a fantastic bonus space featuring a true 4th bedroom and an oversized entertainment room with direct access to the backyard. This is a very rare find! The entire residence is perfect for entertaining many guests at once.    True hardwood flooring all throughout, excellent natural light, floor to ceiling tiled baths, attractive fixtures and lighting, plus multiple storage closets.   Location, Location, Location! On the border of Palisade Ave. Walk to everything! Easy breezy NYC, Downtown JC, & Hoboken commute.        "
260000563,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",78 BEACON AVE,Condominium,2200,6199,"$1,099,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07306,,,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,7,,,"$1,099,000",$499.55,,1/14/2026,,,85,,,1/14/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Laidlaw & Hopkins,"Eligible for a 5-year tax abatement and a special interest rate program with 5.375% (no PMI) and only 5% down, this home offers an incredible opportunity to experience the best of modern city living. Nestled in the vibrant Jersey City Heights neighborhood this stunning new construction duplex condo is 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathrooms offering over 2,000 square feet of modern elegance and thoughtfully designed living space. Upon entry, you’re welcomed into a bright open concept living and dining area, filled with natural light from expansive windows and enhanced by real oak hardwood floors throughout. The modern European-style kitchen serves as the focal point of the home, featuring a sleek quartz waterfall island, stainless steel appliances, ample storage, and contemporary finishes — perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. The main level offers two spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom, providing flexibility for guests, a home office, or family use. The upper level hosts two additional bedrooms and one-and-a-half baths, including a serene primary suite with a spa-like en-suite featuring a glass-enclosed shower and refined fixtures.  Completing the home are desirable features such as in-unit laundry, abundant closet space, and a serene deck patio that extends your living space outdoors. Located in the heart of Jersey City Heights, residents enjoy easy access to local shops, trendy restaurants, parks, and transportation — offering the perfect blend of neighborhood charm and urban convenience."
220016480,SOLD,"JC, Heights",152 CONGRESS ST,Condominium,2693,1653,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,9,,"$1,100,000","$925,000",$408.47,$408.47,9/13/2022,9/23/2022,12/9/2022,10,10,,12/9/2022,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave,"Welcome to 152 Congress St - a two unit condo building with all high end lux modern finishes. Unit 1 is very spacious with over 2600 sqft - making it one of the largest condo units on the market in Jersey City Heights.  This duplex condo unit has 4 generous size bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a large rec room that leads out to the private backyard, and a bonus room with a wet bar that can be used as a game room, dining area, library, or bar area. 1 Car Parking in driveway deeded to the unit (not tandem). Some features include hardwood floor, beautiful chic tile designs, two tone shaker cabinets with quartz countertop, crown molding, custom closets, fireplaces, and Samsung appliances. The master has a large walk in closet, a double sink vanity in the bathroom, and sliding doors leading out to a relaxing private terrace. Lots of natural sunlight all throughout. Conveniently located steps away from Central Ave Shopping District, Restaurants and Coffee Shops, Washington Park, and Congress St Lite Rail. Transportation to NYC, Hoboken, WTC, JSQ are steps away."
240017342,SOLD,"JC, Heights",98 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1752,6494,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,04503,00001,,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$1,100,000","$1,100,000",$627.85,$627.85,9/4/2024,12/7/2024,2/3/2025,94,94,,2/7/2025,,,,,,$520,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton,"This is it - the perfect home at last! Bright and beautiful 3 BR, 2 Bath with private roofdeck and garage parking. Every inch of this amazing home has been carefully curated to impress, and includes floor to ceiling windows in the living room flooding the home with natural light. This open, expansive living area is perfect for either entertaining or a growing family. The modern and chic kitchen features Bertazzoni and Bosch appliances and gleaming quartz countertops. To highlight the open, airy feel, the home has 9 inch white oak flooring throughout and soaring ceilings just under 11 ft.! The large primary BR boasts two large walk-in closets and an oversized spa-like bath with luxurious finishes. Relax on your private roofdeck oasis with views of NYC in one of the most highly sought after streets in the Heights, just a short walk to all the best restaurants, shops and Riverside Fisk Park. Be part of the exciting energy of this hip, rapidly growing neighborhood! It doesn't get any better than this!!!  thewebstercollective.com"
250022043,SOLD,"JC, Heights",617 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1603,1597,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$1,100,000","$1,195,000",$686.21,$686.21,10/24/2025,11/26/2025,2/27/2026,33,33,,2/27/2026,,,,,,$201,,Conventional,,,,,,Congress St & North St,"Seller offering $20K concession towards closing costs!  Brand new and unexpected, this home redefines modern living with rich tones, bespoke design, and a depth of finishes rarely seen. Featuring a 3 bed, 2 bath layout, residents will delight in this private backyard, offering the perfect setting for expanded entertaining or simply unwinding outdoors.  Inside, oversized windows welcome with striking scale, illuminating the wide oak hardwood floors and deep-hued color-cap tray ceiling. The atmospheric fireplace is framed in pale oak and makes a statement, and includes a built-in beveled niche designed to cradle a flatscreen. The dynamic kitchen is open and inviting, with custom light-oak upper cabinetry with under lighting, pepper-toned lower with matching hood and island kick-plate, tying it all together with clean white quartz countertops and backsplash. Additional finishes include stainless appliances like the Thermador appliance suite, as well as a brass pot filler and matching designer pendant lighting.   In the primary suite, design carries with the continued color-cap ceiling treatment, plus a fluted wood accent wall lit by mounted sconces. The bathroom brings beauty and function together with a marble-tiled wet room, where a glass-enclosed shower with niche and accent lighting compliment the freestanding soaking tub, and the spacious double vanity in the same serene space. Conscientious storage abound with fully built walk-in closets throughout for effortless everyday luxury.  Set on a tree-lined street in Jersey City Heights, this modern tan brick façade gives excellent curb appeal. Just minutes to the 9th Street Light Rail elevator and beloved local favorites like Riverview-Fisk Park, Corto, Froth on Franklin and more, these homes offer the best of lifestyle and location."
240008052,SOLD,"JC, Heights",36 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1876,1597,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,04501,00016,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$1,100,000","$975,000",$586.35,$586.35,5/1/2024,5/7/2024,7/22/2024,6,6,,7/22/2024,,,,"$13,240",2023,$276,2024,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin St & Manhattan Ave,"Step into your dream home nestled in the heart of The Heights, where modern luxury meets comfort and convenience. This stunning two-story residence was built in 2022 and boasts three bedrooms, two and a half baths, plus a bonus room, garage with non tandem parking and a private backyard. From the moment you enter, natural light floods through oversized windows, highlighting the gleaming hardwood floors and custom finishes throughout.  Entertain with ease in the open-concept living space, featuring a gourmet kitchen with a sleek island, waterfall quartz countertops, pot filler and top-of-the-line Samsung appliances. The downstairs bonus room, complete with a wet bar and wine fridge, sets the stage for unforgettable gatherings. Step outside to your own private oasis—a fenced backyard with lush greenery, pavers, and a gas grill hookup, perfect for alfresco dining.  Retreat to the luxurious primary suite, boasting dual walk-in closets with custom built-ins and a spa-like ensuite bath with a double vanity, glass shower, and indulgent rainfall showerhead. Additional bedrooms offer ample space and closets with custom built-ins, while stylish bathrooms feature designer tile, spacious vanities, and smart mirrors.  Convenient amenities abound, including non tandem garage parking with an EV charger, custom window treatments, speakers located throughout & outside home, central vacuum, Nest thermostat for heating/cooling, and side-by-side Samsung washer/dryer. Plus, enjoy the benefits of a tax abatement for the next three years (independently verified).  Located just steps from Riverview Fisk Park and the 2nd Street Light Rail, this home offers easy access to top rated restaurants, coffee shops, stores, boutiques, and the vibrant arts scene of Jersey City Heights. With its unbeatable location, luxurious amenities, and thoughtful details, this is urban living at its finest. "
240003428,SOLD,"JC, Heights",81 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1960,1713,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & 3,3,"JC, Heights",07307,4406,12,,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$1,100,000","$1,100,000",$561.22,$561.22,2/23/2024,3/7/2024,4/24/2024,13,13,,4/26/2024,,,2022,$0,,$183,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton & Franklin,"Welcome to the epitome of modern urban living in Jersey City Heights! Unveiling a newly renovated 4-unit condo, this exquisite residence offers a seamless blend of sophistication and comfort. Nestled in the sought-after neighborhood, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom duplex boasts a private roof deck, defining the perfect oasis in the heart of the vibrant community. Meticulously designed, the spacious living area unfolds seamlessly, merging the living, dining, and kitchen spaces into an inviting expanse, ideal for both entertainment and relaxation. Four generously sized bedrooms bathed in natural light, provide ample space for personalized style. Contemporary fixtures and elegant tile work adorn both bathrooms, with frameless shower doors adding a touch of modernity and creating a spa-like feel. The condo's clever use of space and thoughtfully crafted floor plan optimizes the expansive layout, ensuring every inch is functional and aesthetically pleasing. Step onto 4” Select Red Oak Hardwood Floors that span the unit, setting the stage for an elegant experience. The kitchen, a culinary haven, features Kraus kitchen sink & faucet, Jenn Air Appliances, and is graced with a peninsula and quartz countertops, embodying the perfect fusion of style and functionality. Solid core interior doors, extra-wide moldings & trims with crown molding throughout the house create an air of sophistication. The unit also features a dedicated roof deck, low voltage with proficient brand speakers, custom closet designs, wall decor moldings, and claddings in the master bedroom. Located in the thriving Jersey City Heights neighborhood, renowned for its diverse community, shops, cafes, and cultural attractions, this residence offers easy access to transportation, making New York City just a breezy commute away. A shining example of luxury and convenience in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Welcome home!"
250018697,SOLD,"JC, Heights",53 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1502,6429,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3802,13,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,5,,"$1,100,000","$1,150,000",$732.36,$732.36,9/11/2025,9/17/2025,10/28/2025,6,6,,10/28/2025,,,,"$8,415",2023,$233,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton and Griffith,"Exceptional 3BR/2.5BA condo in Jersey City Heights blending modern design with refined finishes. The chef’s kitchen features a quartz waterfall island, KitchenAid appliances, pot filler, and custom cabinetry, opening to a sunlit living area with electric fireplace, built-ins, and LED lighting. Ceiling speakers in the living room enhance the entertainment experience, perfect for movie nights or music. A beverage bar, thoughtfully placed just inside the entrance to the private roof deck, makes entertaining seamless. The primary en-suite bath offers a spa-level retreat with a steam shower, heated floors, and a heated shower bench for ultimate comfort, while the additional bathroom also include heated flooring. Smart-home upgrades include keyless entry, Nest thermostats, and a tankless hot water system. Outdoor living includes balconies plus a private roof deck with sweeping Manhattan views and a gas line for grilling. Added convenience comes with one parking space in an oversized garage with side-by-side layout — no need to move cars or coordinate with neighbors"
250021036,SOLD,"JC, Heights",545 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1380,1724,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,4,"JC, Heights",07307,02305,00029,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$1,100,000","$1,150,000",$797.10,$797.10,10/10/2025,10/16/2025,3/10/2026,6,6,,3/11/2026,,,,,,$429,,Conventional,,,,,,South St. & Bowers,"Luxury penthouse with direct in-unit elevator access, located in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This modern home combines elegance, comfort, and convenience — featuring a private elevator entrance, private balcony off the gourmet kitchen, exclusive rooftop deck with built in kitchen, and sweeping New York City skyline views.  This inviting open-concept customizable 2 or 3 bedroom, 2-bathroom condo  with wide-plank hardwood floors, a gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, high-end stainless steel appliances, and custom cabinetry is perfect for the discerning end user. An abundance of natural light brightens this entire 4th floor home. The massive primary en-suite offers a spa-style bathroom with a double vanity and rainfall shower, while spacious secondary bedrooms provide flexibility for guests or a home office.  Relax or entertain on your private rooftop oasis, with a built in outdoor kitchen and pizza oven. Perfect for enjoying city sunsets or hosting gatherings under the stars.  Located on Palisade Avenue, you’re just steps from Riverview-Fisk Park, boutique cafés, local restaurants, and direct NYC transit. Enjoy all the perks of The Heights — charm, culture, and convenience — with quick access to Hoboken, Downtown Jersey City, and Manhattan."
260004674,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",33 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1910,6705,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,1504,14,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,6,,,"$1,100,000",$575.92,,3/17/2026,,,23,,,3/17/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Summit & Central Ave,"Welcome to 33 Graham St, Unit 1, a beautifully crafted, newly constructed 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence offering modern design and comfortable living. Thoughtfully laid out with an open-concept floor plan, the home features a bright, sun-filled living and dining area that flows seamlessly into a sleek, contemporary kitchen with ample counter spaceperfect for everyday living and entertaining. Each of the three spacious bedrooms provides excellent closet space and comfort, while the three well-appointed bathrooms feature stylish, modern finishes. The primary suite serves as a peaceful retreat, complete with a spa-inspired bath. Additional highlights include in-unit laundry and access to a modest outdoor space, ideal for enjoying fresh air, light gardening, or a quiet moment outside. Located in a quiet, established neighborhood with convenient access to public transportation to and from NYC, as well as nearby shopping, dining, and parks, this home offers a wonderful blend of convenience and modern living. A great opportunity to own new construction, schedule your private showing today. "
240016416,SOLD,"JC, Heights",294 PATERSON PLANK RD,Condominium,0,1713,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,3&4,2,"JC, Heights",07307,1703,25,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$1,100,000","$1,250,000",,,6/20/2024,7/13/2024,1/10/2025,23,0,,1/14/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Ogden and Paterson Plank,"Welcome to the epitome of modern urban living in Jersey City Heights! Nestled in the sought-after Ogden Ave, this 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom duplex boasts a private roof deck and parking, defining the perfect oasis in the heart of the vibrant community. Meticulously designed, the spacious living area unfolds seamlessly, merging the living, dining, and kitchen spaces into an inviting expanse, ideal for both entertainment and relaxation. Four large bedrooms bathed in natural light, provide ample space for personalized style. Contemporary fixtures and elegant tile work adorn the bathrooms, adding a touch of modernity and creating a spa-like feel. The condo's clever use of space and thoughtfully crafted floor plan optimizes the expansive layout, ensuring every inch is functional and aesthetically pleasing. The kitchen, a culinary haven, features stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops, embodying the perfect fusion of style and functionality.  Located in the thriving Jersey City Heights neighborhood, renowned for its diverse community, shops, cafes, and cultural attractions, this residence offers easy access to transportation, making New York City just a breezy commute away. A shining example of luxury and convenience in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Welcome home!"
250016065,SOLD,"JC, Heights",134 MANHATTAN AVE,Condominium,1926,6565,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,04302,00011,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$1,100,000","$1,100,000",$571.13,$571.13,8/6/2025,9/25/2025,11/14/2025,50,50,,11/15/2025,,,,"$14,543",2024,$175,,Conventional,,,,,,Summit Ave. and Sanford Pl.,"Straight out of the pages of Architectural Digest, we proudly present this impeccably designed, nearly 2,000 sq ft residence by Blue Chip Living—offering 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and 1-car non-tandem parking, ideally located on Manhattan Avenue in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This luxurious home masterfully blends modern elegance with everyday functionality. Step into the expansive open floor plan featuring soaring 12-foot ceilings and sun-drenched living spaces that create a bright, inviting atmosphere. The generous living room is adorned with custom blinds from The Shade Store, flowing seamlessly into the dining area and chef’s kitchen—complete with sleek quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and abundant cabinetry.  Retreat to the primary suite, a serene oasis with a spa-inspired ensuite bath, a custom-designed walk-in closet, and sliding doors that lead to a private balcony. Down the hall are three additional well-proportioned bedrooms, each with ample closet space, and a beautifully appointed full bathroom with a double vanity. A stylish powder room and a convenient side-by-side laundry room add to the home's thoughtful layout.  The crown jewel of this home is the expansive private rooftop deck, enhanced by a large pergola—perfect for outdoor entertaining, dining, or relaxing under the stars. Plus, enjoy the benefits of smart home features including a Ring doorbell, Nest thermostat, and Smart Fridge, ensuring ease and comfort in everyday living.  Additional highlights include:  Custom primary closet system Custom window treatments in the living room EV charger-ready parking spot 3 years remaining on the tax abatement Nestled in a prime residential location with quick access to Jersey City’s vibrant energy, this one-of-a-kind home offers the ultimate in contemporary city living."
210013239,SOLD,"JC, Heights",126 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,2381,1641,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,4F,"JC, Heights",07307,04503,00017,,Hugo Pronti Artist Lofts,,,,2,0,2,8,,"$1,100,000","$1,080,000",$461.99,$461.99,6/2/2021,6/12/2021,7/30/2021,10,10,,8/4/2021,,,,"$14,312",2020,$536,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin & Hutton Streets,"Tribeca comes to JCH!!!! A house in the sky. Come home everyday to this staggering stunner of a loft, a true loft - as in a perfectly appointed industrial space that was once a luggage factory - so Soho!!!. Where do we start? This wonderful corner 2 bed (easily made into a 3 bed) 2 bath Penthouse puts the OPEN into open-concept - an entertainers dream. Enjoy your gourmet kitchen that includes a Viking Stove, Sub-zero fridge, Bosch dishwasher, marble counters, as the light streams through huge over-sized windows. Wind down every evening enjoying the sweeping view of downtown NYC from your own private balcony. If the exposed brick, beams and extra extra high ceilings weren't enough, glide upstairs to the second floor to find another large living space that includes a bedroom, living room, work space, workout space, luxurious bathroom and massive walk-in closet. Need more space? Feel free to put your snowboards and luggage in your own storage unit. And of course there's the PARKING - your own private garage space. Welcome home to the Heights, the established Riverview Arts District, minutes from everything, quick commute to NYC, wonderful parks and restaurants just a short walk away."
220016201,SOLD,"JC, Heights",266 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,2216,1702,"$1,100,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-3,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,2,2,7,,"$1,100,000","$1,150,000",$496.39,$496.39,9/9/2022,10/14/2022,11/29/2022,35,35,,11/30/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Bowers & South,"Welcome to 266 Webster, a professionally designed boutique condo building located in one of the most desirable sections of Jersey City Heights. This ground up new development features two very large luxury condos. Unit 1 features 3 bedrooms, 2 full and 2 half bathrooms spread over 3 floors and 2216sf. Throughout the home, you'll notice its 9ft ceilings, 4in oak flooring, central A/C, oversized windows, and an open floorplan. The designer kitchen features quartz countertops w/ a waterfall island, matching quartz backsplash, built-in microwave, 5-burner stove and a compact hood that exhausts outside. Bathrooms include high-end tiling, fixtures and hardware. Lastly, completing the unit, you will receive half of the oversized garage (set up for electric car charging) and a PRIVATE backyard! The location is very ideal - just a block away from Washington Park, two blocks from Riverview Park, 5 blocks from the 9th St Light Rail station and within a short distance of all of Jersey City Heights best restaurants, bars and shopping options."
240018754,SOLD,"JC, Heights",15 ZABRISKIE ST,Condominium,1750,5069,"$1,120,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3703,22,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$1,120,000","$1,149,000",$640.00,$640.00,9/22/2024,10/7/2024,11/29/2024,15,15,,11/16/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central and Summit,"Welcome to 15 Zabriskie, Blue Chip Properties’ latest New Construction unit to date. This OVERSIZED 3 bedroom 2 full bath duplex unit spans an impressive 1,750 sqft, which was designed with timeless interior design, top line finishes and fixtures, quality craftsmanship and modern technological features.    This home sits right off of Central Ave, minutes from Hoboken, Congress St Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park and Central & Palisades gourmet restaurants! Your main floor enters to an oversized open concept Dining & Living featuring 12 ft high walls lined with oversized Andersen windows, natural light, floor to ceiling glass accent wall and realistic flame fireplace.    Your Chefs kitchen features top of line designer - two tone cabinetry, Thermador Stove, Thermador Heating Drawer, Panel Ready Fridge, pot filler, pantry, oversized double waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash. The kitchen is further enhanced by the West elm accent lighting and mulitple OVERSIZED windows for plenty of natural sunlight within your kitchen. Main level features OVERSIZED Primary bedroom designed with custom millwork, bedside pendant lighting, walk in-closet with custom built ins and large picturesque private balcony.  Your ensuite bath has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience and offers double vanity, warm pendant lighting, OVERSIZED shower with multiple jets and rain fall shower head.  Two additional bedrooms with finished custom closets and OVERSIZED full bath, laundry room with Top Line Washer / Dryer complete your main level. Your upper floor level enters from a recessed lit staircase which includes wet bar backed with custom backsplash, recessed lighting and wine fridge. This leads out to an oversized rooftop with turf and NYC views, gas / electric and water hook ups making it perfect for entertaining and creating memories.  Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Security Cameras, Google Smart Hub, Smart Thermo and Smart Touch Screen Switches, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smart phone. Garage features OVERSIZED SIDE BY SIDE parking and separate Level 2 High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit. Home is complete with exterior facade and recessed driveway lighting and landscaping. Property comes with 10 year warranty. Please note that sqft is approx."
250004536,SOLD,"JC, Heights",22 BEACON AVE,Condominium,2030,1597,"$1,125,000",CONDO-COOP,,2 & 3,2,"JC, Heights",07306,,,Journal Square,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$1,125,000","$1,150,000",$554.19,$554.19,3/11/2025,3/24/2025,5/23/2025,13,13,,5/28/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Palisade & Baldwin,"Few homes can genuinely transform the way you live, but this one delivers. From the moment you step inside, experience a level of design and detail that define next-level luxury. Set at the edge of Jersey City Heights- a quick 15 minute walk to the JSQ Path Station, the beautifully constructed bold black brick exterior captivates, while the expansive extra-wide layout and over 2,000 square feet feel simultaneously grand and welcoming. Offering a 4- bedroom floorplan, this 2-story residence with tandem driveway parking provides modern living at its finest-- also including secluded and serene private rooftop space.   Light oak hardwood floors flow effortlessly through the home with a stunning glass stairwell complementing beautifully curated light fixtures for contemporary edge. Impressive kitchen design sets new standards with style and sophistication in every design selection and finish. Dark-stained wood ceilings, white quartz countertops with a waterfall island, sleek black or gray custom cabinetry, and gold fixtures create contrast in a polished bold look, while high-end stainless-steel appliances add a finishing touch.   An expansive top floor space takes entertaining to a whole new level. The indoor wet bar features exposed wood shelves, foiled wallpaper, and a wine fridge, just before you step out onto the full-size rooftop equipped with all the hookups and stunning NYC skyline views.   The classic floorplan positions all four bedrooms on the upper level for an ideal living environment. The primary ensuite stands out with a private balcony, cozy electric fireplace, striking accent wall, and a fully built-out walk-in closet, plus an indulgent soaker tub and skylight in the bathroom. Overall bathroom design does not disappoint with features like a spacious double vanity, heated towel racks, and an oversized glass shower with floor-to-ceiling tile.    Every detail has been carefully considered to create an elevated living experience. Set on a tree-lined street in a quiet corner of The Heights, these homes offer easy access to Hoboken, the 1 & 9 and Holland Tunnel, and nearby Pershing Field Park and Reservoir with nature paths, sports facilities, dog run, playgrounds and swimming pool. Jersey City Heights is known for its vibrant community, excellent parks and schools and access to NYC and surrounding neighborhoods.  "
230012808,SOLD,"JC, Heights",139 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1500,5069,"$1,125,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$1,125,000","$1,149,000",$750.00,$750.00,8/1/2023,8/15/2023,9/22/2023,14,14,,9/22/2023,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Palisade Ave and Webster,"Welcome to 139 New York, a Luxurious New Construction 3 bedroom 2 full bath duplex designed by one of Jersey City’s top Home Builders, Blue Chip Properties, known for their modern interior design, high end finishes and quality craftsmanship.  This home is the sough area enclave of New York Ave, minutes from Hoboken, Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park and Palisades gourmet restaurants! Your main floor enters into an open concept Dining Room / Living Room featuring 12 ft high walls lined with Andersen windows flooded with natural light.  The living space feels large and airy due to the Floor to Ceiling Glass spanning the entire length of the wall.  Your Chefs kitchen features Top-Line two tone cabinetry, WOLF Stove, smart stainless-steel appliances, pot filler, waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash and accent lighting. Main level features Primary bedroom designed with custom millwork, modern bedside lighting, barn door walk in-closet and large picturesque private balcony. Your ensuite bath has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience. Two additional bedrooms with finished custom closets and laundry room complete your main level.  Your private rooftop showcases unobstructed NYC views from downtown to midtown which provides an exceptional ambience to your entertainment space. The rooftop area also features a custom interior wet bar as well as gas, water and electric exterior hookups. Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Google thermostat and smart hub, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smart phone. Garage features non-tandem parking and High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit. Property comes with 5 Year Tax Abatement and 10 year warranty."
210027129,SOLD,"JC, Heights",124 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1665,1419,"$1,130,000",CONDO-COOP,,5,502,"JC, Heights",07307,04504,00001,,The York,,,,4,0,2,7,,"$1,130,000","$1,150,000",$678.68,$678.68,12/14/2021,4/4/2022,10/12/2022,111,111,,10/13/2022,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,St. & Franklin St.,"Don't miss this opportunity to see The Jersey City Heights newest development - The York! This elevator building optimizes every square foot of the floor plan and includes two communal rooftop decks, a large garage, and a bike rack on the 1st floor. A tranquil oasis is located on the top floor and has one of the largest outdoor spaces in Jersey City; huge private roof deck and private terrace with unobstructed Manhattan views right off of the living room. Bright and captivating, this spacious penthouse condominium entails 3 or even 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with approximately 1,700 sq ft of living space. The striking 12 ft ceiling heights add to the spaciousness of this home. Equipped with chef's kitchen, Bosch stainless steel appliances, modernized cabinetry, in-unit washer/dryer, and in-ceiling speakers managed by Sonos amplifier. 5 wide plank oak hardwood floors throughout, Porcelanosa tile and plumbing fixtures, LED lighting and heated bathroom floors create a true luxurious experience. The builder spared no cost in making this home sound proofed by using sound channels and sound clips, Quietrock, green/noise proofing compound, and even foam insulation, dampening the noise. This unbeatable Heights location is easily commutable and accessible to public transportation being only 1 block from Palisade Ave; with direct bus lines to NYC Port Authority, Hoboken, and Downtown JC. The Hudson Light Rail Stations are only minutes away as well as Pershing Field's indoor pool and ice skating rink being only 3 blocks away. Riverview Park with its amazing views offers Farmers Market, movie nights, and neighborhood events. Garage parking available. 5 year new construction tax abatement. Please contact listing agent for private showing! "
260003838,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",29 CARLTON AVE,Condominium,2000,1751,"$1,137,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,3,0,2,8,,,"$1,137,000",$568.50,,3/5/2026,,,35,,,3/5/2026,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Montrose Ave & Summit Ave,"Luxury Living Meets Urban Convenience in Jersey City Heights Welcome to 29 Carlton Ave #1 — a brand-new, first-floor luxury condo offering the perfect blend of modern design, expansive space, and unbeatable location. Spanning approximately 2,000 sq ft of refined interior living, this residence impresses with soaring 11-foot ceilings, abundant natural light, and high-end finishes throughout.  Highlights include: Massive private backyard (25 x 100) – a rare find in the Heights! Perfect for entertaining, gardening, outdoor dining, or simply relaxing in your own city oasis. 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 designer bathrooms – including a serene primary suite featuring a private terrace for morning coffee or evening unwinding. Expansive open layout – a sun-drenched living, dining, and kitchen area ideal for both gatherings and day-to-day comfort. The sleek chef’s kitchen boasts contemporary cabinetry, premium finishes, and modern appliances. Private driveway with one-car parking – a valuable convenience in this sought-after neighborhood. Prime location – nestled next to Pershing Field Park with walking trails, playgrounds, sports fields, and an ice rink. Steps from local restaurants, shops, bus lines, and just minutes to Journal Square PATH for an easy NYC commute. If you’ve been searching for a brand-new, oversized condo that combines luxury, comfort, outdoor space, and prime location — look no further. Experience the best of Jersey City Heights living at 29 Carlton Ave. COntact for details and sowing"
250004555,SOLD,"JC, Heights",12 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,1645,5069,"$1,149,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,2802,31,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,"$1,149,000","$1,149,000",$698.48,$698.48,3/11/2025,3/29/2025,7/10/2025,18,18,,7/10/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central Ave and Summit ave,"   Introducing 12 Lincoln, a brand new luxury duplex! This south-facing, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence seamlessly blends modern design with natural tones, offering smart home features, oversized floor-to-ceiling windows, and exceptional craftsmanship. The first floor showcases an open-concept living and dining area that flows into the kitchen. The kitchen is a chef’s dream, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, custom two-tone cabinetry, sleek quartz countertops and backsplash, and a wood-accented island. Designer pendant lighting frames the space, while oversized Andersen windows flood the room with natural light. The main bedroom is equally light-filled, with triple-wide Andersen windows, custom closets, and an interior accent wall with pendant lighting. The luxurious en-suite bathroom includes a double vanity, matte black high-end shower fixtures, and a rainfall showerhead. The main floor also features two additional bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a laundry room. The private, full-size rooftop is perfect for entertaining, offering stunning NYC views, Trex flooring, and a turf section that adds a touch of greenery to the outdoor space. The garage provides non-tandem parking, and the property comes with a 5-year tax abatement and a 10-year warranty."
250011561,SOLD,"JC, Heights",34 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1790,5069,"$1,149,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,1505,44,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,6,,"$1,149,000","$1,149,000",$641.90,$641.90,6/9/2025,6/9/2025,6/13/2025,0,0,,6/13/2025,,,,$0,,,,Cash,No,No,Yes,,,Central and Summit ave,"Welcome to 34 Graham, Blue Chip Properties’ most luxurious New Construction home to date. This 3 bedroom 3 full bath duplex, this unit was designed with timeless interior design, top line finishes and fixtures, quality craftsmanship and modern technological features. This home sits on sought after Graham Street for it's close proximity to Congress St Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park, Central Ave and Palisade Ave gourmet restaurants!  Your main floor opens to an open concept Dining & Living featuring 10 ft high walls lined with oversized Andersen Energy Efficient windows, natural light and realistic flame fireplace. Your Chefs kitchen features designer - two tone cabinetry, Thermador Stove, Thermador Heating Drawer, Panel Ready Thermador Fridge, pot filler, oversized double waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash, West elm accent lighting, Oversize Double Window and externally vented Hood Vent.  Main level features an oversized Primary bedroom designed with custom millwork, bedside pendant lighting, double walk-in-closet with custom built-ins and large private balcony with views of Manhattan. Through the frosted glass barn door is your ensuite bath which has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience and offers oversized double vanity, soaking tub, warm pendant lighting, vein matched porcelain and oversized shower with body jets and rainfall shower head.  One additional bedroom with finished custom closets, an Oversized Full bath with oversized double vanity and floor to ceiling limewash tiles, laundry room with Top Line Washer / Dryer complete your main level.  Your ground floor level enters from recessed lit staircase which includes RARE full bath and oversized bedroom / entertaining room, wet bar backed with accent lit custom backsplash and wine fridge, large closet and wide plank floors. This leads out to private backyard with professional landscaping, paver patio, accent lighting, gas / electric and water hookups making it perfect for entertaining and creating memories.  Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Security Cameras, Google Smart Hub, Smart Thermo and Smart Touch Screen Switches, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smartphone. Garage features RARE Side-by-Side parking and a separate Level 2 High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit as well as security camera. Home is complete with exterior facade and recessed driveway lighting and landscaping. Property comes with 10 year warranty and may qualify for 5 Year Tax Abatement . Please note that sqft is approx."
