230012207,SOLD,"JC, Heights",541 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,1600,5069,"$1,149,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,B,"JC, Heights",07307,803,26,Heights,,,,,2,0,2,5,,"$1,149,000","$1,149,000",$718.13,$718.13,7/21/2023,8/14/2023,10/17/2023,24,24,,10/17/2023,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central Ave,"541 Central B, an Oversized ultra-lux Duplex PentHouse built by a top luxury home builder. This home offers 2 oversized bedrooms and 2 ensuite baths across 1600 sqft. Your main living room level consists of a range of high end finishes: wide white oak floors, Legrand smart tone lighting, ecobee smart thermo, all encased within top line noise suppression materials and Marvin windows. Your kitchen also showcases a wide range of high end finishes / fixtures: custom cut Italian porcelain waterfall island with warm recessed lighting underneath, Subzero Refrigerator, Wolf Range with Miele Hood, Sharp microwave drawer, Miele dishwasher hidden seamlessly within your custom Italian cabinetry. Your main bedroom suite enters from a private wood and smoked glass door to a warm space lit by pendant lighting, Marvin windows, oversized bathroom with Italian double vanity, bronze pendant lights, floor to ceiling porcelain slab as well as multi head matte black shower fixtures. Your main suite is completed with an Italian custom built closet with dark wood tones, warm lighting and configurable shelving and drawers. Completing your main level is an additional oversized bedroom with floor to ceiling built in closets and high end full bath which includes pendant lighting, Italian vanity, full slab porcelain shower with matte black shower finishes. Your upper level consists of dry bar and full roof length rooftop perfect for entertaining amongst views of Mid Town and Downtown NYC, complete with gas, water and electric hook ups.   Tandem garage with State of Art Autel EV charger, tinted glass garage door, padded floors and security system completes this home. This home’s location offers convenient access to Washington Park, award winning restaurants, shops and stores, Congress St Light Rail and easy NYC bus access. Home also includes 5 year tax abatement and 10 year warranty."
250001454,SOLD,"JC, Heights",64 WEBSTER AVE,Condominium,1550,5069,"$1,150,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,4505,3,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$1,150,000","$1,199,000",$741.94,$741.94,1/22/2025,2/18/2025,3/29/2025,27,27,,3/29/2025,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Ferry st and Franklin St,"MOMENTS FROM RIVERVIEW FISK PARK and HOBOKEN. Welcome to 64 Webster, built by one of Jersey City's most sought out Developers' Blue Chip Properties’. This 3 bedroom 2 full bath duplex unit was designed with timeless interior design, top line finishes and fixtures, quality craftsmanship and modern technological features. This home sits on sought after Webster Ave Enclave for it's close proximity to Hoboken, Riverview-Fisk Park, Central Ave and Palisade Ave gourmet restaurants!  Your main floor opens to an open concept Dining & Living featuring 12 ft high walls lined with oversized Andersen Energy Efficient windows, floor to ceiling tempered glass accent wall, natural light and realistic flame fireplace. Your Chefs kitchen features designer - two tone cabinetry, Thermador Stove, Thermador Heating Drawer, Panel Ready Thermador Fridge, pot filler, oversized double waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash, West elm accent lighting, Oversize Double Window and externally vented Hood Vent.  Main level features Primary bedroom designed with custom millwork, bedside pendant lighting, double walk-in-closet with custom built-ins and large private balcony with NYC views. Your ensuite bath which has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience and offers oversized double vanity, soaking tub, warm pendant lighting, multiple Kohler Body Sprays and  shower head. Two additional bedrooms with finished custom closets, an Oversized Full bath with oversized double vanity and floor to ceiling limewash tiles, laundry room with Top Line Washer / Dryer complete your main level.  Your upper outdoor level enters from recessed lit staircase, glass accent wall and wet bar backed with accent lit custom backsplash and wine fridge and custom cabinetry. This leads out to an oversized rooftop with SOME OF THE BEST NYC VIEWS in the heights, top line astroturf and trex decking, gas / electric and water hookups making it perfect for entertaining and creating memories. Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Security Cameras, Google Smart Hub, Smart Thermo and Smart Touch Screen Switches, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smartphone. Garage features RARE Side-by-Side parking and a separate Level 2 High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit as well as security camera. Home is complete with Blue Chip Properties' Signature exterior facade and recessed drive and landscaping. Property comes with 10 year warranty and may qualify for 5 Year Tax Abatement . Please note that sqft is approx."
250002087,SOLD,"JC, Heights",32 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1790,5069,"$1,150,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,1505,44,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$1,150,000","$1,149,000",$642.46,$642.46,1/31/2025,3/9/2025,5/6/2025,37,37,,5/6/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central and Summit ave,"   Welcome to 32 Graham, Blue Chip Properties’ most luxurious New Construction home to date. This 3 bedroom 3 full bath duplex, this unit was designed with timeless interior design, top line finishes and fixtures, quality craftsmanship and modern technological features. This home sits on sought after Graham Street for it's close proximity to Congress St Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park, Central Ave and Palisade Ave gourmet restaurants!  Your main floor opens to an open concept Dining & Living featuring 10 ft high walls lined with oversized Andersen Energy Efficient windows, natural light and realistic flame fireplace. Your Chefs kitchen features designer - two tone cabinetry, Thermador Stove, Thermador Heating Drawer, Panel Ready Thermador Fridge, pot filler, oversized double waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash, West elm accent lighting, Oversize Double Window and externally vented Hood Vent.  Main level features an oversized Primary bedroom designed with custom millwork, bedside pendant lighting, double walk-in-closet with custom built-ins and large private balcony with views of Manhattan. Through the frosted glass barn door is your ensuite bath which has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience and offers oversized double vanity, soaking tub, warm pendant lighting, vein matched porcelain and oversized shower with body jets and rainfall shower head.  One additional bedroom with finished custom closets, an Oversized Full bath with oversized double vanity and floor to ceiling limewash tiles, laundry room with Top Line Washer / Dryer complete your main level.  Your ground floor level enters from recessed lit staircase which includes RARE full bath and oversized bedroom / entertaining room, wet bar backed with accent lit custom backsplash and wine fridge, large closet and wide plank floors. This leads out to private backyard with professional landscaping, paver patio, accent lighting, gas / electric and water hookups making it perfect for entertaining and creating memories.  Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Security Cameras, Google Smart Hub, Smart Thermo and Smart Touch Screen Switches, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smartphone. Garage features RARE Side-by-Side parking and a separate Level 2 High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit as well as security camera. Home is complete with exterior facade and recessed driveway lighting and landscaping. Property comes with 10 year warranty and may qualify for 5 Year Tax Abatement . Please note that sqft is approx."
260005068,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",252 BOWERS ST,Condominium,1800,1750,"$1,150,000",CONDO-COOP,,2/3,2,"JC, Heights",07307-1111,2604,42,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,10,,,"$1,150,000",$638.89,,3/23/2026,,,17,,,3/23/2026,,,,"$10,288",2023,$125,2026,,No,No,Yes,,,Milton and Kennedy,"Welcome to 252 Bowers Street #2, a beautifully designed true 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence offering an exceptional blend of scale, style, and modern luxury in Jersey City Heights, INCLUDING 1 CAR PARKING. The first level is thoughtfully designed for everyday living and entertaining, featuring a sun-drenched open-concept layout with wide-plank hardwood floors, oversized bay windows, designer accent walls, recessed lighting, a stylish powder room, and a stunning chef’s kitchen complete with sleek custom cabinetry, a quartz waterfall island, stainless steel appliances, a wine fridge, and elegant pendant lighting, all flowing seamlessly into the dining area. Upstairs, all four bedrooms and two full baths are privately situated on the second level, along with a dedicated laundry room for added convenience. The spacious primary suite serves as a true retreat, highlighted by a striking designer feature wall, a massive walk-in closet with custom built-ins, an additional closet for even more storage, and a charming Juliette balcony overlooking the backyard below. Crowning the home is an expansive private roof deck, offering the perfect setting for entertaining, relaxing, or enjoying open views from above. A rare opportunity to lease a polished, high-end home with beautifully layered indoor-outdoor living in one of Jersey City Heights’ most desirable locations. Private Showings welcome."
210003859,SOLD,"JC, Heights",112 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,2493,1683,"$1,150,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & G,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,,,,,,4,1,2,7,,"$1,150,000","$1,295,000",$461.29,$461.29,2/16/2021,3/12/2021,7/13/2021,21,21,,7/16/2021,,,,$0,,$590,,Conventional,,,,,,Booraem & Reservoir,"Built on coveted Ogden Avenue with subdued modern flair and impeccable design, one of Jersey City Height’s most trusted developers is coming to market with a residence that truly stands out amongst the crowd. This incredibly spacious duplex feels more like a suburban house and wows the senses upon entry with tall ceilings and open spaces flooded with natural light.  Step inside to thoughtful finishes and top quality - wide plank oak floors carry throughout the perfectly laid out main level, anchored by a centralized chef's kitchen complete with custom cabinetry and built-in pantry along with an impeccable appliance package that includes Bosch stainless steel refrigerator and Bertazzoni gas range and hood.  The kitchen's black fixtures and beautiful Italian marble backsplash add a sense of sublime elegance.  The main floor includes a powder room, dining area and study while the wide open living area's huge sliding glass doors allow access to your private multi-leveled and fenced yard. The sleeping areas are located downstairs and allow for peace and privacy while the massive master bedroom with custom walk-in closet and en-suite is truly a dream come true with an oversized rainfall shower.  Walk right out on to the lower level of your private backyard directly from the master suite and enjoy unobstructed views of NYC from the cliffs of Ogden Avenue!  This little slice of heaven is perfectly situated on a picturesque, quiet, tree-lined street with a community garden at one end and a small dog run and playground directly across the street.  Pershing Field and Riverview Park are nearby as this location offers walkability to surrounding Central & Palisade Avenue for essential shopping and transportation needs."
240006139,SOLD,"JC, Heights",18 CAMBRIDGE AVE,Condominium,2882,1725,"$1,150,726",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07030,04405,00006,,,,,,4,1,3,7,,"$1,150,726","$1,150,000",$399.28,$399.28,4/3/2024,4/9/2024,6/13/2024,6,6,,6/14/2024,,,,"$12,998",2022,$256,,Conventional,,,,,,Franklin and Hutton St.,"Your search ends here! Welcome to 18 Cambridge Ave. and to the kind of space you thought you’d have to move out of town to find! Built in 2020, this oversized 2,882 sq. ft. duplex is wholly unique in both design  and scale. Step right into your condo from the front porch and one flight of stairs will take you directly into an unbelievably large living/kitchen/dining area with a powder room, fantastic natural light and plenty of closet/pantry space.  The beautiful open concept chef’s kitchen features a marble waterfall island with inlay porcelain farm sink, Fabuwood Nexus cabinetry, dual zone Avanti wine fridge, Samsung stainless steel black appliances and Kohler fixtures. An extra wide (4'3) staircase never seen in town leads you up to four generously apportioned bedrooms, two of which have custom built walk in closets and en suite bathrooms with double vanities and multiple shower heads. You’ll also find the laundry room and third full bathroom on this floor before heading up to the massive roof deck to soak in gorgeous City Views. Herringbone deck treads, aluminum railings, water line, and built in sound system make this a perfect space to enjoy an evening cocktail or wear out your dog with a game of fetch. Other notable building features include South, East and West facing Pella Windows (that actually clear the neighboring buildings!), extra wide molding and crown throughout, integrated vacuum system, extra soundproofing and insulation, Ring camera/security system, nest thermostats, and home entertainment wiring with 5.1 speakers. This one of a kind home is nestled on a great block with amazing neighbors, minutes from both Pershing Field and Central Ave with all of its exciting shopping and dining options."
210026220,SOLD,"JC, Heights",73 IRVING ST,Condominium,1835,1468,"$1,155,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,PH,"JC, Heights",07307,00805,00001,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$1,155,000","$1,152,750",$629.43,$629.43,11/28/2021,1/27/2022,3/29/2022,60,60,,3/29/2022,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Corner of Kennedy Blvd,"The watercolor sunset views from your large private rooftop with your 360 degree, truly unobstructed views of midtown Manhattan, lower Manhattan and the entire west side of New Jersey, and the warm amber glow that warms the entire top floor of your penthouse, must be experienced in person. This 4-story new construction building sits on a corner lot and clears every neighboring building in a multi-block radius. This building is actually situated at the highest elevation point in Jersey City of over 181 feet. Take the elevator to the 4th FL where you will exit the elevator into your unit. Greeting you is a very large window and a private laundry room with oversized units, ample cabinetry and sink. Walk the 8” white oak floors into the true definition of a great room! This entirely open layout concept features separate living & dining spaces, utterly enveloped in floor-to-ceiling windows. Your custom kitchen features Fisher Pykall appliances, custom cabinetry, custom quartz countertops, wine fridge, a large island with a custom, beautifully ribboned quartz countertop and an invisible dishwasher. The large master bedroom will be flooded with afternoon sunlight and features an inset wall lined with custom lighting, features a large walk-in closet and a bathroom offering custom floating quartz countertops/storage. There are 2 additional bedrooms surrounded by windows in a true split-plan perfect for children, guests or a private work space! Solid core 8-foot doors throughout, a 4 ton cooling/heating system, a custom accent wall, cement-fiber structural 3/4 tongue and groove sub flooring (mitigates floor movement) and deeded parking complete this truly unique Jersey City Heights condo living experience. HOA approximate and taxes TBD/should be independently verified by Jersey City tax assessor.  "
230012807,SOLD,"JC, Heights",139 NEW YORK AVE,Condominium,1750,5069,"$1,160,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,4,0,3,8,,"$1,160,000","$1,199,000",$662.86,$662.86,8/1/2023,8/29/2023,10/5/2023,28,28,,10/5/2023,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Palisade Ave and Webster,"Welcome to 139 New York, a Luxurious New Construction 4 bedroom 3 full bath duplex unit designed and built by Jersey City’s very own Blue Chip Properties, known for their modern design, high end finishes and quality craftsmanship.  This home is the sough area enclave of New York Ave, minutes from Hoboken, Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park and Palisades gourmet restaurants! Your main floor enters to an open concept Dining & Living featuring 10 ft high walls lined with Andersen windows and natural light. Your Chefs kitchen features top of line two tone cabinetry, WOLF Stove, smart stainless-steel appliances, pot filler, waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash and accent lighting.  Main level features Primary bedroom designed with custom millwork,  bedside pendant lighting, walk in-closet and large picturesque private balcony. Your ensuite bath has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience. Two additional bedrooms with finished custom closets, full bath and laundry room complete your main level. Your ground floor level includes full bath and oversized bedroom / entertaining room, which features wet bar and large closet.  This leads out to a tree lined private backyard with professional landscaping, paver patio and accent lighting making it perfect for entertaining and creating memories.    Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Google thermostat and smart hub, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smart phone. Garage features non-tandem parking and separate Level 2 High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit. Property comes with 5 Year Tax Abatement and 10 year warranty."
250014701,SOLD,"JC, Heights",17 LEONARD ST,Condominium,1900,1597,"$1,165,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,504,17,,,,,,4,0,3,8,,"$1,165,000","$1,150,000",$613.16,$613.16,7/18/2025,8/18/2025,10/10/2025,31,31,,10/26/2025,,,,,,,,Cash,,,,,,Summit and Central Ave,"Expertly crafted 4 bedroom, 3 bath residence in the heart of Jersey City Heights, offering exceptional space, design, and functionality. This expansive condo features soaring ceilings, a private roof deck, and premium finishes throughout. Abundant natural light pours in through oversized windows, highlighting the open layout and architectural details. The chef’s kitchen is outfitted with professional-grade appliances, including a pot filler, double oven, fully vented hood, and custom cabinetry that blends elegance with everyday utility. The expansive primary suite includes a sleek en suite bath with radiant heated floors, plus three custom walk-in closets. Bathrooms throughout the home feature refined designer tile work and high-end fixtures. Additional highlights include two private entrances, dedicated basement storage, and extensive closet space. Every detail reflects thoughtful planning and uncompromising quality. "
250019186,SOLD,"JC, Heights",11 CAMBRIDGE AVE,Condominium,1619,1623,"$1,175,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,4404,33,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$1,175,000","$1,100,000",$725.76,$725.76,9/17/2025,10/20/2025,11/21/2025,33,33,,11/24/2025,,,,"$12,914",2024,$250,2024,Conventional,,,,,,Corner of Franklin,"Experience luxury living in this bright, quiet 3-bedroom, 2-bath top-floor condo in the Jersey City Heights, offering a thoughtfully designed space with exceptional flow and stunning views of the NYC skyline from your oversized private roof deck with a built-in BBQ/kitchen, gas and water hookups, bistro lighting, and self-irrigating planters — a perfect space for entertaining.  Inside, enjoy a chef’s kitchen with white marble waterfall island, farm sink, and Samsung stainless steel appliances. Master bedroom outfitted with custom walk-in closets, high-end porcelain-tiled baths, ceiling fan, and premium finishes throughout. Smart tech features include built-in multi-room and roof speakers, Ring security system, central vacuum, and Nest thermostat. Additional perks include automatic Hunter Douglas shades, Pella windows, soundproofing, garage parking, and abundant storage. This modern, move-in-ready condo combines top-quality finishes, outdoor living, and convenience in one of Jersey City’s most desirable neighborhoods.  Easy commute to NYC by the 119 bus at Central and Franklin Avenue (1 block away) or to Hoboken by the 87 at Central and Ferry (2 blocks away). Enjoy the newly renovated Historic Reservoir and Pershing Field Park, only a few blocks away, restaurants and shopping also nearby."
250018087,SOLD,"JC, Heights",244 SHERMAN AVE,Condominium,1700,1713,"$1,175,000",CONDO-COOP,,1-2,A,"JC, Heights",07307,2302,8,,,,,,3,1,2,9,,"$1,175,000","$1,249,000",$691.18,$691.18,9/4/2025,9/26/2025,11/4/2025,22,22,,11/5/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Bowers & Griffith,"Discover this stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom duplex nestled in the vibrant Jersey City Heights. This meticulously designed home seamlessly blends modern amenities with comfortable living spaces, making it an ideal urban sanctuary. Enjoy the unparalleled convenience of non-tandem garage parking with individual EV chargers for each unit owner, offering direct access and catering to the needs of the modern electric vehicle owner.  The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting elegant two-tone cabinetry and seamlessly integrated paneled appliances for a sleek, contemporary look. It's equipped with a professional-grade Wolf range, a built-in Bosch microwave, a convenient pot filler, and under-cabinet lighting that illuminates the beautiful matching stone backsplash.  Flowing effortlessly from the kitchen, the upstairs living and dining area provides a perfect setting for entertaining. This space features a cozy built-in fireplace and dedicated TV hookups, ensuring a comfortable and connected experience.  Descend to the downstairs living room, which offers direct access to your private backyard – an urban oasis for relaxation and entertaining. This lower level also includes another built-in fireplace with dedicated TV hookups and a convenient powder room for guests.  The primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring an expansive closet and a spa-like ensuite bathroom. Indulge in the double vanity, a stylish lit mirror, and a spacious glass-enclosed shower. The second full bathroom is thoughtfully designed with a relaxing tub.  This exceptional duplex also offers the convenience of a full-size washer and dryer and ample storage throughout.  Enjoy all the benefits of living in Jersey City Heights, known for its strong community feel, excellent public transportation options (including easy access to NYC), lush parks, and diverse dining scene. Don't miss the opportunity to own this remarkable duplex that perfectly combines luxury, comfort, and practicality in this desirable neighborhood."
240020051,SOLD,"JC, Heights",22 BEACON AVE,Condominium,2020,1597,"$1,175,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07306,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,"$1,175,000","$1,200,000",$581.68,$581.68,10/10/2024,10/18/2024,1/6/2025,8,8,,1/6/2025,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Palisade & Baldwin,"Few homes can genuinely transform the way you live, but this one delivers. From the moment you step inside, experience a level of design and detail that define next-level luxury. Set in Jersey City Heights, the beautifuly constructed bold black brick exterior captivates, while the expansive extra-wide layout and over 2,000 square feet feel simultaneously grand and welcoming. Offering a 3-bedroom floorplan, this 2-story residence provides modern living at its finest including secluded and serene private backyard space.   Light oak hardwood floors flow effortlessly through the home with a stunning glass stairwell complementing beautifully curated light fixtures for contemporary edge. Impressive kitchen design sets new standards with style and sophistication in every design selection and finish. Dark-stained wood ceilings, white quartz countertops with a waterfall island, sleek black or gray custom cabinetry, and gold fixtures create contrast in a polished bold look, while high-end stainless-steel appliances add a finishing touch.   Feel the true spaciousness of this home the moment you step inside, as the open floor plan reveals itself across the extra-wide lot, allowing you to see from the front through to the back of the home. The dining room features a tray ceiling with dramatic lighting and an architecturally elegant archway showcasing the wet bar with exposed wood shelves, foiled wallpaper, and a wine fridge. Step outside the sliding glass doors to the private backyard beautifully finished with pavers, lush lawn, and landscaping, creating a serene space for relaxation or extended entertaining space.    One bed and bath are located on the main floor of this home, with two additional bedrooms and bathrooms upstairs. The primary ensuite stands out with a private balcony, cozy electric fireplace, striking accent wall, and a fully built-out walk-in closet. Meanwhile, bathrooms do not disappoint with features like a spacious double vanity, heated towel racks, and an oversized glass shower with floor-to-ceiling tile.   Every detail has been carefully considered to create an elevated living experience. Set on a tree-lined street in a quiet corner of The Heights, these homes offer easy access to Hoboken, the 1 & 9 and Holland Tunnel, and nearby Pershing Field Park and Reservoir with nature paths, sports facilities, dog run, playgrounds and swimming pool. Jersey City Heights is known for its vibrant community, excellent parks and schools and access to NYC and surrounding neighborhoods."
230006179,SOLD,"JC, Heights",281 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,1680,1597,"$1,175,000",CONDO-COOP,,5,,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$1,175,000","$1,175,000",$699.40,$699.40,4/18/2023,4/29/2023,6/6/2023,11,11,,6/6/2023,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton & Sherman,"Soak in downtown Manhattan views and an endless list of upgrades in this ultra-exclusive penthouse at The Beckford. Settled on Central Avenue in Jersey City Heights, style, smart-tech and sophistication come together in this sleek home. Use the ButterflyMX Smart Entry to take your private elevator directly to your 1,828 sq ft, three bedroom, two and a half bath urban oasis including a private rooftop with Manhattan views. Relax into 560 sq ft of outdoor living featuring a full outdoor kitchen featuring Kalamazoo Grill, Dekton by Cosentino waterfall countertops, built-in refrigerator and sink and surrounding West Elm outdoor planters.   Inside, floor to ceiling living room windows plus a juliet balcony showcase the downtown NYC and Jersey City skylines. Elegant interior finishes include white oak herringbone hardwood flooring, slatted wood or wallpapered accent walls, sophisticated Lutron Caseta and Kasa smart dimmer lighting, and blackout Bali motorized roller shades for added privacy. Spectacular chef-inspired kitchen features Caesarstone matte quartz waterfall countertop and backsplash, and sleek matte black Shiloh custom cabinetry. Accents include exposed walnut shelving, Brizo faucet and pot filler, plus luscious natural walnut paneling on the eat-in island. Panel front Fisher & Paykel appliances include built-in refrigerator, professional induction range and exterior vented range hood.  Luxurious bathrooms invite with floor to ceiling Nemo tile, vessel sinks, floating vanities, wall mounted matte black faucets and Kohler soaking tub in primary ensuite. Spacious bedrooms host custom closet systems, while the primary showcases a striking wood panel accent wall. The penthouse offers central a/c and heat and full-size washer and dryer for added convenience.  Central Avenue offers the ultimate access to all that Jersey City Heights has to offer. The main thoroughfare is home to the vibrant artist community, essential shops and award-winning restaurants, while also 2 blocks to massive Pershing Field Park and Reservoir and easy NYC access. Building amenities include the massive shared roof deck and garden, secured entrance and elevator. Built by one of Jersey City’s most prestigious builders, M2M Development, known for their quality construction and ultra-stylish design."
240020251,SOLD,"JC, Heights",281 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,1828,6078,"$1,190,000",CONDO-COOP,,4,PH 5A,"JC, Heights",07307,3702,29,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$1,190,000","$1,198,000",$650.98,$650.98,10/14/2024,11/8/2024,12/5/2024,25,25,,1/7/2025,,,,"$14,102",,$653,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton and Sherman,"Marvel at the spacious layout of this approx 1828 s.f 3 bed, 2.5 bath exclusive penthouse unit in The Beckford with stunning Manhattan views from every room and private roof deck. Seamlessly combining modern style with cutting-edge smart technology this unit offers the pinnacle of urban living. Upon entering from your private elevator you are greeted by an expansive foyer leading to the spacious open concept living/dining rooms adorned with stunning oak hardwood herringbone floors and floor-to-ceiling windows providing a stunning panorama of both the NYC and Jersey City skylines, while filling the home with natural light. The private deck, spanning 650 square feet, is designed for luxurious entertaining, complete with a fully equipped kitchen that includes a Kalamazoo Grill with its own dedicated gas line, a double-drawer refrigerator and sleek Dekton countertops. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, boasting an Induction Range, Caesarstone quartz countertops, custom Shiloh cabinetry, oversized island, a vent hood, garbage disposal and pot filler. The meticulously designed bathrooms feature upscale Nemo tile, modern Vessel sinks, and a luxurious Kohler soaking tub, creating a spa-like retreat within your home. Smart home features include smart lighting, motorized solar and blackout shades, a motorized video screen descending from the ceiling, and a nest thermostat. Additional features include recessed lighting, a 2-zone central HVAC with nest thermostats, and in-unit washer and dryer. Located on Central Avenue, this penthouse offers unparalleled access to the vibrant Jersey City Heights neighborhood, known for its eclectic mix of shops, dining options, and the scenic Pershing Field Park. The Beckford, completed in 2021 by renowned M2M Development, epitomizes quality craftsmanship and modern elegance. Additional building amenities include a remote activated secure entrance system by Butterfly, and an auxiliary storage area for bikes or other storage needs. Convenient parking is readily available with a dedicated space, transferable to Buyer, 1 block away, as well as low-cost municipal lot adjacent to the building, along with additional parking options nearby. This residence offers a rare combination of luxury, convenience, and style in one of Jersey City Heights’ most desirable locations."
240020925,SOLD,"JC, Heights",74 BOWERS ST,Condominium,2200,1713,"$1,195,000",CONDO-COOP,,3&4,PH,"JC, Heights",07307,2301,1,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,8,,"$1,195,000","$1,195,000",$543.18,$543.18,10/24/2024,11/1/2024,12/6/2024,8,8,,12/12/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Sherman & Webster,"Welcome to this luxurious 2,200 sq ft oversized, open concept single level condo located in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This spacious 3BR/2.5B residence offers modern amenities and an unbeatable urban lifestyle, perfect for those seeking comfort and convenience. Step inside to discover an open-concept layout featuring high-end finishes and built-in speakers, creating an immersive audio experience throughout the home. This sundrenched corner unit offers ample natural light highlighting the thoughtfully designed interiors and quartz countertops. Each unit is equipped with an in-unit washer and dryer, tankless hot water heater and central air conditioning providing energy efficiency and year-round comfort. One of the standout features of this property is the private roof deck, where you can enjoy breathtaking views and outdoor living. Additionally, the condo includes one dedicated garage parking spot, an additional storage room, and EV chargers for electric vehicles, making it a perfect choice for those who value convenience and sustainability."
260003158,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",619 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1603,5069,"$1,195,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,6,,,"$1,195,000",$745.48,,2/24/2026,,,44,,,2/24/2026,,,,,,,,,No,No,Yes,,,Congress & North St,"Seller offering $20K concession towards closing costs!  Welcome to 619 Palisade Avenue unit 2, a premier high-end new construction condo from NKAY Developers in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Conveniently located on Palisade Avenue, just steps from Washington Park, this unit features 3 XL bedrooms, 2 full baths and private backyard. Custom designed kitchen offers top of the line stainless steel Thermador appliances including wine fridge, XL quartz waterfall counters and backsplash, oversized stainless steel sink, two-tone custom cabinetry, pot filler, stylish gold hardware and fixtures, and high-end pendant lighting. Open-Concept living and dining room are complete with a fireplace framed with custom millwork and wall to wall oversized Andersen windows with NYC views. Just off the main living area, a built-in workstation provides a dedicated space for work or study. Main bedroom suite offers ample natural light and boasts a luxurious accent wall with dual pendant lighting, walk in custom closet with custom built-in shelving and drawers and frosted glass doors and private balcony. Ensuite bathroom offers clean design with white tile and porcelain slabs as well as oversized double vanity, dramatic warm accent lighting, and a top of the line waterfall shower, complete with sprayer and jets and soaking tub. Each of the additional 2 bedrooms feature high end custom built-in closets and common bathroom. Washer/dryer in unit add to the convenience of the home. An additional storage closet provides extra space for home essentials, maximizing functionality.The home is also equipped with a smart doorbell, keyless entry, Legrand smart dimmers, and energy-efficient smart thermostats. The exterior facade has been designed with modern yet timeless features, exterior lighting, professional landscaping, and a fenced-in front yard. This property comes with a 10-year warranty. Highly sought after location being steps from new restaurants, shopping, palisade ave bus stop, Congress st light rail, Riverview Fisk park and much more! Please note that square footage is approximate. Off-site parking available."
230019334,SOLD,"JC, Heights",132 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,1750,1724,"$1,199,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,12002,00044 01,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$1,199,000","$1,199,000",$685.14,$685.14,11/16/2023,12/9/2023,2/2/2024,23,23,,2/5/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy and Sanford,"Experience the epitome of high-end luxury in this immaculate Brand New Construction condominium built on an oversized lot, located on one of the most desirable streets in JC Heights. Just steps away from Gordon Park,  this spacious 1750-square-foot residence features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, along with a Private Roof Deck.  The interior is adorned with contemporary accents, showcasing elegant elements such as high ceilings, light-finished 6 wide plank hardwood flooring, Anderson windows, custom built in electric fireplace and 8-foot Custom entry doors throughout. Indulge in a state-of-the-art chef's kitchen complete with 60-inch sleek custom soft-closing cabinets, quartz countertops and backsplash, a spacious center island, and a full suite of VIKING appliances and wall ovens.  The bathrooms are adorned with sophisticated tiles and a glass-enclosed rain shower. The generous Primary Bedroom features a walk-in closet, a private balcony, a spacious en-suite bathroom with floor-to-ceiling custom tiling,  glass shower, a soaking tub, and double vanity sinks.  Nestled on a street with beautiful historic preserved homes and walking distance to Pershing Field Park, this home offers the best of urban living. Owners will appreciate its proximity to NYC transportation, neighboring districts, and nearby shops, restaurants, and more. This exceptional property also includes indoor WIDE garage UNOBSTRUCTED ASSIGNED NON-TANDEM indoor garage parking and two deeded storage closets.     "
250004565,SOLD,"JC, Heights",12 LINCOLN ST,Condominium,1950,5069,"$1,199,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,8,,"$1,199,000","$1,199,000",$614.87,$614.87,3/11/2025,4/15/2025,7/10/2025,35,35,,7/10/2025,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Summit Ave and Central Ave,"Introducing 12 Lincoln Unit 2, a brand new OVERSIZED luxury duplex built one of Jersey City's Premier Developers and design by renowned Interior Designer Walk This House! This south-facing, 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence seamlessly blends modern design with natural tones, offering smart home features, oversized floor-to-ceiling windows, and exceptional craftsmanship. The first floor showcases an open-concept living and dining area that flows into the kitchen. The kitchen is a chef’s dream, featuring top-of-the-line Fisher & Paykel appliances, custom two-tone cabinetry, sleek quartz countertops and backsplash, and a custom cut waterfall island. Designer pendant lighting frames the space, while oversized windows flood the room with natural light. The main bedroom is equally light-filled, with triple-wide Andersen windows, custom cool tone pendant lighting, designer overhead light fixture, recess lit tray ceiling and custom closets The luxurious main en-suite bathroom includes a wood tone double vanity, matte black high-end shower fixtures, and a rainfall shower head. The main floor also features two additional bedrooms with oversized double-wide windows, an interior design award worthy full bathroom, and a RARE TRUE laundry room with LG Washer and Dryer and custom cabinetry and countertop. Your OVERSIZED Ground floor is complete with custom designed wet bar with matte black cabinetry and accent wall, oversized rec / bedroom, full bathroom and your near floor to ceiling quad-wide sliding glass doors open to your professionally designed private backyard. Private backyard will be complete with paver patio with recessed accent lighting, custom built seating area, grass, tall fence for complete privacy, natural brick wall that will be complete by Local Artist. This home is completed with SIDE BY SIDE garage parking, smart home capabilities, energy efficiency capabilities, custom designed exterior facade with multiple high end materials and lighting including frosted glass garage. Property comes with 10 year warranty and property may qualify for 5 Year Tax Abatement! Please note that all sqft are approx."
240008243,SOLD,"JC, Heights",43 CHARLES ST,Condominium,1950,5069,"$1,199,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2803,7.02,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,6,,"$1,199,000","$1,199,000",$614.87,$614.87,5/2/2024,6/13/2024,8/12/2024,42,42,,8/12/2024,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central and summit,"Welcome to 43 Charles, Blue Chip Properties’ most luxurious New Construction home to date.  This 3 bedroom 3 full bath duplex spans an impressive 1,950 sqft, this unit was designed with timeless interior design, top line finishes and fixtures, quality craftsmanship and modern technological features. This home sits conveniently within Summit and Central, minutes from Hoboken, Congress St Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park and Palisades gourmet restaurants!   Your main floor enters to an oversized open concept Dining & Living featuring 10 ft high walls lined with oversized Andersen windows, natural light and realistic flame fireplace. Your Chefs kitchen features designer - two tone cabinetry, Thermador Stove, Thermador Heating Drawer, Panel Ready Fridge, pot filler, pantry, oversized double waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash and West elm accent lighting.   Main level features oversized Primary bedroom designed with custom millwork, bedside pendant lighting, double walk in-closet with custom built ins and large picturesque private balcony. Through frosted glass doors is your ensuite bath which is one of the largest bathrooms to ever be built within Jersey City Heights! It has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience and offers oversized double vanity, soaking tub, warm pendant lighting, vein matched porcelain and oversized shower with body jets and rain fall shower head.   One additional bedroom with finished custom closets and ensuite bath, laundry room with Top Line Washer / Dryer complete your main level.   Your ground floor level enters from a glass and recessed lit staircase which includes full bath and oversized bedroom / entertaining room, wet bar backed with custom backsplash and wine fridge, large closet and wide plank floors. This leads out to a tree lined private backyard with professional landscaping, paver patio, accent lighting, gas / electric and water hook ups making it perfect for entertaining and creating memories.   Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Security Cameras, Google Smart Hub, Smart Thermo and Smart Touch Screen Switches, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smart phone. Garage features non-tandem parking and separate Level 2 High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit. Home is complete with exterior facade and recessed driveway lighting and landscaping. Property comes with 5 Year Tax Abatement and 10 year warranty. Please note that sqft is approx."
260003652,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",31 GRAHAM ST,Condominium,1900,5069,"$1,199,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,2,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,3,7,,,"$1,199,000",$631.05,,3/3/2026,,,37,,,3/3/2026,,,,$0,,,,,No,No,Yes,,,Summit & Central,"Welcome to 31 Graham St, Unit 2 a 3 bedroom, 3 full bath, 1 half bath duplex by Green Home Developers, offering approximately 1,900 square feet of living space and RARE MULTI CAR SIDE BY SIDE GARAGE PARKING in Jersey City Heights. Your main level showcases an open concept living and dining area with 10 foot ceilings and oversized windows. Your chef’s kitchen features premium stainless steel appliances, waterfall quartz countertops, vented hood, and custom wood cabinetry, designed for both everyday living and entertaining. Your primary suite offers a walk-in closet with custom built-ins, and ensuite bath with floor to ceiling large format tile, a smart mirror, and top-of-the-line shower fixtures. Also on the main level are two additional spacious bedrooms with built-in closets, a full bathroom with double vanity, powder room, dedicated laundry area, linen and coat closets for added storage, and a flexible office space. Your rooftop expands your entertaining space offering sweeping NYC views. The XL garage offers RARE MULTI CAR SIDE BY SIDE GARAGE PARKING, plus additional private storage closets. Situated on a quiet stretch of Graham Street, known for its elevated position and sweeping NYC views, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility. Just moments from Central Avenue shops, the 9th Street Light Rail, Washington Park, and the restaurants along Palisade Avenue, you’ll enjoy both breathtaking surroundings and exceptional convenience. Square footage is approximate."
260004469,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",91 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1600,5069,"$1,199,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,4,1,2,7,,,"$1,199,000",$749.38,,3/13/2026,,,27,,,3/13/2026,,,,,,,,,No,No,Yes,,,Bowers and Griffith,"Off-site Parking options available.  Welcome to 91 Hancock Avenue—Unit 1, a brand new 4-Bedroom, 3-Bathroom build by Jack & Lumber, Jersey City’s premier ultra-luxury home builder and the only one in The Heights crafting true boutique residences. Owning one is more than an achievement; it is a richly deserved reward for your years of vision, ambition, and hard work. Reimagine your life in a home so extraordinary it inspires daily pride and leaves your guests in awe. We believe profoundly that our clients deserve something truly extraordinary, and work with unwavering dedication to deliver it. Our next-generation homes are defined by dazzling bespoke Italian kitchens—visually striking by incorporating glass and integrated LED lights and crafted with meticulous attention to detail. A Sub-Zero Designer Series paneled refrigerator and black glass Wolf appliances underscore our commitment to refined contemporary minimalism. The island, clad in Neolith porcelain from Spain, features an integrated sink and Wolf precision-control induction cooktop with advanced safety features, including automatic pan detection. We’ve partnered with Buster & Punch of London for our interior lighting and kitchen hardware—perhaps the most style-forward brand to emerge in design this past decade. Their solid brass fixtures, diamond-knurled with watchmaker-like precision, add sculptural tactility to every interaction. A hallmark of our design is the signature Jack & Lumber floating staircase—a sculptural centerpiece framed in minimalist glass and illuminated with integrated LED lighting. Both engineering marvel and art installation, it’s a defining statement of the home. The bespoke Italian walk-in closets are nothing short of spectacular—designed to rival the most exclusive retail boutiques. Framed by smoked glass doors and illuminated by integrated LED lighting, each closet exudes a sense of drama and refinement. Custom shelving and meticulously planned layouts showcase both form and function, while premium finishes and precise detailing create an atmosphere that is as indulgent as it is organized. These wardrobes aren’t just storage—they’re immersive, high-design spaces that elevate the everyday ritual of dressing. Windows and oversized sliding doors are custom-fabricated by Drutex of Poland, featuring triple-pane construction with insulating gas layers. This not only enhances energy efficiency but also dramatically reduces exterior noise,  creating a peaceful interior environment all year round. Our passion for exceptional materials continues into the bathrooms. Clad in large-format Neolith slabs and illuminated by Buster & Punch lighting, each bathroom features Ditra-Heat radiant floors—a German-engineered system known for reliability, seamless integration, and comfort. Individual thermostats allow for intuitive temperature control, and all bathrooms include smart toilets, offering elevated hygiene and comfort through cutting-edge technology. Throughout the residence, millwork reflects our uncompromising craftsmanship—from custom European interior doors imported from Spain to thoughtfully integrated architectural details. The solid 8-foot doors are custom-fabricated and clad in American walnut veneer, paired with concealed hinges and magnetic locks for a clean, uninterrupted profile. Even the base molding has been meticulously fabricated to match the walnut finish, reinforcing the residence’s seamless design language.    Property comes with 10-Year Builder Warranty. Off-site Parking options available.  Schedule a private appointment—and fall in love with a Jack & Lumber masterpiece."
260005898,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",252 BOWERS ST,Condominium,2775,1750,"$1,199,999",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307-1111,02604,00042,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,10,,,"$1,199,999",$432.43,,4/3/2026,,,6,,,4/3/2026,,,,,,$125,2026,,No,No,Yes,,,JFK and Milton,"Welcome to 252 Bowers Street #1, a beautifully designed 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath triplex residence spanning 2,775 square feet offering an exceptional blend of scale, style, and modern luxury in Jersey City Heights. Thoughtfully designed for both everyday living and entertaining, this newly constructed home features 9-foot ceilings, wide-plank hardwood floors, oversized windows, recessed lighting, and a sun-drenched open-concept layout anchored by a stunning chef’s kitchen with sleek glossy European cabinetry, quartz countertops, high-end JennAir appliances, and sophisticated contemporary finishes throughout. The primary suite is a true retreat, complete with a spa-like bath featuring a rain head shower, a large double vanity, and a generous walk-in closet, while the additional bedrooms are well-proportioned and beautifully finished. The lower level offers impressive 8-foot ceilings, a spacious and flexible bonus living area with a powder room, storage, and mechanical room, all flowing directly to a spacious private backyard that creates a rare and seamless indoor-outdoor lifestyle. Set near transportation and the vibrant shops, restaurants, and conveniences of Central Avenue, this is a rare opportunity to own a polished, high-end home with beautifully layered living space in one of Jersey City Heights’ most desirable locations. Book a private tour today!"
240012508,SOLD,"JC, Heights",502 PALISADE AVE,Condominium,1624,1713,"$1,200,000",CONDO-COOP,,5&6,503,"JC, Heights",07307,2401,1.01,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,7,,"$1,200,000","$1,199,999",$738.92,$738.92,6/27/2024,7/16/2024,9/4/2024,19,19,,9/5/2024,,,,"$16,041",,$475,,Conventional,,,,,,Corner of Holland Street and Palisade Ave,"Welcome to Palisade Square, a mid-rise steel and concrete elevator building offering high-end luxury. This bright, spacious 1624 sq ft, 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom duplex has it all with outdoor space and parking and meticulous design, highlighted by a wall of windows with sunset views and featuring hardwood floors, over 9.5  ft ceilings, and oversized windows with access to an outdoor terrace. The kitchen showcases top-of-the-line Kitchen-Aid appliances, brand-new custom wood cabinetry, quartz countertops, ceramic tile backsplash - and additional storage cabinets in the island. The primary bedroom has a large custom-built walk-in closet. Contemporary fixtures and Porcelanosa tiles adorn the primary bathroom, including heated floors, double vanities, quartz countertops, Moen 90 Degree bath fixtures, and glass shower doors. Upstairs are two generously sized bedrooms bathed in natural light and a elegant bathroom with a tub. Additional features include an in-unit full-size washer and dryer, custom Hunter Douglas large living/dining room windows featuring motorized solar shades, and blackout honeycomb shades in all the bedrooms. Nestled in the vibrant and diverse neighborhood of The Heights in Jersey City. Known for its unique charm and eclectic atmosphere, this area offers a mix of historic architecture and modern amenities. Close to Riverview Fisk Park, local shops, restaurants, farmers market, and cafes, just steps away from your doorstep. The community is well-connected with easy access to public transportation, including buses and light rail, facilitating a seamless commute to downtown Jersey City and New York City."
260004715,ACTIVE,"JC, Heights",45 CHARLES ST,Condominium,1950,1526,"$1,200,000",CONDO-COOP,,1 & 2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2803,7.01,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,7,,,"$1,200,000",$615.38,,3/18/2026,,,22,,,3/18/2026,,,,,,$230,,,,,,,,Central & Summit,"Modern Sophistication Meets Smart Living 2 Bedrooms + Expansive Flex Space | 3 Bathrooms | Approx. 1,950 Sq Ft | Built in 2024 Step into a world of refined elegance and cutting-edge innovation in this newly built, two-story luxury residence. Designed for the discerning buyer, this modern condominium/townhouse blends architectural sophistication with intuitive smart home technology, creating a lifestyle that is as effortless as it is extraordinary. The home features an expansive open floor plan with seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. The chef’s kitchen is outfitted with top-of-the-line Thermador appliances, dual pantries, and soft-touch cabinetry, while a stylish wet bar with custom designer backsplash and wine fridge adds another level of convenience and luxury. The primary suite serves as a true private retreat, complete with its own balcony, two walk-in closets, and a spa-inspired bath featuring an oversized shower with body jets and a rainfall shower head. A generously sized second bedroom offers comfort and privacy, while the oversized flex room with its own full bathroom provides exceptional versatility. Perfect as an entertainment lounge, guest suite, home office, media room, or potential in-law setup, this space adds tremendous value and flexibility to the layout. Smart living is integrated throughout with Google Nest doorbell, security cameras, Smart Hub controls, touchscreen switches, electric remote shades, and a sleek modern electric fireplace. Additional highlights include a dedicated laundry room with premium washer and dryer, high-voltage EV charging station, recessed driveway lighting, lush landscaping, and a private backyard oasis ideal for al fresco dining or quiet evenings outdoors. Nestled in a coveted neighborhood, this residence offers the perfect balance of privacy and convenience. Whether you are hosting guests or enjoying a peaceful night at home, this property delivers a rare blend of modern luxury, thoughtful design, and functional flexibility. A truly exceptional opportunity to own a trophy residence that redefines contemporary living."
240011792,SOLD,"JC, Heights",45 CHARLES ST,Condominium,1950,5069,"$1,200,000",CONDO-COOP,,1,1,"JC, Heights",07307,2803,7.01,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,6,,"$1,200,000","$1,199,000",$615.38,$615.38,6/19/2024,7/1/2024,8/1/2024,12,12,,8/5/2024,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,Yes,,,Central and Summit,"Welcome to 45 Charles, Blue Chip Properties’ most luxurious New Construction home to date. This 3 bedroom 3 full bath duplex spans an impressive 1,950 sqft, this unit was designed with timeless interior design, top line finishes and fixtures, quality craftsmanship and modern technological features. This home sits conveniently within Summit and Central, minutes from Hoboken, Congress St Light Rail, Riverview-Fisk Park and Palisades gourmet restaurants! Your main floor enters to an oversized open concept Dining & Living featuring 10 ft high walls lined with oversized Andersen windows, natural light and realistic flame fireplace. Your Chefs kitchen features designer - two tone cabinetry, Thermador Stove, Thermador Heating Drawer, Panel Ready Fridge, pot filler, pantry, oversized double waterfall quartz center island and countertops backed with luxurious porcelain backsplash and West elm accent lighting. Main level features oversized Primary bedroom designed with custom millwork, bedside pendant lighting, double walk in-closet with custom built ins and large picturesque private balcony. Through frosted glass doors is your ensuite bath which is one of the largest bathrooms to ever be built within Jersey City Heights! It has been designed with modern yet warm natural tones to create a spa like ambience and offers oversized double vanity, soaking tub, warm pendant lighting, vein matched porcelain and oversized shower with body jets and rain fall shower head. One additional bedroom with finished custom closets and ensuite bath, laundry room with Top Line Washer / Dryer complete your main level. Your ground floor level enters from a glass and recessed lit staircase which includes full bath and oversized bedroom / entertaining room, wet bar backed with custom backsplash and wine fridge, large closet and wide plank floors. This leads out to a tree lined private backyard with professional landscaping, paver patio, accent lighting, gas / electric and water hook ups making it perfect for entertaining and creating memories. Full Smart Home technology allows for ease of living, complete with Google Nest doorbell, Security Cameras, Google Smart Hub, Smart Thermo and Smart Touch Screen Switches, Lighting Dimmer Switches, and more all accessible via smart phone. Garage features non-tandem parking and separate Level 2 High Voltage EV Charging outlet for each unit. Home is complete with exterior facade and recessed driveway lighting and landscaping. Property comes with 5 Year Tax Abatement and 10 year warranty. Please note that sqft is approx."
240009977,SOLD,"JC, Heights",527 CENTRAL AVE,Condominium,1978,6078,"$1,200,000",CONDO-COOP,,2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,,,Heights,,,,,3,1,2,6,,"$1,200,000","$1,249,000",$606.67,$606.67,5/24/2024,6/28/2024,7/26/2024,35,35,,7/26/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,North and Irving,"When WASHINGTON PARK IS IN YOUR FRONT YARD .. !! Welcome to 527 Central Ave, a collection of two ultra-luxurious brand new condominiums, in the heart of Jersey City Heights. Property qualifies for CENSUS TRACT program, with interest offered in the high 5’s, making this property and location an Attractive Investment..!! This exquisite property is an epitome of comfort, space and modern design. Elevate your standards of living with these massive, meticulously designed, duplex homes, featuring designer finishes throughout, White Oak flooring, Recessed Lighting, Crown and Baseboard Moulding, Central HVAC, Nest Thermostat, Ring Doorbell, Camera Security, Pella Awning Windows, 10-foot ceilings, 8-foot doors and contemporary Matte black fixtures, with breathtaking views of Washington Park.  Immerse yourself in an impressive audio experience with surround sound WIFI/Bluetooth speakers installed throughout this smart home.  Expansive Unit 1 condominium spans over 1978 SQFT square feet, spread across two separate floors, offering oversized 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and a coveted private outdoor space. Step inside this thoughtfully crafted home, and be greeted by an open and airy layout that seamlessly integrates a spacious living and dining area. The sophisticated living room features Brooklyn-Style BRICK TV wall with integrated ultra-thin electric fireplace, pine wood walnut paneling, modern LED lighting fixture, pre-wired wifi-speakers for entertainment, and oversized black windows allowing abundance of natural light throughout the day. The living/dining room seamlessly flows into the sophisticated chef’s kitchen showcasing an abundance of dramatic yin-yang glossy cabinetry with fine white/black modern trim, elegant quartz countertops, electrifying glossy black drop-ceiling filled with spotlights and integrated pendant lighting, Samsung Bluetooth Refrigerator, 5-burner Gas/Oven range, Pot Filler, Wine Cooler, Microwave, Dishwasher, Stainless Steel Sink, making it a culinary enthusiast's dream kitchen. The master-suite, a true retreat, provides a dedicated office/den space, also boasts access to a private balcony overlooking the serene backyard. The elegantly designed Ensuite Master Bathroom, equipped with Rain Shower, Waterfall and Panel style unique porcelain tiles, white high-gloss double vanity, creates a spa-like experience. Master bedroom also features Custom Walk-In Closet finished with solid wood barn-door that seamlessly glides on a black metallic rail. This magnificent condominium that rivals Manhattan standard luxury, provides two additional queen size bedrooms, a second bathroom and a laundry room with full-size LG washer and dryer units. Travel downstairs to the lower level, where you'll discover treasured private entertainment space with kitchenette, the third full bathroom and outdoor space. Each unit offers Exclusive Non-Tandem Garage Parking for our new homeowners looking to take advantage of covered parking in R1 zone, without hassling the neighbors.   Settled on bustling Central Ave, extra wide street of Jersey City Heights, provides an unparalleled living experience. Walking distance to boutique shops, restaurants, cafés and parks, this home is ideally located for a balance of urban living and secluded sanctuary. Located at 10 mins walk to 9th st light rail station, or hop on bus 85, 88 from your front door, for direct connections to NYC,  making commuting to New York City a breeze. Jersey City Heights is known for its tight-knit community, great schools and easy access to NYC. **10-Year Builders Warranty, Eligible for 5 year Tax Abatement.."
230019333,SOLD,"JC, Heights",132 SHERMAN PL,Condominium,2200,1724,"$1,200,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,12002,00044 01,Heights,,,,,4,0,3,11,,"$1,200,000","$1,249,000",$545.45,$545.45,11/16/2023,12/15/2023,2/9/2024,29,29,,2/9/2024,,,,,,,,Conventional,,,,,,Kennedy and Sanford,"Experience the epitome of high-end luxury living in this immaculate Brand New Construction condominium built on an oversized lot,  located on one of the most desirable streets in JC Heights. This expansive 2200-square-foot residence spread out over two floors which features 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, separate laundry room, along with a Private Backyard and full wet bar Kitchen.  The interior is adorned with contemporary accents, showcasing elegant elements such as high ceilings, light-finished 6 wide plank hardwood flooring, Anderson windows, custom built in electric fireplace and 8-foot custom entry doors throughout. Indulge in a state-of-the-art chef's kitchen complete with 60-inch sleek custom soft-closing cabinets, walk-in pantry closet, quartz countertops and backsplash, a spacious center island, and a full suite of VIKING appliances and wall ovens.  The bathrooms are adorned with sophisticated tiles and a glass-enclosed rain shower. The generous Primary Bedroom features a walk-in closet, a private balcony, a spacious en-suite bathroom with floor-to-ceiling custom tiling,  glass shower, a soaking tub, and double vanity sinks. Nestled on a street with beautiful historic preserved homes and walking distance to Pershing Field Park, this home offers the best of urban living. Owners will appreciate its proximity to NYC transportation, neighboring districts, and nearby shops, restaurants, and more. This exceptional property also includes indoor WIDE garage UNOBSTRUCTED ASSIGNED NON-TANDEM indoor garage parking and two deeded storage closets.     "
250024885,SOLD,"JC, Heights",192 CAMBRIDGE AVE,Condominium,1870,1597,"$1,200,000",CONDO-COOP,,2/3,4,"JC, Heights",07307,2203,2.01,Heights,,,,,3,0,2,7,,"$1,200,000","$1,250,000",$641.71,$641.71,12/11/2025,2/12/2026,4/3/2026,45,45,,4/3/2026,,,,$0,,,,Conventional,No,No,No,,,Congress Street & South Street,"Five new-construction condominium homes redefine modern living in Jersey City Heights. Each home showcases a refined aesthetic and carefully curated details. Chef-inspired kitchens feature expansive Taj Mahal quartz islands, premium LG stainless appliances with gas range, a Frigidaire wine cooler, and Sharp built-in microwave. Primary baths offer a spa-like escape with porcelain and ceramic tiles, frameless glass showers, brushed gold hardware, Kohler fixtures, and natural teak vanities, while secondary baths boast sleek subway tiles, matte black channels, Moen fixtures, and LED mirrors. Wide-plank French oak flooring, soaring ceilings, custom lighting, and built-in electric fireplaces bring warmth and style throughout, creating homes that balance modern sophistication with everyday comfort.  192 Cambridge sits in prime location only one block to Washington Park and a few short blocks to The Arts District surrounding Riverview Park.  Enjoy neighborhood cafés, Central Avenue shops, and vibrant restaurants, with the Congress Street Light Rail a short walk away, you’ll enjoy effortless access to Hoboken and Manhattan while keeping the Heights’ neighborhood charm at your doorstep. This home includes a massive private rooftop with NYC views. 1 garage parking space included with EV charging station and can fit additional car in driveway.  Not the average floor plan you are used to seeing all over The Heights - must see in person!"
220012686,SOLD,"JC, Heights",97 LAIDLAW AVE,Condominium,1872,1603,"$1,200,000",CONDO-COOP,,PH,PH,"JC, Heights",07306,05705,00014,Heights,,,,,4,0,3,7,,"$1,200,000","$1,300,000",$641.03,$641.03,7/12/2022,10/12/2022,12/14/2022,44,44,,12/15/2022,,,,$0,,$697,,Conventional,,,,,,Central Ave & Oakland Ave,"97 Laidlaw Ave is a collection of five timeless new construction condominium homes consisting of three and four bedrooms, two and three bath homes. This 4 bedroom home features 3 private outdoor spaces including rooftop with NYC views. Elevator opens up directly to this unit only!  Each residence features a captivating blend of clean, contemporary lines, quality craftsmanship and a rich selection of handpicked materials. Every home offers unparalleled detail from expansive open floor plan living spaces and high-end finishes to massive private balconies, exclusive backyards, elevator, garage parking and deeded rooftop spaces with NYC views. Full-service kitchens designed to flow smoothly into and out of living areas. This elegant space is perfectly suited for casual dining as well as entertaining. Luxurious bathrooms offering you a spa-like retreat with an assortment of carefully selected materials and textures that are exceptional. 97 Laidlaw Ave sits in prime location only a few short blocks from Pershing Field Park and only one block to the Central Ave shopping district. Commute with ease to NYC via NJ Transit buses right on Central Ave or a quick 15 minute walk to the JSQ PATH train. City-bikes located one block from the property as well. Offering you larger living spaces at desirable price points while maintaining close proximity to NYC, these new construction homes are so luxurious you’ll never want to leave!   "
250014973,SOLD,"JC, Heights",53 HANCOCK AVE,Condominium,1822,1713,"$1,220,000",CONDO-COOP,,1&2,1,"JC, Heights",07307,3802,13,,,,,,3,1,2,10,,"$1,220,000","$1,275,000",$669.59,$669.59,7/22/2025,8/14/2025,10/17/2025,23,23,,10/21/2025,,,,"$8,415",2023,$0,,Conventional,,,,,,Hutton & Griffith Streets,"Welcome to 53 Hancock #1, a truly exceptional 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom duplex in Jersey City Heights that seamlessly blends classic charm with cutting-edge modern amenities. This expansive two-level unit offers an unparalleled living experience, designed for both comfort and sophisticated entertaining. The heart of this home is its gourmet kitchen, a chef's dream featuring elegant two-tone cabinetry, top-of-the-line KitchenAid Appliances, a stunning quartz waterfall countertop on the center island, and an incredibly convenient over-range pot filler. A dedicated beverage center and wet bar elevate your entertaining options, making hosting a delight. The open-concept living area is perfect for gatherings, enhanced by speakers integrated into the ceilings and an inviting electric fireplace with built-in shelving and LED lights, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. Throughout the home, Marvin Windows ensure abundant natural light and superior energy efficiency, complementing the modern aesthetic. Indulge in the spa-like bathrooms, where every detail is designed for ultimate comfort and luxury. Both full bathrooms feature heated floors, while the master bathroom takes indulgence to the next level with a steam shower and a heated bench for a truly relaxing experience. Enjoy the convenience of adjustable recirculating hot water for instant warmth, and a master shower that offers a customizable experience with a three-function shower head, rain head, and handheld sprayer. All bathrooms boast modern aesthetics with sleek wall-hung toilets and floating vanities. The thoughtful design of these spaces has allowed for generously oversized bedrooms, maximizing livable space throughout the duplex. This home is equipped with smart technology and energy-efficient features for ultimate convenience and peace of mind. Enjoy effortless keyless entry with smart locks and optimize your climate control with intelligent Nest thermostats. The highly efficient tankless hot water heater, located conveniently in the garage, provides endless hot water while significantly minimizing energy consumption. For added security and ease, the main water shut-off valve is easily accessible in the laundry room, allowing you to shut off water to the entire apartment with a simple turn. Aesthetic and practical details like LED lights on the stairs enhance both safety and the home's contemporary feel. Step outside to discover your private outdoor oasis. The duplex features private balconies, offering tranquil spaces perfect for morning coffee or evening relaxation. The backyard is ready for your next barbecue, complete with a dedicated natural gas line for your grill. Practical outdoor features include frost-freeze hose faucets in both the front and back of the house, ensuring year-round functionality. Parking is a dream with an oversized non tandem side-by-side parking garage with one spot dedicated to each unit, that also includes an EV car charging station, catering to modern needs and providing unparalleled convenience in the city."
