250010641,SOLD,"JC, Heights",263 OGDEN AVE,Condominium,1936,1713,"$1,225,000",CONDO-COOP,,2/3,2,"JC, Heights",07307,3903,43,Heights,,,,,3,0,3,8,,"$1,225,000","$1,225,000",$632.75,$632.75,2/13/2025,2/14/2025,4/29/2025,1,0,,6/3/2025,,,,,,$156,2025,Conventional,,,,,,Griffith & Franklin St,"Introducing a stunning new construction condo located at Number One Block Ogden Ave, in the heart of Jersey City Heights. This exquisite three-bedroom, three-bathroom residence offers the epitome of luxury living, complete with a dedicated office space for the modern professional.  Step inside and be captivated by the super white block design, showcasing high-end finishes and meticulous attention to detail throughout. The open-concept living area seamlessly blends sophistication and comfort, perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. Each bedroom serves as a serene retreat, with ample space and pristine en-suite bathrooms.  The primary bedroom has a balcony, and the bathroom includes a custom 72” vanity and Electric Towel Warmer for that spa-like feel in your very own home.  Beyond the interiors, this exceptional condo features a roof deck with unobstructed skyline views—an urban oasis ideal for relaxation or al fresco gatherings. Nestled in the vibrant Jersey City Heights, you'll enjoy the perfect balance of tranquility and proximity to the city's finest dining, shopping, and entertainment.  Experience unparalleled luxury and contemporary elegance in this one-of-a-kind residence at Ogden Ave—your new home awaits."
